{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1001", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Geoffrey Hinton, known as the \"godfather of AI,\" has expressed serious concerns about the risks artificial intelligence could pose to humanity.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "He has said he is worried about the existential threat that AI might become for the human species.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "Using OpenAI\u2019s ChatGPT made Hinton uneasy after some of its responses, such as implying Fox News was fake news.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "Hinton has pointed out that current AI systems \"are not alive\" and aren't more intelligent than humans yet\u2014but he believes they might surpass us soon.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "The rapid progress of AI surprised many in the field, as few expected such quick advances.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "Yann LeCun, another top AI expert, disagrees with some fears, arguing that intelligence does not necessarily lead to a desire for domination in AI.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "Hinton told the BBC that, for now, AI is not more intelligent than humans, but he expects this to change soon.", "citations": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079"]}, {"text": "The Biden White House is concerned about AI being developed with few safeguards, raising issues of public safety and control.", "citations": ["abd90351-b865-4002-b72d-7c84d3f6fa6c_702017578"]}, {"text": "Many industry leaders, scientists, and the U.N. Secretary-General have recently warned that risks from AI\u2014such as extinction-level threats\u2014should be treated as seriously as pandemics or nuclear war.", "citations": ["99b06f2f-6f17-498d-82f9-5c50811e3477_211656408"]}, {"text": "There is specific worry about \"human-level AI,\" which could perform tasks as well as humans and might, if misused, create mass-scale fake realities by hacking social media.", "citations": ["99b06f2f-6f17-498d-82f9-5c50811e3477_211656408"]}, {"text": "AI existential risk is not yet taken seriously enough by society, but this is starting to change.", "citations": ["99b06f2f-6f17-498d-82f9-5c50811e3477_211656408"]}, {"text": "Work by Hinton and other experts comes at a pivotal time with countries like the UK and US taking active interest in regulating AI\u2019s rapid growth.", "citations": ["beaaba1c-d058-4db5-bac2-c02fb4c0de39_677251007"]}, {"text": "Demis Hassabis, CEO of Google DeepMind, estimates that human-level AI could arrive in as little as five years, or within a decade.", "citations": ["0b0a6638-7cfb-483c-bf6d-bc4b844b884a_253543854"]}, {"text": "Yoshua Bengio, another leading AI scientist, emphasizes that we still do not know how to design AI systems that always behave as we intend.", "citations": ["14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816"]}, {"text": "Hinton\u2019s resignation and warnings have sparked major debate among experts, the public, and governments worldwide about how to develop and manage AI safely.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "The public is encouraged to recognize that while AI has transformative potential, not enough safeguards are yet in place to prevent significant risks.", "citations": ["99b06f2f-6f17-498d-82f9-5c50811e3477_211656408"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1003", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves working remotely from various countries, immersing yourself in new destinations, and often contributing to local communities through your skills.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "To become a digital nomad, you\u2019ll need a valid passport, and most countries require proof of employment, contracts, or specific income thresholds to grant nomad visas, such as Norway's independent contractor visa or Germany\u2019s visa for self-employment.", "citations": ["3316165f-7882-41a1-9d57-1c659727fb5d_289188030"]}, {"text": "Many countries, especially in the Asia-Pacific region, are introducing digital nomad visa programs to attract global talent and tax revenue, for example, Japan\u2019s and UAE\u2019s initiatives requiring proof of IT or digital work and minimum annual earnings.", "citations": ["f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041"]}, {"text": "Digital nomad visas usually last from a few months up to a year, and applicants need to apply at embassies or online, with criteria like earning more than $24,000 USD or \u00a510 million yen per year.", "citations": ["f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041"]}, {"text": "Popular destinations for digital nomads include the US, France, UK, Germany, UAE, Argentina, the Philippines, and India.", "citations": ["ecf3362e-b403-4224-b08a-f302d3e88373_435843940"]}, {"text": "Types of work suited to this lifestyle include writing, graphic design, product and design roles, various IT jobs, and other trade or remote positions that allow travel and flexibility.", "citations": ["e2e5695e-5664-4b13-9684-77a67f6d4397_888512071"]}, {"text": "Productivity requires self-discipline, effective time management, and establishing routines like waking up at the same time daily to avoid burnout and distraction from travel activities.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Challenges include staying focused amidst distractions, managing work-life balance, coping with time zone differences, meeting visa and legal requirements, and creating a sense of home despite frequent movement.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "A growth mindset and choosing work aligned with your interests and skills are key for long-term success.", "citations": ["e2e5695e-5664-4b13-9684-77a67f6d4397_888512071"]}, {"text": "Common tools for digital nomads include laptops, global connectivity apps, productivity software, remote work platforms, and job search resources like Citizen Remote.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "Remote and hybrid working is now widely accepted, allowing greater freedom for those who seek continuous movement across countries and cultures.", "citations": ["7a6698fe-19e8-49cb-81b5-e3bf847aa5e9_763641129"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1005", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle allows remote workers to live in different places while working or studying abroad.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "This lifestyle can be rewarding for individuals and can also create positive impacts for local communities, depending on one\u2019s approach.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "Understanding what it means to be a digital nomad and assessing personal compatibility is crucial before making this lifestyle change.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Effective time management, such as maintaining a consistent daily routine, helps prevent burnout and distractions from travel activities.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Choosing work that fits your interests and studies ensures professional focus and personal authenticity.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Digital nomads often take job searches into their own hands.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Essential tools for mobile work include a reliable device, a WiFi hotspot that avoids roaming fees, quality earbuds with long battery life, and a portable wireless mouse.", "citations": ["23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909"]}, {"text": "Establishing a mobile office is integral to sustaining productivity on the go.", "citations": ["23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909"]}, {"text": "Balancing work and leisure is key to maximizing experiences in new locations, such as Itacar\u00e9 in Bahia or coworking communities like the one in Pipa.", "citations": ["90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315"]}, {"text": "The COVID-19 pandemic has shown the impermanence of traditional work structures, with remote work now more widely accepted in some sectors.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "However, industries like manufacturing still require in-person attendance.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "The freedom to define personal values and flexible work schedules has become more prominent, requiring increased trust between employers and employees.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Embracing digital nomads as contributors to the workforce is seen as a potential benefit for businesses.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Despite the advantages, digital nomads must also navigate visa regulations; for example, some countries offer visas that cannot be extended or converted to permanent stays.", "citations": ["c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462"]}, {"text": "The future of work continues to evolve, and adapting to new work-life dynamics remains an ongoing process for individuals and organizations.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1007", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "China\u2019s J-10 fighter jet has been highlighted in the export market, with Pakistan being the most prominent country reportedly negotiating its purchase, particularly to replace the aging F-7PG fighters of the Pakistan Air Force used for pilot conversion training.", "citations": ["71100976-5a62-4b13-b449-5fcd327a8fcc_221821377"]}, {"text": "During the 2023 Dubai Air Show, China\u2019s Hongdu Aircraft Company confirmed that Pakistan is in formal talks with China regarding the acquisition of light attack aircraft, which includes the J-10C.", "citations": ["71100976-5a62-4b13-b449-5fcd327a8fcc_221821377"]}, {"text": "Some commentators from defense forums and media sources have questioned the reliability and production readiness of Chinese combat aircraft, with critics pointing to delays and ongoing development issues in indigenous projects such as India\u2019s LCA.", "citations": ["4bc40faf-e9dc-4a5d-8c3a-0d2f20ba848d_123806756"]}, {"text": "Chinese defense media and officials emphasize ongoing upgrades to Chinese fighter jets, including plans to replace the WS-10C engine in the J-10C with the more advanced WS-15, aiming to improve performance and narrow the gap with American fighters such as the F-22 Raptor.", "citations": ["bbd66630-067c-4256-adc2-97dd5f5878ed_41790305"]}, {"text": "Media coverage often compares China\u2019s rapid progression in military aviation R&D to other countries\u2019 more methodical approaches, with the goal of achieving comparable or superior capabilities.", "citations": ["bcb10cf5-a993-47e6-9165-f43f42c766aa_206491725"]}, {"text": "There have also been international reports about the quality of Chinese military equipment, with some critics stating that a proportion of Chinese military planes, including exports, are considered inferior to Russian or Western counterparts.", "citations": ["a84c2df3-abc5-42e2-888f-a3be0506538d_982792363"]}, {"text": "Feedback from buyers and observers remains mixed, with some Pakistani sources expressing optimism about the J-10C\u2019s capabilities, while other media pundits caution about operational reliability and the readiness of the jets for large-scale export.", "citations": ["ce32c1be-e02a-4d52-bd5f-d35b9737080b_987151109"]}, {"text": "Discussions in Western and South Asian media sometimes reference alleged technology copying from sources like the Dassault Mirage or purportedly from F-22 and F-35 fighters, raising questions about originality and stealth effectiveness.", "citations": ["a84c2df3-abc5-42e2-888f-a3be0506538d_982792363"]}, {"text": "As of now, no other export deals for the J-10 besides Pakistan have been publicly confirmed, and broader international acceptance of the type remains a topic of ongoing debate in defense circles.", "citations": ["71100976-5a62-4b13-b449-5fcd327a8fcc_221821377"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1009", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "San Antonians may want to stay indoors next week due to incoming Saharan dust.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "A noticeable change in the air will arrive to the Alamo City as heavier amounts of dust remain over the Gulf Coast by Monday.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "The dust event is not limited to this region and will continue to impact other areas.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "Residents are advised to keep windows and doors closed to limit indoor dust exposure.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "Annually, trade winds transport 180 million tons of dust from the Saharan Desert across the Atlantic during late spring to early fall.", "citations": ["847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659"]}, {"text": "This influx often results in a visible haze, creating a milky hue in normally clear skies.", "citations": ["847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659"]}, {"text": "Recent weekend rain has provided little relief to existing severe water shortages on the Rio Grande.", "citations": ["3f3d97a9-5753-477f-b92f-e7eb5b3af635_359923960"]}, {"text": "Citizens and officials are encouraged to take preparatory steps for this and future crises.", "citations": ["3f3d97a9-5753-477f-b92f-e7eb5b3af635_359923960"]}, {"text": "For several months each year, the Desert Southwest sees increased storm activity creating unique weather phenomena.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "The monsoon typically begins in July in cities like Phoenix, bringing fluctuating moisture due to moving air masses.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "Last year saw a slow start to the monsoon, affecting annual rainfall in Phoenix.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "A significant portion of rainfall is lost to recycling or evapotranspiration, while winter precipitation is better retained in the soil.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "Land use practices have contributed to loosening topsoil, making it more susceptible to wind erosion.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "Thunderstorm bases can often be more than a mile above ground, intensifying wind events.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "San Antonio experienced its hottest May on record, with five days of triple-digit temperatures.", "citations": ["4755901b-5f20-43d6-bb98-ae62df4aeee0_1026333416"]}, {"text": "This heat is linked to La Ni\u00f1a, climate change, and results in higher energy consumption and utility bills.", "citations": ["4755901b-5f20-43d6-bb98-ae62df4aeee0_1026333416"]}, {"text": "The U.S. plastics industry is projected to surpass coal in climate impact by 2030, increasing environmental vulnerability.", "citations": ["59d543d3-87d5-4050-aea9-1765993f8446_179252107"]}, {"text": "Disaster response agencies recognize that future challenges will differ from past events, requiring adaptive strategies.", "citations": ["59d543d3-87d5-4050-aea9-1765993f8446_179252107"]}, {"text": "Recent record-setting wind storms highlight extreme weather impacts across the Great Plains and Midwest.", "citations": ["6e28cd56-93cc-4295-b3c8-828a7d7fda04_579755132"]}, {"text": "Prolonged heat and drought have increased wildfire risks due to dry vegetation.", "citations": ["4755901b-5f20-43d6-bb98-ae62df4aeee0_1026333416"]}, {"text": "Changes in the water cycle are becoming more apparent as climate effects intensify.", "citations": ["90be0790-695c-45e3-b944-a130c20a1991_417506747"]}, {"text": "Efforts are underway in cities, including creating master plans to improve climate resilience and urban watershed management.", "citations": ["fbef4801-b151-4f9f-9003-3a4f26b8f22c_629267606"]}, {"text": "Experts emphasize the importance of community preparedness, resilience, and equitable outcomes after climate events.", "citations": ["fbef4801-b151-4f9f-9003-3a4f26b8f22c_629267606"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1011", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Since Mohammed bin Salman (MBS) became Crown Prince in 2017, Saudi Arabia has embarked on a remarkable period of social and economic transformation under Vision 2030.", "citations": ["3e6ce080-5be8-4139-9ebb-2465c6f80d4c_721618053"]}, {"text": "Sports events, movie screenings, art exhibitions, and music concerts are now increasingly common, with Saudis embracing these new cultural opportunities.", "citations": ["1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850"]}, {"text": "Reform efforts include addressing the ideological teachings that previously fostered sectarianism and intolerance, signaling progressive change at the kingdom's core.", "citations": ["acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949"]}, {"text": "However, the permanence of these ideological shifts is not guaranteed.", "citations": ["1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850"]}, {"text": "Women's workforce participation has nearly doubled over the last five years, rising from almost 18% to 32% according to official statistics.", "citations": ["f14b5c9e-084a-4291-8dc9-a631b84e6c4c_107673090"]}, {"text": "Saudi women now contribute to research and entrepreneurship, highlighting expanding opportunities.", "citations": ["8d9e78ed-f484-406d-8778-c733be2554ab_670261581"]}, {"text": "In social life, the climate is also changing, with greater flexibility in practices surrounding public spaces and prayer times.", "citations": ["acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949"]}, {"text": "Empowerment of women is a stated goal of Vision 2030, encouraging women to pursue careers and leadership roles.", "citations": ["8cba1092-ce88-49ba-9609-d092f4489d28_624730938"]}, {"text": "Crowds attending sports events and fashion activities reflect an increasingly lively public sphere.", "citations": ["1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850"]}, {"text": "Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman has maintained significant government investment to support economic growth and diversification.", "citations": ["de7bafe3-0613-4f8d-a925-cd3f5a571d98_897868556"]}, {"text": "The expansion of Saudi fashion is part of a strategy to modernize the economy and promote cultural change.", "citations": ["acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949"]}, {"text": "Investment in global industries, including fashion and fragrances, is opening new avenues for Saudis, particularly women, to launch businesses and creative ventures.", "citations": ["8d9e78ed-f484-406d-8778-c733be2554ab_670261581"]}, {"text": "Women like TV presenter Sara Murad emphasize the sense of empowerment and support they feel from these reforms.", "citations": ["8d9e78ed-f484-406d-8778-c733be2554ab_670261581"]}, {"text": "With the National Strategy for Industry, the kingdom aims to increase total investments in the sector and dramatically boost technology exports.", "citations": ["3e6ce080-5be8-4139-9ebb-2465c6f80d4c_721618053"]}, {"text": "The government\u2019s ongoing reforms continue to shape a new future for Saudi Arabia's women and youth.", "citations": ["8cba1092-ce88-49ba-9609-d092f4489d28_624730938"]}, {"text": "Vision 2030\u2019s broad reforms are paving the way for a more open, economically diverse, and progressive Saudi society, while balancing tradition and change.", "citations": ["acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1013", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Traditional Caribbean dishes are rooted in adaptation and intuitive seasonal cooking.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "One cook describes recreating family recipes, like Palau, guided by memories passed down through generations.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "An environmental writer commuting between Barbados and Cayman Islands reflects on the importance of food, agriculture, and safeguarding biodiversity, even in times of crisis.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "Recent efforts, like a cooking trip to Lviv, Ukraine, symbolize global collaboration for a future aligned with slow food values.", "citations": ["3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363"]}, {"text": "Artisanal food made with traditional methods and tools is rising in popularity and is mostly produced on a small scale.", "citations": ["86f0531e-4d76-40fa-9d32-2249450d475e_725694039"]}, {"text": "People are increasingly supporting small local businesses, making choices that reduce carbon emissions and benefit the environment.", "citations": ["86f0531e-4d76-40fa-9d32-2249450d475e_725694039"]}, {"text": "Regenerative farming\u2014prioritizing healthy soil and sustainable practices\u2014is highlighted as key to the future of food security.", "citations": ["d81bd102-edab-45d8-9e07-7eabfd506ff6_213163074"]}, {"text": "Supporting small-scale farmers helps foster a sustainable food system.", "citations": ["d81bd102-edab-45d8-9e07-7eabfd506ff6_213163074"]}, {"text": "In Lamu, the historic Amu House exemplifies cultural heritage intertwined with food traditions.", "citations": ["e9951c05-7d63-4215-ba1f-f774e81ccb42_799247081"]}, {"text": "Community activities, like whale shark safaris, reflect broader connections between food, ecology, and local identity.", "citations": ["e9951c05-7d63-4215-ba1f-f774e81ccb42_799247081"]}, {"text": "In Napa, the cool food movement encourages reducing waste, sharing produce, and being mindful of food consumption.", "citations": ["eec6fa37-518f-43fd-9c9d-1a12428f4853_258820982"]}, {"text": "Pope Francis recently supported Italian activists in Rome working to safeguard biodiversity, emphasizing the urgent need to protect bees and nature.", "citations": ["90c089b4-9707-45ba-af3b-77dd18799bed_763079563"]}, {"text": "Global supply chain failures reveal the risks of overreliance on international trade for food, and the price of basic foods like chicken is rising in the UK.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8038-548b14438087_146567024"]}, {"text": "Such crises show the value of localized economies and the growing local food movement on every continent.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8038-548b14438087_146567024"]}, {"text": "Localization benefits not just food systems but overall resilience in times of crisis.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8038-548b14438087_146567024"]}, {"text": "The new year brings a fusion of innovative foods that are both healthful and environmentally friendly.", "citations": ["e0b3fd04-8c44-4ed3-aeb8-a6bbd77a4cfb_179649275"]}, {"text": "Food trends for 2024 honor ancestral traditions while promoting gut health and awareness of the food\u2019s journey from source to plate.", "citations": ["e0b3fd04-8c44-4ed3-aeb8-a6bbd77a4cfb_179649275"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1015", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Individuals who reject widely accepted scientific facts, such as flat Earth believers, are often viewed as outliers but have gained a visible presence online in recent years.", "citations": ["ed34cfa8-e40f-4433-8f1d-349b4c1ea5d9_323897139"]}, {"text": "Organizations like the Flat Earth Society in the United States and the United Kingdom, as well as \u201cGlobe Lie\u201d groups in Germany and other European countries, actively promote flat Earth beliefs through websites, conferences, and social media.", "citations": ["8659627b-c8b3-43b0-9807-68112c459c78_360348511"]}, {"text": "A small number of public figures, including former NBA player Kyrie Irving and social media influencer B.o.B, have publicly supported or promoted flat Earth theories, drawing further attention to the movement.", "citations": ["8659627b-c8b3-43b0-9807-68112c459c78_360348511"]}, {"text": "Common arguments from flat Earthers include claims that photos of Earth from space are fabricated, that water\u2019s surface always finds its level (allegedly disproving curves), and that airline flight patterns are easier to explain on a flat map.", "citations": ["a94246fc-797c-4c50-a483-67da2cb3d7d9_233255905"]}, {"text": "Some assert that governments and scientists are conspiring to conceal the \u201ctruth\u201d of a flat Earth for financial or political gain, which feeds into broader distrust of institutions.", "citations": ["ed34cfa8-e40f-4433-8f1d-349b4c1ea5d9_323897139"]}, {"text": "The resurgence of flat Earth beliefs in the Internet era is linked to social media algorithms, which can create echo chambers; viral videos and forums foster communities where these views go unchallenged and feel validated.", "citations": ["a94246fc-797c-4c50-a483-67da2cb3d7d9_233255905"]}, {"text": "People attracted to flat Earth beliefs often share traits such as distrust of authority, a desire for certainty in a complex world, feeling marginalized by mainstream society, or seeking a sense of belonging.", "citations": ["ed34cfa8-e40f-4433-8f1d-349b4c1ea5d9_323897139"]}, {"text": "Online, the movement uses memes, YouTube videos, podcasts, and discussion forums to spread ideas and recruit new adherents, often linking flat Earth to other conspiracy theories.", "citations": ["1c98e81a-4445-4394-9f66-41534d112628_366362006"]}, {"text": "Psychologists note that subscribing to such beliefs can give people a sense of personal empowerment, but can also make them more isolated from mainstream thinking.", "citations": ["ed34cfa8-e40f-4433-8f1d-349b4c1ea5d9_323897139"]}, {"text": "While most flat Earthers are peaceful and not inherently dangerous, the movement\u2019s deep skepticism of science can expose adherents to other harmful misinformation and anti-establishment ideologies.", "citations": ["ed34cfa8-e40f-4433-8f1d-349b4c1ea5d9_323897139"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1017", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Disney\u2019s strategy of producing live-action remakes of its classic animated films is deeply tied to the company\u2019s legacy and the emotion of nostalgia.", "citations": ["800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286"]}, {"text": "Projects like Once Upon a Studio and the Wonderful World of Disney\u2019s 100th Anniversary Special reunite beloved characters, drawing on multi-generational affection for Disney icons.", "citations": ["444d326b-fc76-4890-b9de-335e5c3cb621_534261207"]}, {"text": "Significant effort goes into updating familiar stories and characters, as seen in the process of including Robin Williams\u2019 Genie in Aladdin by working closely with his estate.", "citations": ["440ee913-7016-4f8d-b2e0-3fce141e4dac_73458855"]}, {"text": "Modern remakes carefully merge technological artistry with storytelling, facing creative challenges such as making characters from different visual worlds, like Moana and Flounder, appear cohesive on screen.", "citations": ["800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286"]}, {"text": "Disney adapts its classics through mindful casting\u2014prioritizing actor spirit and talent over physical resemblance, as in the casting of Ariel in The Little Mermaid.", "citations": ["800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286"]}, {"text": "Remakes are sometimes extended with new characters, such as Queen Salina, and launched in conjunction with related products like animated series, broadening a film\u2019s reach.", "citations": ["e6068745-f488-4f0e-9910-2f016b0f9a10_884726436"]}, {"text": "Some viewers and industry voices express concern about the authenticity of remade characters and updates to classic tales, especially regarding diversity and representation, as seen in public reactions to Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs.", "citations": ["e6068745-f488-4f0e-9910-2f016b0f9a10_884726436"]}, {"text": "Technological advances mean the blending of reality and animation is more seamless, but creators emphasize that animation\u2019s heart lies in personal artistic inspiration rather than realism alone.", "citations": ["800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286"]}, {"text": "Every remake is a complex endeavor that pays homage to Walt Disney\u2019s original vision and the painstaking effort involved in creating foundational works like Snow White.", "citations": ["800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286"]}, {"text": "The creative process at Disney increasingly centers on giving new, diverse voices opportunities for leadership, ensuring stories reflect contemporary values while acknowledging the company\u2019s storied past.", "citations": ["440ee913-7016-4f8d-b2e0-3fce141e4dac_73458855"]}, {"text": "Filmmakers and actors bring their distinct perspectives and energies, building trust within teams that evolve naturally as individuals are drawn to the material.", "citations": ["800e6594-4a58-4429-a918-25f13f8757aa_119137286"]}, {"text": "Ultimately, live-action remakes serve as both a tribute to Disney\u2019s history and a means to introduce its stories to new audiences, balancing reverence for the originals with the demands of modern entertainment and identity.", "citations": ["440ee913-7016-4f8d-b2e0-3fce141e4dac_73458855"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1019", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Exercise programs aimed at preventing falls in seniors may also reduce injuries caused by falls, according to a recent review.", "citations": ["184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782"]}, {"text": "Falls among older adults increase the risk of nursing home admission and have a significant economic impact.", "citations": ["184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782"]}, {"text": "The U.S. National Institute on Aging provides resources about falls in older adults.", "citations": ["184485a7-25df-4efa-b2f3-f28ae72d25e3_199781782"]}, {"text": "\"Every player on the field is important and if a player is not working, then your team \u2014 your balance \u2014 is going to be impacted.\"", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Even if a fall does not result in injury, it can trigger a fear of falling in seniors.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Fee recommends that a fall risk assessment is an important first step toward preventing falls.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Physicians or health care providers can refer older adults to physical therapists to evaluate their risk for falls.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Goralnik noted that many falls and fall-related injuries lead to difficulty with daily activities and a need for supportive care.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "It is crucial for seniors to speak with their doctor about any changes in walking, new instability, or new musculoskeletal pain.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "\"Without any change, the number of Americans with Alzheimer's disease could more than double.\"", "citations": ["86768892-e5eb-480f-a579-4396f9100369_738292996"]}, {"text": "Snyder reported no conflicts of interest.", "citations": ["86768892-e5eb-480f-a579-4396f9100369_738292996"]}, {"text": "A financial analyst described how practicing tai chi helped her manage the stress of her career and avoid burnout, saying she had more energy and an easier time navigating challenges.", "citations": ["885d7b96-d3cf-4d10-a3e7-5ac07edbd0bb_331812203"]}, {"text": "Tai chi can help people remain centered and focused, preventing distraction.", "citations": ["885d7b96-d3cf-4d10-a3e7-5ac07edbd0bb_331812203"]}, {"text": "Alcohol use is another risk factor for falls that can be managed.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Fractures are the most common injury from falls among seniors.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Once an older adult has fallen, their risk of future falls increases.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Fatal falls are most often due to hip fractures or head injuries.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Fatal head injury falls are more common in men, those on blood thinners, and those without a musculoskeletal diagnosis.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Dr. Michael Mosley reported that four minutes a day spent on balance exercises, including tai chi, can support longer life, based on studies including balance tests.", "citations": ["a3e8fc90-96ac-491a-9391-1d36b954f8e8_220672298"]}, {"text": "Balance training is important as breaking a hip from a fall is a major risk for older adults.", "citations": ["a3e8fc90-96ac-491a-9391-1d36b954f8e8_220672298"]}, {"text": "Balance exercises, such as tai chi or yoga, provide numerous benefits beyond balance alone.", "citations": ["a3e8fc90-96ac-491a-9391-1d36b954f8e8_220672298"]}, {"text": "A study published in the BMJ found that the ability to stand on one leg was the best predictor of longevity among middle-aged people.", "citations": ["a3e8fc90-96ac-491a-9391-1d36b954f8e8_220672298"]}, {"text": "Staying balanced requires coordination of multiple body systems.", "citations": ["a3e8fc90-96ac-491a-9391-1d36b954f8e8_220672298"]}, {"text": "YMCA programs for seniors can improve health through exercise.", "citations": ["34a5ef86-794c-4dd0-95a9-b1b3c3632633_326815735"]}, {"text": "Consuming adequate vitamins, protein, and vegetables is recommended to maintain muscle mass and energy in older age.", "citations": ["e9eb5771-7ac9-4da2-b8e6-83b613a4bf78_711721744"]}, {"text": "How we respond to a trip affects whether we fall or recover balance, and practicing such situations is valuable.", "citations": ["9aef89be-a1de-42e1-8c46-7b3ceadee58f_797019169"]}, {"text": "Falls are a global problem among the elderly.", "citations": ["59adae63-1ce9-4b72-9918-a3b07f35626b_385233152"]}, {"text": "Further research is needed to inform clinical practices for fall prevention and balance control.", "citations": ["59adae63-1ce9-4b72-9918-a3b07f35626b_385233152"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1021", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Occupational therapy aims to help patients achieve goals based on their individual needs and desires.", "citations": ["67665702-bd2a-4af8-9293-8ce0aaf2176a_280162833"]}, {"text": "This personalized approach is especially beneficial for older adults where fall risk increases annually due to various factors.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Brain health significantly influences balance and the ability to prevent falls.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Even without injury, falls often lead to a lasting fear of falling.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Age alone does not determine balance impairment, as medications can also increase fall risk.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Conducting a fall risk assessment is an important first step in fall prevention.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Healthcare providers can refer individuals to physical therapists for evaluation of fall risk.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Improving balance requires continually challenging the body\u2019s systems.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Falls and related injuries often result in decreased ability to perform daily activities and the need for additional support.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Older adults should promptly report changes in gait or new pain to their doctors.", "citations": ["08b29f61-ad72-46e6-859d-df2e6233ec1b_349742184"]}, {"text": "Alcohol consumption is a modifiable risk factor for falls.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Fractures are the most frequent result of falls.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Prolonged time on the ground after a fall can cause muscle breakdown, kidney failure, and even death.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "Fatal falls are usually due to hip fractures or head injuries, with head injury deaths more common in men, those on blood thinners, and people without musculoskeletal diagnoses.", "citations": ["cf35f7cc-4afe-4e57-aaa1-60eec2e0d061_430451653"]}, {"text": "The COVID-19 pandemic has intensified challenges for patients and healthcare providers, with growing demand for physical therapy as the population ages.", "citations": ["85cf836e-c158-4112-9701-cdfb3fa5902b_808634048"]}, {"text": "Home-based rehabilitation is critical for patients recovering from stroke and other conditions.", "citations": ["ad9a5016-3d7e-48c9-ace8-581589428946_216293142"]}, {"text": "After a stroke, patients may have weakness and limited movement on one side of the body, requiring coordinated care at home to enhance quality of life.", "citations": ["ad9a5016-3d7e-48c9-ace8-581589428946_216293142"]}, {"text": "More than 40% of adults over 40 experience dizziness, increasing fall risk, particularly after stroke or neurological injury.", "citations": ["ab6a3ef1-d316-41fa-8eda-92056179046d_239704851"]}, {"text": "Balance programs assist patients with stroke, brain injury, and other neurological conditions.", "citations": ["3624ad80-21b0-4779-a0bf-139136df3885_603007344"]}, {"text": "Community and family involvement are essential in supporting rehabilitation and improving lives.", "citations": ["90e1b4f1-39bd-49e0-b4e0-1cf9583e286d_1000867933"]}, {"text": "Social engagement and supportive environments reduce mental health challenges among older adults.", "citations": ["b1b357b1-21c5-4479-bf63-c07c723b95be_800938764"]}, {"text": "A strong support system maximizes an older adult's ability to safely remain at home.", "citations": ["b3833179-2a6f-413d-af2e-1331a7e6d556_164261740"]}, {"text": "Cognitive health strategies from organizations like the CDC promote aging in place.", "citations": ["b3833179-2a6f-413d-af2e-1331a7e6d556_164261740"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1023", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The global single-aisle aircraft market is projected to reach $222.20 billion by 2030, reflecting a robust long-term trend despite the severe impact of the COVID-19 pandemic.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Aircraft manufacturers are increasingly investing in research and development focused on sustainability and reducing carbon emissions, including the creation of more eco-friendly models.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Turboprop engines, known for fuel efficiency and reliability, have become a preferred choice for regional carriers, particularly in the Asia-Pacific region, which is the largest market segment.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Airlines in Asia-Pacific are expanding their fleets to meet growing air travel demand, while Europe leads in terms of growth, and North America remains a stable, vital market servicing both domestic and international routes.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "The surge in air travel is driving increased demand for aircraft leasing, with the market segmented by lease type, aircraft type, and region, including North America and Canada.", "citations": ["59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_445106883"]}, {"text": "There is rising use of connected aircraft for maintenance and repair, expected to drive market growth, although the high cost of technology integration and lack of skilled personnel pose challenges.", "citations": ["226d9601-5c18-49af-bc51-d007f5d3617d_932016380"]}, {"text": "The global connected aircraft market is forecasted to grow rapidly, driven by demand for real-time information, flight safety, passenger comfort, and advanced communication and navigation systems.", "citations": ["226d9601-5c18-49af-bc51-d007f5d3617d_932016380"]}, {"text": "FTAI Aviation Ltd reported a rebound to $41,307 net income in Q3 2023, contrasting a net loss of $18,929 in Q3 2022.", "citations": ["51c3f977-a25c-489c-ba32-19d3fc347912_726903928"]}, {"text": "The aviation carbon fiber market is forecasted to reach $4.4 billion by 2031, with PAN-based and continuous carbon fibers showing significant growth due to rising global air travelers.", "citations": ["4a9091b3-af57-4bf2-b787-6f10c6a4c451_510642838"]}, {"text": "Major aircraft manufacturers like Airbus and Boeing received a combined 1,439 orders in the first 11 months of 2021, three times more than in 2020, signaling strong recovery and future demand.", "citations": ["da8890be-3b30-4aea-a1d6-b59e0f69a62e_1004451542"]}, {"text": "Airbus received a surge of orders during the Dubai Air Show, while KLM committed to several dozen A321 aircraft.", "citations": ["59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_445106883"]}, {"text": "Textron\u2019s strides in sustainable fuel initiatives and a valuable defense contract\u2014potentially worth up to $70 billion\u2014reflect the industry\u2019s ongoing investment in efficiency and sustainability.", "citations": ["d0868668-650b-41ae-bf3a-02d9a523015c_20700738"]}, {"text": "Sustainable fuel investments and advanced materials are expected to deliver long-term value as airlines and manufacturers compete with innovative, fuel-efficient models.", "citations": ["d0868668-650b-41ae-bf3a-02d9a523015c_20700738"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1025", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "To become a forklift driver, you must be at least 18 and hold a high school diploma.", "citations": ["642fd5b0-ed80-4d08-8091-c65b63653018_247813657"]}, {"text": "Once certified, a wide variety of jobs become available, so it is important to choose a program that matches your goals.", "citations": ["642fd5b0-ed80-4d08-8091-c65b63653018_247813657"]}, {"text": "Application for Forklift Operator Certification is straightforward for eligible candidates.", "citations": ["642fd5b0-ed80-4d08-8091-c65b63653018_247813657"]}, {"text": "LUS Fiber recently hired its first woman lineworker, a graduate of the SLCC Power Lineman program.", "citations": ["5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769"]}, {"text": "Several women, including a former Miss England finalist, an England rugby star, and an ex-finance worker, have switched to driving 44-tonne lorries across Great Britain, highlighting a positive shift in the industry.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "The former model trained for both Class 1 and Class 2 HGV licences and achieved her dream of becoming a lorry driver.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "She was crowned Miss Charity after raising the most money for good causes.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Inspired by the fact that less than one percent of British HGV drivers are female, she encourages others to join the field.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "She believes \u201cwe\u2019re in modern times and there\u2019s nothing to stop girls getting involved.\u201d  \nBreaking stereotypes is important and she wants these qualifications under her belt.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Her progression from driving tractors to large trucks felt natural.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Chantelle Crowl, an England and Super League rugby star, drives a HGV and manages her driving job around her demanding sports schedule.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Crowl pursued her Class 1 certification after finding a company online willing to provide training and support.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Other women have changed careers due to dissatisfaction with office work, seeking greater control over their environment.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Challenges such as balancing work and family and adapting to new communities were initially difficult, but perseverance led to personal success.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Support from family was crucial for women like Two Eagle, who celebrated her graduation as a shared achievement.", "citations": ["e8c236e0-322e-4ea5-b004-7de7b3c473f9_781615632"]}, {"text": "Difficult beginnings are common, but continued effort pays off.", "citations": ["e8c236e0-322e-4ea5-b004-7de7b3c473f9_781615632"]}, {"text": "Ms Naliaka, a mother of four, persisted despite the challenges of balancing work and family, gradually mastering her duties.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "She confronted skepticism from men but advises standing firm and advocating for oneself when needed.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Industry leaders like Mike Ellis of American Commercial Barge Line highlight growing opportunities, better pay, and technological advancements in the sector.", "citations": ["b24091fe-8d0a-4801-b368-2b00c8793fc6_9518928"]}, {"text": "AI and new equipment are generating excitement and expanding possibilities for women in construction and maritime fields.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Mentorship, using one\u2019s voice, and taking an active role are emphasized as keys for women aspiring to succeed in these traditionally male-dominated roles.", "citations": ["0e63a60c-9a64-4f48-96b4-74b563b0f840_886601763"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1027", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "A woman has recently broken gender barriers by being assigned the job of Hyva operator.", "citations": ["c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220"]}, {"text": "Subodh Pandey, Vice President, TSM, along with other TSM executives, congratulated and interacted with the new recruits, reflecting management encouragement.", "citations": ["c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220"]}, {"text": "Ryder was named one of Women In Trucking\u2019s 2023 Top Companies for Women to Work For in Transportation, showcasing industry progress.", "citations": ["63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585"]}, {"text": "The Trucker News Staff provides content on the trucking segment from Little Rock, Arkansas, emphasizing gender diversity\u2019s benefits for employers and women alike.", "citations": ["63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585"]}, {"text": "Women such as Nathalie van de Poel, Maria Willshee, Heather Gould, and Hilary Hart actively contribute to high-level and community-level work in waste management.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "James David of Skip Hire Glasgow recommends fostering inclusivity in hiring as a way to bring more women into these fields.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "Most construction sites remain male-dominated, and terms like \u2018foreperson\u2019 are still uncommon compared to \u2018foreman.\u2019  \nTemplates for heavy equipment operator job applications help streamline and fairly track hiring processes.", "citations": ["c40b5c1c-6e7a-45f6-a314-adcf276acb8c_663217418"]}, {"text": "A female construction worker recounts her passion for the work, her role on sites, and the challenges and joys of the job, especially in different weather conditions.", "citations": ["e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603"]}, {"text": "She loves her team and wishes more women would pursue site roles while participating in school outreach to inspire others.", "citations": ["18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479"]}, {"text": "She remembers being one of only three girls in her construction studies class, highlighting the gender gap in education pipelines.", "citations": ["18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479"]}, {"text": "Rachael Reresi\u2019s entry and success in the mechanics sector of Warrior Industry exemplifies women\u2019s determination to thrive where they are rare.", "citations": ["1cd9e393-4db2-462d-ae50-377c72aa0dc4_1038775602"]}, {"text": "Her achievements challenge norms and set a precedent for future generations.", "citations": ["1cd9e393-4db2-462d-ae50-377c72aa0dc4_1038775602"]}, {"text": "While British Columbia\u2019s construction sector faces short-term employment contraction, diversity and inclusiveness remain focus areas.", "citations": ["6a6d4ff9-70fb-4925-9af7-9894eb74951b_152515651"]}, {"text": "Women in the industry often start as minorities in tough conditions but are now encouraging others to pursue such careers, leading to rising program enrollments.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "Women in construction affirm their capability and intelligence, serving as witnesses and role models for breaking industry stereotypes.", "citations": ["e54d5d6e-0c6a-47f4-9834-81419f13a22e_14234603"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1029", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The evolution of science fiction has involved a blending of genres and a questioning of reality, as N.K.", "citations": ["01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677"]}, {"text": "Jemisin discusses in her lecture about how people build worlds and make choices that shape society.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "Jemisin points out youth's natural inclination to challenge the structures around them, tying this to the genre's power of imagination and inquiry.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "She emphasizes that science fiction is like all genres and can be personal and transformative, with stories that change readers.", "citations": ["dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587"]}, {"text": "Fiction, according to Sen, is a valuable way to understand real-world problems, dismissing the notion that escapism is less important.", "citations": ["dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587"]}, {"text": "Authors often draw from personal views and experiences, as illustrated in stories where gods and scientists intersect, such as Tu Lala and Shawu Incarnate.", "citations": ["ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341"]}, {"text": "Wang Jinkang notes that the science fiction writer's perspective is expansive, often thinking in millennia, making short-term trends less influential on enduring themes.", "citations": ["ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341"]}, {"text": "Recognition like the Hugo Awards serves as a gift from readers to authors, showcasing the genre\u2019s evolving community.", "citations": ["ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341"]}, {"text": "Classic titles such as L. Frank Baum's \"Ozma of Oz,\" H.G.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Wells\u2019 \"The War of the Worlds,\" Isaac Asimov\u2019s \"I, Robot,\" and Ursula K. Le Guin's \"The Left Hand of Darkness\" are traditional canonical works.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Contemporary and indie authors expand the field with new perspectives, like J. Dianne Dotson's \"Heliopause\" and Gareth L. Powell's \"Embers of War.\"", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Science fiction frequently speculates about technology and society, asking what it means to live or travel on planets like Mars or navigate changing times.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Authors reflect on their own lives and inspirations; reading Ray Bradbury and books about magic influenced current writers, who observe how the genre and their stories keep evolving.", "citations": ["2ae6927f-bef9-4b8b-b9fc-80626f4e0499_180621382"]}, {"text": "Fiction allows for meaning and closure often lacking in real life and remains a way for writers and readers to make sense of the world as they return to old and new tales.", "citations": ["2ae6927f-bef9-4b8b-b9fc-80626f4e0499_180621382"]}, {"text": "Women, people of color, and international voices such as Jemisin and Wang Jinkang have increasingly shaped the genre, demonstrating the expanded reach and richness of science fiction literature today.", "citations": ["01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677"]}, {"text": "Writing can heal and connect, as authors revisit settings and ideas, building new worlds with words on the page.", "citations": ["2ae6927f-bef9-4b8b-b9fc-80626f4e0499_180621382"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1031", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Kenyan students are set to benefit from a Sh33 billion Mastercard-funded digital education scheme aimed at addressing high primary school dropout rates.", "citations": ["6510e519-38cf-4427-8eaa-be83653c75d7_197203581"]}, {"text": "The program is supported by an impact study conducted by the Perivoli Africa Research Centre (PARC) at the University of Bristol.", "citations": ["6c2c94a4-3c75-40e8-94b1-a256110aa1fd_608042394"]}, {"text": "Special Economic Zones (SEZs) and free zones are being promoted as viable mechanisms to accelerate wealth creation and reduce brain drain across Africa.", "citations": ["c2baacaf-1ba7-4969-905f-2e96f5b34a99_259689578"]}, {"text": "Africa Employer of Record (EOR) services are helping foreign businesses enter African markets, offering benefits such as access to skilled labor, streamlined payroll and tax management, and enabling companies to focus on strategic goals.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "Future trends in EOR services in Africa include greater automation, AI implementation in payroll and HR, updates in labor regulations, and increasing demand for flexible solutions supporting remote work and global expansion.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "US-Africa partnerships are being strengthened, and there is a push to include higher education perspectives within these formalized networks.", "citations": ["0ff094d9-ef9b-44ec-98a6-9c4bae0d4ca0_416320635"]}, {"text": "African legal services are evolving, presenting opportunities for firms and legal professionals who combine legal expertise with management skills.", "citations": ["c10bb651-06ed-41fb-b281-f9397484efe7_654463001"]}, {"text": "SGS, a leading Testing, Inspection and Certification (TIC) firm, has launched advanced digital operations with plans to expand globally, including in Africa.", "citations": ["c10bb651-06ed-41fb-b281-f9397484efe7_654463001"]}, {"text": "India has announced that Africa is a top priority, emphasizing a unique development partnership model tailored to African needs and promoting inclusion, technology sharing, public service delivery, and mutual support.", "citations": ["69290114-ec48-48e8-b0df-223245abf7c9_468636098"]}, {"text": "India\u2019s collaboration with Africa now covers new sectors such as defense, and India has advocated for the African Union\u2019s full membership in the G20.", "citations": ["69290114-ec48-48e8-b0df-223245abf7c9_468636098"]}, {"text": "The evolving economic and technological landscape in Africa positions the continent as an increasingly important global voice and partner for future growth.", "citations": ["69290114-ec48-48e8-b0df-223245abf7c9_468636098"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1033", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "During the COVID-19 pandemic, more businesses adopted a four-day week as remote working prompted a major rethinking of work practices, according to a University of Reading poll of 500 UK senior business leaders.", "citations": ["4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730"]}, {"text": "A majority (65%) reported offering a four-day workweek to at least some employees, up from 50% in 2019.", "citations": ["4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730"]}, {"text": "The pandemic demonstrated that flexible approaches can be successful, with advances in technology driving these changes and making the trend increasingly appealing.", "citations": ["4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730"]}, {"text": "The world\u2019s largest four-day workweek trial, organized by 4 Day Week Global, began in the UK on June 6.", "citations": ["04b2f2a0-28da-4acb-915d-4a601d16aec2_892204018"]}, {"text": "Some models reduce the number of working days while maintaining pay, while others shorten daily hours.", "citations": ["941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754"]}, {"text": "Benefits of reduced working hours include improved work-life balance and increased personal time.", "citations": ["941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754"]}, {"text": "Evidence suggests a widespread desire for shorter workweeks, but questions remain about mainstream adoption.", "citations": ["941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754"]}, {"text": "One company highlighted staff quality of life as a primary motivator, resulting in a workforce focused on operational streamlining and staff satisfaction.", "citations": ["e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821"]}, {"text": "A four-day week yields an additional 50 days of free time annually, a significant gain for employees.", "citations": ["e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821"]}, {"text": "Employees have reported using this extra time for personal enrichment, such as travel and family activities.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "While not all companies may find the model feasible, employee buy-in has been strong where it has been implemented.", "citations": ["e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821"]}, {"text": "Some believe a shortened week could be stigmatized at other firms, but it can offer the best of both worlds for businesses and staff.", "citations": ["941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754"]}, {"text": "Only three companies surveyed said they would not consider a shortened workweek.", "citations": ["c81c5dee-23ff-495f-ab91-7887d6ee6c8b_554937375"]}, {"text": "Participants in the six-month UK trial are now more than halfway through.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Atom Bank reported that its customer service rating on Trust Pilot improved after switching to the new structure.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Some firms, like Merthyr Valley Homes, implemented a 30-hour, four-day week with no loss of pay.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Employees report that the additional free day improves their home life and work focus, acting as a \u201creset day\u201d that enhances their productivity and well-being.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Proper preparation is essential when shifting from five days to four, as each person adapts differently.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Workers and employers alike report better work-life balance, greater creativity, and no reduction in pay.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Feedback from customers and suppliers has also been positive, with some expressing interest in joining such companies.", "citations": ["5335aaf9-f947-4283-a183-38034b100c56_264196256"]}, {"text": "Implementing the four-day workweek is challenging but often rewarded with higher productivity and satisfaction.", "citations": ["e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1035", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Biohacking is a movement focused on reprogramming the mind and body to live better, originating in Silicon Valley.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "Women are noted as the original biohackers, and as more women participate, the trend becomes more intuitive and less about achieving every imposed benchmark.", "citations": ["0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574"]}, {"text": "Previously, some biohackers, like Vand, believed in multitasking and stacking habits, but the approach is shifting towards sustainability.", "citations": ["0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574"]}, {"text": "Biohacking includes activities such as weight training, yoga, Ayurveda, and nutritional planning (like questioning what to eat before a workout).", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "People pursue practices such as gluten-free, dairy-free, and keto diets, bulletproof diet, intermittent fasting, supplement intake, and exercise regimens to optimize health, reduce inflammation, and promote longevity.", "citations": ["0d8c27cc-fe14-4171-b4c0-1e5ffcb86d87_53197859"]}, {"text": "Some individuals report practices that support well-being, such as walking daily or adopting active lifestyles.", "citations": ["0d8c27cc-fe14-4171-b4c0-1e5ffcb86d87_53197859"]}, {"text": "CRISPR gene editing, seen as a form of advanced biohacking, has revolutionized biology and enabled precise DNA alterations; researchers continue to refine these methods, though most results so far are seen in laboratory animals.", "citations": ["861bcdac-3a6d-4b74-8b46-fb8fd675a647_752012545"]}, {"text": "There are efforts to use biohacking principles, such as gene editing and immune-boosting interventions, to fight diseases, but much remains experimental or only partially accessible.", "citations": ["861bcdac-3a6d-4b74-8b46-fb8fd675a647_752012545"]}, {"text": "Fights against diseases like lupus or RA may involve expensive treatments unavailable to all, although proponents suggest there are affordable healthy habits anyone can adopt.", "citations": ["936c65fa-80e6-47ba-8442-e5e77a4826a5_411498914"]}, {"text": "Reducing inflammation is a widely discussed goal among biohackers, with the claim that it brings the body back into harmony, but scientific support is variable.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "Studies define the \u201cmetabolically healthy obese\u201d as those who maintain healthy lifestyle habits\u2014such as regular exercise and diet\u2014despite obesity, though their degree of protection from chronic disease remains uncertain.", "citations": ["0d8c27cc-fe14-4171-b4c0-1e5ffcb86d87_53197859"]}, {"text": "Research in gene regulation and cellular mechanisms is ongoing, deepening our understanding but often not directly translating into everyday health interventions yet.", "citations": ["97c5f95d-b32e-4675-b2fb-fb0aec17cb7c_123228338"]}, {"text": "Biohacking's popularity and promise are growing, but while some methods have scientific merit, many are under-researched and their safety and effectiveness are not established for all.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1037", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "After Hagia Sophia, Turkey has converted the ancient Byzantine Chora Church\u2014used as a museum for 79 years\u2014into a mosque.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Some Orthodox Christians expressed disappointment but suggested focusing on unity rather than division over the conversion.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Muslim worshippers celebrated the mosque\u2019s rededication as a national achievement for Turkey.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Recent videos show fragments falling from Hagia Sophia\u2019s dome, highlighting preservation concerns.", "citations": ["9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018"]}, {"text": "A new tourist entrance to Hagia Sophia now exists in front of the Topkapi Palace Museum.", "citations": ["3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190"]}, {"text": "According to the Turkish ministry, starting January 15, tourists can visit Hagia Sophia Mosque without disrupting prayers.", "citations": ["3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190"]}, {"text": "Christian leaders in Turkey are interested in a new law regarding the management of religious foundations, which is crucial for local Christian communities.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "The Turkish Greek community administers 77 religious foundations, the highest in the country.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "The Chora Church, built in the 5th century by the Byzantines, is a significant historical structure.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "T\u00fcrkiye\u2019s President Recep Tayyip Erdogan has also reopened the Ayasofya Mosque\u2019s Fatih Madrassa, Istanbul\u2019s first Ottoman religious school.", "citations": ["aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472"]}, {"text": "The conversions of Hagia Sophia and Chora have provoked debate over religious freedom and the changing use of World Heritage Sites.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Christian communities and Western leaders have voiced concern about the religious implications and the preservation of these sites\u2019 multicultural legacies.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "Critics argue the mosque conversions serve political purposes for Erdogan, aiming to solidify nationalistic and religious support.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "There are ongoing discussions regarding the balance between tourism, preservation, and religious practices at these significant historical locations.", "citations": ["8a5b5f0c-d288-4106-8fac-c33115f17aeb_1035332071"]}, {"text": "The controversial reconversions have shifted access and use while raising questions about cultural heritage management in Turkey.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1039", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Turkish President Recep Tayyip Erdogan\u2019s decision to reconvert Hagia Sophia from a museum into a mosque in 2020 sparked widespread controversy due to the building's historical and religious significance as both a Byzantine cathedral and an Ottoman mosque.", "citations": ["85166e84-a226-4814-a536-c05974cf345b_568214374"]}, {"text": "Critics argue that the move challenged the secular foundation laid by modern Turkey\u2019s founder, Mustafa Kemal Ataturk, who had converted Hagia Sophia into a museum in 1934 as a symbol of secularism and coexistence.", "citations": ["85166e84-a226-4814-a536-c05974cf345b_568214374"]}, {"text": "UNESCO, which designated Hagia Sophia as a World Heritage Site, expressed deep regret, warning the decision could undermine the monument\u2019s universal value and called for dialogue to prevent negative impacts on the site\u2019s heritage status.", "citations": ["85166e84-a226-4814-a536-c05974cf345b_568214374"]}, {"text": "Religious minorities and secularists in Turkey voiced concern that the reconversion sent a message of religious exclusivity and risked alienating non-Muslims as well as those committed to a secular state.", "citations": ["85166e84-a226-4814-a536-c05974cf345b_568214374"]}, {"text": "Internationally, Greece and other countries criticized the move for endangering interfaith relations and described it as a disregard for the building\u2019s significance to Christianity.", "citations": ["85166e84-a226-4814-a536-c05974cf345b_568214374"]}, {"text": "Some observers described Erdogan\u2019s move as a political calculation to consolidate support among his conservative and nationalist base, especially ahead of key elections, by asserting Turkey\u2019s sovereignty and Islamic heritage.", "citations": ["4be3198e-4b52-4d86-ac36-cdbbf203b746_4388865"]}, {"text": "Observers also noted that the timing fit a pattern in which Erdogan invoked religious and nationalist rhetoric to counteract criticism of his rule and economic challenges facing his government.", "citations": ["4be3198e-4b52-4d86-ac36-cdbbf203b746_4388865"]}, {"text": "Supporters of the reconversion argued it restored a central piece of Ottoman-Islamic heritage and was a sovereign domestic matter for Turkey to decide.", "citations": ["066f24ec-ce3a-4224-827a-236e86f3a93e_474971019"]}, {"text": "The issue thus laid bare the intersection of religion, politics, and national identity in modern Turkey, and highlighted diverging interpretations of historical legacy.", "citations": ["85166e84-a226-4814-a536-c05974cf345b_568214374"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1041", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "HealthRoots has launched two flagship herbal products in India aimed at preventing headaches, increasing endurance, and reducing tiredness and stress.", "citations": ["9070a5c5-cd76-46ba-8c07-33e91b535e03_742183461"]}, {"text": "THIP Media and \u0100C\u0100RA have formed a partnership to fact-check Ayurveda-based misinformation in India.", "citations": ["aff59da3-6da1-4757-beaf-37fabdebd098_598370846"]}, {"text": "Dr. P. Rammanohar from the Amrita Centre for Advanced Research in Ayurveda emphasized the importance of highlighting proven facts of Ayurveda.", "citations": ["aff59da3-6da1-4757-beaf-37fabdebd098_598370846"]}, {"text": "THIP Media\u2019s chatbot RAKSHA (Readily Accessible Knowledge and Support for Health Action) will help answer questions and address doubts about Ayurveda.", "citations": ["aff59da3-6da1-4757-beaf-37fabdebd098_598370846"]}, {"text": "Sood stated that pre-competitive research and development in this area should be prioritized globally, especially considering challenges such as pandemics.", "citations": ["12285aa1-5cd6-475f-82fe-271921520848_381225395"]}, {"text": "He noted that India\u2019s rich traditions of Ayurveda, Siddha, and Unani all play significant roles and should be integrated with other medical streams.", "citations": ["12285aa1-5cd6-475f-82fe-271921520848_381225395"]}, {"text": "Ayurvedic biology was coined to address the need for scientific validation in Ayurveda.", "citations": ["12285aa1-5cd6-475f-82fe-271921520848_381225395"]}, {"text": "IIT Delhi researchers claim that Yoga and Ayurveda may be effective in treating high-risk COVID-19 cases by relieving anxiety and aiding post-treatment recovery.", "citations": ["362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295"]}, {"text": "Dr. Alka Mishra reported that belief in the efficacy of these traditional systems was significantly enhanced in patients receiving Ayurveda treatment.", "citations": ["362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295"]}, {"text": "Healthy Directions has partnered with Dr. Kulreet Chaudhary to combine traditional Ayurvedic practices with modern science, resulting in new clinically informed Ayurvedic herbal blends.", "citations": ["2b3d1f11-a45e-4ea7-ae82-52bef644a2c4_103444846"]}, {"text": "The Prajna Ayurveda formulas are based on four essential herbs.", "citations": ["2b3d1f11-a45e-4ea7-ae82-52bef644a2c4_103444846"]}, {"text": "Chamomile, known for its calming properties, is one of many herbs with a safe and long-standing medical history and is used for remedies against tiredness and cold and flu symptoms.", "citations": ["ad2986b6-7563-4f28-8a26-aa55569c414f_272149114"]}, {"text": "Knowledge transfer and expert exchanges occurred at the 25th International Ayurveda Symposium in Birstein involving the European Academy for Ayurveda.", "citations": ["e0db411f-d7f9-4ebc-8ae7-aeedae92cce3_222050536"]}, {"text": "Current research investigates how culinary herbs and spices, common in Indian medicine, can modulate the gut microbiome.", "citations": ["dafa9da5-38cf-4c0c-8b4f-09b814ce1c2e_365620837"]}, {"text": "Jain, with extensive experience in urban life, stresses that happiness and mental wellbeing should be addressed alongside physical health.", "citations": ["ca1d01b3-eef6-4c60-92af-594cea61cd59_675032225"]}, {"text": "He notes that while Western medicine is vital for acute care, there are traditional practices in India that have shown success, such as reversing diabetes, and should be more openly considered.", "citations": ["2b3d1f11-a45e-4ea7-ae82-52bef644a2c4_103444846"]}, {"text": "The Happiness Centre is designed to foster mental harmony by integrating contact with nature, herbs, and traditional knowledge.", "citations": ["ca1d01b3-eef6-4c60-92af-594cea61cd59_675032225"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1047", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Oceans cover most of our planet and play a crucial role in sustaining life on Earth.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}, {"text": "Climate change and fossil fuel use are causing ocean acidification, affecting both marine ecosystems and human communities.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}, {"text": "Ocean acidification and increased carbon dioxide are damaging coral reefs, which are home to a huge variety of fish species and protect coastal areas.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}, {"text": "More than 80 percent of living corals are affected, and fish populations around degraded reefs have dropped dramatically.", "citations": ["a8f2946f-727f-4a7c-952d-22a94801e636_904417068"]}, {"text": "Aside from coral bleaching, harmful algal blooms and expanding ocean \u201cdead zones\u201d now threaten marine life and can contaminate drinking water.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "The number of dead zones, areas where marine life cannot survive due to low oxygen, increased to about 900 by 2019.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}, {"text": "Phytoplankton, tiny organisms at the base of the ocean food chain, absorb carbon dioxide but are also at risk from changing ocean chemistry.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "Cephalopods, marine mammals, bivalves, and many other species are sensitive to these chemical changes, which threaten their growth and survival.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "Recent experiments show that kelp, when farmed, can help reduce acidity in the water and benefit bivalves like oysters and clams.", "citations": ["af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060"]}, {"text": "Indigenous groups and conservationists are planting kelp to help heal polluted waters, remove carbon and nitrogen, and create healthier habitats.", "citations": ["c024df85-6885-448a-ae9d-e9d231319c98_521833846"]}, {"text": "International science missions are working to better understand how aerosols and phytoplankton interact with climate and weather patterns.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "Protecting oceans includes community outreach, reducing plastic waste, and participating in coastal cleanups to prevent further harm.", "citations": ["a8f2946f-727f-4a7c-952d-22a94801e636_904417068"]}, {"text": "Projects like forest conservation also help by absorbing CO2 before it reaches the oceans, easing the effects of acidification.", "citations": ["434546d9-4567-4d42-ac75-341decac6254_30626304"]}, {"text": "Monitoring and restoring marine species and habitats requires coordinated effort, such as training more certified divers and increasing local conservation actions.", "citations": ["a8f2946f-727f-4a7c-952d-22a94801e636_904417068"]}, {"text": "Ocean acidification is a growing issue with wide-ranging impacts on marine ecosystems, food security, and climate stability for everyone on Earth.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1053", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Global demand for avocados has surged, with sales increasing over 25% in the past year and record consumption reported in places like New Zealand, where more than 80 million avocados were sold last season.", "citations": ["16a00b71-6e6c-4015-b1b2-d5437d613bb8_463765569"]}, {"text": "The United States remains the largest importer, sourcing about 83% of its avocados from Michoac\u00e1n, Mexico, and brands like Avocados from Mexico have become dominant in the U.S. market.", "citations": ["0322ac10-0b65-44dd-bfea-28394f226eb7_167385622"]}, {"text": "The popularity of the Hass avocado, originally a chance discovery, has been central to the fruit's rise as the world\u2019s most common variety, especially since its nationwide adoption in the 1970s.", "citations": ["d4cf71aa-8523-4555-bbbd-50f6ad116aa8_793168503"]}, {"text": "Strong demand has led to supply shortages and rising prices, making avocados an almost luxury item, though price fluctuations also affect growers with sometimes bargain-basement returns.", "citations": ["16a00b71-6e6c-4015-b1b2-d5437d613bb8_463765569"]}, {"text": "Mexico's avocado sector, vital for local economies, faces challenges from organized crime groups drawn to the industry\u2019s profitability, prompting additional security measures to protect U.S. inspectors after temporary import bans.", "citations": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532"]}, {"text": "In Kenya, avocados have emerged as a top export, empowering some farmers and increasing domestic prices, but only 38% of the country\u2019s production potential is currently being exploited.", "citations": ["8e0f97c5-48f7-4229-bcbb-68237075e78b_180091580"]}, {"text": "Sustainable farming practices and explaining value chains to farmers are seen as crucial for ensuring that economic benefits from avocados genuinely improve local livelihoods.", "citations": ["08243776-6209-4f58-bf9b-6eba959ce05f_94533784"]}, {"text": "Bans or disruptions in international supply chains can quickly impact both export markets and local prices, indicating how intertwined global and domestic markets have become.", "citations": ["8e0f97c5-48f7-4229-bcbb-68237075e78b_180091580"]}, {"text": "Major restaurants and chains are seeking to diversify sourcing amid concerns over availability and price volatility.", "citations": ["0322ac10-0b65-44dd-bfea-28394f226eb7_167385622"]}, {"text": "Despite rising economic opportunities, avocado production in places like Mexico is projected to fall, and growers in various countries have faced tough years amidst fluctuating prices and market uncertainties.", "citations": ["114d1622-c9c5-4614-b132-9c9189790987_442554566"]}, {"text": "The environmental pressures associated with avocado farming, such as deforestation and water use, remain ongoing concerns as global demand continues to grow.", "citations": ["16a00b71-6e6c-4015-b1b2-d5437d613bb8_463765569"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1055", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Fish oil is the fat extracted from fish tissue and is a source of omega-3 fatty acids EPA and DHA, which are important for heart health and cognitive function.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "If people do not regularly consume enough fatty fish, fish oil supplements can help meet omega-3 requirements, but it is important these supplements are tested for heavy metals such as mercury to avoid health risks.", "citations": ["3182f50b-5ca2-4c5a-b67f-fb7d793b213b_790782815"]}, {"text": "Farmed salmon are often fed fish and vegetable oils, but the latter lack the vital omega-3 fatty acids found in seafood, reducing the omega-3 content in the final product.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "Astaxanthin is an additive that gives salmon their pink color and acts as an antioxidant with potential health benefits.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Feed acidifiers are also used in salmon feed to improve gut health and feed efficiency; the feed acidifiers market is forecasted to grow significantly.", "citations": ["f5d0e854-eb55-4d44-ab24-b5048804780e_793015685"]}, {"text": "While the use of antioxidants like TBHQ in farmed salmon feed is approved in countries such as the United States, their presence raises food safety considerations among some consumers.", "citations": ["9a8f5226-915a-45aa-b628-1c206c6bb61d_694540388"]}, {"text": "The European Union recently gave approval for the methane-reducing feed additive Bovaer, which is primarily targeted at cows, and is not currently widespread in salmon farming.", "citations": ["19a72dbf-3566-40b4-ae9b-f102cbfc2f92_400224801"]}, {"text": "Regulations governing additives in salmon feed differ by region, with the European Union and United States enforcing safety standards on approved additives and restricting or monitoring levels of substances like heavy metals and certain preservatives.", "citations": ["3182f50b-5ca2-4c5a-b67f-fb7d793b213b_790782815"]}, {"text": "Supplementation is a common strategy for consumers to ensure sufficient nutrient intake, though label verification for purity and safety is recommended.", "citations": ["3182f50b-5ca2-4c5a-b67f-fb7d793b213b_790782815"]}, {"text": "Premium farmed salmon may not always provide more omega-3 than value brands, due to differences in feed composition.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "Salmon is also a source of selenium and phosphorus, nutrients important for overall health.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "The growing demand for sources of omega-3, such as krill oil, highlights the emphasis placed on these nutrients in both aquaculture and consumer health markets.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1065", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Here is your requested summary of the provided extracts, rewritten into a coherent report with one sentence per line, within 2000 characters:\n\nLabubu, a character and collectible plush toy created by Hong Kong designer Kasing Lung and marketed by Chinese toy company Pop Mart, has become a viral sensation among teenagers and young adults.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}, {"text": "The popularity of Labubu figurines has contributed to a surge in global revenue for Pop Mart, significantly increasing the wealth of the company\u2019s founder.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}, {"text": "Fans are often seen lining up to buy these collectible toys, and celebrities such as Rihanna have been spotted with Labubu, adding to its appeal.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}, {"text": "The trend has gained significant traction on platforms like TikTok, where users create and share videos featuring Labubu, often highlighting unboxing experiences, collection showcases, and creative storytelling.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}, {"text": "The appeal of Labubu is attributed to its unique and whimsical design, evoking nostalgia, individuality, and a sense of belonging to a wider community of collectors.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}, {"text": "Limited edition releases and blind box purchasing formats create excitement and exclusivity, encouraging fans to purchase multiple figurines in hopes of completing their collections.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}, {"text": "Social media algorithms amplify viral content about Labubu, helping the trend spread rapidly across global markets.", "citations": ["f26b8167-9480-44d1-9c98-f5d00de6d2ee_710972358"]}, {"text": "This phenomenon reflects a broader movement towards collectible culture and designer toys, with Labubu becoming a symbol of self-expression and social connection among Gen Z and Millennial consumers.", "citations": ["f26b8167-9480-44d1-9c98-f5d00de6d2ee_710972358"]}, {"text": "The \u201cLabubu Phenomenon\u201d has prompted parents and educators to take note of shifting youth interests and the influence of digital communities on consumer behavior.", "citations": ["f26b8167-9480-44d1-9c98-f5d00de6d2ee_710972358"]}, {"text": "As Pop Mart continues to expand internationally, the Labubu brand exemplifies how creative design, strategic marketing, and social media synergy can drive a product to global prominence.", "citations": ["93c1ca5f-5db0-47b1-941f-0bc438c7f4b0_16982591"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1067", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Robotic animal dolls, though unconventional, have been embraced as companion pets by individuals like Diana Wise and Carol Brown.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Wise established the \u201cShare the Love\u201d Helen Espinoza Memorial Fund to support bringing robotic pets to seniors.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Joy for All offers lifelike robotic pets that can be muted as needed, allowing users to control noise levels.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Providing these robotic pets gives recipients something comforting to hold and care for.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Through partnerships with organizations like WACOG, donations of robotic puppies and kittens have been made to seniors.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Some users crate their robotic pets at night, mirroring real pet routines for comfort and familiarity.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Diana Wise feels personally connected and believes her mother would be proud of this initiative.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Robotic pets have also helped individuals like Cathy\u2019s husband cope with pet loss and loneliness.", "citations": ["86a5cace-32cc-4d47-84d0-f7cc4c349c73_788487252"]}, {"text": "They may offer emotional comfort and help alleviate the pain of losing loved ones.", "citations": ["86a5cace-32cc-4d47-84d0-f7cc4c349c73_788487252"]}, {"text": "Many seniors lack nearby family or friends, as noted by Charlotte Mather-Taylor of the Area Agency on Aging of Broward County.", "citations": ["86a5cace-32cc-4d47-84d0-f7cc4c349c73_788487252"]}, {"text": "Rosemary Mullarkey was among the first 300 people to receive a robotic pet.", "citations": ["86a5cace-32cc-4d47-84d0-f7cc4c349c73_788487252"]}, {"text": "Agencies now seek grants to cover the $89 monthly fee per person for these robotic companions after initial funding ends.", "citations": ["86a5cace-32cc-4d47-84d0-f7cc4c349c73_788487252"]}, {"text": "Conversational AI companions, such as ElliQ, greet users daily and ask how they feel, potentially reducing isolation.", "citations": ["d1d4726c-6f01-4b2d-b52c-0fc4f631de1e_501256233"]}, {"text": "Greg Olsen from the New York State Office for the Aging notes that the future of such technology is already here.", "citations": ["8d3cfa15-2f2c-4024-b792-0a8eb09c20cc_478295722"]}, {"text": "In 2017, the U.S. recognized the role of technology in older adults' care but admitted it cannot replace human interaction.", "citations": ["8d3cfa15-2f2c-4024-b792-0a8eb09c20cc_478295722"]}, {"text": "For some, naming and caring for robotic pets offers routine, a sense of purpose, and satisfaction.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Events like CES 2024 have showcased advancements in AI, mobility, and pet technology.", "citations": ["683d920a-717e-458d-997b-97c42fa52075_217671007"]}, {"text": "AI companions provide emotional support via chatbot capabilities, marking a new era of technological companionship.", "citations": ["d1d4726c-6f01-4b2d-b52c-0fc4f631de1e_501256233"]}, {"text": "While robotic and AI technology helps lessen loneliness, it is not a perfect solution for emotional or social needs.", "citations": ["1f64ec71-b884-4f7d-bf83-86fa509e92a2_291318248"]}, {"text": "Domestic robots carry out household tasks but are increasingly used for education, entertainment, and elderly assistance.", "citations": ["29d7ca89-34f0-4714-9823-b40934a865be_32797163"]}, {"text": "Advancements in AI, augmented and virtual reality are still emerging, especially in healthcare settings.", "citations": ["89ef05a3-83f8-4d9d-8ea9-48d7d59af826_180431731"]}, {"text": "Although technology can help address isolation, experts emphasize it is no substitute for meaningful human connection.", "citations": ["8d3cfa15-2f2c-4024-b792-0a8eb09c20cc_478295722"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1069", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Brad Fitzpatrick started LiveJournal in 1999 as a journaling application he built for himself while in high school, which he soon transformed into a website that allowed others to keep personal journals online.", "citations": ["8ebe97ab-0b2e-49bb-bbc6-3d61dd79ad37_908936567"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal quickly became popular because it enabled users to not only post journal entries but also connect with a network of friends, comment on each other\u2019s posts, and control who could see their content by using privacy settings that were more advanced than other blogging platforms at the time.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "A unique feature of LiveJournal was the \u201cfriends list,\u201d which let users keep track of other people\u2019s updates, and the \u201ccommunities,\u201d where users with shared interests could post and interact.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "Users could filter who saw their posts, either sharing them publicly, with selected friends, or keeping entries private, a flexibility that attracted many who valued controlling their online identities and interactions.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "This friend-based network led to tight-knit online communities, artistic expression, and collaborative storytelling, setting LiveJournal apart from other early blogging and social media platforms that focused mostly on public broadcasting.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "At its peak, in early 2005, LiveJournal had more than 2.5 million active accounts and played a pivotal role in shaping the early online culture and internet communities for the English-speaking world.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "However, over time, competition from newer blogging sites and social networks like Facebook, MySpace, and Tumblr drew users away, as these platforms offered more modern interfaces, new features, and larger audiences.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal's sale to Six Apart in 2005, and later to the Russian company SUP Media in 2007, led to changes in management and site policies that some users disliked, causing further loss of trust and community members.", "citations": ["d15a580b-3ee1-42a5-be38-0d60db9d1280_1046851966"]}, {"text": "As a result, with changing internet trends and stiff competition, LiveJournal\u2019s popularity declined, and most of the English-speaking world stopped using the site, though it retained a significant user base in Russia.", "citations": ["a71441b9-1697-4835-bf00-89a049c53616_150539943"]}, {"text": "Despite its decline, LiveJournal\u2019s legacy lives on in the interactive and community-based features that have become standard on many modern blogging and social media platforms.", "citations": ["8ebe97ab-0b2e-49bb-bbc6-3d61dd79ad37_908936567"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1075", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Voice cloning technology uses artificial intelligence, specifically artificial neural networks, to generate highly realistic speech in multiple languages and accents, sometimes requiring only a three-second sample clip.", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427"]}, {"text": "These AI systems, such as those developed by ElevenLabs, can accurately mimic public figures\u2019 voices, making it possible for someone like former US President Donald Trump to \"speak\" flawless Hindi or other languages.", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427"]}, {"text": "Voice cloning applications are wide-ranging, supporting uses in entertainment (such as creating deepfake songs with artists like Drake and The Weeknd), language learning (Loora AI tutors users in English and helps refine accents in interactive sessions), and global communication (as with China Media Group\u2019s AI-dubbed documentaries).", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427"]}, {"text": "AI-driven technology also enables advertising companies to create and monetize deepfake virtual characters using cloned faces and voices from a growing pool of volunteers.", "citations": ["ed0e0ccd-fad8-4211-be2e-11f7d99b17a0_405519036"]}, {"text": "These AI tools continuously improve over time and handle cultural and linguistic nuances, enhancing worldwide dialogue and human-computer interaction (HCI), especially through advanced natural language processing (NLP).", "citations": ["2e68c907-f8fc-4a5a-bcd2-8026341b8437_243153369"]}, {"text": "However, as AI voice cloning becomes more accessible, serious concerns about privacy, data security, and potential misuse arise, such as the risk of AI-generated scams, extortion, or election fraud.", "citations": ["41bd9456-8f03-4f9c-a982-cce5ce02311e_150565513"]}, {"text": "The ability to steal votes or extort money by mimicking voices is a new threat highlighted by law enforcement, with AI fraud now possible with minimal voice samples.", "citations": ["41bd9456-8f03-4f9c-a982-cce5ce02311e_150565513"]}, {"text": "Legal and ethical debates intensify as developers use large, often unstructured, datasets without clear consent, as seen in instances where actors\u2019 voices are imitated without permission, raising questions about intellectual property and personal rights.", "citations": ["41bd9456-8f03-4f9c-a982-cce5ce02311e_150565513"]}, {"text": "UNESCO and other organizations call for regulations for generative AI in sensitive scenes such as schools, emphasizing the risks for young and unprepared learners.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_829150911"]}, {"text": "Voice AI\u2019s rapid progress brings both opportunities for language learners and accessibility, and urgent challenges around consent, authenticity, and regulation.", "citations": ["8f3f12ad-a7a4-450a-b410-09e5a5d380da_495855107"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1077", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "President Javier Milei of Argentina has introduced sweeping reforms through an Emergency Decree and an extensive omnibus bill titled \"Foundations and Starting Points for the Freedom of the Argentine People\" sent to Congress shortly after taking office.", "citations": ["de62bbf7-5a19-4522-a025-9cc9f72e3f03_277776986"]}, {"text": "Milei openly regards the state and career politicians as adversaries, positioning himself as both a controversial figure and a symbol of hope in Argentina's complex political and economic landscape.", "citations": ["42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_948388057"]}, {"text": "Central to his libertarian agenda is an aggressive austerity plan, featuring drastic budget cuts, tax increases, and a push to achieve a fiscal surplus in the administration's first year.", "citations": ["f07189c5-e66f-4350-b753-b6364c16813a_91241603"]}, {"text": "Milei has signaled a commitment to abolishing the central bank and dollarizing the economy, though critics question whether Argentina has sufficient US dollars for such a transition.", "citations": ["36a995ad-394b-45c9-b960-f32df7845ec0_490038837"]}, {"text": "While expressing skepticism about climate change politics, Milei has stated that there will be no diplomatic break with major trading partners China and Brazil, and signaled that Brazilian President Lula would be welcomed if he visited.", "citations": ["4b67c948-7841-4206-b5b8-acbb37d68ba2_104775091"]}, {"text": "The austerity plan's severe measures are expected to cause widespread social pain, which may test both the resilience of Milei's government and public tolerance, especially as poverty, protests, and social unrest rise.", "citations": ["f07189c5-e66f-4350-b753-b6364c16813a_91241603"]}, {"text": "Labor unions, long influential in Argentine society, have responded with massive strikes to protest Milei's moves to shrink the central government and overhaul the economy.", "citations": ["474c6eec-ebe5-4196-bca0-46e92bb6f014_959262116"]}, {"text": "Austerity policies have also provoked pushback from feminist organizations, who highlight growing poverty, worsening food insecurity, and a spate of violence against women and LGBTIQ people under the new administration.", "citations": ["6370ff20-0aef-4c5f-9655-68810eca5ff3_778249682"]}, {"text": "Milei asserts that his reforms mark the end of Argentina's \"model of decadence\" and promises to avoid dictatorship.", "citations": ["36a995ad-394b-45c9-b960-f32df7845ec0_490038837"]}, {"text": "His administration contends that deep cuts and structural changes are essential to restore economic stability, even as they spark significant discord across Argentine society.", "citations": ["42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_948388057"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1079", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Jane Goodall, world-famous for her research with chimpanzees, now focuses on the human condition and the role everyone plays in conservation.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "Roots & Shoots, her youth program, emphasizes that every individual has a role to play in making a difference.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "She believes it is critical for people to understand that their individual actions matter for the future of the planet.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "Goodall emphasizes the urgent need to act to address the ongoing environmental crisis we have created.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "She reminds everyone that it is up to each person to choose the kind of impact they have on the world.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "Humans are part of the ecosystem and depend on the interrelated mix of animal and plant species.", "citations": ["1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734"]}, {"text": "Goodall encourages young people not to lose hope in the face of environmental challenges, saying that there is still a window of time to act.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "She is aware that young people today are surrounded by \u201cdoom and gloom\u201d but stresses the importance of hope and positive action.", "citations": ["f684acbb-658a-47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399"]}, {"text": "She believes the best way to change minds is through empathy and connection, not by overwhelming people with unwanted facts.", "citations": ["f684acbb-658a-47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399"]}, {"text": "Goodall creates understanding by appealing to people's compassion and personal values rather than confrontation.", "citations": ["f684acbb-658a-47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399"]}, {"text": "She stresses that true change comes from within and that individuals become champions for the environment through commitment.", "citations": ["f684acbb-658a-47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399"]}, {"text": "When addressing climate change denial, she notes that some acknowledge it but dismiss its seriousness or cause.", "citations": ["7c73f556-2cc5-4294-a058-528b88e7f39d_241321095"]}, {"text": "She wants future stewards of the ocean and environment to fall in love with and care for nature.", "citations": ["772f79c9-c542-4652-8079-b78e4bdfe43c_89387719"]}, {"text": "Goodall values creative ways to teach about ecosystems, such as \u201cdry dives\u201d to reveal hidden aspects of the natural world.", "citations": ["772f79c9-c542-4652-8079-b78e4bdfe43c_89387719"]}, {"text": "She sees teaching as one of her gifts for inspiring action on conservation.", "citations": ["772f79c9-c542-4652-8079-b78e4bdfe43c_89387719"]}, {"text": "Projects like community-based water quality monitoring connect students and volunteers to environmental stewardship.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "Collaboration in such projects helps students develop problem-solving skills and a deeper connection to ecosystems like the Chesapeake Bay.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "By actively using new tools and sharing their work publicly, students are inspired to take meaningful action.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "Goodall\u2019s approach continues to raise awareness, hoping more individuals and communities are motivated to participate in conservation.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1081", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Researchers at the University of Bristol have achieved a dramatic speedup\u2014a billion times faster than previous methods\u2014in simulating optical quantum computers.", "citations": ["898194cf-8289-4b9d-9d88-4579c4c2fbf7_53534682"]}, {"text": "There are significant intermediate milestones in the quest to build useful quantum computing devices, with potential applications in clean energy and healthcare.", "citations": ["898194cf-8289-4b9d-9d88-4579c4c2fbf7_53534682"]}, {"text": "Progress includes advances in atom trapping using lasers as optical tweezers, simplifying research systems through tools like DDS (Direct Digital Synthesis), and employing flexible equipment such as Spectrum AWG cards, which are now popular in quantum research for their analog performance and speed.", "citations": ["e43ad7f5-2dce-4f60-9b70-8690d322fcc2_518507734"]}, {"text": "DDS is a widely used technique for signal generation and has become an essential tool for researchers, enabling rapid progress in labs.", "citations": ["e43ad7f5-2dce-4f60-9b70-8690d322fcc2_518507734"]}, {"text": "Studies have shown that classical computers can sometimes match or even surpass quantum computers for certain tasks, as seen in results from New York University supported by major research grants.", "citations": ["8fe2fa3f-708b-40ce-b0c3-b798decf5a8b_254961000"]}, {"text": "Recent innovations combine quantum computing with generative AI to advance drug discovery, underscoring the broad potential of the field.", "citations": ["4047ad5d-bb0e-457d-ad56-6f4dab40520a_38938283"]}, {"text": "IBM\u2019s quantum initiatives are affecting demand in industrial markets, demonstrating continued corporate investment.", "citations": ["9158c003-9dc2-4633-9d8e-fb420ba363bb_151236669"]}, {"text": "Intel has developed new Tunnel Falls chips to advance silicon spin qubit research; these qubits are up to one million times smaller than other qubit types, potentially leading to greater scalability.", "citations": ["549e6513-f49a-47e3-ae9e-725f8356418b_342083110"]}, {"text": "Young scientists in the EU continue to innovate, such as competing with quantum and classical algorithms for machine learning and AI applications.", "citations": ["02937896-53e7-4cfe-9dca-1b391fb4e359_243860904"]}, {"text": "Efforts to increase diversity in STEM, particularly through programs like the EU Contest for Young Scientists (EUCYS), highlight the need for more opportunities and platforms for young researchers.", "citations": ["02937896-53e7-4cfe-9dca-1b391fb4e359_243860904"]}, {"text": "Breakthroughs also include new methods for integrating quantum dots with metasurfaces for enhanced luminescence, pointing to continued materials innovation.", "citations": ["8f861074-fbc5-4c05-8bf5-031446863109_419270055"]}, {"text": "Material science research, such as work at the University of Tennessee focused on scaling up quantum computers, is a major area of international focus, with new centers and fellowships supporting advancements.", "citations": ["eca2d750-e178-4514-ad24-6a81da1d6ccf_374091781"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1083", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Dr. Bataille said the high degree of mobility may have been part of the mammoth\u2019s mating strategy.", "citations": ["13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_453229130"]}, {"text": "As a juvenile it moved regularly in a north-south pattern, during a time when it was likely part of a herd, the researchers said.", "citations": ["13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_453229130"]}, {"text": "\u201cThat would be an ideal set-up for intercepting a really big ticket meal item like a mammoth,\u201d he said, suggesting that mammoths could have been sought after by hunters.", "citations": ["13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_453229130"]}, {"text": "The specimen was dated to between 22,000 and 39,500 years old, living toward the end of the time of the cave bears, who are thought to have gone extinct 24,000 years ago.", "citations": ["074b2976-a44d-4f0e-a2e7-dbdf8e0f8b07_764530440"]}, {"text": "They could be found across Europe and Asia, including in the UK.", "citations": ["074b2976-a44d-4f0e-a2e7-dbdf8e0f8b07_764530440"]}, {"text": "Some of these animals at the site were actually potentially declining, indicating a reduction in populations.", "citations": ["4548d75b-8c6f-4f51-9d25-488c637fab22_100579483"]}, {"text": "Following up on that study, another showed that Earth is now hotter than its been in at least 120,000 years, seeming to settle a major conflict over climate models in favor of \"Yeah, it really is that bad.\"", "citations": ["16ef0ebe-3b9a-4ea7-ab19-de0b70702637_331702616"]}, {"text": "This suggests that climate warming has occurred since the time of the mammoth, impacting their habitat.", "citations": ["13ea93b3-b90a-433c-83f5-d01dbdf2cf08_453229130"]}, {"text": "The Late Cretaceous was the next warm period and global temperatures reached 24\u00b0C by 80 Ma, which is a little colder than the last glacial maximum, so the animals that survived the blast got hit with the cold.", "citations": ["eff9988f-d296-45b2-8991-616959ff31cd_540787137"]}, {"text": "Extinctions were mostly due to higher temperatures, but this is unclear, according to McInerney and Wing.", "citations": ["eff9988f-d296-45b2-8991-616959ff31cd_540787137"]}, {"text": "The primary focus of conservation efforts needs to be on the prevention of species loss, not on de-extinction.", "citations": ["0a81051f-2d25-4a93-9ec6-b902eb792647_997407507"]}, {"text": "Western science is slowly coming to the same conclusion, helped in part by the exceptionally low water levels of the past two years.", "citations": ["4548d75b-8c6f-4f51-9d25-488c637fab22_100579483"]}, {"text": "Some of the more productive sites are also known by collectors, who remove the artifacts before researchers can document them.", "citations": ["4548d75b-8c6f-4f51-9d25-488c637fab22_100579483"]}, {"text": "Natural selection and genetic drift also played a role in species extinctions.", "citations": ["c1e6db3c-0326-4e04-a106-0a4c7aad96bb_386798691"]}, {"text": "Modern science has not yet analyzed DNA from the most recent Wrangel Island mammoths.", "citations": ["c1e6db3c-0326-4e04-a106-0a4c7aad96bb_386798691"]}, {"text": "De-extinction, if it is ever possible, will not be simple.", "citations": ["0a81051f-2d25-4a93-9ec6-b902eb792647_997407507"]}, {"text": "The study implies that both environmental changes and human hunting pressures contributed to the extinction of the mammoth.", "citations": ["eff9988f-d296-45b2-8991-616959ff31cd_540787137"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1085", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "AEX Gold aims to invest in Greenland through a new gold mining project, focusing on asset growth and value creation.", "citations": ["4ae7f149-1ea4-4da8-9d73-8f0641b266ca_887720299"]}, {"text": "CEO Eldur Olafsson states they have a five-year plan to start production at Nalunaq and use profits to fund wider exploration.", "citations": ["4ae7f149-1ea4-4da8-9d73-8f0641b266ca_887720299"]}, {"text": "Many deposits have been found in the region, though developing them remains a challenge.", "citations": ["4ae7f149-1ea4-4da8-9d73-8f0641b266ca_887720299"]}, {"text": "LKAB, Sweden\u2019s state-owned mining company, found over 1 million tonnes of rare earth metals in northern Lapland.", "citations": ["be0e1159-bd31-403e-acf1-b495b0455519_773343369"]}, {"text": "LKAB views this discovery as a potential \u201csignificant building block\u201d for Europe\u2019s supply chain problems, but extraction may take at least a decade.", "citations": ["be0e1159-bd31-403e-acf1-b495b0455519_773343369"]}, {"text": "Rare earth minerals, a group of 17 elements including scandium, yttrium, and lanthanides, pose environmental concerns due to potential radioactive materials in their ores such as thorium and uranium.", "citations": ["be0e1159-bd31-403e-acf1-b495b0455519_773343369"]}, {"text": "The new Swedish find is considered significant for Western consumers, especially as the global supply is dominated by China, which has utilized its rare earth resources as a geopolitical instrument.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "While rare earths are not actually rare, mining and refining them is complex and can generate hazardous waste.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "Although the U.S. once led rare earth production, it now trails behind, with Brazil and Vietnam also holding significant but largely untapped reserves.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "Australia is investing in a rare earths mine and processing plant, aiming to reduce dependence on China.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "Rare earths have critical uses in technology like iPhone displays, electric vehicles, and wind turbines, key to the clean energy transition.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "Europe welcomed LKAB\u2019s discovery amid energy insecurity and its goal to become climate neutral by 2050.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "E.U.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "officials have highlighted China\u2019s near-monopoly and rising rare earth prices as a geopolitical challenge.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "Sweden's Deputy Prime Minister said European independence from Russian and Chinese supply will begin with local mining.", "citations": ["11f28cac-793c-4f5c-b370-7e1a5a11fae4_52895041"]}, {"text": "Greenland\u2019s ice sheet meltwater contains sand with valuable mineral content, seen as increasingly valuable in the future.", "citations": ["02e0cc0e-6a99-4de7-92b7-45909fe1b7f5_1034133963"]}, {"text": "Demand and price for sand could rise sharply by 2100, potentially making extraction from Greenland more economically viable.", "citations": ["02e0cc0e-6a99-4de7-92b7-45909fe1b7f5_1034133963"]}, {"text": "Norway has also discovered substantial minerals and metals resources on its seabed.", "citations": ["79f73441-31e2-4a33-b672-5f84b4a0d9db_255527108"]}, {"text": "Globally, over 3 billion tons of minerals and metals will be needed for future clean energy infrastructure.", "citations": ["7f4725c2-f800-469c-af5c-c9b11977154e_560688234"]}, {"text": "China has imposed restrictions and considered export bans in reaction to geopolitical tensions, highlighting supply risks.", "citations": ["6d272cdc-f7ad-4c0d-a4c4-6fd55599eb35_204429244"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1087", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "India and Russia signed a program of cooperation to boost trade and joint investment projects in Russia's Far East during Modi-Putin talks on Tuesday.", "citations": ["792e3539-8d3e-404d-925f-2d2e14af8105_958547503"]}, {"text": "Russia and India are working together to implement the idea of a 'Greater Eurasian Space.'", "citations": ["792e3539-8d3e-404d-925f-2d2e14af8105_958547503"]}, {"text": "Meanwhile, India\u2019s strategic partnership with the U.S. has remained steady overall, though its refusal to condemn Russia\u2019s invasion of Ukraine and increased energy trade with Moscow after Western sanctions have strained ties with Washington.", "citations": ["6afc284d-bc28-459a-9b12-4474f635e88f_70179025"]}, {"text": "The India-U.S. partnership has experienced other stress points in recent years.", "citations": ["6afc284d-bc28-459a-9b12-4474f635e88f_70179025"]}, {"text": "India\u2019s close relationship with both the Quad and BRICS has strategic significance.", "citations": ["6afc284d-bc28-459a-9b12-4474f635e88f_70179025"]}, {"text": "India and Russia rely on each other beyond diplomacy, with mutual trust at the core of their engagement.", "citations": ["9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430"]}, {"text": "Prime Minister Modi and President Putin did not meet at major summits such as BRICS in Johannesburg or the G20 in New Delhi, as Putin was absent from both events.", "citations": ["9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430"]}, {"text": "Putin has described Modi\u2019s policy as the main guarantor for developing bilateral ties, and Russia respects India's strategic autonomy.", "citations": ["9796598e-e5cd-4b19-8665-f50cecfea01d_371231430"]}, {"text": "Modi\u2019s high-profile Russia visit, even at the risk of U.S. displeasure, shows India's commitment to pursuing its own foreign policy agenda.", "citations": ["a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382"]}, {"text": "Historical India\u2013Russia relations, dating to the Cold War, have expanded further since Russia\u2019s war in Ukraine, especially in energy trade, with India as a major buyer of Russian oil.", "citations": ["a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382"]}, {"text": "Modi is seeking to reinforce ties with Russia partly to counter Chinese advances in the region.", "citations": ["a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382"]}, {"text": "Ajit Doval\u2019s high-stakes visits to Russia and the U.S. underscore India\u2019s balancing act between rival superpowers.", "citations": ["aa25bf63-902a-4c8a-9f40-2197785a048e_44334882"]}, {"text": "India has emphasized enhancing cooperation with Russia in trade, energy, and defense.", "citations": ["aa25bf63-902a-4c8a-9f40-2197785a048e_44334882"]}, {"text": "India\u2019s stance of non-alignment and deft diplomacy following Russia\u2019s invasion of Ukraine has placed it in a strategic \u201cgeopolitical sweet spot.\u201d  \nIndia is seen by the Global South as a voice highlighting the war\u2019s impact on developing nations, though its growing potential is often discussed more than its current stature.", "citations": ["44dc0a24-30a1-4d4d-b53c-3d665b1e6164_215958292"]}, {"text": "Under Modi, India is less constrained by fears of displeasing Moscow or Beijing and exercises greater freedom in foreign policy.", "citations": ["a8edad1b-d157-466a-9ba5-057e6b4399d9_841501382"]}, {"text": "China\u2019s rise continues to drive closer India-U.S. ties, even as India looks to strengthen maritime security and consolidate its Indo-Pacific presence with Russia.", "citations": ["aa25bf63-902a-4c8a-9f40-2197785a048e_44334882"]}, {"text": "China remains a key factor as India and Russia discuss regional security, even if not mentioned directly in joint statements.", "citations": ["feee8f8c-96fd-4000-a30c-d587af7a839e_36543815"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1002", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Geoffrey Hinton, often called the \u201cGodfather of AI,\u201d resigned from Google in 2023 to speak more freely about his growing concerns regarding artificial intelligence.", "citations": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079"]}, {"text": "Hinton has been worried about the potential of AI to do harm and he often talks about the existential threat that AI might pose to the human species.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "He has used OpenAI\u2019s ChatGPT and this has made him uneasy.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "Dr Hinton told the BBC: \"Right now, they\u2019re not more intelligent than us, as far as I can tell.", "citations": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079"]}, {"text": "But I think they soon may be.\"", "citations": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079"]}, {"text": "Hinton\u2019s unease intensified as AI systems rapidly improved and began demonstrating abilities like simple reasoning that he had thought were years away.", "citations": ["0b0a6638-7cfb-483c-bf6d-bc4b844b884a_253543854"]}, {"text": "He has raised alarms that AI could one day surpass human intelligence and, combined with its ability to manipulate information, create convincing fake realities or even become uncontrollable.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "Hinton worries that productivity gains from AI could lead to mass unemployment and widen the gap between rich and poor, possibly increasing social unrest and violence.", "citations": ["f51eec6d-22b3-4ed2-95e9-d127cda3300b_321145537"]}, {"text": "After hundreds of industry and science leaders warned that \u201cmitigating the risk of extinction from AI should be a global priority alongside other societal-scale risks such as pandemics and nuclear war,\u201d the U.N. Secretary-General recently echoed their concern.", "citations": ["99b06f2f-6f17-498d-82f9-5c50811e3477_211656408"]}, {"text": "Some of Hinton\u2019s peers, like Yann LeCun, argue that intelligence does not equate to a desire for domination; AI systems are not alive and may not want anything at all.", "citations": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_296881079"]}, {"text": "However, others, like Yoshua Bengio and DeepMind CEO Demis Hassabis, support calls for careful development; Hassabis claims AI could match human intelligence within five to ten years.", "citations": ["0b0a6638-7cfb-483c-bf6d-bc4b844b884a_253543854"]}, {"text": "Experts note that we do not know how to design AI systems that reliably behave exactly as we intend them to, and biases in how AI depicts professions show the technology\u2019s flaws.", "citations": ["14190bf2-5114-4846-bdc2-bca381772686_999456816"]}, {"text": "The rapid progress of AI development has prompted calls for government regulations, industry \u201cpauses,\u201d and efforts to ensure fairness and safety.", "citations": ["beaaba1c-d058-4db5-bac2-c02fb4c0de39_677251007"]}, {"text": "The Biden White House has expressed concern about tech sector AI being released without adequate safeguards.", "citations": ["abd90351-b865-4002-b72d-7c84d3f6fa6c_702017578"]}, {"text": "Agencies in the UK and US are moving to address AI\u2019s risks, while the European Union is working to protect responsible advances.", "citations": ["beaaba1c-d058-4db5-bac2-c02fb4c0de39_677251007"]}, {"text": "Hinton\u2019s warnings have brought global attention to the urgent need for oversight and careful management of AI\u2019s power and risks.", "citations": ["99b06f2f-6f17-498d-82f9-5c50811e3477_211656408"]}, {"text": "The public should understand that while AI offers great promise, its rapid evolution brings unpredictable challenges that require vigilance, ethics, and regulation to avoid harm.", "citations": ["ecdf4a88-257b-447c-97d4-af3263c416a5_302105403"]}, {"text": "Alex Carp, CEO of Palantir, states that only companies without AI products want to pause development.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "He argues that the AI race has started, and the main question is whether to maintain the lead or fall behind.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "Carp emphasizes that slowing down AI progress will not halt the competition.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "Multiple experts have signed an open letter warning about potential societal risks from AI.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "It\u2019s noted that none of the most innovative AI firms are headquartered in the UK.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "There is ongoing work on a voluntary code for AI regulation that could be drafted in weeks.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "Mass protests against AI are predicted in the future as more people lose jobs to automation, potentially resulting in millions unemployed.", "citations": ["16928c84-8ff1-4e7d-b095-8a1e3650e3d6_507234292"]}, {"text": "The White House has announced it will study the risks posed by artificial intelligence.", "citations": ["35481bf2-4a24-4244-8e44-aa5765ce15f7_674948774"]}, {"text": "Geoffrey Hinton, described as the \"spiritual father\" or \"godfather\" of AI, publicly acknowledges the dangers of the technology.", "citations": ["7aaf3d3c-e64b-4611-b8e8-93c6d88622b5_362908194"]}, {"text": "Hinton raised concerns that a bad actor, like Putin, could enable robots to develop independent sub-goals, such as increasing their own power.", "citations": ["0307d215-8853-482c-b377-d9200f6e962a_543190127"]}, {"text": "Hinton points out that chatbots can amass and share far more knowledge than any individual human.", "citations": ["0307d215-8853-482c-b377-d9200f6e962a_543190127"]}, {"text": "Artificial intelligence has been compared in risk to global pandemics and nuclear war.", "citations": ["ee1953df-2cca-4349-b2aa-7687c38d2071_135782380"]}, {"text": "Such warnings about AI dangers are not unprecedented.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Key AI threats cited include the possibility of AI systems developing unanticipated goals and displaying deceptive behaviors.", "citations": ["ee1953df-2cca-4349-b2aa-7687c38d2071_135782380"]}, {"text": "Companies\u2019 arguments for rapid AI development have resonated across sectors.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Notable signatories to warnings about AI risk include Hinton and OpenAI\u2019s CEO Sam Altman.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Both had previously discussed AI\u2019s dangers before making these recent statements.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Hinton likens AI learning to a process where knowledge acquired by one becomes accessible to thousands.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Regulatory frameworks are being called for to ensure AI develops safely.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Currently, these regulatory proposals remain in draft form without legal enforcement.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "China\u2019s approach to AI regulation is markedly different from that in Western countries.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "There is a growing chorus of experts raising concerns about the trajectory of AI.", "citations": ["a2940351-61e9-4f55-9118-295514128d46_641158369"]}, {"text": "Microsoft and Google are heavily investing in AI-producing companies.", "citations": ["ae7a3750-139e-4f47-a1c3-a9ff04521b1e_809747170"]}, {"text": "Google, once seen as a leader in AI, saw a pivotal moment with the launch of ChatGPT.", "citations": ["ae7a3750-139e-4f47-a1c3-a9ff04521b1e_809747170"]}, {"text": "Geoffrey Hinton left Google in 2023 and has since outlined his growing apprehension about the technology in interviews.", "citations": ["ae7a3750-139e-4f47-a1c3-a9ff04521b1e_809747170"]}, {"text": "These developments demonstrate both AI\u2019s tremendous value and its potential to shape the future.", "citations": ["ae7a3750-139e-4f47-a1c3-a9ff04521b1e_809747170"]}, {"text": "Some observers believe the fundamental problem is not AI rebelling but the risk of algorithms deceiving humans.", "citations": ["712c45f5-19bf-472f-a358-9de488c9a4b6_1018370605"]}, {"text": "For example, Google\u2019s LaMDA impressed even knowledgeable engineers with its realistic answers, despite not being built to impersonate humans.", "citations": ["712c45f5-19bf-472f-a358-9de488c9a4b6_1018370605"]}, {"text": "Experts suggest the Turing Test is no longer an effective benchmark for advanced AI models.", "citations": ["712c45f5-19bf-472f-a358-9de488c9a4b6_1018370605"]}, {"text": "Now, some AIs are so sophisticated they appear to have their own will, raising new societal concerns.", "citations": ["712c45f5-19bf-472f-a358-9de488c9a4b6_1018370605"]}, {"text": "Training these models requires massive data and computational resources.", "citations": ["712c45f5-19bf-472f-a358-9de488c9a4b6_1018370605"]}, {"text": "Modern AI aims to produce results as human-like as possible, making oversight vital.", "citations": ["712c45f5-19bf-472f-a358-9de488c9a4b6_1018370605"]}, {"text": "ChatGPT\u2019s ease of use enables people without technical expertise to write essays and code.", "citations": ["908cbc7a-a6c4-482f-a8d9-e882e7b36a14_762450658"]}, {"text": "There is a consensus that AI technologies are transforming society and require strict management.", "citations": ["908cbc7a-a6c4-482f-a8d9-e882e7b36a14_762450658"]}, {"text": "OpenAI was formed with the goal of developing beneficial AI that does not harm humanity.", "citations": ["908cbc7a-a6c4-482f-a8d9-e882e7b36a14_762450658"]}, {"text": "The influence of OpenAI is regarded as similar in scale to the impact of Microsoft in the broader IT sector.", "citations": ["908cbc7a-a6c4-482f-a8d9-e882e7b36a14_762450658"]}, {"text": "Geoffrey Hinton, often called the \"godfather of artificial intelligence,\" announced his resignation from Google in 2023, expressing regret over his role in advancing AI technology.", "citations": ["042ce256-aaa2-4944-8725-7deb68b8b43f_125182681"]}, {"text": "Hinton's groundbreaking work on deep learning and neural networks paved the way for modern AI systems such as ChatGPT.", "citations": ["a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134"]}, {"text": "He worked part-time at Google for a decade, contributing to the company's AI development efforts.", "citations": ["d0bcd28d-1ef5-4a5a-9dc4-fc842c33ad73_883812304"]}, {"text": "In a statement to the New York Times and later interviews, Hinton explained that he left partly due to his age\u2014he is 75\u2014but also due to rising concerns about AI's potential dangers.", "citations": ["a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134"]}, {"text": "He emphasized he did not want to criticize Google, which he described as \"very responsible,\" but feared how AI could be misused or become uncontrollable.", "citations": ["a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134"]}, {"text": "Hinton fears that AI could become smarter than humans and worries developers may not be sufficiently focused on how to prevent it from gaining too much control.", "citations": ["9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653"]}, {"text": "He cautioned that before AI becomes more intelligent than humans, research should focus on understanding how it could attempt to manipulate or control people.", "citations": ["9f2305a4-5741-4eef-9e53-fd05af571cdf_241409653"]}, {"text": "At present, Hinton believes AI tools like GPT-4 have more general knowledge than any individual, though humans still surpass them in real creative thinking.", "citations": ["a8c7f219-9432-4551-9378-a113dfbbae07_297203134"]}, {"text": "He noted that both positive and negative uses of AI are possible, and the same technology that enables \"bad AI\" could also help combat its misuse.", "citations": ["73578dea-46ff-4ea8-bef0-411024d49f39_27873992"]}, {"text": "Hinton also pointed out that AI, like humans, can be biased based on the data it is trained on.", "citations": ["73578dea-46ff-4ea8-bef0-411024d49f39_27873992"]}, {"text": "He raised concerns that rapid advances in AI could lead to jobs disappearing but also acknowledged new jobs will be created as a result.", "citations": ["47120e3f-95ae-4a83-9c70-69d4b9024a90_677032321"]}, {"text": "Some experts and committees have echoed Hinton\u2019s warnings, emphasizing the need for greater transparency and regulation of AI, such as making source code available for oversight.", "citations": ["e51371a3-998b-41a5-b422-776df320f0b4_171512511"]}, {"text": "Others assert that AI is the most important tool for serving humanity's interests and that its ultimate impact is not yet fully understood.", "citations": ["c5cef6d0-53f1-4994-b0d5-98541532d068_394921676"]}, {"text": "There are also concerns from governments about AI\u2019s potential to accelerate cyber-attacks and other threats that might be hard to detect or defend against.", "citations": ["47120e3f-95ae-4a83-9c70-69d4b9024a90_677032321"]}, {"text": "Hinton observed that continued AI development could worsen inequality if wealth generated by AI goes only to the rich, resulting in a \"very bad society.\"", "citations": ["eb2b1c5a-6402-4fc8-98d3-a91481c6902d_20427601"]}, {"text": "He stated that as AI becomes cheaper and more powerful, \"AI for all\" could be realized, but emphasized that without checks, misuse could occur.", "citations": ["73578dea-46ff-4ea8-bef0-411024d49f39_27873992"]}, {"text": "Hinton said his consolation is that if he hadn't advanced AI, someone else would have, reflecting on the inevitability of the technology's evolution.", "citations": ["792ba802-fc52-4ca2-bb1a-ee90ce0fe3de_704363760"]}, {"text": "Public discussion continues around the future of jobs, the risks and benefits of AI, and the need for responsible management as these systems grow more advanced.", "citations": ["73578dea-46ff-4ea8-bef0-411024d49f39_27873992"]}, {"text": "Geoffrey Hinton is a pioneer in artificial intelligence, known for his foundational work on neural networks and deep learning, which underpin current AI systems like ChatGPT and Google\u2019s Bard chatbot.", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_496813334"]}, {"text": "Dr. Hinton worked for Google for 10 years, contributing to software that mimics abstract human thinking using code as a connection between artificial neurons.", "citations": ["d2deb389-3761-4e46-82f2-9b4e753196d5_416878875"]}, {"text": "He explained that humans cannot simply transfer knowledge directly, but AI learning can be rapidly shared and improved, making AI systems capable of surpassing human intelligence in the future.", "citations": ["28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678"]}, {"text": "Hinton expressed both praise and concern for Google, stating he left the company in 2023 so he could speak openly about AI\u2019s potential risks without harming Google\u2019s reputation.", "citations": ["28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678"]}, {"text": "He warned in interviews with Reuters, the BBC, and The New York Times that AI could pose a more urgent threat than climate change if not properly controlled, and highlighted the growing risk of AI-generated misinformation flooding the Internet so convincingly that the average person cannot tell what is real.", "citations": ["d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942"]}, {"text": "Hinton believes that competition among tech giants is contributing to the hurried release of AI technologies, potentially endangering jobs and enabling the spread of dangerous content.", "citations": ["d0d53bd7-a835-4e68-9f88-55c12fd01693_76481654"]}, {"text": "He noted the rapid progress of AI has even outstripped his own expectations, and said, \u201cLook at how it looked five years ago and now, the difference and growth, it\u2019s really scary.\u201d\n\nDespite believing AI may pose an existential threat to humanity, Hinton does not support suspending AI research, arguing its benefits and application value cannot be erased.", "citations": ["d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942"]}, {"text": "Hinton stresses the importance of instilling fair values in AI to avoid machines that could harm humanity, using the metaphor of the \u201ccurtain of ignorance\u201d to describe how neutrality could encourage fairness.", "citations": ["28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678"]}, {"text": "He tries to \u201cblow the whistle\u201d on AI risks, hoping people will take them seriously and work on ways to prevent systems from taking control.", "citations": ["3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684"]}, {"text": "Other tech leaders, including Elon Musk and Steve Wozniak, have called for a pause in the development of advanced AI systems due to profound risks to society, though Hinton did not sign the petition advocating a six-month halt.", "citations": ["3afb956b-40d5-4ecb-8918-2675d6b68006_521301684"]}, {"text": "In response, governments such as the US and the European Union have begun considering regulations to address AI risks, with the EU proposing the world\u2019s first comprehensive AI regulation bill.", "citations": ["28a083d6-e397-4b10-96c8-683ddd70ae01_452338678"]}, {"text": "A Google spokesperson stated that the company remains committed to taking a responsible approach to AI, emphasizing its history as an early publisher of AI principles.", "citations": ["e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513"]}, {"text": "Hinton also discussed his belief that AI needs accelerated development of solutions and input, rather than a pause.", "citations": ["abd90351-b865-4002-b72d-7c84d3f6fa6c_433457856"]}, {"text": "He is worried about misuse of AI by bad actors, stating it\u2019s difficult to see how bad people could be prevented from doing harm with these technologies.", "citations": ["e1466ebf-84b4-41ed-8497-d39fc984abd1_839419513"]}, {"text": "Hinton\u2019s warnings have made headlines because they come from one of AI\u2019s most respected founders, igniting global debate over how AI advances should be handled to protect society.", "citations": ["d490c53b-a3c0-4442-9a80-1a11110c988f_899870942"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1004", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle is growing, with places like Athens seeing an estimated 2,000 remote workers in a single month, according to Nomad List.", "citations": ["2ce1675b-59e5-4a2d-a835-5a8677dd0cd5_534458820"]}, {"text": "Countries such as Croatia attract thousands of digital nomads but have restrictive rules, such as requiring nomads to leave for six months after a year-long visa expires before reapplying.", "citations": ["c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462"]}, {"text": "The purpose of most digital nomad visas is not to allow permanent residence, and in Croatia, it is not legally possible to extend such visas or convert them into tourist permits for a longer stay.", "citations": ["c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462"]}, {"text": "If digital nomads overstay or try to stay longer, they become classified as immigrants.", "citations": ["c529ac8d-80af-410a-a327-3546b54a14c8_242137462"]}, {"text": "Some locals feel that digital nomads drive up housing costs and do not integrate well into communities, but nomads are encouraged to give back, for example, by volunteering or helping locals.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "Remote work allows digital nomads to live and work in different places, experiencing local life beyond being a tourist.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "Norway offers an independent contractor visa for digital nomads, which is valid for up to two years per period with a six-year maximum; applicants must show contracts as proof of work.", "citations": ["ecf3362e-b403-4224-b08a-f302d3e88373_435843940"]}, {"text": "Those who choose this lifestyle often do not report to a physical office or keep fixed schedules and can also study and work while traveling.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Effective time management and discipline, such as maintaining set routines and having reliable technology and noise-canceling headphones, are vital to prevent burnout.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "It is recommended to choose flexible remote work that aligns with personal interests and values, and self-directed job searches are common.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Germany provides several visa options for digital nomads, though residency registration and tax payments may be required, especially in places like Baden-Baden, which offer good infrastructure and healthcare.", "citations": ["ecf3362e-b403-4224-b08a-f302d3e88373_435843940"]}, {"text": "Visa policies supporting digital nomads have been increasing globally, particularly to attract IT and digital professionals who can prove a sufficient income, with the Asia Pacific region joining this trend.", "citations": ["f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041"]}, {"text": "To qualify for many of these programs, applicants must be able to show work in a digital field and meet a minimum annual income, such as $24,000 USD.", "citations": ["f9238697-72e5-45a4-88bd-8504c4016eba_427630041"]}, {"text": "Digital nomadism has shifted the perception of working life, with more seeking flexibility, global experiences, and sometimes early retirement.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Despite the apparent glamour portrayed on social media, the lifestyle involves careful planning, adaptation to legal constraints, managing potential local backlash, and ensuring personal well-being.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves living in different places for relatively short periods, with many nomads residing in one location for an average of 70 days.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "Rather than buying property, most digital nomads prefer to rent housing, and there has been a significant increase in demand for rentals by Russian IT professionals in places like Thailand over the past two years.", "citations": ["38cf69bf-6946-4ac0-a7fb-ea5b106d22b5_430479613"]}, {"text": "Nomads often earn income remotely from their home country and spend it abroad, resulting in potential tax issues and concerns of 'human capital' loss for their countries of origin.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "Some economists suggest maintaining a 13% income tax rate for such workers to preserve their capital within the home country.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "This trend has been amplified by the outflow of IT personnel from Russia due to political events, though about 85% reportedly returned by mid-2022.", "citations": ["cf58e6c6-c3e8-485d-b30a-70689cba1777_149442504"]}, {"text": "Remote work is strongly favored among Russian IT professionals, many of whom would readily resign if required to return to office-based work.", "citations": ["7b742b0d-15ee-4b7b-bf98-a83a747cc62f_394368227"]}, {"text": "Remote work is appreciated for enabling workers to save on commuting costs and for making it possible to live anywhere, even outside Russia, though not all companies support this.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "People who worked in foreign-owned companies sometimes lost their jobs when those companies withdrew, prompting a rise in freelancers and self-employed, encouraged by state policies.", "citations": ["e9fff66d-bee2-41b1-bdea-13cc907fcb0e_792339023"]}, {"text": "Experts point out that Russia lacks enough training opportunities to meet the demand for upskilling self-employed and remote workers.", "citations": ["cc1df2e2-8056-4eff-9668-3ef90cc37915_165460898"]}, {"text": "Relationships between employers and remote workers are changing, with professional loyalty and management practices becoming more important.", "citations": ["7b742b0d-15ee-4b7b-bf98-a83a747cc62f_394368227"]}, {"text": "Some Russian-founded companies operate abroad and hire remotely for positions in IT, marketing, and other fields, sometimes supporting candidates with relocation.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "Types of work especially suited to the nomad lifestyle include software development, iOS and backend development, and app marketing management.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "Countries that support digital nomads include Mexico and all 12 South American countries, which currently allow Russians to visit visa-free, making them attractive destinations.", "citations": ["cf58e6c6-c3e8-485d-b30a-70689cba1777_149442504"]}, {"text": "Challenges for digital nomads often include job insecurity, adapting to new work systems, the difficulty of launching foreign startups without significant capital, and questions over national loyalty and tax residency.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "Overall, while the digital nomad lifestyle offers freedom and economic benefits, it poses risks related to job stability, taxation, upskilling, and integration into new cultures.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "Useful tools for this lifestyle typically include remote work platforms, freelance job boards, communication apps, and relocation support services.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "Russia has experienced a significant brain drain in the IT sector, with more than 100,000 digital specialists leaving the country due to economic decline and sanctions-related movement restrictions.", "citations": ["3dad3eb9-5168-47c0-9466-661a32aa7662_531567834"]}, {"text": "Those who have left often settle in countries such as Turkey, Georgia, Armenia, the UAE, and the Central Asian region, allowing them to continue remote work and receive payments.", "citations": ["3dad3eb9-5168-47c0-9466-661a32aa7662_531567834"]}, {"text": "Popular digital nomad destinations in Europe include places like Bansko in Bulgaria, which attract remote professionals seeking vibrant communities and better quality of life.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "Many digital nomads initially worked for large companies but shifted to independent freelance work once they realized the freedom remote work could provide, enabling travel across countries like Russia and the USA.", "citations": ["fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379"]}, {"text": "It is important for digital nomads to communicate that they are not on vacation, as remote work requires dedication and time management while traveling.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "Co-working and co-living spaces have become a central part of the digital nomad lifestyle, with some entrepreneurs aiming to create community-owned workspaces.", "citations": ["fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379"]}, {"text": "Understanding the motivation for establishing shared workspaces is crucial for those looking to build similar environments.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "The trend of remote work expanded significantly after the Coronavirus pandemic, with governments progressively accepting digital nomads as pioneers rather than dropouts.", "citations": ["fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379"]}, {"text": "Some governments, like Algeria\u2019s, have implemented favorable conditions allowing digital service exporters and freelancers to benefit from their full earnings and work internationally.", "citations": ["89fdf7ff-3b6b-4585-958f-4339473b8a6d_985493493"]}, {"text": "Salaries and the cost of living for digital nomads can vary greatly from country to country, and tools such as salary calculators help assess potential earnings abroad.", "citations": ["ebab0f53-84d3-493d-b518-3c9aef084e83_419430032"]}, {"text": "Portugal stands out as a digital nomad destination due to progressive labor laws, including prohibiting employers at larger companies from contacting employees after working hours, with substantial fines for violations.", "citations": ["b30f6e18-320f-40e7-9d82-a852d8151cba_29302288"]}, {"text": "Remote work and the digital nomad lifestyle are increasingly seen as game changers, and countries like Portugal actively seek to attract nomads and remote workers.", "citations": ["b30f6e18-320f-40e7-9d82-a852d8151cba_29302288"]}, {"text": "Countries like the UAE and Israel also support remote work, with companies opening new branches and employing specialists internationally.", "citations": ["b30f6e18-320f-40e7-9d82-a852d8151cba_29302288"]}, {"text": "A surge of Russian professionals in Dubai has pushed up rent and living costs, causing some expats to consider relocating elsewhere or returning to Russia, though the UAE remains attractive to many.", "citations": ["7ea23f8e-14da-44e6-bc7d-9521501c2d40_752368766"]}, {"text": "Freelance platforms and government initiatives in some countries, such as training grants, assist young professionals in adapting to remote and freelance work.", "citations": ["e02ee547-ef66-4a3b-9bad-8af65fdadfb1_503806613"]}, {"text": "In summary, while the digital nomad lifestyle offers flexibility, travel opportunities, and the potential for higher earnings, it also presents challenges such as isolation, the need for strong self-discipline, navigating local regulations, and fluctuations in cost of living and job security.", "citations": ["ebab0f53-84d3-493d-b518-3c9aef084e83_419430032"]}, {"text": "She was a digital nomad for almost two years but found it too stressful and stopped.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "Now, she adopts a \u201cSlow Digital Nomad\u201d approach, staying at least a month in one place or as long as her visa allows.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "She currently has a \u201cheadquarters\u201d in Montenegro but still travels every month and maintains a home base.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "Using the correct debit card is important due to high overseas bank fees, which sometimes cost her $30-$40 per cash withdrawal.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "She had to call her bank frequently, highlighting the headaches of managing money on the move.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "She emphasizes the need to thoroughly research living and working costs ahead of traveling to a new place.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "Unexpected expenses, such as up to $20 per day extra in London, can add up quickly, so being smart about budgeting is essential.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "Digital nomads bring their culture and technology when working abroad, impacting local communities.", "citations": ["ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442"]}, {"text": "The rise of digital nomadism is attributed to flexible working arrangements where individuals can sometimes spend time sightseeing or meeting people.", "citations": ["eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186"]}, {"text": "Kristie, a digital nomad, says the lifestyle helped her simplify her life and start anew.", "citations": ["f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267"]}, {"text": "She was inspired by families traveling the world together and meeting diverse people, leading her to experience multiple \u201clives\u201d along the way.", "citations": ["f2d39679-7714-4818-8520-3a94256d29a9_256892267"]}, {"text": "The COVID-19 pandemic led to a greater demand for IT talent and accelerated the normalization of remote work globally.", "citations": ["15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219"]}, {"text": "There is little guidance on how to strategically build a remote career, though it is an attractive path, especially for women in tech.", "citations": ["eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186"]}, {"text": "Young people must develop both soft and hard skills to adapt to this evolving work landscape.", "citations": ["eb9bb425-89ea-45e2-9b52-ed2a0f921fe9_132088186"]}, {"text": "Japan is introducing a new visa for digital nomads, responding to increased remote work since the onset of COVID-19.", "citations": ["15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219"]}, {"text": "Digital nomads are defined as people who use the internet to work remotely, support themselves financially, and move freely without geographic constraints.", "citations": ["15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219"]}, {"text": "Countries such as Japan and Spain have introduced Digital Nomad Visas to attract high-skilled foreign workers and stimulate local economies.", "citations": ["09cbaa0c-5e42-4814-a1a1-3e28d939b1c4_202321090"]}, {"text": "Spain\u2019s digital nomad visa requires proof of income and residence, is initially valid for one year, renewable up to five years, and allows close family members to join.", "citations": ["d687297a-7db2-44f7-aecb-450e2bc50213_217010740"]}, {"text": "Many digital nomad visa holders in Spain prefer rural areas with lower rent due to comprehensive 4G coverage.", "citations": ["d687297a-7db2-44f7-aecb-450e2bc50213_217010740"]}, {"text": "A total of 15 European countries now have similar digital nomad visa programs.", "citations": ["d687297a-7db2-44f7-aecb-450e2bc50213_217010740"]}, {"text": "Adapting to the digital nomad lifestyle often requires learning to use new tools, including AI, for work and personal productivity.", "citations": ["b2358f49-b2b6-4f53-8eaa-b4945451baed_525191053"]}, {"text": "Design and creative jobs, along with IT and tech roles, are particularly suited to remote, location-independent work enabled by these tools and skills.", "citations": ["15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1006", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves working away from home and living in another place.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "To succeed as a digital nomad, it is important to understand what the lifestyle will be like and prepare for the changes it brings.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Time management is crucial for avoiding burnout and achieving daily goals.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Productivity can be challenged by distractions from local activities when traveling, so having reliable work essentials is key.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "These essentials include a good laptop with appropriate software, noise-canceling headphones, a WiFi hotspot, a portable wireless mouse, and long-lasting earbuds.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "The Microsoft Surface 4 Pro is highlighted as an ideal travel laptop.", "citations": ["23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909"]}, {"text": "Backpacks with laptop compartments and built-in charging ports are also recommended for convenience.", "citations": ["23980c8b-8970-4b9b-96ce-6f690a62ec45_787468909"]}, {"text": "Choosing remote work that matches your interests or studies can help make the lifestyle sustainable.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Some nomads find work independently, reflecting the flexibility of this life.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "It is also necessary to create a budget for travel and living expenses, invest in remote work equipment, and research visa requirements.", "citations": ["07d9d65d-d81d-41ca-a816-eb0878fc0b2d_436034532"]}, {"text": "Certain countries now offer special digital nomad visas to attract remote workers, providing legal routes to stay and work there.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Balanced work and leisure time is important to make the most out of each location.", "citations": ["90884408-0e81-4e82-b05c-6d5e3880f722_235045315"]}, {"text": "Destinations like Itacar\u00e9 in Bahia offer favorable climates and infrastructures suitable for remote work.", "citations": ["d812d020-b4d6-4b3b-a420-9f195bdf4ac4_35559448"]}, {"text": "Some digital nomads maximize their travel by house-sitting or seeking scholarships to reduce costs while learning new skills.", "citations": ["c7b767c9-09fd-43c7-83f7-b07f61e38ae6_818229618"]}, {"text": "Minimalist packing helps stretch every earning further, with some nomads living on limited wardrobes and prioritizing travel on a budget.", "citations": ["563a878d-ecb0-49fe-8fdd-3710bf8326b5_61386701"]}, {"text": "The pandemic shifted perspectives on what defines work and where it occurs, with many valuing flexibility over traditional office roles.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Employers increasingly recognize the advantages of remote workers who contribute from anywhere in the world.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Confidence and openness are required to integrate locally, while social media can sometimes hinder real-life interactions.", "citations": ["d5133b55-9937-4199-a715-4f1b3a0ed928_861729327"]}, {"text": "The importance of values, freedom to choose locations, and a mindset of continual adaptation are central to the digital nomad experience.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "Work life is evolving, focusing more on a person\u2019s contribution than physical presence, and the last two years highlighted the potential for lasting change.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Embracing digital nomadism can mean taking risks, pursuing passions, and blending work with broader life experiences.", "citations": ["4acd88c5-7d2b-4157-a17b-8edb9d9769ad_4928390"]}, {"text": "The digital nomad lifestyle involves individuals choosing to live in different locations for an average of 70 days, often renting instead of owning homes and migrating to warmer climates for winter.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "This group is primarily composed of digital workers who can work remotely from anywhere with a laptop and internet connection, such as homes, libraries, and cafes.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "Some digital nomads focus their projects around specific interests, such as food, and their numbers are increasing in places like Russia.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "In countries lacking dedicated digital nomad visas, these individuals often rely on tourist or student visas, with local authorities sometimes overlooking this practice.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "The lifestyle offers a unique opportunity to blend work with leisure, but prompts questions about who will remain to contribute to their home countries.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "Despite the appeal, people are often still bound to their place of residence due to personal circumstances.", "citations": ["72836102-23df-4f82-b338-56a356464891_682732748"]}, {"text": "Remote work and the digital nomad lifestyle make it possible to earn money from anywhere, with emerging \u201cdigital nomad\u201d visas facilitating legal stays for remote workers.", "citations": ["2859f8ca-8608-4fca-9f8c-a999cd159cc8_459273502"]}, {"text": "Japan is planning to introduce such a visa, which would allow remote work in the country for up to six months, subject to certain eligibility and income requirements, with implementation expected soon.", "citations": ["2859f8ca-8608-4fca-9f8c-a999cd159cc8_459273502"]}, {"text": "Kazakhstan's labor market faces challenges like unsatisfactory workforce quality and insufficient job creation, with large numbers of graduates working outside their specialties or being unemployed.", "citations": ["3cf67053-e2ac-4755-9988-9204edac5d6d_943181"]}, {"text": "Quality education and collaboration between schools and technical education are seen as keys to greater labor productivity and employment, including for people with disabilities.", "citations": ["3cf67053-e2ac-4755-9988-9204edac5d6d_943181"]}, {"text": "Ratings for users and customers are used to assess performance, with many digital nomads acting as speakers or organizers to spread awareness of technology.", "citations": ["997d5424-bf51-4cc8-b41c-9375c62d6653_126551212"]}, {"text": "Job roles in digital industries can be demanding, often increasing workload and requiring adaptation, but also offer valuable life experience.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "Company digital transformation is ongoing, with large companies more equipped to support remote work and digitalize processes than small businesses, who face greater challenges.", "citations": ["b54ed508-bcca-4c98-ad80-12ff0f8d6adb_148083272"]}, {"text": "Solutions like Kyivstar\u2019s \u201cOffice is where you are\u201d help configure business processes for remote work from any device, supported by big data and analytics for tasks like identifying optimal business locations.", "citations": ["b54ed508-bcca-4c98-ad80-12ff0f8d6adb_148083272"]}, {"text": "Governments are also adopting digital solutions, using data analytics and smart city technologies to manage public services and population mobility.", "citations": ["b54ed508-bcca-4c98-ad80-12ff0f8d6adb_148083272"]}, {"text": "Vacancies for IT and marketing specialists are available in international companies, some of which support remote relocation and are open to hiring talent globally, including from Russia and the CIS.", "citations": ["6fcc148a-7fa6-480f-8e58-14c3a8b61344_689414768"]}, {"text": "Governments in many countries are increasingly offering visas that allow people to work there temporarily, welcoming digital nomads as pioneers of a new lifestyle rather than viewing them as job dropouts.", "citations": ["fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379"]}, {"text": "Digital nomads often see themselves as members of a global community, sharing tips online about the best places to live and work.", "citations": ["fd58cfb9-f01b-4078-86a9-871fc3f6410e_322621379"]}, {"text": "Some of the most popular destinations for digital nomads are in Europe, such as Bansko in the Perrin mountain range, which attracts those who love mountains.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "Many digital nomads prefer this lifestyle because working from home can feel monotonous, and co-working spaces allow them to make friends and join activities like ice skating.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "Bansko\u2019s Co-working began as a hobby for Matthias to work and gather friends, and he now aims to transform it into a co-living place owned by the community.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "He advises people to identify their motivations and then pursue their dream projects.", "citations": ["491e1e95-4ffe-4fe3-b435-06b9fcde7b7e_929014990"]}, {"text": "New regulations protect workers\u2019 downtime, such as laws penalizing managers for contacting employees after work hours, a policy now enforced with significant fines.", "citations": ["b30f6e18-320f-40e7-9d82-a852d8151cba_29302288"]}, {"text": "This shift means remote work can be a dream come true for many, especially with growing legal protections.", "citations": ["4388c5c1-ea03-4b15-ba06-b0ea11c2c227_954944958"]}, {"text": "Companies like Remote Pass have received initial funding from Gulf and international investors, citing increased productivity from remote work during the COVID-19 pandemic.", "citations": ["af29091b-7fe9-4f98-b37e-1ac485466be2_859551698"]}, {"text": "Their funding round has strengthened their confidence and reflects investor trust in the company's mission to innovate in remote work platforms.", "citations": ["af29091b-7fe9-4f98-b37e-1ac485466be2_859551698"]}, {"text": "A global survey reports higher salaries and savings as top benefits of remote work, highlighting how telework has accelerated globalization following the pandemic.", "citations": ["4388c5c1-ea03-4b15-ba06-b0ea11c2c227_954944958"]}, {"text": "Attitudes toward digital nomadism vary, with some controversy over \"begpackers\"\u2014travelers busking or asking for donations to fund travel, especially in regions like Asia.", "citations": ["3840cf4d-f528-41d0-9529-3f06715449bc_527284896"]}, {"text": "Some locals appreciate the effort like playing music, while others view it as entitlement, contrasting affordable lifestyles of hostels and street food with luxury travel.", "citations": ["3840cf4d-f528-41d0-9529-3f06715449bc_527284896"]}, {"text": "The rise of digital tools means today\u2019s remote work options didn\u2019t exist a generation ago, and many parents are unfamiliar with these new tech-based professions.", "citations": ["12a1e0fe-6763-4b29-a802-a9971cbe0790_59292822"]}, {"text": "Digitally excluded people may struggle with rapidly changing technology, facing challenges in basic tasks now managed via apps and online platforms.", "citations": ["12a1e0fe-6763-4b29-a802-a9971cbe0790_59292822"]}, {"text": "However, for those who stay informed, new opportunities for remote work and global living grow each year.", "citations": ["12a1e0fe-6763-4b29-a802-a9971cbe0790_59292822"]}, {"text": "Building capacity for remote and sustainable work involves education, training programs, and developing skills at individual and institutional levels.", "citations": ["d6b1dc76-aa2d-48e9-9a4a-5795d1079cda_853670916"]}, {"text": "Digital platforms have transformed nearly every area of life over the past two decades, reshaping our social and professional interactions.", "citations": ["2542f872-4da2-47b8-ab98-cac8a618dad1_554128677"]}, {"text": "Travel and tourism now support an increasingly open global society, with over 1.8 billion users worldwide and rapid growth.", "citations": ["2542f872-4da2-47b8-ab98-cac8a618dad1_554128677"]}, {"text": "For example, surveys in Saudi Arabia show 83 percent of citizens have recently traveled or plan to travel abroad, reflecting surging global mobility.", "citations": ["2542f872-4da2-47b8-ab98-cac8a618dad1_554128677"]}, {"text": "Digital nomads are remote workers who leverage computers and the internet to work from anywhere in the world.", "citations": ["543f79d1-b4ee-4c44-b5ba-bc0dd95cb878_473601805"]}, {"text": "Their rise has reshaped the tourism industry, making digital travellers catalysts for local economies.", "citations": ["495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_561526741"]}, {"text": "Digital nomads often bring economic benefits and new cultural perspectives to communities, but some critics question whether this movement acts as a form of neo-colonization.", "citations": ["ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442"]}, {"text": "Keith, a digital nomad, emphasizes the importance of considering and positively impacting the communities they live in, while Casey values the freedom and lifestyle and stresses being mindful of one\u2019s local impact.", "citations": ["ea90bb4e-0607-4636-afd5-5e325bcbfef8_77576442"]}, {"text": "Despite the appealing lifestyle, digital nomads face unique challenges such as financial planning, cost of living, and managing technology remotely.", "citations": ["77fe7fbf-41e8-4067-9063-0458ea76d448_158447245"]}, {"text": "Loss of access to the main computer or inadequate digital tools can limit productivity for remote workers.", "citations": ["b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649"]}, {"text": "Remote desktop software, like Splashtop, helps digital nomads securely access files and specialized software on their main computers wherever they travel.", "citations": ["b67cd69f-4c83-4193-99ab-2cc0767b6bfd_37536649"]}, {"text": "Several countries, including Japan, now offer digital nomad visas that allow foreign nationals to live and work remotely for extended periods\u2014Japan\u2019s new visa requires applicants to have an annual income over 10 million yen, be citizens of specific countries, and have private health insurance.", "citations": ["15e8540b-5ba4-4152-9f0a-a15471c6bcb8_847147219"]}, {"text": "Visa rules in Japan allow spouses and children to join, with a maximum stay of six months, and local authorities see this as a way to enhance the city\u2019s global reputation.", "citations": ["b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344"]}, {"text": "Many digital nomads choose to stay in one place for at least a month, sometimes longer if their visa allows, preferring a \u201cslow travel\u201d lifestyle.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "Careful financial planning is essential, as digital nomads often encounter unexpected costs, such as higher daily living expenses in major cities.", "citations": ["77fe7fbf-41e8-4067-9063-0458ea76d448_158447245"]}, {"text": "Using the correct debit card and being savvy about where to cut costs can make a significant financial difference for remote workers.", "citations": ["a3c70681-f2b9-494d-bb98-7de9c98f52da_736721641"]}, {"text": "Investment strategies for digital nomads and younger generations often include funds, ETFs, and real estate for stability and income.", "citations": ["60aa4cb5-342f-4247-8498-89094bcd2d2d_720028489"]}, {"text": "Hotels and businesses are increasingly targeting remote workers, especially millennials and Gen Z, by providing amenities suited to their needs.", "citations": ["543f79d1-b4ee-4c44-b5ba-bc0dd95cb878_473601805"]}, {"text": "What makes the digital nomad lifestyle possible is access to reliable technology and the internet, making virtually any location an office.", "citations": ["77fe7fbf-41e8-4067-9063-0458ea76d448_158447245"]}, {"text": "The sustainability and impact of this lifestyle depend on the policies of local governments and the conscious choices of nomads themselves.", "citations": ["b67b7441-6604-4229-82d6-e410e0419e0b_1051067344"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1008", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "China has been striving to close the technological gap with the US Air Force, especially through upgrades to engines like the WS-10 and WS-15, both featuring low bypass ratios and thrust vector control capabilities.", "citations": ["bbd66630-067c-4256-adc2-97dd5f5878ed_41790305"]}, {"text": "The J-20 fighter, a more advanced Chinese jet, first flew a decade ago and has been in service since 2017, while India\u2019s AMCA stealth project is still under development and yet to take flight or see induction.", "citations": ["bbd66630-067c-4256-adc2-97dd5f5878ed_41790305"]}, {"text": "As China increases its J-20 production, there is interest in its technological advances, such as the potential for Directed Energy Weapons, a feature Indian media speculate will also appear on their future planes.", "citations": ["bbd66630-067c-4256-adc2-97dd5f5878ed_41790305"]}, {"text": "However, questions have been raised in online commentary, especially regarding countries shifting from one fighter program to another before the first is complete, noting that projects like the Indian LCA have not yet seen combat, production, or induction but are still marketed for export.", "citations": ["bbd66630-067c-4256-adc2-97dd5f5878ed_41790305"]}, {"text": "At recent air shows, including Zhuhai, eyewitnesses and Chinese commentary noted that the J-20 demonstrated reliable performance, countering concerns such as the appearance of black smoke attributed to engine startup phases rather than system failures.", "citations": ["4bc40faf-e9dc-4a5d-8c3a-0d2f20ba848d_123806756"]}, {"text": "During the 2023 Dubai Air Show, Hongdu Aircraft Company confirmed that Pakistan is in formal negotiations to purchase light attack aircraft from China, likely to replace its aging F-7PGs.", "citations": ["71100976-5a62-4b13-b449-5fcd327a8fcc_221821377"]}, {"text": "This potential sale to Pakistan aligns with longstanding defense ties between the two countries, and while the exact model was not named, it is widely believed to include J-10C fighters, a more advanced and export-ready fighter than earlier Chinese models.", "citations": ["71100976-5a62-4b13-b449-5fcd327a8fcc_221821377"]}, {"text": "The perceptions of Chinese fighter quality abroad are mixed; some commentators highlight advancements and steady improvement, while others remain skeptical, citing examples of unreliable or less capable equipment among Chinese military exports.", "citations": ["bcb10cf5-a993-47e6-9165-f43f42c766aa_206491725"]}, {"text": "Global media and defense observers note that China\u2019s growing sophistication in fighter jet technology is also reflected in changes to its strategic doctrines and export ambitions, particularly as demonstrated in regional military competition and mock engagements.", "citations": ["bcb10cf5-a993-47e6-9165-f43f42c766aa_206491725"]}, {"text": "China\u2019s export efforts are closely watched, but feedback from buyers is still emerging, with Pakistan seen as the initial and primary client for the J-10, with general enthusiasm about acquisitions but no long-term operational feedback yet available.", "citations": ["ce32c1be-e02a-4d52-bd5f-d35b9737080b_987151109"]}, {"text": "In summary, while China is actively promoting its J-10 and other fighters to foreign customers\u2014with Pakistan as the main buyer so far\u2014international and online commentary remains divided, recognizing notable progress but also raising concerns about operational reliability and the utility of these jets against established Western aircraft.", "citations": ["bbd66630-067c-4256-adc2-97dd5f5878ed_41790305"]}, {"text": "China\u2019s J-10 fighter jet has been developed as an indigenous aircraft by China\u2019s defense industry, aiming to reach the level of leading world powers in combat aviation.", "citations": ["9112a124-a3ec-4a5d-977e-acc581fd2fb9_749042120"]}, {"text": "The J-10 program reflects China\u2019s drive to modernize its air force and reduce dependence on foreign aircraft by creating its own models or copying foreign designs.", "citations": ["3d328988-627e-4b76-928f-f0dfc39d752b_690718323"]}, {"text": "Reports confirm that China has equipped parts of its fleet with Russian engines purchased for half a billion dollars.", "citations": ["e4b92110-9fbd-434c-b539-87860d18695f_699124503"]}, {"text": "The bulk of China\u2019s military aircraft fleet, including the J-10, are produced domestically at Chinese defense enterprises.", "citations": ["3d328988-627e-4b76-928f-f0dfc39d752b_690718323"]}, {"text": "The J-10 has not matched the level of stealth or technological sophistication shown by American fighters like the F-22 Raptor or F-35 Lightning, which remain benchmarks for advanced combat aviation.", "citations": ["3d328988-627e-4b76-928f-f0dfc39d752b_690718323"]}, {"text": "Analysts note that the J-10, while significant, is often overshadowed by China\u2019s J-20 stealth fighter, which experts say is already present in over 10 air brigades of the PLA Air Force.", "citations": ["9112a124-a3ec-4a5d-977e-acc581fd2fb9_749042120"]}, {"text": "China has focused on developing its air power to gain air superiority in potential regional conflicts, particularly sending signals to neighbors like Japan and South Korea concerning its build-up.", "citations": ["3d328988-627e-4b76-928f-f0dfc39d752b_690718323"]}, {"text": "Despite its presence in the Chinese Air Force, there is little evidence to suggest widespread international export success for the J-10.", "citations": ["1f83b715-49f9-4cce-96b2-39d5d02bcb6c_998363221"]}, {"text": "To date, only Pakistan has formally ordered the J-10C, with deliveries reported to have started in early 2022.", "citations": ["9112a124-a3ec-4a5d-977e-acc581fd2fb9_749042120"]}, {"text": "Pakistani officials have commented positively on the J-10C, citing its advanced avionics, maneuverability, and modern weapons as necessary upgrades for their air force.", "citations": ["9112a124-a3ec-4a5d-977e-acc581fd2fb9_749042120"]}, {"text": "The Pakistan Air Force sees the J-10C as a potential counterbalance to rival India\u2019s acquisition of Rafale fighter jets.", "citations": ["1f83b715-49f9-4cce-96b2-39d5d02bcb6c_998363221"]}, {"text": "Commentators in Chinese and international media have described the J-10 as a fourth-generation fighter with strong multirole capabilities but not on par with fifth-generation US aircraft.", "citations": ["4133ea76-a638-4651-b0df-8e84c3f49afc_136204308"]}, {"text": "While some Chinese analysts call China\u2019s new fighter \u201can unpleasant surprise\u201d for Russia, most outside evaluations consider the J-10C a competitive but not revolutionary export product.", "citations": ["4133ea76-a638-4651-b0df-8e84c3f49afc_136204308"]}, {"text": "Overall, the jet has attracted some interest due to its lower cost and modern features, but as of now, no other confirmed exports beyond Pakistan have occurred.", "citations": ["4f1076c8-b82b-4655-b053-adef27a475fd_578002133"]}, {"text": "The J-10\u2019s future in the global market may depend on buyer demand for affordable 4.5-generation fighters and China\u2019s ability to offer flexible sales terms.", "citations": ["1f83b715-49f9-4cce-96b2-39d5d02bcb6c_998363221"]}, {"text": "The Chinese J-10 fighter jet, manufactured by Chengdu Aircraft Industry Group in Sichuan, is considered one of China's most advanced military weapons.", "citations": ["bbe91201-3e58-4275-961f-28aef03d4a46_84860852"]}, {"text": "It made its public debut in November 2016 during the Zhuhai Air Show in Guangdong, China.", "citations": ["bbe91201-3e58-4275-961f-28aef03d4a46_84860852"]}, {"text": "The latest variant, the J-10C, features an electronic radar and an infrared guidance system for missiles.", "citations": ["7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203"]}, {"text": "The jet has a length of 23 meters, a height of 5 meters, a maximum speed of 2,468 kilometers per hour, and a range of 5,926 kilometers, according to Aero Corner.", "citations": ["bbe91201-3e58-4275-961f-28aef03d4a46_84860852"]}, {"text": "The unit cost of the J-10 is calculated to be between $100 million and $120 million.", "citations": ["bbe91201-3e58-4275-961f-28aef03d4a46_84860852"]}, {"text": "China\u2019s military focus on producing such advanced aircraft is connected to rising tensions in regions like the Taiwan Strait and South China Sea, and reflects Beijing\u2019s push to develop its defence system.", "citations": ["d076d361-4769-408c-ba73-6dc8c36241b2_332991478"]}, {"text": "Feedback and direct comments from countries operating or acquiring the J-10, notably Pakistan, have noted it as a viable alternative to Western-sourced fighters, offering advanced capabilities at a more competitive price.", "citations": ["7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755"]}, {"text": "In 2022, Turkish Security Council member Kagri Erhan stated that Ankara may move away from American F-16C/D fighters and could consider alternatives such as the Chinese plane sold to Pakistan, Russian fighters, or the Eurofighter.", "citations": ["7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_115461755"]}, {"text": "The J-10 has therefore enhanced its position as a potential replacement or complement for the F-16 in some markets.", "citations": ["7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203"]}, {"text": "Most J-10 exports to date have been to Pakistan, which has publicly displayed and praised the platform as part of its air force modernization.", "citations": ["24341e0d-dc30-41e2-86f6-b9153d23f19e_438552556"]}, {"text": "Pakistani officials and media have presented the J-10 as evidence of deepening military ties with China, citing advanced avionics and weapons compatibility.", "citations": ["bcff9cfc-75a0-4dd4-9431-7dcedbac8579_21954549"]}, {"text": "The global press and analysts have observed that while the J-10 offers an affordable and capable platform for air forces outside of Western alliances, its success in further export markets remains contingent on performance, support, and geopolitics.", "citations": ["bbe91201-3e58-4275-961f-28aef03d4a46_84860852"]}, {"text": "Media commentators have positioned the J-10 among the most significant non-Western fighters but note ongoing scrutiny over China\u2019s ability to develop and sustain advanced jet engines domestically.", "citations": ["7662ae65-98c5-4a3f-9b24-83a5f9fb7a72_1044319203"]}, {"text": "While the J-10 is not generally rated at the same level as the F-16 or other top-tier Western fighters, it is recognized for narrowing the gap with Western technology and is reportedly in consideration by countries seeking alternatives to US or Russian fighters.", "citations": ["bcff9cfc-75a0-4dd4-9431-7dcedbac8579_21954549"]}, {"text": "The Chengdu J-10 fighter, designed in the 1990s under the \"Destroying Project Plan\" with chief designer Song Wenchong, first flew in 1998 and entered service in 2003.", "citations": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939"]}, {"text": "Following service with other Chinese fighters like the Su-27SK, Su-30MKK, and J-11, the J-10 has formed a high-low mix within China\u2019s air combat capabilities.", "citations": ["a834da70-5664-4631-bba7-dba8ef82cd52_942464069"]}, {"text": "The J-10 has a range of 2,500 kilometers and a payload of 1.9 tons, and multiple modifications have resulted in at least 11 derivative aircraft, making it China\u2019s largest family of derivative jets.", "citations": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939"]}, {"text": "Key features include the ability to track and attack multiple targets simultaneously, comparable to the AN/APG-63(V1) radar of the F-15, and a water drop type cockpit cover for enhanced 360-degree pilot visibility.", "citations": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939"]}, {"text": "Military experts suggest the J-10 is most suitably compared to the American F-16.", "citations": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939"]}, {"text": "Although designed to replace foreign third-generation fighters that China could not import due to technical and economic constraints, the J-10 failed to fully meet some border environment challenges.", "citations": ["15d8999d-2d0f-4e22-a82c-078ab058b6d0_885132091"]}, {"text": "Recent developments include the J-10D prototype, which uses conformal fuel tanks for increased range, and is believed to target Pakistan as a primary export customer.", "citations": ["33dcc7ae-d937-40fa-bb01-606ce45830c3_584534808"]}, {"text": "Pakistan became the first confirmed export customer for the latest J-10CE variant, with its acquisition attracting significant foreign media attention to China's indigenous fourth-generation fighter capabilities.", "citations": ["ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561"]}, {"text": "Pakistan\u2019s J-10CE features advanced elements such as improved radars, color coatings to reduce radar cross-section, and reportedly favorable feedback regarding performance expectations.", "citations": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939"]}, {"text": "China\u2019s \"Military Technology\" magazine and other commentators view the J-10C as the fighter with the greatest export potential in China\u2019s market due to its competitiveness and ongoing improvements.", "citations": ["3e945ab6-3a90-49b4-a584-faa7b598737a_769586939"]}, {"text": "The development of advanced military jet engines, including the turbofan-10C with full authority digital engine control (FADEC) and maximum thrust over 130 kN, has further optimized the J-10 performance.", "citations": ["cf11f5d9-fca6-4093-bf81-ca064ae09f08_16507722"]}, {"text": "Other countries besides Pakistan have not been confirmed as buyers, although the J-10 remains a leading candidate in China\u2019s foreign military sales efforts and is frequently discussed in comparison with Western fighters.", "citations": ["ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561"]}, {"text": "Overall, the J-10 program demonstrates China\u2019s progress in indigenous fighter development, with Pakistan\u2019s acquisition seen as a milestone in its export success but with generally cautious but optimistic commentary in international media about further sales and operational performance.", "citations": ["ff09c670-9bf8-4f5d-b6c2-1b4699af2744_618195561"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1010", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "San Antonians may want to stay indoors next week as a noticeable change in the air arrives to the Alamo City.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "On Monday, little changes will be in the forecast as heavier amounts of Saharan dust remain over the Gulf Coast, but the dust doesn't stop there.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "Residents are advised to keep windows and doors closed to limit indoor dust exposure.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "During the afternoons, the sky may appear a more milky white color due to the dust.", "citations": ["5dc9163b-9ad8-4a82-8d61-269b3aa8f216_79048364"]}, {"text": "Saharan dust from Africa moves across the Atlantic every year from late spring to early fall, reaching the Americas.", "citations": ["847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659"]}, {"text": "The phenomenon can combine with other weather events, such as hurricanes, which in the past delivered up to 70 inches of rain north of the Rio Grande watershed.", "citations": ["3f3d97a9-5753-477f-b92f-e7eb5b3af635_359923960"]}, {"text": "Community leaders express hope that the city and county are preparing for this and future crises.", "citations": ["3f3d97a9-5753-477f-b92f-e7eb5b3af635_359923960"]}, {"text": "Concerns continue as growth in northern Texas brings increased demand for water, and military installations like Camp Bullis rely on aquifers linked to the local water supply.", "citations": ["e2abcea0-fc76-42b4-ae2a-664d84224483_447729836"]}, {"text": "All water sources in the region are interconnected in their relationship to the land.", "citations": ["e2abcea0-fc76-42b4-ae2a-664d84224483_447729836"]}, {"text": "The Desert Southwest experiences seasonal monsoons, attracting storm photographers, though the monsoon failed last year but is active this year.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "These patterns allow for pop-up storms and cause variable moisture flows, as air masses move and weather cycles recycle or lose moisture through evapotranspiration.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "Winter rains and mountain snow are more effective at soaking into the soil, while land use changes loosen topsoil, making dust storms more frequent in strong winds.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "Thunderstorms in the region often have high cloud bases, which can be observed from afar, and temperatures have reached record highs, partly attributed to La Ni\u00f1a and climate change.", "citations": ["5796c588-0e1c-4bfe-9805-1bc54cc26e65_397803440"]}, {"text": "Extreme heat contributes to increased power bills for residents served by CPS Energy.", "citations": ["4755901b-5f20-43d6-bb98-ae62df4aeee0_1026333416"]}, {"text": "Other cities, such as Brampton, face flood risks and changes in environmental policy, while plastic pollution and emissions worsen global warming and impact planning.", "citations": ["47613c50-be86-4a1c-b220-1c435aa61837_789806991"]}, {"text": "Disaster response agencies note that future crises will be unlike past events, and equal outcomes for all require targeted support for vulnerable populations.", "citations": ["3f3d97a9-5753-477f-b92f-e7eb5b3af635_359923960"]}, {"text": "Recent storms in the Great Plains and Midwest have set records for hurricane-force winds, while urban design approaches like \"slow water\" and sponge cities aim to manage water and adapt landscapes to changing conditions.", "citations": ["6e28cd56-93cc-4295-b3c8-828a7d7fda04_579755132"]}, {"text": "Planners are urged to see cities as parts of larger watersheds and incorporate landscape-scale solutions to absorb water and prevent future losses.", "citations": ["90be0790-695c-45e3-b944-a130c20a1991_417506747"]}, {"text": "Such preparations and adaptive planning are essential in the face of Saharan dust and other compounding weather events.", "citations": ["847379b8-aea2-4369-b4fb-37b79f3e9753_449770659"]}, {"text": "Long-lived derecho storms are hurricanes that last at least six hours and form a band of fast-moving thunderstorms that destroy everything in their path.", "citations": ["8d2aca41-a4e3-4ffe-a84e-c6b8efc67971_226554753"]}, {"text": "Parts of Europe have experienced these storms.", "citations": ["8d2aca41-a4e3-4ffe-a84e-c6b8efc67971_226554753"]}, {"text": "A recent dust funnel originated in Maryland, with water tornadoes forming off the state's coast due to wind and ocean surface interaction.", "citations": ["5fea1aae-929d-4fbd-a701-7c408562b4c5_955167107"]}, {"text": "Six people died in El Salvador as a result of heavy rains starting in late May and increasing earlier this week.", "citations": ["40964108-2732-4354-aa7c-ba6275aa54c0_209220542"]}, {"text": "A total of 54 landslides were reported in the country.", "citations": ["40964108-2732-4354-aa7c-ba6275aa54c0_209220542"]}, {"text": "Hail in many urban areas was followed by heavy showers, causing widespread flooding and traffic disruptions.", "citations": ["40964108-2732-4354-aa7c-ba6275aa54c0_209220542"]}, {"text": "A Russian climatologist stated that cyclones will become more destructive, referencing catastrophic storms in southern Russia.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "On November 26-27, the most powerful storm in recorded history struck Crimea.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "This intense cyclone moved from the southwest over the Black Sea, resulting in severe catastrophic events.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "Cyclones are commonly generated at this time of year.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "When a cyclone passes over the sea, it collects moisture as water vapor, which is carried and spun with the cyclone.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "The recent cyclone still needs further investigation to determine the link to global warming, which scientists will analyze using climate models.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "Current mitigation measures against warming have shown little effect, and the goal may not be achieved.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "It is necessary to consider the likelihood of weather anomalies in urban and rural planning.", "citations": ["509fca25-bb9d-46f5-88e9-95638a323183_307281017"]}, {"text": "A severe natural disaster struck Oklahoma on April 28, killing four people, including a child.", "citations": ["2de5ac22-8061-404f-8716-13ceaba74df0_314219570"]}, {"text": "Residents, such as Kelly Trussell, were overwhelmed by the tornado\u2019s destruction and the difficulty in responding.", "citations": ["2de5ac22-8061-404f-8716-13ceaba74df0_314219570"]}, {"text": "Tornadoes require careful preparation in high-risk areas.", "citations": ["2de5ac22-8061-404f-8716-13ceaba74df0_314219570"]}, {"text": "In South Dakota, a unique derecho storm occurred with winds up to 159 km/h, turning the sky green.", "citations": ["cbacd971-1280-4ec8-b3d0-82f70edf1d62_747535751"]}, {"text": "Strong winds are expected along the east coast, with cold air reaching as far south as Texas and Florida.", "citations": ["2d206739-b301-47d6-be7d-781b3ed1841b_297740077"]}, {"text": "Airports in Washington, New York, Chicago, and Denver experienced significant flight cancellations.", "citations": ["85b55ba7-26c9-41e1-97df-36006bab38d5_44707987"]}, {"text": "Flooding becomes a risk on flat terrain due to heightened rainfall, overwhelming sewer systems and causing street flooding.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "Construction is not recommended in low-lying coastal areas or river floodplains.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "Residents need timely warnings about prolonged rainfall and potentially dangerous water levels.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "Cities are increasingly adopting \u201cnatural\u201d stormwater management techniques.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "During immediate danger, sandbags can be used at entry points, drainage pipes disconnected, and sewer valves closed.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "Potential electrical hazards from flooding require prompt shutting off of the electrical system.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "It is crucial to avoid contact with floodwater and, if necessary, to swim to solid ground.", "citations": ["8fb79465-3c23-472f-969e-ecc12407773a_364782789"]}, {"text": "In Samara, Russia, air quality is closely monitored with 200,000 samples analyzed annually for 30+ hazardous substances.", "citations": ["5016171b-a41d-4bf7-a332-1e05e09e518a_589915761"]}, {"text": "Weather stagnation can allow pollutants to accumulate locally, leading to higher measurements.", "citations": ["5016171b-a41d-4bf7-a332-1e05e09e518a_589915761"]}, {"text": "During poor air dispersion, businesses are required to reduce emissions.", "citations": ["5016171b-a41d-4bf7-a332-1e05e09e518a_589915761"]}, {"text": "Unpleasant odors can be perceived even if measured levels remain within accepted standards.", "citations": ["5016171b-a41d-4bf7-a332-1e05e09e518a_589915761"]}, {"text": "Here is a coherent summary of your extracts, each sentence based on a fact from the sources, and all together under 2500 characters:\n\nJuly has been reported as the hottest ever, with the United Nations warning of 'global boiling'.", "citations": ["195c51d3-d4d6-4870-9f10-acec5699eb37_1049283115"]}, {"text": "A heatwave, worsened by global warming, has struck Europe, Asia, and North America alongside extensive wildfires in Canada and southern Europe.", "citations": ["195c51d3-d4d6-4870-9f10-acec5699eb37_1049283115"]}, {"text": "The World Meteorological Organization notes the eight years ending in 2022 are the hottest on record, even accounting for La Ni\u00f1a\u2019s cooling effect.", "citations": ["195c51d3-d4d6-4870-9f10-acec5699eb37_1049283115"]}, {"text": "A more urgent need exists to reduce greenhouse gas emissions.", "citations": ["195c51d3-d4d6-4870-9f10-acec5699eb37_1049283115"]}, {"text": "The governor of Kentucky reported 25 deaths due to floods, and numbers are expected to rise as rescues continue.", "citations": ["22611aa8-3de1-4583-b9e8-3daadb805652_895358825"]}, {"text": "Flood survivors remain unaccounted for, making it difficult to determine the number of missing.", "citations": ["22611aa8-3de1-4583-b9e8-3daadb805652_895358825"]}, {"text": "Floods in the United States are among a series of extreme weather events linked to climate change.", "citations": ["22611aa8-3de1-4583-b9e8-3daadb805652_895358825"]}, {"text": "Forty-six migrants died in an abandoned truck in San Antonio due to heat and drought.", "citations": ["e801e538-67f8-4aba-9aad-edc2872eadc2_643361019"]}, {"text": "This was described as a terrible human tragedy, with workers shocked by what they found in the truck.", "citations": ["e801e538-67f8-4aba-9aad-edc2872eadc2_643361019"]}, {"text": "San Antonio\u2019s southern side connects highways leading to Texas border towns, routes often used by migrants seeking better lives.", "citations": ["e801e538-67f8-4aba-9aad-edc2872eadc2_643361019"]}, {"text": "The risks for border-crossing families are huge, especially as the area was recently hit by a heatwave.", "citations": ["e801e538-67f8-4aba-9aad-edc2872eadc2_643361019"]}, {"text": "Efforts to address weather-related risks in Texas are underway.", "citations": ["6ac54237-caae-4625-b412-f7dbc2cef79b_570944296"]}, {"text": "Some areas at greatest risk are already familiar with extreme weather, including long droughts and extreme heat.", "citations": ["4f283a60-78d0-422d-9805-599e23c3d017_203838030"]}, {"text": "Drought risks and severe flooding are increasing as the climate warms.", "citations": ["4f283a60-78d0-422d-9805-599e23c3d017_203838030"]}, {"text": "Recent winter storms in the region caused flooding and damage to homes, farmland, and infrastructure.", "citations": ["4f283a60-78d0-422d-9805-599e23c3d017_203838030"]}, {"text": "Experts warn that risks for California and the U.S. West will worsen as the climate crisis intensifies.", "citations": ["4f283a60-78d0-422d-9805-599e23c3d017_203838030"]}, {"text": "Rapid spring thaws have led to havoc from the southwest to the Rocky Mountains, with water rescues and flooded homes in New Mexico and Arizona.", "citations": ["4f283a60-78d0-422d-9805-599e23c3d017_203838030"]}, {"text": "President Joe Biden has called rising temperatures an existential threat and cannot deny climate change\u2019s effects.", "citations": ["87500f5f-fc08-439b-a135-38f1e3fe1313_939296275"]}, {"text": "He announced new measures to protect outdoor workers and boost meteorological funding.", "citations": ["87500f5f-fc08-439b-a135-38f1e3fe1313_939296275"]}, {"text": "Biden addressed Phoenix and San Antonio mayors, cities known for high temperatures.", "citations": ["87500f5f-fc08-439b-a135-38f1e3fe1313_939296275"]}, {"text": "Heat is the deadliest weather-related hazard in the U.S., killing 600 annually.", "citations": ["87500f5f-fc08-439b-a135-38f1e3fe1313_939296275"]}, {"text": "Phoenix's mayor said her city is famous for the heat but this summer was unprecedented and damaging.", "citations": ["87500f5f-fc08-439b-a135-38f1e3fe1313_939296275"]}, {"text": "A local expert described society as on the front lines of climate change.", "citations": ["87500f5f-fc08-439b-a135-38f1e3fe1313_939296275"]}, {"text": "Some areas saw light rain, strong winds, and possible sandstorms, particularly near water bodies.", "citations": ["f8d07273-84b6-4fc0-ab9f-6374130bce4f_167959417"]}, {"text": "Sandstorms triggered states of emergency in the west and caused fatal traffic accidents, such as in Glizan.", "citations": ["07a11b22-9e9e-47a8-b896-f7095baddcbd_1022319053"]}, {"text": "More than 100 cases of shortness of breath were reported over 48 hours, mainly affecting those with asthma and allergies.", "citations": ["07a11b22-9e9e-47a8-b896-f7095baddcbd_1022319053"]}, {"text": "These winds also caused electrical system failures and roof collapses in old houses, though major losses were avoided.", "citations": ["07a11b22-9e9e-47a8-b896-f7095baddcbd_1022319053"]}, {"text": "The Central Weather Bureau reported that Taiwan\u2019s weather is unstable due to a southwest airflow and a low-pressure zone, leading to noticeable rain, especially in central and southern regions, with heavy rainfall potentially delayed.", "citations": ["0d112bb3-0018-49c5-9587-6d22cb8ac503_491741771"]}, {"text": "Chen Tai Tin confirmed that ongoing construction works are strengthening fencing and wind prevention measures.", "citations": ["0d112bb3-0018-49c5-9587-6d22cb8ac503_491741771"]}, {"text": "Typhoon Lupi made landfall in coastal China.", "citations": ["f1f95f61-4aa3-41f6-8602-e9c43eb74224_302527813"]}, {"text": "The Taichung City Government reported receiving 57 disaster calls from 8:00 PM to 7:00 AM; 26 cases have been resolved and 31 are being processed, with immediate deployment of personnel and machinery.", "citations": ["f1f95f61-4aa3-41f6-8602-e9c43eb74224_302527813"]}, {"text": "Typhoon Lupi has a chance to pass through the northern coast and possibly northern land areas.", "citations": ["f1f95f61-4aa3-41f6-8602-e9c43eb74224_302527813"]}, {"text": "People are advised to avoid mountain areas during periods of rainfall.", "citations": ["f1f95f61-4aa3-41f6-8602-e9c43eb74224_302527813"]}, {"text": "Mayor Huang Weizhe instructed the Tainan city team to remain vigilant against Typhoon Canshu and urged the public to prepare.", "citations": ["a50c64db-65e2-4124-a1cb-79b4a66f3c19_885364973"]}, {"text": "For road safety, Tainan\u2019s Works Bureau has established a rapid response force to tackle toppled trees or road obstructions from broken branches as quickly as possible.", "citations": ["a50c64db-65e2-4124-a1cb-79b4a66f3c19_885364973"]}, {"text": "The Environmental Protection Bureau will focus on inspecting and clearing flood-prone areas, sending staff to remove blockages from drainage holes promptly.", "citations": ["a50c64db-65e2-4124-a1cb-79b4a66f3c19_885364973"]}, {"text": "People are encouraged to apply for assistance through local offices if needed.", "citations": ["a50c64db-65e2-4124-a1cb-79b4a66f3c19_885364973"]}, {"text": "Mayor Huang Weizhe informed Premier Su Chen-chang that Tainan had no major disasters following the recent events.", "citations": ["5b8d1901-f199-47e2-8748-f3d9b01b49bd_981813889"]}, {"text": "Taipei Vice Mayor Li Sichuan presided over a typhoon preparedness meeting at the Taipei Disaster Response Center.", "citations": ["947c0bd8-c8c5-4243-9d32-611b78a37a6a_342169752"]}, {"text": "After heavy spring rains, weather stabilized, but the expected rainfall did not significantly relieve southern reservoirs\u2019 drought, so water scarcity persists.", "citations": ["81896a13-2331-40bd-988c-1dba0b05a11f_995217371"]}, {"text": "Spring rain failed to improve water reserves in Nantai Bay.", "citations": ["81896a13-2331-40bd-988c-1dba0b05a11f_995217371"]}, {"text": "This year, the first wave of cross-border pollution began to affect Taiwan, with easterly winds expected to bring particulates and ozone southward.", "citations": ["3fa713d9-0cdd-4e89-90fe-1c404f46f7e9_515904210"]}, {"text": "Use of leaf blowers will be suspended, and the Agriculture Bureau will remind farmers not to burn in the open, broadcasting air quality alerts via social media and public displays.", "citations": ["3fa713d9-0cdd-4e89-90fe-1c404f46f7e9_515904210"]}, {"text": "President Tsai Ing-wen emphasized flood control and disaster response as priorities, highlighting recent investments in flood prevention infrastructure.", "citations": ["dcd8407e-ced3-4161-a022-202b7967f568_827776679"]}, {"text": "She noted that infrastructure is costly and slow to deliver results, and prefers investing in urban green areas and landscape construction, like waterfront parks and flood ponds, primarily increasing green space rather than water storage.", "citations": ["dcd8407e-ced3-4161-a022-202b7967f568_827776679"]}, {"text": "Hualien and Northeast regions still need attention following the 0403 earthquake, especially regarding collapsed barrier lakes, requiring central-local cooperation.", "citations": ["ac7fabd0-721b-4533-9727-541ae54a0c15_754558924"]}, {"text": "People are reminded to monitor weather updates and to avoid outdoor activities in mountain areas during adverse weather events.", "citations": ["8a2eb117-0514-4359-baec-c0133a3a9108_630546764"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1012", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Since 2017, when Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman (MBS) assumed his role, Saudi Arabia has been undergoing a significant transformation, as part of his ambitious Vision 2030 plan.", "citations": ["72fc1da6-5cba-4a49-ab3a-b305274e11f9_241486159"]}, {"text": "The country has witnessed a surge in sports events, movie screenings, art exhibitions and music concerts, becoming increasingly common and widely embraced by Saudi citizens.", "citations": ["1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850"]}, {"text": "MBS has spent billions under his Vision 2030 plan to make Saudi Arabia a cultural and economic powerhouse and attract global attention.", "citations": ["72fc1da6-5cba-4a49-ab3a-b305274e11f9_241486159"]}, {"text": "Saudi investment in international cinema, such as Johnny Depp's \"Jeanne du Barry,\" and his attendance at cultural events like the Red Sea Film Festival, underscore these new priorities.", "citations": ["72fc1da6-5cba-4a49-ab3a-b305274e11f9_241486159"]}, {"text": "This cultural shift is reflected in the nearly doubled percentage of Saudi women working outside the home, reaching 32% from almost 18% over the past five years.", "citations": ["f14b5c9e-084a-4291-8dc9-a631b84e6c4c_107673090"]}, {"text": "Women have gained the right to attend sports events since 2018 and now participate in public life, with many expressing ambition to pursue education and careers.", "citations": ["f14b5c9e-084a-4291-8dc9-a631b84e6c4c_107673090"]}, {"text": "Notable Saudi women entrepreneurs, like Sara Murad, exemplify how Vision 2030 has empowered women to launch their businesses, drawing inspiration from their cultural heritage.", "citations": ["8d9e78ed-f484-406d-8778-c733be2554ab_670261581"]}, {"text": "The government has also made a clear commitment to economic growth, focusing on expanding government spending and private sector participation.", "citations": ["de7bafe3-0613-4f8d-a925-cd3f5a571d98_897868556"]}, {"text": "As part of a broader diversification strategy, the Saudi fashion industry\u2014highlighted by designers like Mohammed Ashi at Paris Fashion Week\u2014demonstrates cultural openness and innovation.", "citations": ["acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949"]}, {"text": "Tourism is targeted to account for 10% of Saudi Arabia\u2019s GDP by 2030, with sports and entertainment positioned as essential to reducing oil dependence.", "citations": ["f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_130988937"]}, {"text": "Both public and private sectors recognize the nation's capability for rapid financial growth, attracting international partners and investment.", "citations": ["f2ef50c0-4817-4aae-bd18-4208e7c369cb_130988937"]}, {"text": "The National Strategy for Industry, launched by MBS, aims to increase advanced technology exports six-fold, generate tens of thousands of high-value jobs, and attract over a trillion riyals in new investment.", "citations": ["3e6ce080-5be8-4139-9ebb-2465c6f80d4c_721618053"]}, {"text": "At the same time, the influence of the Wahhabi religious establishment has been curbed by restricting powers of the religious police, promoting religious tolerance, and fostering an inclusive society.", "citations": ["1ec84a30-fdcd-4f1f-a0a0-4429222362aa_712309850"]}, {"text": "These sweeping reforms are part of a work in progress, aiming not only to modernize Saudi Arabia\u2019s economy but to reshape the country\u2019s social fabric and global image.", "citations": ["acfb0cea-fea6-41de-8259-b55498d43f7d_493804949"]}, {"text": "A thousand years after the golden age of Islamic scientific innovation, Saudi Arabia is once again exploring the frontiers of science by sending its first female astronauts, Rayyanah Barnawi and Maryam Fardus, to the International Space Station.", "citations": ["986b88ef-41ad-4adc-b83a-0e3a6fbed652_784402729"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has become a space pioneer among Arab and Islamic countries, reflecting the ambitious spirit driving Mohammed bin Salman Al Saud's reforms since becoming Crown Prince in 2017.", "citations": ["986b88ef-41ad-4adc-b83a-0e3a6fbed652_784402729"]}, {"text": "Central to his transformative Vision 2030 is the goal to diversify the Kingdom\u2019s economy beyond oil, promote technological advancement, and invest in grand projects like NEOM, a $1.5 trillion \"city of the future,\" though securing funding remains a challenge.", "citations": ["6fb00458-2f33-4be0-9d82-fa15c144e9e2_746956331"]}, {"text": "The Sovereign Wealth Fund declined to allocate NEOM's 2024 budget, illustrating a cautious approach to investment despite the scale of ambition.", "citations": ["83eccc82-a52a-4cca-891e-5c7a2f78e459_880336803"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has also taken steps to build international alliances and assert regional influence, including participating in a diplomatic blockade of Qatar in 2017 alongside Egypt and other Gulf states, citing concerns over terrorism financing.", "citations": ["0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681"]}, {"text": "This move was criticized, as Saudi Arabia itself has long promoted Salafi Islam worldwide, often linked to extremism, according to international commentators.", "citations": ["0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681"]}, {"text": "The powerful religious clergy still hold sway in the kingdom and pose obstacles to the Crown Prince's progressive agenda, especially in a nation with significant youth unemployment.", "citations": ["0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681"]}, {"text": "Despite risks, MBS has curtailed the powers of the infamous religious police and worked to sever the deep entrenchment of Wahhabi influence in public life.", "citations": ["0f1b1e80-0ad8-47a9-958c-d307747ea092_404328681"]}, {"text": "A visible sign of his reforms is the improved status and rights of women, highlighted by female astronaut missions and broader access for women to the workforce, sports, and public life.", "citations": ["986b88ef-41ad-4adc-b83a-0e3a6fbed652_784402729"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia competes for global stature, vying to host the 2030 FIFA World Cup with Egypt and Greece as partners, an effort entangled with wider European and geopolitical interests.", "citations": ["d59998ab-4eb9-437b-944e-10959956e59c_666549583"]}, {"text": "The partnership with Greece, now a major ally, strengthens Saudi influence in Europe; France and Germany have supported this effort.", "citations": ["d59998ab-4eb9-437b-944e-10959956e59c_666549583"]}, {"text": "Vision 2030 also aims to boost the sports sector, with high-profile investments and privatization of sports clubs to improve performance and international rankings.", "citations": ["6fb00458-2f33-4be0-9d82-fa15c144e9e2_746956331"]}, {"text": "Internationally, Saudi foreign policy has met mixed results, including ongoing challenges in Yemen, Lebanon, and relations with Qatar, Iran, and Turkey.", "citations": ["7ea23f8e-14da-44e6-bc7d-9521501c2d40_245829920"]}, {"text": "Despite setbacks, Saudi Arabia remains a key player in global energy markets and strives to balance regional security and international partnerships, seeking to maintain its role in OPEC and the G20.", "citations": ["01c139e1-62f7-4338-8b21-9ae59feef871_497090123"]}, {"text": "MBS's ambitious reforms have started to reshape the West's perception of the Kingdom, aiming for openness, innovation, and a reduced role for religious conservatism in Saudi society.", "citations": ["01c139e1-62f7-4338-8b21-9ae59feef871_497090123"]}, {"text": "After the announcement of the Kingdom\u2019s Vision 2030, King Salman declared his goal for Saudi Arabia to become a successful and leading global model at all levels.", "citations": ["3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452"]}, {"text": "Eight years after its launch, Vision 2030 has achieved significant milestones.", "citations": ["3070d6a1-fc25-41bc-8539-08c048cf7606_862949452"]}, {"text": "The Kingdom now aims to strengthen ties with multiple global powers, not relying solely on the West or the United States.", "citations": ["9d333eca-3204-402a-a29f-47f8d71b253b_230205988"]}, {"text": "By the end of 2022, the Kingdom\u2019s GDP was projected to exceed $1 trillion.", "citations": ["9d333eca-3204-402a-a29f-47f8d71b253b_230205988"]}, {"text": "A notable improvement has been in the social sphere, with numerous reforms implemented.", "citations": ["9d333eca-3204-402a-a29f-47f8d71b253b_230205988"]}, {"text": "Turki Al Sheikh credited the Crown Prince with saving the Kingdom and charting a promising path for the future.", "citations": ["f8ac333a-df70-4537-8689-122137e47402_654120225"]}, {"text": "The drop in oil prices in 2015 exposed the risk of dependence on a single resource, provoking economic anxiety and crisis.", "citations": ["3575335e-eed6-4f6d-be45-e0b382b2a227_139594759"]}, {"text": "The timing of Vision 2030 was pivotal, launching reforms and development to elevate Saudi Arabia\u2019s status globally.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "Hani Wafa, editor-in-chief of Al-Riyadh, emphasized the Kingdom\u2019s growing local, regional, and international influence in both politics and the economy.", "citations": ["06c02d9c-b98f-47a5-9573-e7dccfa76092_78227085"]}, {"text": "Vision 2030, under Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman, positions Saudi Arabia as a stable partner in creating a more integrated world.", "citations": ["06c02d9c-b98f-47a5-9573-e7dccfa76092_78227085"]}, {"text": "The Kingdom has become a source of opportunity and an incubator for innovation, highlighted during Riyadh\u2019s hosting of the World Economic Forum.", "citations": ["06c02d9c-b98f-47a5-9573-e7dccfa76092_78227085"]}, {"text": "Vision 2030 is described by the Crown Prince as a continuous march toward progress, not an endpoint.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "The strategy has shaped a vibrant society and influenced every aspect of life in the Kingdom.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia has assumed a pivotal role in international matters, contributing to a stronger global order.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "Non-oil GDP accounted for more than 50% of Saudi Arabia\u2019s economy in 2023.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "Research and Development are key priorities, enabling businesses to adopt emerging technologies rapidly.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "The digital economy is expanding three times faster than the global average in the Kingdom.", "citations": ["bd18bfb8-3df1-40fe-80d2-e6f7164cb150_463168187"]}, {"text": "Many observers saw recent diplomatic initiatives as paving the way for President Biden\u2019s visit to Saudi Arabia.", "citations": ["0f37144d-1ae3-4b17-aa7e-e87704c24a29_359865985"]}, {"text": "Photographs of the Crown Prince with President Biden signified the international recognition he has sought.", "citations": ["b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190"]}, {"text": "Women\u2019s participation in the workforce has increased, positively impacting the economy, though some restrictions on dissent remain.", "citations": ["b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia\u2019s approach to women\u2019s rights has progressed but is still incomplete, especially regarding critics.", "citations": ["b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190"]}, {"text": "Closing sources of direct opposition is used as a means of maintaining stability.", "citations": ["b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190"]}, {"text": "The Crown Prince has significantly shaped Saudi foreign policy, brokering a truce in Yemen as a step toward regional peace.", "citations": ["b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190"]}, {"text": "Mohammed bin Salman is viewed as the driving force behind these changes, enacting reforms that were previously subjects of public debate.", "citations": ["b07a8d73-e542-437e-8984-decb47d00cb5_125623190"]}, {"text": "His crowning as \u201cArab Leader\u201d is seen as the result of an ambitious strategy and sustained effort.", "citations": ["b7fead8a-a07f-4c14-aa03-da188b12ad11_646421381"]}, {"text": "The Kingdom has contributed to balancing energy markets and addressing complex international issues, reinforcing Riyadh's status as a sought-after partner for Washington, Beijing, and Moscow alike.", "citations": ["b7fead8a-a07f-4c14-aa03-da188b12ad11_646421381"]}, {"text": "Since his appointment as Crown Prince in 2017, Mohammed bin Salman (MBS) has embarked on a sweeping reform program under Vision 2030 to transform Saudi Arabia\u2019s economy and society.", "citations": ["83a827e2-cbf1-406d-bf2b-3949bd5c94e6_343919030"]}, {"text": "Saudi Aramco, at the heart of these reforms, produces more than one in every eight barrels of crude oil globally, highlighting the Kingdom\u2019s crucial role in world energy markets.", "citations": ["83a827e2-cbf1-406d-bf2b-3949bd5c94e6_343919030"]}, {"text": "MBS\u2019s efforts come amid global shifts, including the rise of U.S. shale oil and changing diplomatic priorities, leading some to assert that America\u2019s energy reliance on the Middle East is decreasing.", "citations": ["b40411e8-7566-47c7-a2d3-1fcf32e07fde_843888380"]}, {"text": "Despite debates in U.S. politics\u2014such as whether President Biden should engage directly with MBS\u2014Saudi Arabia remains an indispensable partner due to its economic and geopolitical significance.", "citations": ["60d24f6f-11c1-4fa7-b01c-19de8707f495_804944464"]}, {"text": "Tensions between the U.S. and Saudi Arabia have at times surfaced, especially as America considers rekindling ties with Iran and manages broader regional uncertainties.", "citations": ["b40411e8-7566-47c7-a2d3-1fcf32e07fde_843888380"]}, {"text": "MBS has prioritized regional relations, demonstrated by hosting the 41st Gulf Cooperation Council summit in Al Ula, while countering foreign pressure and asserting Saudi sovereignty.", "citations": ["131995e1-303b-4ce8-9d70-77b71e27ef12_986520401"]}, {"text": "To reshape Saudi Arabia\u2019s image, MBS launched high-profile initiatives such as sending the country\u2019s first female astronaut on a space mission in 2023.", "citations": ["9f4ba525-e4f1-411a-a23c-4ea366f11b61_57841039"]}, {"text": "Economic diversification is a cornerstone of Vision 2030, as Saudi Arabia aims to reduce dependency on oil, attract foreign investment, and develop new sectors.", "citations": ["443cc2be-3fb9-423f-84b3-deca4f4a274b_683418803"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia\u2019s business climate has improved, evidenced by the nation\u2019s jump from 92nd to 62nd in the World Bank\u2019s Ease of Doing Business rankings.", "citations": ["6515794f-ecce-42c8-a1fe-d16672b87eb6_1892359"]}, {"text": "The government offers incentives for investors, including no personal income tax, a user-friendly tax system, and region-specific tax breaks, while maintaining a requirement that at least 75% of company employees be Saudi nationals.", "citations": ["6515794f-ecce-42c8-a1fe-d16672b87eb6_1892359"]}, {"text": "Major cities like Riyadh, Jeddah, and Dammam have become investment hubs, supporting growth in non-oil sectors alongside traditional energy industries.", "citations": ["6515794f-ecce-42c8-a1fe-d16672b87eb6_1892359"]}, {"text": "MBS has introduced significant social reforms by curtailing the powers of the religious police, limiting the influence of the Wahhabi religious establishment, and liberalizing restrictions on daily life.", "citations": ["83a827e2-cbf1-406d-bf2b-3949bd5c94e6_343919030"]}, {"text": "Women\u2019s rights have seen dramatic advancement, including the appointment of female flight crew and the broader opening of the workplace and public sphere to women.", "citations": ["f57733f0-7f63-4bab-a018-63f8d2820816_253912464"]}, {"text": "In response to the global climate crisis, Saudi Arabia has committed to reaching net zero carbon emissions by 2060, underscoring its willingness to align with international climate goals.", "citations": ["443cc2be-3fb9-423f-84b3-deca4f4a274b_683418803"]}, {"text": "Despite ongoing challenges in international relations and domestic debates, MBS\u2019s policies have fundamentally altered the course of Saudi Arabia, positioning it as a more open and dynamic player on the global stage.", "citations": ["83a827e2-cbf1-406d-bf2b-3949bd5c94e6_343919030"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1014", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Shopping in large grocery stores has become the norm for many, making us more reliant on them than we realize.", "citations": ["3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363"]}, {"text": "Foods associated with specific regions often originate from tradition rather than recipe books, cooking shows, or social media.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "Food connects us to life, yet many people have lost that connection.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "Consuming a pumpkin, for instance, does not require killing the pumpkin plant.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "A cookbook aiming to preserve culinary heritage was inspired by the author's mother's oral instructions on making traditional Palau.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "Such books serve as forums for cooks to share, laugh, and learn together.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "Dishes are ready when the chef deems them so, not when a timer buzzes.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "Environmental writers focused on food and agriculture often work across the Caribbean.", "citations": ["8df2ef49-d78a-4e0e-8415-42c8926e769c_330576672"]}, {"text": "In times of war, safeguarding biodiversity may not seem urgent, but traditional markets and food production remain crucial.", "citations": ["d2492db9-afe6-4877-a586-087d469a4cff_581432463"]}, {"text": "The Slow Food network helps Ukrainians retain family production and farmers' markets traditions.", "citations": ["d2492db9-afe6-4877-a586-087d469a4cff_581432463"]}, {"text": "Some chefs and supporters travel with ingredients to cities like Lviv to promote Slow Food.", "citations": ["d2492db9-afe6-4877-a586-087d469a4cff_581432463"]}, {"text": "Each act to support Slow Food is a step toward a better future.", "citations": ["d2492db9-afe6-4877-a586-087d469a4cff_581432463"]}, {"text": "Slow Food is part of a global network with active initiatives, including in Ukraine.", "citations": ["d2492db9-afe6-4877-a586-087d469a4cff_581432463"]}, {"text": "Slow Food products are usually produced on a small scale.", "citations": ["3fc1cd45-38d0-4612-8e8e-21d9a4fd7376_751985363"]}, {"text": "Traditional methods and tools are used to make these products.", "citations": ["86f0531e-4d76-40fa-9d32-2249450d475e_725694039"]}, {"text": "Artisanal foods offer significant health benefits.", "citations": ["86f0531e-4d76-40fa-9d32-2249450d475e_725694039"]}, {"text": "Locally made artisanal foods also reduce carbon emissions and are environmentally friendly.", "citations": ["86f0531e-4d76-40fa-9d32-2249450d475e_725694039"]}, {"text": "Regenerative farming is key to a sustainable food future, as soil\u2019s health is crucial for the planet.", "citations": ["d81bd102-edab-45d8-9e07-7eabfd506ff6_213163074"]}, {"text": "Supporting small-scale farmers who use regenerative practices is essential for a resilient food system.", "citations": ["d81bd102-edab-45d8-9e07-7eabfd506ff6_213163074"]}, {"text": "Exploring regions like Lamu allows visitors to engage directly with local food cultures.", "citations": ["e9951c05-7d63-4215-ba1f-f774e81ccb42_799247081"]}, {"text": "In the 20th century, individuals in the US contributed to the movement's growth.", "citations": ["e9951c05-7d63-4215-ba1f-f774e81ccb42_799247081"]}, {"text": "Local establishments like Amu House in Lamu Stone Town offer accessible experiences.", "citations": ["e9951c05-7d63-4215-ba1f-f774e81ccb42_799247081"]}, {"text": "Other eco-tour activities, like whale shark safaris, complement slow travel experiences.", "citations": ["e9951c05-7d63-4215-ba1f-f774e81ccb42_799247081"]}, {"text": "With climate change, food production accounts for a significant part of our carbon footprint.", "citations": ["eec6fa37-518f-43fd-9c9d-1a12428f4853_258820982"]}, {"text": "Individuals can reduce impact by making their own meals.", "citations": ["eec6fa37-518f-43fd-9c9d-1a12428f4853_258820982"]}, {"text": "Nutrition experts say some current trends, like meal kits and food boxes, are likely to continue.", "citations": ["41a61425-cc5e-4b7f-bc3a-fafb55782d6e_163254111"]}, {"text": "Awareness of sugar intake and upcycled foods are increasingly important in food choices.", "citations": ["41a61425-cc5e-4b7f-bc3a-fafb55782d6e_163254111"]}, {"text": "The pandemic prompted many people to leave cities and reconnect with local food sources.", "citations": ["41a61425-cc5e-4b7f-bc3a-fafb55782d6e_163254111"]}, {"text": "Upcycled foods address food waste by reusing materials that would otherwise be discarded.", "citations": ["41a61425-cc5e-4b7f-bc3a-fafb55782d6e_163254111"]}, {"text": "International concern for biodiversity, such as bee preservation, has drawn support from figures like Pope Francis.", "citations": ["90c089b4-9707-45ba-af3b-77dd18799bed_763079563"]}, {"text": "Movements like the ECI aim to protect insects, which face alarming declines.", "citations": ["d2492db9-afe6-4877-a586-087d469a4cff_581432463"]}, {"text": "The Pope has publicly blessed these biodiversity initiatives.", "citations": ["90c089b4-9707-45ba-af3b-77dd18799bed_763079563"]}, {"text": "Multiple crises indicate the fragility of global supply chains.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8038-548b14438087_146567024"]}, {"text": "Food supply problems are exacerbated by global dependence on trade.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8038-548b14438087_146567024"]}, {"text": "During COVID, local farmers across the world quickly increased production, demonstrating their resilience.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8038-548b14438087_146567024"]}, {"text": "The local food movement is growing internationally.", "citations": ["ea8efe93-815c-4f57-8