old and requires a walking aid for daily activities.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "The incidence of falls in Parkinson\u2019s disease patients is 50%.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "Grandpa Liu considered physical therapy after experiencing a fall.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "Concerns exist about exercises being too minimal to be effective if continued over the long term.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "The ideal rehabilitation allows for training and assessment, even when medications aren\u2019t effective.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "Exercise is more effective than inactivity.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "Studies show exercise improves mobility and walking balance in patients with Parkinson\u2019s disease.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "It\u2019s vital to share such helpful information.", "citations": ["59c0eb4e-e325-4297-a518-cd3e0286d830_727827473"]}, {"text": "There are still many lingering doubts, which are addressed here individually.", "citations": ["891cfb22-1148-46f0-9286-e01479cbfc56_781295824"]}, {"text": "Home care for elderly involves more than daily attention\u2014physical therapists help with pain and disability while occupational therapists boost recovery and quality of life, making both crucial.", "citations": ["891cfb22-1148-46f0-9286-e01479cbfc56_781295824"]}, {"text": "\u201cOccupational Therapy\u201d (OT) does not relate to overtime work.", "citations": ["0cc09431-be8d-4bc6-956a-03c87e2251c1_1056498973"]}, {"text": "Home rehabilitation ensures continuous recovery.", "citations": ["2268afb3-a846-40f2-8508-149822480232_685798680"]}, {"text": "Thus, Liu sought help from Chi Mei Medical Center\u2019s rehab department.", "citations": ["2268afb3-a846-40f2-8508-149822480232_685798680"]}, {"text": "Mr. Chen advised Mr. Jiang to purchase a walker for safer transfers from bed with family support.", "citations": ["2268afb3-a846-40f2-8508-149822480232_685798680"]}, {"text": "(Advertisement wording omitted)  \nAn octogenarian who fell twice in two weeks progressed from being bedridden to self-care, showing that too much pampering can inhibit recovery.", "citations": ["660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_80882257"]}, {"text": "A professional nurse urges moving beyond \u201cdoting care\u201d to encourage independence and autonomy, restoring dignity and self-care in disabled or elderly individuals.", "citations": ["660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_80882257"]}, {"text": "Grandpa Lin regained self-care abilities and confidence so his family could resume work with peace of mind.", "citations": ["660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_80882257"]}, {"text": "Some need significant help sitting up due to severe physical weakness.", "citations": ["660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_80882257"]}, {"text": "Upon discharge, some elderly need help leaving bed and using a wheelchair, sometimes becoming reluctant to leave home.", "citations": ["660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_80882257"]}, {"text": "Many people thrive into their 80s and continue to find happiness.", "citations": ["660c1a12-bdbf-470e-88ba-7046d4faea0a_80882257"]}, {"text": "Wu Anan emphasizes multiple strategies exist to prevent falls.", "citations": ["07cb31bf-8e92-4c5a-bd19-32339f0d9b2e_92421089"]}, {"text": "Falls are more likely when elderly wake up abruptly in the morning.", "citations": ["07cb31bf-8e92-4c5a-bd19-32339f0d9b2e_92421089"]}, {"text": "Elders should sit up or stand slowly to avoid dizziness.", "citations": ["07cb31bf-8e92-4c5a-bd19-32339f0d9b2e_92421089"]}, {"text": "After any fall with injury, a doctor should be notified.", "citations": ["07cb31bf-8e92-4c5a-bd19-32339f0d9b2e_92421089"]}, {"text": "Some patients may not recognize injury, especially if they\u2019re on medications causing unconsciousness.", "citations": ["07cb31bf-8e92-4c5a-bd19-32339f0d9b2e_92421089"]}, {"text": "After a fall, check for any changes and consult medical professionals.", "citations": ["07cb31bf-8e92-4c5a-bd19-32339f0d9b2e_92421089"]}, {"text": "(Non-medical sentences omitted for focus)  \nAh Nang participates in regular community activities and rehabilitation.", "citations": ["653fea6b-17b9-4800-b544-e701e3cb14ea_1018975522"]}, {"text": "He remarks about aging and slower response times.", "citations": ["653fea6b-17b9-4800-b544-e701e3cb14ea_1018975522"]}, {"text": "Activities transition from hospital to home with support, such as walking canes and caregivers.", "citations": ["653fea6b-17b9-4800-b544-e701e3cb14ea_1018975522"]}, {"text": "Weekly rehabilitation sessions are maintained as consistently as possible.", "citations": ["ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_99859557"]}, {"text": "Quitting smoking is crucial; otherwise, conditions like COPD can worsen rapidly.", "citations": ["aa6071f8-5937-4224-9db7-398dde0ee2ab_373587635"]}, {"text": "At age 62, a patient was hospitalized for asthma, later diagnosed as COPD, leading to retirement and multiple admissions.", "citations": ["aa6071f8-5937-4224-9db7-398dde0ee2ab_373587635"]}, {"text": "Some patients worry about exercise space at home or needing oxygen equipment.", "citations": ["aa6071f8-5937-4224-9db7-398dde0ee2ab_373587635"]}, {"text": "With increasing future demand, greater inclusion of professionals in rehabilitation will be needed.", "citations": ["df1a5ab1-8526-4072-ba85-13e44bbf721d_881084938"]}, {"text": "Therapists teach patients how to use home equipment for exercise.", "citations": ["ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_99859557"]}, {"text": "The core goal is enabling self-care like using the toilet and shower independently.", "citations": ["ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_99859557"]}, {"text": "The next ambition is to re-enter the kitchen and reduce the burden on family.", "citations": ["ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_99859557"]}, {"text": "Persistence leads to daily improvements for each patient.", "citations": ["ef8828ff-2a00-4f86-a538-28497980cec7_99859557"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1024", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Even though the COVID-19 pandemic had a severe impact on the aviation industry, the long-term trend remains robust.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "With a growing emphasis on sustainability and reducing carbon emissions, aircraft manufacturers are investing in research and development to create more eco-friendly models, including the use of advanced materials, aerodynamic improvements, and more efficient engines.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Airlines are leveraging these trends to enhance the passenger experience and gain a competitive edge.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Narrow-Body aircraft are well-suited for both domestic and international routes, making them the preferred choice for many carriers.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Airlines are looking to replace older aircraft with more fuel-efficient and environmentally friendly Narrow-Body models, driving the growth of this segment.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "Asia-Pacific emerges as the largest region in this segment as airlines in the region expand their fleets to meet increasing demand for air travel.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "In terms of growth, Europe takes the lead, driven by the need to improve operational efficiency, reduce maintenance costs, and enhance passenger comfort.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_922454685"]}, {"text": "A recent report by Report Ocean forecasts that the aircraft leasing market size is poised to exceed USD 453.2 billion by 2026, with a robust growth rate of 6.8% during the forecast period.", "citations": ["59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_445106883"]}, {"text": "The surge in air travel rates is a primary driver propelling the demand for aircraft leasing, with Latin America, the Middle East, and Africa presenting lucrative opportunities for market players due to infrastructure development and tourism growth.", "citations": ["59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_445106883"]}, {"text": "Dry leasing and wet leasing represent the primary lease types, catering to the diverse needs of airlines.", "citations": ["59271291-9f4e-455a-b133-f91be9278e03_445106883"]}, {"text": "Parker Hannifin has raised full-year estimates on sustained demand from plane manufacturers.", "citations": ["b4adfd15-a03f-4587-8232-1b76b7845939_588773683"]}, {"text": "Boeing's new deals, including a significant 787 order outfitted with GE engines and a $34 billion sale of over 200 aircraft to Air India, underscore strong demand.", "citations": ["07673e60-b3da-415b-abc9-3665c6416001_634673151"]}, {"text": "Saudi Arabia is aiming to transform into a global aviation hub, with Boeing and Airbus competing for major new orders.", "citations": ["07673e60-b3da-415b-abc9-3665c6416001_634673151"]}, {"text": "Since early 2020, General Electric has seen varying levels of recovery in global aviation markets, with aviation forecasted to fully recover in two years.", "citations": ["09bf597a-3101-4762-86c1-5b7cd6f08581_137894313"]}, {"text": "North America stands out for the increasing use of connected aircraft for maintenance and repair, driven by demand for real-time information, improved safety, and advanced communication systems, though high integration costs and limited skilled workers pose challenges.", "citations": ["226d9601-5c18-49af-bc51-d007f5d3617d_932016380"]}, {"text": "Boeing cut its 20-year outlook for industrywide deliveries but reiterated that long-term fundamentals remain strong, with a recovery trajectory closely tied to GDP and air traffic resumption.", "citations": ["fae811af-1764-4940-ba22-c25d1fc471e7_4521139"]}, {"text": "Carbon fiber, particularly the PAN-based and continuous segments, is increasingly used to reduce weight and costs throughout military and commercial aviation, with the aviation carbon fiber market forecasted to reach $4.4 billion by 2031.", "citations": ["4a9091b3-af57-4bf2-b787-6f10c6a4c451_510642838"]}, {"text": "Boeing predicted a decline in demand for aircraft amid sanctions against Russian aviation.", "citations": ["6f67df6d-141d-4dd0-b5f7-b04e98c8819d_893198852"]}, {"text": "Airbus has launched its first global aircraft recycling project in Southwest China with the building of the Airbus Full Life Cycle Service Center (ALSC) in Chengdu, Sichuan Province.", "citations": ["0208b946-03d7-4a90-be65-59f0357fb4ff_74086998"]}, {"text": "The city of Chengdu is actively promoting the rapid development of its aviation industry.", "citations": ["0208b946-03d7-4a90-be65-59f0357fb4ff_74086998"]}, {"text": "The International Air Transport Association (IATA) has improved its forecast twice for global civil aviation\u2019s post-pandemic recovery, now expecting the industry\u2019s net profit to reach $9.8 billion in 2023, more than double the previous December forecast of $4.7 billion.", "citations": ["4ed2f327-339b-4558-8cfb-fed88867a4e1_557369222"]}, {"text": "However, cargo transportation is expected to reach 57.8 million tons, remaining below the 61.5 million tons moved in 2019, mostly due to a drop in international trade.", "citations": ["4ed2f327-339b-4558-8cfb-fed88867a4e1_557369222"]}, {"text": "Prices for aviation fuel fell in the first half of the year, offering some cost relief, though they remain high, according to IATA CEO Willy Walsh.", "citations": ["4ed2f327-339b-4558-8cfb-fed88867a4e1_557369222"]}, {"text": "A global recession leading to job losses could worsen industry prospects.", "citations": ["4ed2f327-339b-4558-8cfb-fed88867a4e1_557369222"]}, {"text": "Supply chain challenges continue to disrupt the delivery and servicing of new aircraft fleets.", "citations": ["4ed2f327-339b-4558-8cfb-fed88867a4e1_557369222"]}, {"text": "There is significant attention to import-substitution in aviation, particularly in aircraft production and the large market for aviation-related IT solutions.", "citations": ["3fece070-88e7-4522-96ba-466947672c1d_301158559"]}, {"text": "IATA expects air travel to reach 4.35 billion passengers in 2023, nearly matching the 4.54 billion passengers of 2019.", "citations": ["c869c77e-08a9-494e-b285-3943ca1a4cb7_1045129805"]}, {"text": "Asian companies, and especially those in China and India, are expected to be the main drivers of future demand growth in civil aviation.", "citations": ["5441001d-5c90-459e-ba13-63792d01320e_1052129711"]}, {"text": "Airbus\u2019s global orderbook has increased 2.5 times, and its operating profit from core activities rose four percent to 5.8 billion euros, with expectations to reach 6.5 to 7 billion euros this year.", "citations": ["ec5677bb-9461-4e63-a75f-3259dd0e47e2_353111266"]}, {"text": "Efforts are underway at various aerospace manufacturing centers, including plans to modernize production and expand into international markets, emphasizing more efficient and competitive operations.", "citations": ["bcb51f60-616d-4a2c-8171-a2d016190073_43330191"]}, {"text": "HyPoint has invested $15 million in a research and manufacturing center to address energy storage limitations in hydrogen fuel cells for aviation, with new high-temperature membrane technology offering significantly higher specific power.", "citations": ["5360068d-f0c2-4c44-a8ae-06ab47ed4b43_616926246"]}, {"text": "This investment could facilitate the development of environmentally friendly aviation, including urban air mobility solutions powered by hydrogen.", "citations": ["5360068d-f0c2-4c44-a8ae-06ab47ed4b43_616926246"]}, {"text": "There is growing interest and investment in alternative energy aviation startups, supported by venture capital clubs and new pitch opportunities.", "citations": ["5360068d-f0c2-4c44-a8ae-06ab47ed4b43_616926246"]}, {"text": "International and regional initiatives are underway to ensure that aviation policies consider the needs and expectations of users and civil society stakeholders.", "citations": ["0955c166-5e0d-4c3a-8351-0b36526e5383_44122162"]}, {"text": "Honeywell has secured contracts exceeding $10 billion in its advanced air transport business, reflecting its global efficiency and ability to attract diverse talent.", "citations": ["800b263d-55d6-4e35-b026-0cced3cd6df1_525501174"]}, {"text": "Despite surging demand, aircraft manufacturers confront challenges from increased costs, supply chain disruptions, and skilled labor shortages post-pandemic.", "citations": ["467e182e-0585-4a85-b54a-09801d8bea14_484067037"]}, {"text": "The Dubai Airshow, held in the shadow of the Ukraine conflict with the absence of Russian participation, highlights shifts in the aviation industry's competitive landscape.", "citations": ["467e182e-0585-4a85-b54a-09801d8bea14_484067037"]}, {"text": "Air India may soon finalize its significant recent order split between Airbus and Boeing, while Avolon, an Irish lessor, quietly completes a new deal with Boeing after a wave of earlier orders.", "citations": ["467e182e-0585-4a85-b54a-09801d8bea14_484067037"]}, {"text": "Airbus is currently outperforming Boeing in new orders, exemplified by a firm order for 255 single-aisle A321s at the Dubai show, valued for their range and flexible passenger capacity.", "citations": ["daae9fd2-8a07-4edc-9903-3bad74d44234_57653713"]}, {"text": "Boeing recently confirmed a major Saudi Arabian order for 121 aircraft, valued at $35 billion, as it forecasts strong future demand in the Middle East.", "citations": ["daf4c75c-3870-4467-9566-86868603f4ff_388897130"]}, {"text": "Boeing predicts its 2025-2026 profits to approach $100 billion, with a 10% operating margin and $10 billion in free cash flow, allocating $3 billion to research and development.", "citations": ["daf4c75c-3870-4467-9566-86868603f4ff_388897130"]}, {"text": "Boeing continues to bolster its defense segment with classified Pentagon contracts, while facing persistent challenges in the labor market and supply chain.", "citations": ["467e182e-0585-4a85-b54a-09801d8bea14_484067037"]}, {"text": "In its latest outlook, Boeing has reduced its commercial aircraft demand forecast, excluding future deliveries to Russia due to ongoing sanctions.", "citations": ["0b69f45d-424f-4c58-98b9-4c2055b67d53_855170679"]}, {"text": "Despite near-term setbacks, Boeing projects the global commercial aircraft fleet will double over the next twenty years, with cargo plane demand growing at 3.5% annually, outpacing overall trade growth.", "citations": ["5867527f-48e2-4543-921b-79edad641fbf_327309205"]}, {"text": "The Dubai Airshow underscores the rising importance of the space sector for future aviation industry expansion.", "citations": ["4229ab8d-3cbd-4c2c-b7c2-6c021d94db0e_329341986"]}, {"text": "The aviation sector remains a $110 billion industry, contending with unpredictable supply chain issues.", "citations": ["1b649385-6b5e-4153-9781-9b58c0d4caa3_421154067"]}, {"text": "Engine manufacturers derive most profits from servicing engines, supported by a global repair network and independent providers such as U.S.-based AAR.", "citations": ["1b649385-6b5e-4153-9781-9b58c0d4caa3_421154067"]}, {"text": "GE recorded a 44% increase in parts sales year-on-year for the third quarter, while RTX emphasized the ongoing struggle to boost maintenance output amid material and energy constraints.", "citations": ["1b649385-6b5e-4153-9781-9b58c0d4caa3_421154067"]}, {"text": "Price competition continues to be fierce, placing added pressure on lead times and margins.", "citations": ["1b649385-6b5e-4153-9781-9b58c0d4caa3_421154067"]}, {"text": "Airbus reported record profits of \u20ac4.2 billion, distributing dividends of \u20ac1.5 per share, whereas U.S. rival Boeing posted its third consecutive annual loss in 2021 due to costly production issues and delivery delays.", "citations": ["53e1bc39-a404-4748-8db7-e73ce35b4f71_583331001"]}, {"text": "Air travel volumes are projected to return to pre-pandemic levels in 2023 for domestic and 2025 for long-haul flights, with global passenger numbers expected to double by 2050.", "citations": ["53e1bc39-a404-4748-8db7-e73ce35b4f71_583331001"]}, {"text": "Manufacturers are shifting production from large aircraft to more efficient, smaller models in response to evolving market trends that started before the pandemic.", "citations": ["9973d6d5-a9dc-411f-a89d-969510946c96_466373894"]}, {"text": "Cirium projects 45,000 more fuel-efficient aircraft deliveries by 2040, valued at $2.9 trillion.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "If these projections are realized, the global passenger fleet will reach approximately 47,200 aircraft by the end of 2040.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "New aircraft deliveries will address both rising air transport demand and the replacement of less fuel-efficient, older aircraft.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "China is expected to lead the world in air passenger traffic growth with over 6% annual growth, accounting for 20% of total global aircraft deliveries.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "The Middle East, representing an estimated 7% of global deliveries, will contribute 11% of aircraft value due to a focus on larger twin-aisle models.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "Most new deliveries will be single-aisle jets.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "Both Airbus and Boeing are expected to introduce a new generation of single-aisle aircraft in the early to mid-2030s.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "A larger, 90-seat aircraft model is slated to enter the market starting in 2030.", "citations": ["65a6d821-4ded-4ba5-874a-2aa5ee48ba5e_72581204"]}, {"text": "Electric vertical take-off and landing (eVTOL) aircraft are a key area of ongoing aerospace research and development.", "citations": ["1e53dfdc-2c0c-4633-aa41-270065b5df71_499034918"]}, {"text": "Toward the future, the air cargo market is forecast to be strong, with growth predicted in both new and modified cargo aircraft.", "citations": ["bf2732d0-bb7b-4e55-9d35-f1d548672746_296106203"]}, {"text": "Supply chains in the aviation industry have been significantly affected by the pandemic, though market recovery is anticipated but will differ from historical patterns.", "citations": ["e492c015-2ad6-44ef-a4e1-27b571b2648a_262392137"]}, {"text": "Some companies have exited the sector due to pandemic-related impacts, while others, like Zilong, have gained new component orders and maintained consistent deliveries.", "citations": ["47a91382-9e36-40d4-b0e1-0f834a0e9567_310676830"]}, {"text": "Monthly aircraft delivery volumes continue to show steady growth.", "citations": ["1c226a6a-72ce-4f97-9550-28bd7665d3e9_187259902"]}, {"text": "Delivery forecasts from Boeing and Airbus, along with new orders turning into mass production for companies such as Zilong, point to ongoing resilience.", "citations": ["1c226a6a-72ce-4f97-9550-28bd7665d3e9_187259902"]}, {"text": "Huaxin (1605) is expanding capital by issuing new shares, intending to maintain its growth momentum.", "citations": ["1c226a6a-72ce-4f97-9550-28bd7665d3e9_187259902"]}, {"text": "Product innovation is driving financial results, as May revenue figures reflect an annual increase of 107.85%.", "citations": ["1c226a6a-72ce-4f97-9550-28bd7665d3e9_187259902"]}, {"text": "Stock prices for certain aerospace suppliers, such as those in Taiwan, have reached record highs, supported by substantial purchase activity from major institutional investors.", "citations": ["f657c1cb-e50f-4660-96f7-9689ae899a44_958115065"]}, {"text": "Increased orders from Airbus and Boeing are boosting demand for special steel throughout the East Asian supply chain, benefiting markets in countries including South Korea and India.", "citations": ["f657c1cb-e50f-4660-96f7-9689ae899a44_958115065"]}, {"text": "Boda has returned to profitability, with profit attributable to shareholders rising by 52.0% to HK $582.0 million.", "citations": ["04c71ca1-6234-4294-baca-b47a8d32cc6e_372867299"]}, {"text": "The Group will continue expanding production capacity and actively pursue mergers and acquisitions as part of its strategic growth.", "citations": ["04c71ca1-6234-4294-baca-b47a8d32cc6e_372867299"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1026", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "To pursue a job as a forklift driver, you must be at least 18 years old, hold a high school diploma, and obtain a certification card by choosing the right program for your desired job.", "citations": ["642fd5b0-ed80-4d08-8091-c65b63653018_247813657"]}, {"text": "Changing the type of forklift you operate may require additional certification.", "citations": ["642fd5b0-ed80-4d08-8091-c65b63653018_247813657"]}, {"text": "In traditionally male-dominated industries like trucking, women are proving that \"anybody can do it\" and that skill matters more than gender.", "citations": ["86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569"]}, {"text": "A Penske service manager describes how her shop\u2019s culture is results-focused, not gender-focused\u2014if you can do the work, you get the job done.", "citations": ["b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776"]}, {"text": "She enjoys mentoring her male colleagues and demonstrates her expertise by diagnosing and repairing trucks.", "citations": ["b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776"]}, {"text": "Amelia, the technician, often outperforms less experienced male coworkers and is trusted to complete difficult repairs independently.", "citations": ["b4382681-f199-43dc-a190-ef39b5bf9a5d_476864776"]}, {"text": "LUS Fiber has hired its first woman lineworker, showing that barriers are being broken in utility and construction work.", "citations": ["5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769"]}, {"text": "Some female professionals, such as a former Miss England finalist, have left careers like modeling to become lorry drivers, driven by their passion and the desire to challenge gender norms.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "This beauty queen was crowned Miss Charity and inspired by the fact that fewer than one percent of UK HGV drivers are female, finding the evolving industry \"really exciting\" and encouraging other women to join.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Driving tractors on her family farm led her to pursue HGV licenses, seeing it as a progression in her career.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "England rugby star Chantelle Crowl also works as a HGV driver, advising women interested in the field to \"just go for it\" and appreciating the flexibility the job provides.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Domino Homer entered the industry after seeing an advertisement and self-funded her license, saying that it\u2019s important to \"follow your heart\" to find the right career.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Many women in these fields face personal challenges, such as balancing family with demanding training or work schedules, but persevering and support from family help them succeed.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Despite these advances, women make up just 1%-2% of the UK\u2019s HGV driver workforce, but efforts like XPO Logistics\u2019 female driver academy aim to attract more women.", "citations": ["86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569"]}, {"text": "In the maritime and barge industries, leaders like Mike Ellis, ACBL\u2019s CEO, emphasize that increasing diversity is possible and necessary for future growth.", "citations": ["b24091fe-8d0a-4801-b368-2b00c8793fc6_9518928"]}, {"text": "Industry shifts are being supported by new technology, innovation, and a focus on hiring and retaining diverse talent, including women.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Opportunities for women in construction, logistics, and maritime fields are expanding, and while challenges remain, determined women are breaking barriers and excelling in these rewarding careers.", "citations": ["67fbda18-297b-4b52-92d7-bbbebeb2fcdf_400565819"]}, {"text": "Farkhana Safargaleeva, after finishing school, chose to become a crane operator alongside her friend and immediately enjoyed the job.", "citations": ["485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500"]}, {"text": "Her passion for the profession is evident both at work and at home.", "citations": ["485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500"]}, {"text": "Andrey Nekrasov, Chief Engineer at Unity LLP, notes that women are vital in ensuring the uninterrupted production of cement products, with special recognition and appreciation shown to female employees on March 8, International Women\u2019s Day.", "citations": ["485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500"]}, {"text": "The war has impacted the labor market, prompting many Ukrainian women to take up traditionally male professions as they relocate within or outside the country.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "A clear trend shift was observed around summer 2022, with women\u2019s teams showing highly effective performance and a strong inclination toward continuous learning and new opportunities, which they are supported in.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Many leaders are now promoted from within such teams.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Over 4,500 ATB employees have joined the armed forces and related national services, while the company's personnel policies emphasize human resource development.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "There are no restrictions for women who aim to excel and achieve top positions.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Within three years, the number of women in Grade 10+ (management) roles has risen by 60%, thanks to a focused approach.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Elena, after five years working in a quarry, advanced to driving large dump trucks after obtaining the necessary license, supported by a company program allowing for further career progression regardless of gender.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "NLMK recently held a competition to select the best crane operator, which encourages professional skill development, with winners receiving awards and corporate recognition.", "citations": ["ecab6dcb-e837-480d-93de-bd45c3ca82e0_161225094"]}, {"text": "Career advancement is accessible through special courses, continuous skill improvement, and internal company programs, with employers increasingly willing to invest in promising personnel.", "citations": ["d28a5581-c411-4bde-9c3f-8cc53540749c_905240997"]}, {"text": "Employees describe entry into large corporations as possible through both job postings and active self-development, such as through refreshers or Olympics first introduced in 2013.", "citations": ["d28a5581-c411-4bde-9c3f-8cc53540749c_905240997"]}, {"text": "A passion for the job and a clear, conscious career choice are highlighted as the surest path to success.", "citations": ["d28a5581-c411-4bde-9c3f-8cc53540749c_905240997"]}, {"text": "Examples abound of young people deliberately choosing technical and industrial careers, with both men and women rising to leadership roles.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Some, like a former \"Miss England\" finalist, have even become truck drivers, expressing enjoyment at operating large vehicles, while stable, well-paying jobs like turners, boatmen, and heavy machinery drivers are growing in demand.", "citations": ["25d201d5-f76c-4642-bd16-7baab320874f_84795335"]}, {"text": "Women are welcomed in technical roles, with their rapid learning and performance highly valued by employers, as seen at the Ulan-Ude instrument-making association.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Support programs exist to ensure equal access to vocational education and guide students like you toward rewarding, self-sufficient careers in high-demand fields.", "citations": ["1467b308-b176-4196-8a6a-1225eda9f936_731162285"]}, {"text": "I learned to drive a loader and faced ridicule and bullying in order to improve my income and support my husband in paying for my children\u2019s treatment.", "citations": ["08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750"]}, {"text": "My husband supported me, even though the community bullied me for pursuing this work, which motivated me to achieve my goals and provide for my children\u2019s healthcare needs.", "citations": ["08bf5561-f112-47d8-ae82-2041a9b4fc15_17345750"]}, {"text": "Saudi women are driving taxis to supplement their income amid rising prices and increased VAT, with some, like one mother, seeking jobs that fit their qualifications and limited time but finding few suitable opportunities.", "citations": ["7fa62590-35de-4e1b-9dab-8ca030322649_899359489"]}, {"text": "Chauffeur Drive encourages young people, including women, to consider entering this profession.", "citations": ["70bbe2ee-d063-4150-968e-e918835a610e_717318440"]}, {"text": "Women are entering the construction sector to address labor shortages, with some, such as Cerato, being introduced to the industry early but not initially seeing it as a viable path because of the lack of female role models.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Despite frustrations and industry obstacles, women are demonstrating resilience and determination in the face of gender barriers.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Women\u2019s representation in construction trades remains low, at about a third overall and a tenth in sectors like painting and carpentry, but leaders expect this to grow as older workers retire.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Industry voices stress that labor shortages mean opportunities must be made accessible to all, including women.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Wallace, the first in her family to earn a college degree, aims to obtain a contractor\u2019s license and establish a business as a legacy for her family.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "She completed building skills training to repair her rental properties and has managed to work alongside male colleagues, though she experienced tensions and sometimes had to prove herself more than the men.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Some male workers still resist taking instructions from women, reflecting ongoing challenges.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Project engineer Golsby, known as \u201cBecky Nicky,\u201d believes her unique perspective enables her to excel in her job.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Cerato is one of three women among nine managers and the only Latina, highlighting growing diversity in management.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Sara Al Olama of Amazon notes that their workplace supports women, enabling them to feel safe and perform at their best.", "citations": ["a8ce5eea-102c-41df-8836-eb2b473fa2a3_880785842"]}, {"text": "She views initiatives like International Women\u2019s Day as opportunities to rally efforts against discrimination and promote gender equality.", "citations": ["a8ce5eea-102c-41df-8836-eb2b473fa2a3_880785842"]}, {"text": "She says that a dynamic and varied work environment allows her to learn and grow continuously.", "citations": ["a8ce5eea-102c-41df-8836-eb2b473fa2a3_880785842"]}, {"text": "A recent initiative, supported by the Egyptian Ministry of Youth and Sports, DeliveryHero Egypt, the Egyptian Gulf Bank, and Alfi Foundation, is providing training and support to young women, with applicants required to be between 19 and 35 years old.", "citations": ["bab89816-e294-4fc0-9abc-afd183ab5673_500206081"]}, {"text": "Training and development are emphasized, with continued support for drivers to maintain safe and up-to-date licenses.", "citations": ["faba7f97-1c37-4e30-8014-9337f2bcdabe_499331478"]}, {"text": "Organizations in regions such as Aswan are also organizing training programs for people of determination in fields such as mobile maintenance, contributing to broader workforce inclusion.", "citations": ["49860d77-4fdd-4c27-854e-4da06f5cdc16_967191532"]}, {"text": "A growing number of women are entering the construction and maritime industries, breaking long-standing gender barriers and excelling in traditionally male-dominated roles such as crane operation.", "citations": ["05eead2a-2a01-469f-8504-17e7c441add7_858308521"]}, {"text": "Women like crane operator Nirwanaaa have leveraged social media to share their work experiences, inspiring others and reshaping perceptions about gender roles in heavy industry.", "citations": ["05eead2a-2a01-469f-8504-17e7c441add7_858308521"]}, {"text": "Despite her success, the dangers of the job are real, as illustrated by a tragic crane accident involving Nirwanaaa and another worker, prompting an ongoing investigation by authorities.", "citations": ["05eead2a-2a01-469f-8504-17e7c441add7_858308521"]}, {"text": "At the same time, training and recruitment initiatives, like those organized by the Taiwan Power Company and district offices, are supporting more women to become skilled technical workers by providing thorough education, hands-on experience, and worksite exposure.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}, {"text": "The unique strengths women bring, such as attention to detail and thoroughness, are increasingly valued on construction teams, helping to improve work quality and efficiency.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}, {"text": "The industry has seen improvements in workplace safety, fewer fines, and increased hiring of female truck and machinery operators, reflecting a broader shift towards inclusivity.", "citations": ["f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211"]}, {"text": "Role models such as Selagea, who grew up with nine brothers and developed expertise and passion for machinery, demonstrate that women can thrive in these environments and become advocates for safe, high-quality work.", "citations": ["f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211"]}, {"text": "Case studies from related sectors highlight similar progress, such as Fang Fang, a mainland woman who became a successful construction worker and provider for her family, refusing social welfare and instead supporting her children through hard work at construction sites.", "citations": ["c6231990-38bf-49a9-9b45-ba447bc63d9c_68125205"]}, {"text": "Education and technical training programs celebrate the inclusion of female students like Liang Ya-ting, recognizing their capabilities in physical and detail-oriented tasks.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}, {"text": "Industry leaders emphasize that determination, continual learning, and innovation are essential for success, regardless of gender, and stress that anyone with the drive can become skilled and respected in their field.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}, {"text": "Women in construction often express pride in their achievements and optimism about the future, demonstrating resilience in the face of social and professional challenges.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}, {"text": "Success stories are increasingly visible, encouraging more young women to pursue rewarding and well-paid careers in construction, heavy machinery operation, and technical trades.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}, {"text": "As women continue to gain recognition and achieve leadership positions, they are helping drive a cultural shift toward greater gender equality and diversity in construction and related industries.", "citations": ["0cba40be-84c2-4ac7-9c5a-98e16d4699f9_1070461585"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1028", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "LUS Fiber has hired its first woman lineworker, a graduate of the SLCC Power Lineman program.", "citations": ["5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769"]}, {"text": "The new recruit emphasized the importance of not being afraid to take on such roles.", "citations": ["5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769"]}, {"text": "Company leadership believes this recruitment will be crucial for their success and support their expansion efforts.", "citations": ["5db3cd35-e9aa-45e4-92a6-f53a64c446d3_904794769"]}, {"text": "Additionally, a woman has recently been assigned as a Hyva operator.", "citations": ["c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220"]}, {"text": "Executives at TSM, including Subodh Pandey and other HR and operations leaders, congratulated and interacted with the new female recruits.", "citations": ["c0c71277-9cd7-4a17-a7c0-7bea6832abbc_141479220"]}, {"text": "In the UK, women HGV drivers comprise only 1%-2% of the total workforce.", "citations": ["86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569"]}, {"text": "Brown explained that candidates will be employed from day one, allowing them to earn a living while training.", "citations": ["86cbd746-91e5-4583-a65d-05c1f8904f44_169456569"]}, {"text": "Ryder has been recognized as a top company for women in trucking.", "citations": ["63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585"]}, {"text": "Women In Trucking\u2019s 2023 Top Companies for Women to Work For in Transportation includes Ryder in its listings.", "citations": ["63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585"]}, {"text": "The Trucker News Staff provides content covering developments in the trucking industry and is based in Little Rock, Arkansas.", "citations": ["63293454-a4ca-48c4-8a16-eba4dfe87ee5_38683585"]}, {"text": "The gender gap in construction and related sectors is rooted in historical factors.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "Women are breaking barriers in waste management and similar industries.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "Skip Hire Glasgow\u2019s James David believes inclusive hiring practices foster greater female participation.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "Construction sites remain predominantly male environments, and language such as \u2018foreman\u2019 persists over more inclusive terms like \u2018foreperson.\u2019  \nTools such as the Heavy Equipment Operator Job Application Form Template help categorize, organize, and track candidates efficiently.", "citations": ["46326561-3540-413e-abf8-efea2dea58ef_79594562"]}, {"text": "Industries traditionally led by men are actively seeking to recruit more women to balance their workforces.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Many women are drawn to driving and heavy equipment operation through personal interest.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Some women express they never considered such work unusual despite being the only female on a team, and supportive environments helped them adapt.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "With time and experience, women in these roles have grown more skilled and confident.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Women in this field sometimes face skepticism from family and deal with the challenges of balancing work and motherhood.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Work schedules can be demanding, with early starts and long hours required for logistics and transport roles.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Female workers often express internal conflicts about time away from home but remain dedicated to both family and career.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "The work itself can be stressful and at times intimidating, especially for newcomers.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Some male colleagues perceive women as a threat to their positions, and workplace biases persist, including doubts about women's capabilities due to physical attributes.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Women leaders advise standing firm and speaking up when faced with resistance.", "citations": ["14193eea-fdc7-4148-bbfe-1de87c1dd491_114152281"]}, {"text": "Among women in construction, there is a drive to break outdated stereotypes and inspire future generations.", "citations": ["18936b99-e516-4cca-b846-d29e85b6c832_522368479"]}, {"text": "Women in the industry often report high job satisfaction and are eager to share their experiences in educational outreach to encourage more women to join.", "citations": ["37e0b781-4c2a-44c1-bed6-e2c232792ed9_107068371"]}, {"text": "After the start of Russia\u2019s full-scale invasion of Ukraine, more Ukrainian women began mastering traditionally \u201cmale\u201d professions.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Meest has established all-women teams in positions historically held by men.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "During the war, a woman who was previously an operator became the head of a regional branch, successfully taking on her new responsibilities.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "As of now, over 56,000 Ukrainians work at ATB enterprises, with women making up 67% of these employees.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "In 2022, women held 21% of leadership positions at ATB, with the company targeting 25% by 2030.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Elena accepted a job as a BelAZ driver without prior experience, showing women\u2019s increasing entry into new roles.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "The company offers a male leave program, enabling women to continue advancing in their careers.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Some women report missing their jobs during leave, illustrating their dedication.", "citations": ["65fbc85d-e429-4d5a-9efc-ced8faf79161_540514178"]}, {"text": "Women are increasingly seen in \u201cmale\u201d occupations and their commitment extends from the workplace to the home.", "citations": ["485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500"]}, {"text": "Andrey Nekrasov, Chief Engineer at Unity LLP, has been involved in the industry for 16 years, ensuring operations like cement supply do not stop.", "citations": ["485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500"]}, {"text": "At the Novolipetsk plant, a professional crane operator competition crowned Tatiana Shepel as \u201cBest in Profession.\u201d  \nKyivstar\u2019s new program continues the \u201cReturn\u201d project, combating employer bias against certain candidates since August 2023.", "citations": ["ecab6dcb-e837-480d-93de-bd45c3ca82e0_161225094"]}, {"text": "New approaches are needed to fill vacancies, and optimism remains that these challenges will be overcome.", "citations": ["fa56b545-7fd4-4147-9905-8c732476766f_209728494"]}, {"text": "The Ukrainian conflict has forced Russian road workers to find new equipment suppliers, contributing to the industry\u2019s broader challenges.", "citations": ["2406d9ef-c39f-4cad-9bdd-a8ebb6261f3e_256394840"]}, {"text": "The industry faces significant structural problems, with no clear solutions proposed yet.", "citations": ["2406d9ef-c39f-4cad-9bdd-a8ebb6261f3e_256394840"]}, {"text": "Some traditional attitudes remain, with safety occasionally overlooked to maintain construction pace.", "citations": ["ceaf266f-5aee-48a1-a4e1-408211015c04_1051027062"]}, {"text": "Women operators sometimes face conditions such as excessive heat on cranes and threats from management for voicing concerns.", "citations": ["ceaf266f-5aee-48a1-a4e1-408211015c04_1051027062"]}, {"text": "Employers offer incentives such as higher pay for evening or night work and referral bonuses for recruiting new staff.", "citations": ["3be9e882-d2dd-4c21-8670-275d4f80e4ea_34039022"]}, {"text": "Some women have transitioned from jobs like sales assistant to well-paid technical positions.", "citations": ["485cdc95-bbf9-4578-9b0d-47d964d3e7aa_207874500"]}, {"text": "Securing vacation can still be problematic, but employers are open to hiring anyone willing to meet expectations and work hard.", "citations": ["715ac48a-c2b6-4220-ba56-bebfa9774221_467192047"]}, {"text": "There is a high demand for bus drivers, especially women.", "citations": ["715ac48a-c2b6-4220-ba56-bebfa9774221_467192047"]}, {"text": "Efforts are underway to create unique training opportunities for youth in Lipetsk.", "citations": ["715ac48a-c2b6-4220-ba56-bebfa9774221_467192047"]}, {"text": "Training programs range from basic safety briefings to intensive courses that allow workers to quickly master new skills and secure jobs in plants.", "citations": ["f994b156-a035-471b-8386-47bc657252d3_659212610"]}, {"text": "Managers oversee and decide on employee training needs, often collaborating with external organizations for specialized instruction.", "citations": ["f994b156-a035-471b-8386-47bc657252d3_659212610"]}, {"text": "Russia, including St. Petersburg, reports shortages of such skilled workers and takes pride in their teams\u2019 makeup.", "citations": ["f994b156-a035-471b-8386-47bc657252d3_659212610"]}, {"text": "Choosing award winners is difficult, given the quality of female staff.", "citations": ["95912b2a-fc3d-44b5-b59c-96487fff62c8_374871868"]}, {"text": "Several women have been recognized as contest winners, with one becoming deputy chief mechanic at a mine.", "citations": ["95912b2a-fc3d-44b5-b59c-96487fff62c8_374871868"]}, {"text": "Norilsk Nickel received thanks from employees for offering growth opportunities, including the prestigious \u201cProject of the Year\u201d award.", "citations": ["95912b2a-fc3d-44b5-b59c-96487fff62c8_374871868"]}, {"text": "The jury found it challenging to select among the deserving female candidates, highlighting their competence and contribution.", "citations": ["95912b2a-fc3d-44b5-b59c-96487fff62c8_374871868"]}, {"text": "About a third of construction workers in the United States are Hispanic, according to BLS.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "With many veteran workers retiring, the industry recognizes it cannot afford to leave any doors closed.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Some women in construction aspire to earn a general contractor\u2019s license to manage their own projects and businesses.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Goodwill\u2019s construction skills training program, though not targeting women specifically, saw 15 women complete training last year, with about half securing industry jobs.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Wallace, who is the first in her family to earn a college degree, views attaining a contractor\u2019s license as a path to generational wealth for her family.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "She wants to tell her family that their legacy includes new opportunities in the construction sector.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Jenny Parker, a construction worker in North Carolina, expressed her passion for her work, enjoying both its challenges and rewards.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Parker joined building skills training to be able to repair her own rental properties.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Cerato is one of three women managers on her nine-person team, and the only Latina represented.", "citations": ["589ca671-5a89-4831-abc9-9f0a59aeb2b9_935642743"]}, {"text": "Kyolis MHI, operator of Dubai Metro and Tram, celebrated consecutive NAFES Awards for Emiratisation Excellence, demonstrating a commitment to equal opportunities for men and women.", "citations": ["5198c43d-87c7-447c-a030-e5c2f524a182_994286239"]}, {"text": "The UAE promoted gender equality in the successful delivery of Expo 2020 Dubai, from bidding to execution and management.", "citations": ["7dbb0769-902d-45ce-bb13-4592f05ddfab_68172209"]}, {"text": "Emirati women played key roles in Expo 2020, including leadership and major organizational tasks.", "citations": ["7dbb0769-902d-45ce-bb13-4592f05ddfab_68172209"]}, {"text": "The Women\u2019s Pavilion at Expo 2020 was significant for highlighting local and international contributions of Emirati women.", "citations": ["7dbb0769-902d-45ce-bb13-4592f05ddfab_68172209"]}, {"text": "For some, like Nauf Omar, being part of Expo 2020 fulfilled long-standing ambitions for involvement in major national events.", "citations": ["7dbb0769-902d-45ce-bb13-4592f05ddfab_68172209"]}, {"text": "Sara Al Olama notes that workplaces like Amazon foster supportive environments for women to feel secure and perform their best.", "citations": ["a8ce5eea-102c-41df-8836-eb2b473fa2a3_880785842"]}, {"text": "Across industries, a lack of gender diversity persists, with women often not given equal opportunities as men.", "citations": ["d6f64bc3-ed88-4790-a97a-31dd54adab52_742053242"]}, {"text": "Mentoring schemes are proposed as a strategy to help women advance in fields like aviation and aerospace.", "citations": ["d6f64bc3-ed88-4790-a97a-31dd54adab52_742053242"]}, {"text": "Such initiatives recruit talented female candidates and help cultivate diverse, attractive work environments.", "citations": ["d6f64bc3-ed88-4790-a97a-31dd54adab52_742053242"]}, {"text": "The \u201cYour Equipment is Your Company\u201d initiative trains women and men alike for labor market readiness, including machinery operation and maintenance.", "citations": ["c0401757-b668-4870-bfc8-b9a571eeb2a2_238164643"]}, {"text": "Engaging men as allies is identified as an important factor in the push for workplace gender equality.", "citations": ["06304ee5-888b-42bd-a686-6e7c1f92cfb3_615559939"]}, {"text": "A perception remains in some management levels that women are promoted by gender rather than ability, as seen in comments from some women leaders.", "citations": ["06304ee5-888b-42bd-a686-6e7c1f92cfb3_615559939"]}, {"text": "The mining sector has made notable gender equality progress in the last decade.", "citations": ["06304ee5-888b-42bd-a686-6e7c1f92cfb3_615559939"]}, {"text": "The industry is shifting focus from physical strength to a broader skillset, expanding opportunities for women.", "citations": ["d6f64bc3-ed88-4790-a97a-31dd54adab52_742053242"]}, {"text": "Rio Tinto now partially links executive pay to gender diversity performance and regularly reviews progress.", "citations": ["06304ee5-888b-42bd-a686-6e7c1f92cfb3_615559939"]}, {"text": "Women in leadership are encouraged to actively support diversity within their organizations.", "citations": ["d6f64bc3-ed88-4790-a97a-31dd54adab52_742053242"]}, {"text": "Training initiatives, such as \u201cYour Stomach is Your Company,\u201d have provided hands-on equipment training, including for operating wheel loaders.", "citations": ["11ab6d68-4519-4f35-a03c-b936a76014bc_273648372"]}, {"text": "Companies like Aramco Drilling now offer jobs inclusive of mechanical knowledge for equipment operation and maintenance.", "citations": ["19b5e363-b50e-40c3-baa1-e8a97abe925c_573337943"]}, {"text": "These collective efforts across construction, mining, maritime, and transportation industries highlight a growing shift toward gender diversity and equal opportunity for women in traditionally male-dominated fields.", "citations": ["5198c43d-87c7-447c-a030-e5c2f524a182_994286239"]}, {"text": "Fewer fines and accidents have been observed as more female truck drivers join the workforce, with the number of female drivers increasing by 80% over the past 20 years.", "citations": ["f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211"]}, {"text": "Selagea, who grew up with nine brothers and developed a love for cars, emphasizes maintaining her vehicle and encourages her colleagues to do the same.", "citations": ["f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211"]}, {"text": "Studies indicate that women tend to avoid risk and focus more on safety compared to men.", "citations": ["f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211"]}, {"text": "Cornilla Johnson, training to drive a Class A vehicle, highlights the importance of confidence in this field.", "citations": ["f8c8c06e-76b0-48f9-a66b-758fd08d0ac4_246084211"]}, {"text": "In Cixi City, key food-producing areas see pride in local contributions, with significant savings achieved in less than a year.", "citations": ["fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432"]}, {"text": "Operating a tower crane is challenging, but employees like Li Rui express pride in their work and improved working conditions.", "citations": ["fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432"]}, {"text": "Village leaders taking over roles emphasize learning from predecessors, seeking community input, and leveraging local advantages for greater industrial competitiveness.", "citations": ["fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432"]}, {"text": "Green development and partnership with factories are raising local product quality and prices, while initiatives transform tea gardens into productive parks.", "citations": ["fa814205-0346-442b-87c5-93059583ffff_953125432"]}, {"text": "As labor shortages in heavy industry increase, more women are filling roles traditionally held by men, supported by inclusive recruitment efforts.", "citations": ["4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_966556193"]}, {"text": "Job advertisements now welcome both men and women, acknowledging demographic changes and the need for gender diversity.", "citations": ["4c0ee3ad-3947-4c32-9bdc-e1ea45fa3dd9_966556193"]}, {"text": "Fangfang, a divorced woman raising two children, exemplifies the resilience of women in construction, working long hours despite health challenges, and striving to support her family independently.", "citations": ["c6231990-38bf-49a9-9b45-ba447bc63d9c_68125205"]}, {"text": "Her children appreciate her dedication, and she dreams of retiring in her hometown after they complete their education.", "citations": ["c6231990-38bf-49a9-9b45-ba447bc63d9c_68125205"]}, {"text": "Female engineers are also breaking barriers, such as Rita, who inspects gas pipelines in difficult conditions, gaining recognition and fulfillment at work.", "citations": ["a649b74c-2941-44e3-b2f0-cc97e83dfcb2_338229102"]}, {"text": "Women in engineering continue to develop professionally, seeking further education and balancing career with family life.", "citations": ["a649b74c-2941-44e3-b2f0-cc97e83dfcb2_338229102"]}, {"text": "Stories like \"Don't Look at the Little Woman\" showcase women entering construction, receiving significant salary increases, and demonstrating confidence despite hardships.", "citations": ["a1be80ed-4400-42bf-80df-4ed20d0e8cf9_321528602"]}, {"text": "Employment incentives and training programs are available to encourage women and those unemployed to pursue careers in these industries.", "citations": ["a1be80ed-4400-42bf-80df-4ed20d0e8cf9_321528602"]}, {"text": "The construction and maritime sectors have faced significant crew shortages due to recent global events, prompting new memoranda and cooperation efforts to address workforce needs.", "citations": ["9c24efaf-a8f6-45e5-abd7-7fc1892c4a52_969426854"]}, {"text": "Governments and ministries are actively promoting job redesign to create more inclusive and friendly workplaces, supporting both younger and middle-aged talent.", "citations": ["2e7708a3-785b-4bc9-aad7-3242ad203d46_418071283"]}, {"text": "Specialized training programs and financial support for professional development, such as the New Pioneer Program, further help women and other underrepresented groups enter and thrive in heavy industry roles.", "citations": ["061641d6-49c2-4b0c-ac1e-001c86b80a9e_89871675"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1030", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Science has traditionally been managed by the scientific and academic community, but literature provides a way to challenge and expand our visions for the future.", "citations": ["7367a183-7d54-48bb-aae9-3e7eb3267494_824661048"]}, {"text": "Fantasy author N.K.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "Jemisin emphasizes the role of speculative fiction in helping us imagine alternative societies and futures, encouraging readers to question and recreate the structures shaping our real world.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "Jemisin notes that our current world is not arbitrary, but a result of deliberate choices, and resisting inertia requires questioning how society developed and how it might be redesigned.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "Her literary approach balances personal goals and audience expectations, inspiring others to question reality.", "citations": ["dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587"]}, {"text": "Science fiction and speculative stories provide both escape and a lens to view and understand real-world issues, challenging the notion that escapism is a lesser form of literature.", "citations": ["dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587"]}, {"text": "Fiction allows people to reimagine worlds, as seen in works like Jeff VanderMeer's \"Borne,\" which blends the personal and the speculative in ways that change readers.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "There are now diverse venues, such as kh\u014dr\u00e9\u014d magazine, supporting new speculative works from varied perspectives.", "citations": ["b189e16e-b1b0-4531-898b-22bc44ca457e_717111571"]}, {"text": "The evolution of science fiction is visible through milestone works that garner major awards, such as those by women authors, which have often disrupted male-dominated traditions within publishing.", "citations": ["01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677"]}, {"text": "Themes of boundaries and societal differences remain central, illustrated by stories exploring walls and quarantines, as well as different realities depending on perspective.", "citations": ["e0d0eaca-aa98-46fb-ab70-0f03363ebcea_816797857"]}, {"text": "Fiction is increasingly seen as a critical tool for understanding complex societal and ethical problems, with some writers drawing inspiration from both religious and scientific thought.", "citations": ["dc3c3b72-0d32-4b24-827d-e46b2f82f7cd_304953587"]}, {"text": "Authors like Wang Jinkang express that science fiction\u2019s scope, dealing in millennia, is distinct from current technological trends but remains committed to exploring evolving relationships with nature, society, and morality.", "citations": ["ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341"]}, {"text": "The future of science fiction is expected to bring even more mature reflections on the environment, society, and ethics, highlighting both human limitations and potential.", "citations": ["ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341"]}, {"text": "The genre\u2019s relationship with its readers is mutually enriching, energizing both authors and audiences.", "citations": ["ac3a1030-35ca-4592-9ac0-7de59165a212_979870341"]}, {"text": "Influential titles within the traditional science fiction canon include \"The War of the Worlds\" by H.G.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Wells, \"Rendezvous with Rama\" by Arthur C. Clarke, \"I, Robot\" by Isaac Asimov, and \"The Left Hand of Darkness\" by Ursula K. Le Guin.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Contemporary and underrepresented voices\u2014including women and people of color\u2014have increasingly shaped science fiction, earning major awards, and offering expanded visions through works like N.K.", "citations": ["01c44cda-9c26-4674-815e-de91cca921c4_209737677"]}, {"text": "Jemisin\u2019s and others featured in indie publishing and specialty magazines.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Classic and present-day science fiction continually interrogates what it means to imagine and inhabit new realities, urging readers to engage critically while offering hope for change.", "citations": ["8dffe6e3-b2e0-4574-97ae-d3a72b383e10_533797018"]}, {"text": "Her heroes have a lot of problems, ranging from issues with children to the pursuit of happiness.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "The story explores how an entire family learns to reconnect and live together again.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "Fifteen years is portrayed as an age when one is no longer a child but not yet an adult.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "At a significant turning point, some characters do not return as expected.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "\"The Universe Beyond War\" depicts an ideal world where people escape from a reality marked by armed conflict, a world to which Manny and Will retreat.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "Stories such as \"Scary Stories for Little Foxes\" captivate young audiences.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "Magazines are made available in print each month and in a digital PDF format in readers' accounts.", "citations": ["1fd604e6-30ba-4b91-b53c-ecb5241f2624_106570215"]}, {"text": "Literary works can simultaneously function as detailed studies of their subjects.", "citations": ["917832ce-e6f3-4d76-b4c1-a6d93b486106_200590758"]}, {"text": "Some concepts in stories, such as the \"black box,\" require deeper explanation to understand serious underlying reasons.", "citations": ["917832ce-e6f3-4d76-b4c1-a6d93b486106_200590758"]}, {"text": "Attempts to challenge certain ideas in these works often prove predetermined and ineffective.", "citations": ["917832ce-e6f3-4d76-b4c1-a6d93b486106_200590758"]}, {"text": "A fitting comparison is the well-known phrase from \"A Thousand and One Nights\": \u201cBut at the end of this story we will know more than we do now.\u201d  \nRecent media news shares that the star of \"The Mummy\" will lead in a new Zack Snyder film.", "citations": ["d5e05db7-d232-453f-939b-37899f9114f6_535062721"]}, {"text": "Coverage also includes stories of the creation of life on Earth and reviews of Lukyanenko\u2019s new novel among recommended September books.", "citations": ["f04b6a14-434e-4539-8111-c4182598b61b_789470092"]}, {"text": "Characters such as Max, who is described as a surfer, play central roles.", "citations": ["f04b6a14-434e-4539-8111-c4182598b61b_789470092"]}, {"text": "Certain storylines reveal settings where ships act as traps for unsuspecting people.", "citations": ["f04b6a14-434e-4539-8111-c4182598b61b_789470092"]}, {"text": "Authors have shared personal anecdotes about their initial reputations, with some being labeled as children's writers.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Often, stories expand in volume, evolving from short tales to novel-length narratives.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "These works may be difficult to categorize\u2014either as lengthy stories or short novels.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Serial publication was common, with works like \"War and Peace\" originally printed in parts.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Authors frequently generate many ideas over time, not all of which are pursued.", "citations": ["481fdf30-f5c1-448c-a60d-37d82fe50d15_1055014405"]}, {"text": "Some books come with musical accompaniments.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "While some stories appear suited for children, their content transcends simplistic categorization.", "citations": ["481fdf30-f5c1-448c-a60d-37d82fe50d15_1055014405"]}, {"text": "Readers sometimes struggle to find relatable characters within these narratives.", "citations": ["481fdf30-f5c1-448c-a60d-37d82fe50d15_1055014405"]}, {"text": "Characters are often shaped by learned behaviors, but are not one-dimensional.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Authors stress the importance of maintaining truthful narratives, even in fiction.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Writers aim to capture significant moments of their era in their work.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Themes of family, culture, and missed opportunities are evident, such as a character\u2019s regret over not speaking Tatar.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Several authors began their careers as poets before turning to fiction.", "citations": ["7b0affba-b2a2-4fb3-9d52-dd7a7831de9f_1060222361"]}, {"text": "Creative processes often involve collaboration or shared experiences with family members.", "citations": ["4d7c95ff-1156-45ee-b093-351ba239e399_711682467"]}, {"text": "Authors describe sudden moments of inspiration as emotional and almost physical experiences.", "citations": ["c56936f1-0df8-47fb-ae17-9a6f8c812366_267589495"]}, {"text": "Writing and editing are iterative processes that reveal the work\u2019s full nature only upon completion.", "citations": ["7b0affba-b2a2-4fb3-9d52-dd7a7831de9f_1060222361"]}, {"text": "Some writers are adept at choosing unique names for their characters and stories.", "citations": ["7b0affba-b2a2-4fb3-9d52-dd7a7831de9f_1060222361"]}, {"text": "Many works begin as collections of short stories before evolving into full-fledged novels.", "citations": ["b83a4712-8f33-4686-bba4-875a2034a7ba_679320320"]}, {"text": "Some books are intended as gifts for children, highlighting their popularity.", "citations": ["481fdf30-f5c1-448c-a60d-37d82fe50d15_1055014405"]}, {"text": "Space exploration emerges as a recurring theme\u2014where better to imagine the future than in space, a domain where \u201cwe were the first.\u201d  \nSuch stories contribute to building a foundation for societal progress.", "citations": ["4d7c95ff-1156-45ee-b093-351ba239e399_711682467"]}, {"text": "Discussions include government emphasis on space projects, such as Russia\u2019s plans regarding the Moon and Mars.", "citations": ["4d7c95ff-1156-45ee-b093-351ba239e399_711682467"]}, {"text": "Educational interventions like reintroducing astronomy and cosmonautics in schools are suggested.", "citations": ["4d7c95ff-1156-45ee-b093-351ba239e399_711682467"]}, {"text": "Commemoration and celebration of space achievements are encouraged through monuments, festivals, and World Space Week.", "citations": ["4d7c95ff-1156-45ee-b093-351ba239e399_711682467"]}, {"text": "Overall, technology is credited with turning reading into an immersive journey through the facts and events of literary works.", "citations": ["c56936f1-0df8-47fb-ae17-9a6f8c812366_267589495"]}, {"text": "The evolution of science fiction literature has been influenced by both anticipated projects and unexpected developments, emphasizing the importance of reader engagement and learning.", "citations": ["5ec6eede-455a-4325-a5fe-3b403a96cbf8_768801043"]}, {"text": "Authors like Robert Gilmar in \"Alice in Quantum Country\" and Dan Brown in novels such as \"The Lost Symbol\" and \"The Origin\" have introduced complex scientific concepts like quantum mechanics and particle physics to their readers, making these ideas more accessible and enjoyable.", "citations": ["5ec6eede-455a-4325-a5fe-3b403a96cbf8_768801043"]}, {"text": "Works such as \"The Gods of the Universe\" by Dos Santos explore advanced topics like the Big Bang and string theory within engaging narratives, blending educational content with storytelling.", "citations": ["5ec6eede-455a-4325-a5fe-3b403a96cbf8_768801043"]}, {"text": "Science fiction is increasingly valued for providing fun and learning opportunities, with the aspiration that its popularity continues to grow in Arab societies among both specialists and general readers.", "citations": ["5ec6eede-455a-4325-a5fe-3b403a96cbf8_768801043"]}, {"text": "Arabic science fiction, exemplified by Ahmed Khaled Tawfik\u2019s \"In the Rat Corridor\" (2016), contributes distinct voices and settings, telling stories of survivors with erased memories in utopian worlds that challenge perceptions of reality.", "citations": ["babbd892-aaae-47c2-814d-61139b3086eb_802108510"]}, {"text": "Traditional science fiction roots can be traced to early works such as H.G.", "citations": ["5ec6eede-455a-4325-a5fe-3b403a96cbf8_768801043"]}, {"text": "Wells\u2019 \"The Time Machine\" and Jules Verne\u2019s \"From the Earth to the Moon,\" which helped establish the genre\u2019s focus on speculative futures and technological possibilities.", "citations": ["babbd892-aaae-47c2-814d-61139b3086eb_802108510"]}, {"text": "Writers may not always begin with scientific knowledge, as noted by Mabkhout, but often initiate their works based on personal reading experiences and imagination, suggesting a literary approach less constrained by science and more inspired by creativity.", "citations": ["ed522c2d-3c26-4c25-9162-0e48498f925d_110886793"]}, {"text": "Imagination, especially from childhood, plays a fundamental role in creating and engaging with science fiction, allowing both writers and readers to navigate between real and imagined worlds.", "citations": ["38ffa04e-a82a-4750-aa77-a9f80db41c13_166239881"]}, {"text": "Some Arabic writers, like Dr. Khaled Rami, weave philosophical and emotional dimensions into their fiction, exploring concepts such as love as a cosmic force, showing the genre's capacity to address both scientific and existential questions.", "citations": ["764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305"]}, {"text": "Science fiction narratives frequently use dramatic action to provoke reflection on life and destiny, encouraging readers to question and reconsider their own futures as well as those envisioned in the story.", "citations": ["8b0ef215-1d52-43a4-9ba0-15215b7f661c_150233956"]}, {"text": "Contemporary Arabic science fiction explores not only global scientific themes but also local cultural and philosophical ideas, as seen in works addressing issues like future food scarcity and the impact of science on human happiness.", "citations": ["764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305"]}, {"text": "The growing recognition of science fiction is evident in events such as the Jeddah Book Fair, reflecting greater institutional support for the genre and encouraging new voices and stories to emerge.", "citations": ["5ec6eede-455a-4325-a5fe-3b403a96cbf8_768801043"]}, {"text": "This development shows how science fiction has expanded beyond its initial Western canon to include contemporary and underrepresented perspectives, enriching the genre\u2019s global tapestry.", "citations": ["764901a5-ae9e-4bb0-be99-00e9fcaa1a8b_389925305"]}, {"text": "The evolution of science fiction in literature is tied closely to societal and historical changes, and can only sometimes be analyzed fully after events have played out.", "citations": ["b3bd4ee8-ae18-493f-8b92-1f5fb04ff729_1059626783"]}, {"text": "Science fiction has explored a wide range of subjects, from bacteria to insects, mold, and emerging new life in imagined locations such as a rebuilt post-destruction Ethiopia.", "citations": ["b3bd4ee8-ae18-493f-8b92-1f5fb04ff729_1059626783"]}, {"text": "The structure and content of science fiction works are often shaped by editorial decisions, resulting in variations within stories and influencing how narratives unfold.", "citations": ["b3bd4ee8-ae18-493f-8b92-1f5fb04ff729_1059626783"]}, {"text": "Quality content is fundamental to popular science writing, and sharing these works broadens their audience.", "citations": ["6a9c11c3-c3aa-4b51-a7dc-6aeb781217fc_732628314"]}, {"text": "Mary Shelley's \"Frankenstein\" (1818) exemplifies the use of a framing narrative while tackling deep themes like human desire, the act of creation, life and death, and is centered around a love story connected to the author herself.", "citations": ["774699db-8b63-4839-8211-2760098d90ac_1033840002"]}, {"text": "Classic literature such as China's \"History of Sima Qian\" weaves together literature and history, while \"Journey to the West\" integrates Buddhism and \"Dream of the Red Chamber\" delves into psychology.", "citations": ["a2ca7791-1c7d-4c90-ac1b-aa7bac0b2942_144098081"]}, {"text": "Orwell\u2019s \"Animal Farm\" represents the intersection of literature and politics, showing how science fiction and related genres comment on society, governance, and ideology.", "citations": ["a2ca7791-1c7d-4c90-ac1b-aa7bac0b2942_144098081"]}, {"text": "Notable authors such as J. G. Ballard have contributed to the field, though accessing some of these classic works can be challenging today.", "citations": ["313a3381-4790-45a2-8734-d595fd2ee46a_38674691"]}, {"text": "Writers like Du Jian have blended novelistic prose with traditional forms, while contemporary voices such as Liu Yukun show that science fiction can reflect on human nature across time and space and not only look to the future but also re-examine the past.", "citations": ["313a3381-4790-45a2-8734-d595fd2ee46a_38674691"]}, {"text": "Despite the popularity of some contemporary science fiction, such as \"Three Body,\" Chinese science fiction literature remains on the margins with relatively few works being published each year.", "citations": ["495a3813-6b54-48f9-a9d3-18b74a1a72df_1056649424"]}, {"text": "Science fiction as a genre can provide open-ended spaces for interpretation, allowing readers to bring their own perspectives and aesthetic experiences to a story.", "citations": ["18530c71-a38a-4159-aade-be07bf42e52a_777365209"]}, {"text": "Technology has impacted both the content and the distribution of science fiction, as well as the ways authors and readers connect.", "citations": ["18530c71-a38a-4159-aade-be07bf42e52a_777365209"]}, {"text": "Themes in science fiction are not limited to traditional topics but also cross into music, poetry, memory, psychology, and the everyday life experience.", "citations": ["925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162"]}, {"text": "Science fiction\u2019s evolution from the time of H.G.", "citations": ["18530c71-a38a-4159-aade-be07bf42e52a_777365209"]}, {"text": "Wells to the present includes greater diversity, with new perspectives emerging from women authors, people of color, and writers across cultures such as Taiwan and Hong Kong, who address both local memories and universal concerns.", "citations": ["925467ab-7e77-4a0f-b127-d20919e07315_817963162"]}, {"text": "Science fiction continues to change as writers draw on a range of knowledge and experiences, crossing genres and reflecting diverse realities.", "citations": ["18530c71-a38a-4159-aade-be07bf42e52a_777365209"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1032", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Kenyan students are set to benefit from a Sh33 billion Mastercard digital scheme aimed at advancing education and digital skills.", "citations": ["6510e519-38cf-4427-8eaa-be83653c75d7_197203581"]}, {"text": "Foreign investment in Africa is increasingly targeting education, digital infrastructure, and workforce development, recognizing the continent's vast untapped talent.", "citations": ["c2baacaf-1ba7-4969-905f-2e96f5b34a99_259689578"]}, {"text": "Special Economic Zones (SEZs) are highlighted as a promising path for accelerating wealth creation and supporting companies like Andela in harnessing Africa's talent.", "citations": ["c2baacaf-1ba7-4969-905f-2e96f5b34a99_259689578"]}, {"text": "Access to Africa\u2019s skilled workforce is attracting global businesses, who are using Africa Employer of Record (EOR) services to simplify market entry and employment management, reducing administrative burdens and risks.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "Future trends in Africa EOR services include increased automation, AI integration in HR, continuous labor law updates, and rising demand for flexible, scalable solutions for remote work and expansion.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "EU Business School has partnered with the African Enterprise and Entrepreneurship Institute, launching an Elite Successors\u2019 Programme to foster leadership and entrepreneurship.", "citations": ["8f1583b6-d0af-402d-8b04-797b510ad829_329178083"]}, {"text": "African business leaders and angel investors, including members of the Africa Business Angel Network (ABAN), play a substantial role in growing local companies and jobs through investment partnerships.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "Partnerships between African educational institutions and foreign investors facilitate knowledge transfer and equipment provision, enhancing capacity and modernization.", "citations": ["8f1583b6-d0af-402d-8b04-797b510ad829_329178083"]}, {"text": "Significant digital infrastructure projects, such as Rwanda\u2019s plan to connect 3,000 schools to the internet with financing from China Exim Bank and the World Bank, showcase foreign capital driving connectivity.", "citations": ["686edda9-78de-4837-95c2-026183b21cbd_878587742"]}, {"text": "Adoption of new technologies, such as Kenya's planned ban on non-IPv6 devices, demonstrates efforts to modernize and align with global standards, although technology uptake can be slow.", "citations": ["686edda9-78de-4837-95c2-026183b21cbd_878587742"]}, {"text": "International companies like Mastercard, ride-hailing firm Bolt (which recently pledged $530 million to create jobs in Africa), and e-commerce platform Jumia are making major investments and expanding operations.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "African entities are actively forming partnerships with global businesses and financial institutions to support initiative financing, digitalization, and youth employment opportunities.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "Emerging sectors for foreign investment include education, financial technology, digital payments, e-commerce, and advanced connectivity, with both public and private entities involved.", "citations": ["69d1d87e-4e50-4cd3-b89c-1a5f23bb8c67_315197268"]}, {"text": "Technology transfer and local capacity building are recognized as essential to unlocking employment for African youths and fostering sustainable economic growth.", "citations": ["08c71a3b-8df7-4914-bf64-4b617a2a7d1f_984908377"]}, {"text": "Experts from Russia and Africa recently discussed economic prospects, highlighting the need to intensify cooperation in agriculture, energy, and investment.", "citations": ["7a17ba0c-e9f0-4bcc-9c3f-3a4abc36fe09_133122821"]}, {"text": "Export of Russian IT services to Africa is growing, supported by a demographic where nearly 40% of Africa\u2019s population is under 15 years old.", "citations": ["7a17ba0c-e9f0-4bcc-9c3f-3a4abc36fe09_133122821"]}, {"text": "Proposals such as a forum by NSU aim to promote Russian education in Africa, a field where Russia competes with the United States and France.", "citations": ["24f6431e-67b2-4f48-a838-9afa3aabb257_292778230"]}, {"text": "While Russia offers some courses in English and French, most programs of interest to African students remain in Russian.", "citations": ["24f6431e-67b2-4f48-a838-9afa3aabb257_292778230"]}, {"text": "African student enrollment in Russian universities has grown from about a hundred to over three thousand in recent years.", "citations": ["06ca6832-0181-41d6-b973-4e39a413fb83_514659732"]}, {"text": "Participants at the 20th Valdai International Discussion Club observed that in twenty years, Africa could reach the global economic prominence that China and India have today.", "citations": ["06ca6832-0181-41d6-b973-4e39a413fb83_514659732"]}, {"text": "Russia is increasingly prioritizing economic and educational relations with African countries such as Burkina Faso, Mali, and Guinea, signifying a broader multipolar approach.", "citations": ["06ca6832-0181-41d6-b973-4e39a413fb83_514659732"]}, {"text": "African representatives have expressed disappointment with Western policies, emphasizing that mutually beneficial partnerships\u2014where Africa contributes resources and foreign partners offer technology\u2014are essential.", "citations": ["06ca6832-0181-41d6-b973-4e39a413fb83_514659732"]}, {"text": "An agreement on mutual recognition of education has been finalized between Russia and Eritrea, while a Russian language center is set to open in Zimbabwe to support educational collaboration.", "citations": ["f0ada01f-93a4-4354-beb0-7739908dc43b_743849996"]}, {"text": "The Crimea experience is cited by Russian experts as a model for improving political and economic ties with Africa.", "citations": ["5a0df537-e0e9-469d-9e38-3395662f82b6_380222398"]}, {"text": "Developments are not limited to Russia; India is building a solar power plant in Mozambique, boosting renewable energy for southern Africa and seeking African cooperation to enhance India's global status, all while striving to compete with China.", "citations": ["30055377-6c1c-4635-b786-9ff62454f99d_148790140"]}, {"text": "Russia\u2019s President Putin plans to announce new Moscow-led initiatives at upcoming summits to strengthen international relations with Africa.", "citations": ["13d1bd4e-634e-4d6a-8b5c-40f8e3f044ee_200416150"]}, {"text": "PhosAgro, a Russian company, has launched a digital education platform targeting African farmers to support agricultural development.", "citations": ["aa197380-a5f2-4f60-a171-99a76f3768aa_205986269"]}, {"text": "The Second Russia-Africa Summit and Economic and Humanitarian Forum was held July 27-28 in St. Petersburg, featuring wide-ranging discussions and initiatives to deepen Africa\u2019s foreign partnerships.", "citations": ["aa197380-a5f2-4f60-a171-99a76f3768aa_205986269"]}, {"text": "The university offers several master\u2019s programs and full scholarships, aiming to promote women\u2019s participation by attracting experts from Europe and beyond.", "citations": ["7ca6d9cb-5d45-4887-9d96-2874dec58951_966327693"]}, {"text": "The initiative is designed to support businesses led or managed by women and to finance projects that boost female employment.", "citations": ["16d2cf88-7e63-4c3c-9a4c-76a1e6e9b01b_201192779"]}, {"text": "Despite the growing economic role of female-led companies in Egypt, there remain significant challenges to overcome.", "citations": ["16d2cf88-7e63-4c3c-9a4c-76a1e6e9b01b_201192779"]}, {"text": "The \u2018Invest for Employment\u2019 initiative funds up to 25% of the total investment value for projects with potential for job creation.", "citations": ["16d2cf88-7e63-4c3c-9a4c-76a1e6e9b01b_201192779"]}, {"text": "The number of university seats allocated to all Sub-Saharan African countries increased by 25% for the 2023-2024 academic year, according to the Minister of Higher Education.", "citations": ["32125b1a-6372-461b-bbcb-363867ecc132_1033602141"]}, {"text": "The President of the ECA has called for reforms to digital education across Africa.", "citations": ["cd5dad01-bf79-45af-84bc-2410ee4ee409_651913078"]}, {"text": "The African Union is urged to ensure Africa\u2019s education systems are suitable for today\u2019s workforce demands.", "citations": ["cd5dad01-bf79-45af-84bc-2410ee4ee409_651913078"]}, {"text": "Current recommendations ask: \u201cWhat investments do we need today to generate tomorrow\u2019s workforce?\u201d  \nThe report highlights ministerial focus on space research and remote sensing, leading to collaborations that train African researchers in satellite data use for solving environmental issues.", "citations": ["59cd1623-d2b4-4fc9-8441-4930ce100d39_767742646"]}, {"text": "The Global Forum on Remittances, Investment and Development in Nairobi\u2014organized by IFAD, the UN Office of the Special Adviser on Africa, and the World Bank Group\u2014aims to shift mindsets among stakeholders, including public, private, and civil society actors.", "citations": ["fa131fc2-1347-46d1-b5bc-cd929d572937_788403514"]}, {"text": "A key goal is to fully utilize remittances and diaspora investments as major contributors to social and economic progress in low- and middle-income African countries.", "citations": ["fa131fc2-1347-46d1-b5bc-cd929d572937_788403514"]}, {"text": "The second session of the Joint International Forum \u201cThe Future Belongs to Africa: The Power of Education: Creating New Jobs for a Better Future\u201d was opened at Bibliotheca Alexandrina, co-organized with Senghor University and the University Center for Professional Development at Alexandria University.", "citations": ["78d1632e-8c34-4481-8c4d-51f4e5bb227a_693618939"]}, {"text": "The forum reflects Bibliotheca Alexandrina\u2019s mission to improve education, develop skills, and empower Africa\u2019s youth.", "citations": ["78d1632e-8c34-4481-8c4d-51f4e5bb227a_693618939"]}, {"text": "Alexandria University has established two branches in Africa, located in Chad and South Sudan.", "citations": ["78d1632e-8c34-4481-8c4d-51f4e5bb227a_693618939"]}, {"text": "The three-day forum brings together diverse participants for discussions on education and job creation in Africa.", "citations": ["78d1632e-8c34-4481-8c4d-51f4e5bb227a_693618939"]}, {"text": "Partnerships have formed between American and Egyptian universities.", "citations": ["78d1632e-8c34-4481-8c4d-51f4e5bb227a_693618939"]}, {"text": "Professional skills emphasized include self-organization, communication, and teamwork, as well as gaining practical industry experience.", "citations": ["78d1632e-8c34-4481-8c4d-51f4e5bb227a_693618939"]}, {"text": "The African Development Institute is relocating its headquarters to Dakhla.", "citations": ["cdc7f1c1-b149-4ca6-a3a4-3d4efe47bc0e_1018147230"]}, {"text": "Participants are encouraged to collaborate to bridge gaps between higher education and African labor market needs.", "citations": ["9dd2798d-0ba8-4596-b648-1a5f01246531_141785109"]}, {"text": "Increased labor market competition and current challenges drive universities to focus on building real abilities and practical skills in students.", "citations": ["9dd2798d-0ba8-4596-b648-1a5f01246531_141785109"]}, {"text": "Senghor University, representing the French sector, provides training programs responsive to societal changes to serve Africa\u2019s development.", "citations": ["9dd2798d-0ba8-4596-b648-1a5f01246531_141785109"]}, {"text": "Sole reliance on academic systems is inadequate for youth employment; partnerships with companies and factories are vital for innovation and direct student engagement.", "citations": ["9dd2798d-0ba8-4596-b648-1a5f01246531_141785109"]}, {"text": "Crucial skills include critical analysis and interdisciplinary learning, bridging academic disciplines for problem-solving.", "citations": ["9dd2798d-0ba8-4596-b648-1a5f01246531_141785109"]}, {"text": "Direct cooperation with businesses is emphasized for innovation and job creation, involving students continuously in relevant industries.", "citations": ["9dd2798d-0ba8-4596-b648-1a5f01246531_141785109"]}, {"text": "With increasing support from China and other countries, the United Nations has fostered youth development capacity in Africa.", "citations": ["88063b1d-f7d5-4bc7-b94b-117659221c74_467775151"]}, {"text": "Traditionally, Chinese graduates except French majors rarely considered working in Africa, but growing workplace competition has increased their interest in African opportunities.", "citations": ["82eaa7a2-4961-4805-be15-af2b1aadfed2_731005687"]}, {"text": "China has served as Africa's largest trading partner for over a decade.", "citations": ["82eaa7a2-4961-4805-be15-af2b1aadfed2_731005687"]}, {"text": "Major Chinese retail brands and businesses, including hot pot shops, karaoke, milk tea shops, and hotels, are increasingly present in African urban centers.", "citations": ["82eaa7a2-4961-4805-be15-af2b1aadfed2_731005687"]}, {"text": "Many young Chinese entrepreneurs operate small studios or businesses in Africa.", "citations": ["82eaa7a2-4961-4805-be15-af2b1aadfed2_731005687"]}, {"text": "At Chen Zhuo\u2019s company, a freshman earns at least 200,000 RMB a year, substantially reducing financial burden for those from rural families.", "citations": ["82eaa7a2-4961-4805-be15-af2b1aadfed2_731005687"]}, {"text": "However, high salaries overseas often come with social isolation.", "citations": ["82eaa7a2-4961-4805-be15-af2b1aadfed2_731005687"]}, {"text": "Building people-to-people connectedness is recognized as vital for deepening Chinese-African university cooperation.", "citations": ["928a00a3-6681-4da4-938b-17bf409d2876_479576760"]}, {"text": "Africa is a significant partner in the Belt and Road Initiative, with efficient working mechanisms cited as key to project success.", "citations": ["928a00a3-6681-4da4-938b-17bf409d2876_479576760"]}, {"text": "Amu, currently pursuing a doctorate in China, started at a Confucius Institute focused on vocational education and initially had limited Chinese language skills.", "citations": ["59422bdf-1a1f-444d-9ba4-39d6c79a65d8_941797950"]}, {"text": "Wang Sheng chose a Chinese major even before its current surge in popularity.", "citations": ["59422bdf-1a1f-444d-9ba4-39d6c79a65d8_941797950"]}, {"text": "Annually, Chinese students gain opportunities to study in China and return to Ethiopia bringing new knowledge and development ideas.", "citations": ["59422bdf-1a1f-444d-9ba4-39d6c79a65d8_941797950"]}, {"text": "Investing in children\u2019s education is seen as crucial for long-term success, with higher education shown to increase earnings by about 50%.", "citations": ["5ee60ca1-b936-4b51-92e6-e3cdf36dda90_1045501757"]}, {"text": "Chinese oil and gas teams have expanded into Somalia, engaging in successful drilling and local professional training.", "citations": ["0b2dec15-ea49-4228-9e72-eea0d93feafe_844601722"]}, {"text": "Fan Chen-hui emphasized that resource-rich countries need complete underground databases to attract foreign investors and better showcase mining potential.", "citations": ["0b2dec15-ea49-4228-9e72-eea0d93feafe_844601722"]}, {"text": "During his first African visit, Li expressed eagerness to strengthen ties with Kagame and wished Rwanda to enjoy lasting peace.", "citations": ["8b666cfc-eb62-4006-91bb-5b38ec844951_99557189"]}, {"text": "China is advancing the establishment of a high-level China-Africa community of shared future, as stated by President Xi Jinping.", "citations": ["e1224e05-5508-41b2-a20b-ffaf272e9542_822653911"]}, {"text": "President Xi committed to implementing \"Ten Major Cooperation Plans\" with Africa over the next three years.", "citations": ["e1224e05-5508-41b2-a20b-ffaf272e9542_822653911"]}, {"text": "He emphasized respect for African countries\u2019 needs and pledged enduring partnership regardless of changes in the international situation.", "citations": ["e1224e05-5508-41b2-a20b-ffaf272e9542_822653911"]}, {"text": "At Tianjin Vocational and Technical Normal University, the Luban Workshop International Development Research Center was recognized as a new think tank.", "citations": ["69b470f8-26d0-4dd0-bc2c-8eef8e5875f1_194640868"]}, {"text": "The university has partnered with Ethiopian Technical University to establish the Luban Workshop in Ethiopia.", "citations": ["69b470f8-26d0-4dd0-bc2c-8eef8e5875f1_194640868"]}, {"text": "Chinese support has included provision of advanced training equipment like intelligent robotic arms.", "citations": ["69b470f8-26d0-4dd0-bc2c-8eef8e5875f1_194640868"]}, {"text": "Jiang, returning from China to Ethiopia, stated his goal is to help Ethiopia become self-sufficient and independent of foreign assistance.", "citations": ["69b470f8-26d0-4dd0-bc2c-8eef8e5875f1_194640868"]}, {"text": "The China-Africa Forum opened in Dakar, attracting international attention including analysis and reports from Le Monde headlined \u201cAfrica and China: A Moment of Disillusionment.\u201d", "citations": ["b8355676-15fb-4f0a-9908-50eb63204f91_119330086"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1034", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The pandemic accelerated long-standing discussions about flexible working as many firms were forced to implement remote work, according to Fontinha.", "citations": ["4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730"]}, {"text": "Technology is driving these changes and may make the trend toward flexibility and reduced hours irresistible over time, even as obstacles remain for some jobs.", "citations": ["1ca23fc5-1e30-4aa8-ac99-04ecc30df58b_831866648"]}, {"text": "Interest in a four-day workweek has surged, with current models offering employees a weekday off in addition to the weekend, or reducing daily working hours while maintaining a five-day week.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Advocates argue that it is currently impossible to have a meaningful work-life balance with a traditional five-day workweek and two days off.", "citations": ["04b2f2a0-28da-4acb-915d-4a601d16aec2_892204018"]}, {"text": "There are tangible benefits to reduced working hours, which include improved employee well-being, productivity, and satisfaction, as seen in recent trials.", "citations": ["cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395"]}, {"text": "Employees report that a shorter workweek is well-founded and desirable, as echoed by Linsay Moran's views on adapting to the future of work and increasing personal freedom.", "citations": ["941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754"]}, {"text": "Some sectors, like manufacturing, face hurdles in adopting the model due to the nature of their work, which requires in-person presence.", "citations": ["1ca23fc5-1e30-4aa8-ac99-04ecc30df58b_831866648"]}, {"text": "The pandemic was a significant test of alternative work arrangements and exposed weaknesses in traditional employment structures.", "citations": ["4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730"]}, {"text": "Shifting to a four-day week requires rebuilding trust between employers and employees, and a new openness to remote locations and digital nomadism.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "A majority\u201481%\u2014of workers believe a four-day week would increase productivity, particularly in specific sectors.", "citations": ["9e1be21b-78bd-4a02-99be-30592613efad_77733316"]}, {"text": "Recent trials of the four-day workweek found significant improvements in employee health, physical activity, and overall job satisfaction, attributed to more personal time.", "citations": ["cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395"]}, {"text": "For example, one company reduced productivity marginally but quickly regained most of the output, proving adaptability to the new schedule and improved staff quality of life.", "citations": ["cf48d8ac-0386-40b7-9253-77191b543af4_295608395"]}, {"text": "Such changes grant employees approximately 50 additional days off per year\u2014a substantial increase in personal time.", "citations": ["e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821"]}, {"text": "Employees at Advanced RV report positive experiences, though the model may not suit every business or industry.", "citations": ["e482bd93-fd7e-446b-ba03-e2926e0a5753_758874821"]}, {"text": "Some companies designate \u201cFlexible Fridays,\u201d with 87% of employees in one survey saying the policy benefitted their desire to remain at the company.", "citations": ["3815132f-21a3-4c7f-b126-01f4401b6194_770244439"]}, {"text": "There is, however, a gap in expectations for employees attracted to the four-day week but whose industries or employers retain the five-day standard.", "citations": ["8d1e8dce-0568-453d-acaf-717b98c0383c_383141420"]}, {"text": "Flex time and autonomy in task management are valued, but implementation requires systemic changes and ongoing communication.", "citations": ["4c2db427-4932-4b7c-977a-dfac0181fffd_255105730"]}, {"text": "The movement for reduced working hours continues to pick up momentum, with companies and employees increasingly embracing new definitions of productivity and work-life balance.", "citations": ["941bb6a1-0562-49cf-b65d-40a1edf10f98_903436754"]}, {"text": "The COVID-19 pandemic and, specifically, the spread of the Omicron variant, delayed millions of workers' return to traditional workplaces.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "This has led to renewed relevance for shortened work weeks and changing approaches to work structures.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "Prioritizing employee mental health has become more important, as burnout has become a significant problem and more people are leaving or considering leaving their jobs.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "Though experts say offices will still be needed and office space is not expected to shrink, on-site hours may be about 30% less than pre-pandemic levels.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "Predictions about the future of work remain uncertain due to rapid and ongoing changes.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "Health and its preservation have remained the top concern for 2022, continuing trends from previous years.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "In Russia, public opinion surveys indicate varying preferences for holiday timing, with some favoring longer May holidays over extended New Year breaks.", "citations": ["b2927506-8cda-4b92-8aa4-c54084dee51e_332522273"]}, {"text": "An analysis by the BBC evaluated the economic impact of public holidays in the UK but noted several influencing factors.", "citations": ["b2927506-8cda-4b92-8aa4-c54084dee51e_332522273"]}, {"text": "Introducing a four-day work week is not a new idea, but its adoption remains uncertain in Russia.", "citations": ["1efbdb0a-13d5-4470-88cb-cd6c9fe2c382_13900136"]}, {"text": "Advocates argue that increased free time can boost employee productivity.", "citations": ["ebb93ea0-9909-4a70-b579-c33e1a51fda2_955622203"]}, {"text": "Kazakhstan planned to implement a four-day work week starting July 1 of the referenced year.", "citations": ["ebb93ea0-9909-4a70-b579-c33e1a51fda2_955622203"]}, {"text": "Experiments with a four-day week have started in Germany, revealing that such changes can occur without reducing company revenue.", "citations": ["a3e0ae7b-56a3-4cf3-823f-55553ccd39c3_507910685"]}, {"text": "Union arguments for reduced working hours often include the shortage of specialists as a reason for higher compensation.", "citations": ["a3e0ae7b-56a3-4cf3-823f-55553ccd39c3_507910685"]}, {"text": "Russian officials comment that work is still perceived as central in people\u2019s lives, and job satisfaction is not universal.", "citations": ["94164a7b-c89b-49e7-ac1a-274e686e910a_890110960"]}, {"text": "Some workers, like rural women, are entitled to a shorter working week at the same pay.", "citations": ["94164a7b-c89b-49e7-ac1a-274e686e910a_890110960"]}, {"text": "Research indicates that up to 86% of workers might switch to reduced schedules or could request shorter hours.", "citations": ["94164a7b-c89b-49e7-ac1a-274e686e910a_890110960"]}, {"text": "City leaders support the shorter workweek for its potential to promote a healthier and more people-friendly society.", "citations": ["94164a7b-c89b-49e7-ac1a-274e686e910a_890110960"]}, {"text": "Transitioning from the traditional five-day workweek to four days may be initially shocking for employees used to a set routine.", "citations": ["c93b6c62-4b4e-4dc5-9756-5d7414b60b8b_540351926"]}, {"text": "Some enterprises are already implementing the shorter workweek model, and experts predict this may soon become widespread.", "citations": ["7058c1ec-20ea-4496-9ade-e2cda7ccfc06_698203815"]}, {"text": "Employers are expected to increasingly consider employee interests and develop new approaches to working time and workplace organization.", "citations": ["1e67ebc5-2d6b-4a8b-856c-9376ae8a8f68_691825519"]}, {"text": "However, concerns persist that reduced workweeks may raise labor and production costs.", "citations": ["1e67ebc5-2d6b-4a8b-856c-9376ae8a8f68_691825519"]}, {"text": "Despite cost concerns, labor ministries see benefits, including health protection, higher efficiency, personal and professional development, better family-work balance, and more time for recreation and culture.", "citations": ["1e67ebc5-2d6b-4a8b-856c-9376ae8a8f68_691825519"]}, {"text": "Discussions of a four-day workweek date back to the 1960s, and experts caution that adoption requires economic readiness and cannot happen overnight.", "citations": ["1efbdb0a-13d5-4470-88cb-cd6c9fe2c382_13900136"]}, {"text": "Pilot studies, such as a six-month program involving around 3,300 employees at 70 companies, are currently underway to test feasibility.", "citations": ["29ee155a-83fc-45c5-a784-cadcc5f8b8cc_70773650"]}, {"text": "While three-day weekends are becoming more common, the four-day workweek is emerging as a tangible reality in some places.", "citations": ["1efbdb0a-13d5-4470-88cb-cd6c9fe2c382_13900136"]}, {"text": "The 4-day workweek is being trialed in several countries, including Spain, Iceland, the United States, Canada, with Australia and New Zealand expected to join soon.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "In Saudi Arabia, the unemployment rate hit a 50-year low at 3.7% with 1.3 million job offers, reflecting a generally strong labor market context.", "citations": ["f25532ee-612b-4201-9398-777633fc3a59_401207391"]}, {"text": "A major four-day workweek study found that more than 90% of participating companies planned to maintain the reduced schedule.", "citations": ["35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423"]}, {"text": "The study reported that productivity remained stable or improved, with company revenues rising by an average of 1.4% over the trial period.", "citations": ["35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423"]}, {"text": "Companies indicated that shifts in profits and performance were more likely to go up than down during the pilot.", "citations": ["35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423"]}, {"text": "Employee satisfaction was high, with many reporting that three-day weekends improved their overall happiness.", "citations": ["35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423"]}, {"text": "Nathan Jenkinson from Tyler Grange described the change as positive, observing employees becoming more active and engaged.", "citations": ["35b580e6-ba02-4e03-8eb8-12cd488072cb_975295423"]}, {"text": "The four-day week has also led to reduced employee turnover and sick absences.", "citations": ["c42e800f-766d-4a8c-bef1-ef233d0e89e2_742374001"]}, {"text": "The initiative is among the most popular employee wishes, with studies indicating positive outcomes when implemented.", "citations": ["c42e800f-766d-4a8c-bef1-ef233d0e89e2_742374001"]}, {"text": "A shorter week was linked to better work-life and family balance for many participants.", "citations": ["c42e800f-766d-4a8c-bef1-ef233d0e89e2_742374001"]}, {"text": "Firms involved in the trials reported plans to retain the four-day structure.", "citations": ["c42e800f-766d-4a8c-bef1-ef233d0e89e2_742374001"]}, {"text": "Some European governments are introducing measures to give employees more flexibility, including condensing hours over fewer days to allow a three-day weekend.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "The reforms aim to grant workers and organizations greater flexibility in structuring work schedules.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "However, some political parties, including those on the left, worry about the potential costs to public finances.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "Average weekly hours in Germany, for example, currently stand at 34.2.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "In Spain, the government is piloting a four-day week after a proposal by the Mas Pais party, with a trial phase lasting at least one year.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "The UK began a six-month pilot in January involving about 30 companies, with researchers from Cambridge and Oxford monitoring impacts on productivity, well-being, environment, and gender equality.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "Initial findings from these experiments suggest that productivity and well-being either improved or remained unchanged.", "citations": ["05e65951-b854-47e7-9310-16cbbc9f2820_854826109"]}, {"text": "Scotland has launched a trial cutting working hours by 20% while maintaining pay, with positive feedback from participating companies and employees.", "citations": ["c8aa91a4-9a7b-4818-aa03-5115155afdab_60886483"]}, {"text": "Some Glasgow and Edinburgh firms have adopted the new system, supported by staff and industry initiatives.", "citations": ["c8aa91a4-9a7b-4818-aa03-5115155afdab_60886483"]}, {"text": "Despite norms of the 8-hour day, studies show most people only work productively for about three hours, prompting calls for shorter days.", "citations": ["c8aa91a4-9a7b-4818-aa03-5115155afdab_60886483"]}, {"text": "Lawmakers such as Takano in the U.S. are pushing for the 4-day week to advance worker happiness and social justice.", "citations": ["c42e800f-766d-4a8c-bef1-ef233d0e89e2_742374001"]}, {"text": "Organizers called the UK\u2019s pilot the world\u2019s largest four-day workweek trial to date.", "citations": ["0a7e0327-5c09-47de-a5d9-a42fdb8c7128_147602220"]}, {"text": "A growing trend toward a four-day workweek reflects a \"trust war\" between employers and employees over how best to structure working time.", "citations": ["c1abb4c8-1bd2-407c-9c5a-53e31c0be01a_497041419"]}, {"text": "In Taiwan, the government will respond by June 26 to a public proposal to make the country the first in Asia to implement a three-day weekend, a proposal already backed by more than 5,000 people.", "citations": ["c1abb4c8-1bd2-407c-9c5a-53e31c0be01a_497041419"]}, {"text": "Supporters argue that giving workers an extra day off each week benefits both employers and employees by offering more time for rest and personal pursuits, challenging the conventional five-day workweek model.", "citations": ["c1abb4c8-1bd2-407c-9c5a-53e31c0be01a_497041419"]}, {"text": "Andrew Barnes became an advocate for a shorter workweek and partnered with the British non-profit 4 Day Week Global to conduct trials in the United Kingdom.", "citations": ["c1abb4c8-1bd2-407c-9c5a-53e31c0be01a_497041419"]}, {"text": "Employers considering an extra day off must ensure weekly working hours do not increase and that productivity remains high without extended overtime on remaining workdays.", "citations": ["c1abb4c8-1bd2-407c-9c5a-53e31c0be01a_497041419"]}, {"text": "In recent years, some advanced countries have started experimenting with \u201cthree days off\u201d models.", "citations": ["cc3a259a-ce3b-4f94-9713-38685c43f269_916045631"]}, {"text": "Since June 1, 2022, over 3,000 employees from more than 60 UK companies participated in a six-month \"four-day work\" experiment.", "citations": ["1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687"]}, {"text": "The outcome of these trials broadens expectations that a weekly three-day break could benefit employees and employers alike.", "citations": ["1d46f039-99eb-4046-8a7f-5507144417d2_316669687"]}, {"text": "Numerous UK firms joined a four-day workweek pilot in 2022, with most allowing reduced weekly hours, and over half making the arrangement permanent.", "citations": ["2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427"]}, {"text": "Questions remain about whether less work time could reduce overall efficiency or in fact, boost it.", "citations": ["2afb54f5-6e6f-4cd6-9856-49054d7f7c21_155420427"]}, {"text": "Dr. Huang Xuan, reviewing global studies, noted a New Zealand company\u2019s \"four-day week\" experiment succeeded, with positive detailed results reported.", "citations": ["1b8f1b42-e4b0-4ba5-ab22-c7f03fdb33eb_929356573"]}, {"text": "One corporate trial found productivity was stable or slightly improved compared to the same period in the prior year.", "citations": ["95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531"]}, {"text": "Enterprises observed benefits such as increased production efficiency, reduced work pressure, and improved employee health and retention.", "citations": ["95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531"]}, {"text": "Four-day workweek research has been conducted globally, including by teams from the UK think tank Autonomy and the University of Cambridge.", "citations": ["95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531"]}, {"text": "Some employees in trials found it challenging to complete all their work within reduced hours.", "citations": ["95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531"]}, {"text": "Tri0 Media\u2019s CEO Claire Daniels participated in the trial to improve productivity, finding maintaining new work habits was the hardest part.", "citations": ["95484a6c-3484-4ebc-bcd9-0b7ef7fd3d89_98102531"]}, {"text": "Andrew Barnes asserts the reform focuses not just on work-life balance, but on maximizing productivity for business improvement.", "citations": ["fab3c828-582b-4ae0-bf95-7773cf884e4d_871877708"]}, {"text": "Employers see value in returning time to employees if work can be done more efficiently.", "citations": ["fab3c828-582b-4ae0-bf95-7773cf884e4d_871877708"]}, {"text": "The four-day week faces challenges, such as increased pressure and costs for businesses, and requires careful implementation to avoid negative impacts.", "citations": ["3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217"]}, {"text": "While office workers are generally receptive, some business leaders are also considering the four-day system.", "citations": ["a9da1cd3-8356-4637-b1af-02ba8245cc11_415760841"]}, {"text": "Retention concerns are significant, with reports such as over half of Apple\u2019s employees planning to leave, underscoring worker expectations about flexibility.", "citations": ["3494412e-cfc6-4d35-a573-83dd99cb2ee2_162549217"]}, {"text": "Hong Kong illustrates additional challenges; while overwork and \"overwork death\" are concerns, local authorities have been reluctant to legislate regulated working hours.", "citations": ["f19875be-563a-43cb-893e-0538851ab393_788140918"]}, {"text": "A lack of statutory labor protections, such as regulated hours, contributes to labor shortages.", "citations": ["f19875be-563a-43cb-893e-0538851ab393_788140918"]}, {"text": "Research shows that high working hours do not equate to high output; workers are not machines, and excessive hours often lead to absenteeism and stress-related absences.", "citations": ["f19875be-563a-43cb-893e-0538851ab393_788140918"]}, {"text": "Policy creation is an incremental process, and governments must act even if every problem cannot be solved at once.", "citations": ["f19875be-563a-43cb-893e-0538851ab393_788140918"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1036", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Biohacking is the practice of reprogramming the mind and body to live better, and is believed by some to be the key to greater health and self-improvement.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "Originating from Silicon Valley, biohacking includes a range of activities and habits aimed at \"self-optimization,\" health enhancement, and longevity, such as intermittent fasting, specialized diets (like gluten-free, dairy-free, keto, and the bulletproof diet), supplement regimens, intense exercise, and practices for reducing inflammation and optimizing gut health.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "Women have increasingly entered the biohacking space, leading to its evolution toward being more intuitive and less rigid in its benchmarks.", "citations": ["0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574"]}, {"text": "There are concerns that biohacking can become obsessive, as some individuals become fixated on stacking multiple habits or attempting to control every aspect of their health.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "Biohacking is not only about diet or exercise; it can also involve undertaking practices like yoga, Ayurveda, use of ice baths, and adopting mental wellness techniques.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "Research shows that factors like inflammation, which is sometimes targeted by diet or lifestyle modifications, have been linked to the processes underlying aging and chronic disease.", "citations": ["936c65fa-80e6-47ba-8442-e5e77a4826a5_411498914"]}, {"text": "For example, individuals have used anti-inflammatory diets and exercise to achieve health improvements, with some reporting disease remission and better management of symptoms such as arthritis, although such outcomes are often anecdotal.", "citations": ["0d8c27cc-fe14-4171-b4c0-1e5ffcb86d87_53197859"]}, {"text": "Some biohackers follow the latest scientific advances, such as CRISPR gene editing, which allows for precise changes in DNA and has driven new research in disease understanding and potential treatments, though these technologies are largely experimental and not widely available for personal use.", "citations": ["861bcdac-3a6d-4b74-8b46-fb8fd675a647_752012545"]}, {"text": "Biohacking can also mean the use of personalized medical screenings, genetic tests, and adopting technologies for tracking health metrics.", "citations": ["0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574"]}, {"text": "The role of genetics, environment, and lifestyle habits in determining health outcomes is under scientific investigation, as illustrated by studies into \"metabolically healthy obese\" individuals, showing that not all health can be explained by diet and exercise alone.", "citations": ["0d8c27cc-fe14-4171-b4c0-1e5ffcb86d87_53197859"]}, {"text": "Mental health practices, social signal processing, and stress reduction are also part of some biohacking routines, with neuroscience research showing how chemicals and brain regions influence social interactions and well-being.", "citations": ["73dc4426-e3fb-40cb-8c2d-9236031101af_161823384"]}, {"text": "While some elements of biohacking are backed by established science\u2014like the benefits of regular exercise and certain diets\u2014other aspects lack robust clinical evidence, and some practices may even be risky or cause harm if not medically supervised.", "citations": ["0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574"]}, {"text": "As the field matures, advocates acknowledge the importance of balance, self-awareness, and scientific validation to ensure that biohacking methods are safe and truly effective.", "citations": ["0f2ceda1-1145-419b-adad-243aa48471c2_868441574"]}, {"text": "Early detection in oncology is vital, with new methods now able to identify disease using just a drop of blood.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "A proposed diagnostic approach has completed animal testing and is advancing to analysis using human samples.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "Researchers observed how molecular compositions in mice brains changed after glioma-causing cancer cells were introduced.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "Tumor development is frequently, but not always, preceded by inflammation.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "Scientists believe their method may enable detection of glioma as well as other tumor types.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "Gas analyzers can identify marker molecules associated with pathological processes in exhaled air samples from volunteers.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "The diagnostic device covers a wide range and can detect many different marker molecules.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "A healthy individual's gas profile should have four peaks; deviations may indicate a health issue.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "Research in laboratories such as TSU employs gas analyzers and machine learning in laser molecular imaging.", "citations": ["aabfb55b-504e-4642-a448-549e47748b55_225185679"]}, {"text": "The EU is increasing support for patients with rare and poorly understood diseases.", "citations": ["865b7ecc-c60c-4190-9f95-bd064429720c_356473089"]}, {"text": "Genetic consultations are required frequently for these complex conditions, which involve intricate, multi-piece diagnostic puzzles.", "citations": ["865b7ecc-c60c-4190-9f95-bd064429720c_356473089"]}, {"text": "Current therapies for rare diseases are often prolonged and seldom lead to a complete recovery.", "citations": ["865b7ecc-c60c-4190-9f95-bd064429720c_356473089"]}, {"text": "Experts believe the EU has significant potential to improve outcomes for patients with rare diseases.", "citations": ["865b7ecc-c60c-4190-9f95-bd064429720c_356473089"]}, {"text": "Advances in research and attention aim to enhance patient quality of life.", "citations": ["865b7ecc-c60c-4190-9f95-bd064429720c_356473089"]}, {"text": "A groundbreaking cancer therapy using gene editing enabled remission in a terminally ill child with leukemia.", "citations": ["8c0c9125-5547-4872-a3e2-19c93b633f25_322914847"]}, {"text": "Great Ormond Street Hospital used newly developed DNA editing technology for this treatment.", "citations": ["8c0c9125-5547-4872-a3e2-19c93b633f25_322914847"]}, {"text": "DNA's billions of bases encode the human body's instructions.", "citations": ["8c0c9125-5547-4872-a3e2-19c93b633f25_322914847"]}, {"text": "T cells from a healthy donor were engineered to prevent attacks on the patient's own body.", "citations": ["8c0c9125-5547-4872-a3e2-19c93b633f25_322914847"]}, {"text": "Despite initial remission, signs of cancer reappeared after three months.", "citations": ["8c0c9125-5547-4872-a3e2-19c93b633f25_322914847"]}, {"text": "Gene base editing holds potential for treating other genetic conditions; for example, correcting a single-base mutation in sickle cell anemia.", "citations": ["8c0c9125-5547-4872-a3e2-19c93b633f25_322914847"]}, {"text": "Research has found so-called \"depression genes\" across species.", "citations": ["a784a0f2-8e77-4c0d-9675-fa3306fcff1b_347567925"]}, {"text": "Data from animal models do not always translate to human biology.", "citations": ["a784a0f2-8e77-4c0d-9675-fa3306fcff1b_347567925"]}, {"text": "Findings could inform diagnosis and treatment of mood disorders in the future.", "citations": ["a784a0f2-8e77-4c0d-9675-fa3306fcff1b_347567925"]}, {"text": "Scientists have rejuvenated human skin cells by 30 years through cellular reprogramming.", "citations": ["67f7ff11-d382-40d8-9d69-5e24e60296d5_45156483"]}, {"text": "Induced stem cell technology is central to this rejuvenation.", "citations": ["67f7ff11-d382-40d8-9d69-5e24e60296d5_45156483"]}, {"text": "Analysis of extensive medical data from 2020-2021 shows that COVID-19 survivors have increased risk of neurodegenerative diseases.", "citations": ["755609c0-7cfc-4065-bb90-133813724e60_531144099"]}, {"text": "Following past pandemics, such as the Spanish flu, Parkinson\u2019s disease cases also rose, but the long-term effects of COVID-19 remain unclear.", "citations": ["755609c0-7cfc-4065-bb90-133813724e60_531144099"]}, {"text": "Recent findings were published in Frontiers in Neurology.", "citations": ["755609c0-7cfc-4065-bb90-133813724e60_531144099"]}, {"text": "Small changes in non-coding DNA can significantly influence gene expression and increase autism risk.", "citations": ["08014edf-3735-4f26-9ef4-f6f0dc7249c4_5554092"]}, {"text": "About 1% of people possess chromosomal aberrations, underscoring the need for precise genetic diagnostics.", "citations": ["8660bdbf-c5ae-4064-85a9-0581602b005d_678197550"]}, {"text": "Researchers analogize the challenge of genetic diagnosis to reconstructing a living animal from its model.", "citations": ["a784a0f2-8e77-4c0d-9675-fa3306fcff1b_347567925"]}, {"text": "New genes linked to weight gain and loss have been discovered, offering hope for obesity treatments.", "citations": ["b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_36886381"]}, {"text": "Genetics has a prominent role in body weight regulation.", "citations": ["b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_36886381"]}, {"text": "Scientists identified 14 genes promoting weight gain and 3 aiding weight control.", "citations": ["b2e71ca1-f74f-41be-98bf-90b27f0ff99c_36886381"]}, {"text": "Human evolution may eventually incorporate tools into our biology, leading to possible cyborg integration.", "citations": ["19f87c6b-572e-4e6b-b590-5754e2de9fed_652807090"]}, {"text": "Some individuals use drugs to escape life's worries, despite the high risks involved, including the potential for fatal harm.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "All drugs have side effects, which can range from minor headaches to dangerous symptoms requiring further medication.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "People sometimes develop tolerance to these drugs, increasing their dose to keep feeling the effects.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "For some, like one user who began taking them after feeling tired in the morning, use escalated until they felt constantly angry and disconnected.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Another individual named Kate realized her life was unraveling and decided to quit these drugs completely.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Withdrawal symptoms came as a surprise, since no one had warned about possible side effects.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Students like Phoebe and Jonny, who relied on nootropics to help with exams, soon experienced negative impacts such as severe stomach pain and dependency.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Phoebe began to feel lasting severe stomach pain, while Jimmy realized he was relying on the drug every morning without need.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "A cultural pressure exists, according to Wu, across industries: people take drugs to become smarter and more productive, aiming to meet today's definitions of success.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Wanting to be one's best self appears desirable, but it can also lead to immense stress and competition.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "The feeling that there are only a limited number of rewards leads people to take extreme measures to reach success.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Where students once took drugs to experience euphoria, now they use them to achieve better grades.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "In Silicon Valley, some workers reportedly turn to LSD to cope with demands.", "citations": ["6101cf9c-fd45-43fa-87a1-737f1ac2b433_264387869"]}, {"text": "Research shows placental mammals begin development in similar ways, but science cannot yet create fully functional organs or animals solely from stem cells.", "citations": ["fef1a615-0a63-4965-943a-d255ea384bd3_167279001"]}, {"text": "A study published in Nature demonstrated embryonic models can develop early nervous systems in a controlled environment, but complete organ development is still far from reality.", "citations": ["fef1a615-0a63-4965-943a-d255ea384bd3_167279001"]}, {"text": "Research also indicates that early forms of liver disease can impact heart health, showing the need to consider organ interrelationships.", "citations": ["4cca30fe-dc5a-45ce-a960-d77ebc00722f_551394573"]}, {"text": "Scientists suggest features of gut bacteria, fungi, and viruses could one day form the basis for diagnosing conditions such as autism.", "citations": ["39b4587c-a2c6-45f4-9bcc-f0a2014aa7f3_262871929"]}, {"text": "Genomic studies now allow targeted drug treatment earlier in the disease process, as illustrated by Dr. Cotter\u2019s work to improve therapies and lessen harmful side effects.", "citations": ["7734c1f7-707d-4379-9fb2-21d6d129549e_579465295"]}, {"text": "Birth order may shape personality, with significant effects attributed to sibling position and age gaps, but personal factors still play a substantial role.", "citations": ["dd76b242-a982-4d1e-bfa2-88068aa1bee0_445821457"]}, {"text": "Birth order studies, such as a 2007 Norwegian one, find firstborn children often have slightly higher IQs than their younger siblings.", "citations": ["dd76b242-a982-4d1e-bfa2-88068aa1bee0_445821457"]}, {"text": "Experiments with mixing human and animal brain cells suggest changes at the cellular level, raising new scientific questions.", "citations": ["4f94b636-2a53-4750-9203-75d28236ef38_186696245"]}, {"text": "Research links high nighttime temperatures to greater risk of stroke, emphasizing the impact of environment on health.", "citations": ["a2949237-2beb-42ff-ba21-e9ddbdc5e0b4_402458993"]}, {"text": "Research shows that genetic inheritance plays a role in individual success and health, as talent and innate ability may be partially inherited from parents, not only wealth.", "citations": ["8bd5be6b-d422-4a7a-94ad-0f5c141c23ea_228918535"]}, {"text": "Genetic risk can be estimated by analyzing base pairs in DNA, which are often collected from saliva samples and preserved through freezing for research purposes.", "citations": ["8bd5be6b-d422-4a7a-94ad-0f5c141c23ea_228918535"]}, {"text": "It is important to be cautious of misinformation and pseudoscientific claims; many people overestimate their ability to recognize falsehoods, and new forms of misinformation may use scientific or financial jargon to appear credible.", "citations": ["62f49b3d-2751-4cef-80b2-18a6db184c85_974615390"]}, {"text": "To address misinformation, it is crucial to critically challenge questionable claims and understand the motivations and origins of fake information, especially in the context of science and health.", "citations": ["62f49b3d-2751-4cef-80b2-18a6db184c85_974615390"]}, {"text": "A surge has occurred in people's reliance on online sources like YouTube for health and nutrition information, making it easier for unsubstantiated health trends and supply issues (like calcium, iron, and cancer drug shortages) to gain attention.", "citations": ["62f49b3d-2751-4cef-80b2-18a6db184c85_974615390"]}, {"text": "Scientific developments, such as the EMA certification of the biological drug Anakinra for COVID-19 treatment, illustrate the value and process of evidence-based medical advances.", "citations": ["8661a9a6-97e3-44cb-853a-d46bea32f574_887887787"]}, {"text": "Recent biohacking techniques include genetic testing for disease risk, extreme diets (gluten-free, dairy-free, keto, bulletproof diet), supplement use, intermittent fasting, ice baths, and high-intensity exercise, all aimed at self-optimization and longevity.", "citations": ["8bd5be6b-d422-4a7a-94ad-0f5c141c23ea_228918535"]}, {"text": "Mental and behavioral research is also growing, such as studies on the effects of sleep loss and recovery on food-related behavior and psychology, with experiments carefully controlled to minimize risk.", "citations": ["7c761162-5292-4005-969e-1aa92d8c5d12_90650723"]}, {"text": "Technology is helping people with severe physical limitations communicate, while broader research into developmental and genetic conditions underscores the importance of supporting quality of life for everyone, regardless of their innate abilities.", "citations": ["4e77bdd4-17ee-43b4-8f80-ca4cddee2e32_802626663"]}, {"text": "Published research from medical and public health experts, such as studies on mental health phenomena and advancements in big data analysis, demonstrates ongoing efforts to use scientific evidence to inform health interventions.", "citations": ["0cc9c8fa-73bb-4533-9028-68ca3595fefe_9951451"]}, {"text": "Ultimately, biohacking remains a mix of proven and unproven practices: while some interventions are supported by clinical data, others lack scientific validation and may even pose risks, highlighting the need for critical evaluation and reliance on high-quality evidence.", "citations": ["62f49b3d-2751-4cef-80b2-18a6db184c85_974615390"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1038", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "After the reconversion of the Hagia Sophia, Turkey has also converted the ancient Byzantine Chora Church, which had been a museum for 79 years, into a mosque.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Some Orthodox Christians have expressed disappointment but emphasize the importance of finding common ground.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Muslim worshippers at the newly rededicated mosques see these conversions as symbols of Turkey\u2019s national pride and victory.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "The reconversion is considered by many as a significant symbol of the Ottoman conquest.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "The Hagia Sophia has recently seen maintenance concerns, with reports of fragments falling from its dome.", "citations": ["9ba1561a-fc64-4cc3-b0ee-218d2b7a3e8d_609947018"]}, {"text": "A new entrance for tourists has been added in front of the Topkapi Palace Museum, allowing visitors access without interrupting prayer times.", "citations": ["3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190"]}, {"text": "A Ministry statement announced that tourists can now visit Hagia Sophia without disturbing the praying environment due to new regulations starting January 15.", "citations": ["3886289d-abc9-433e-9ed3-f3bd8c9a9f7d_513279190"]}, {"text": "Christian leaders in Turkey are looking forward to new legislation on religious foundations, which is significant for local Christian communities who manage important places of worship.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "The Turkish Greek community manages 77 religious foundations, the highest among minorities.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "Both Hagia Sophia and the Chora Church were converted into museums after the fall of the Ottoman Empire and the creation of modern Turkey.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "The Church of the Holy Saviour in Chora was originally built by the Byzantines in the 5th century.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "In 1985, Hagia Sophia was designated a UNESCO World Heritage Site recognizing its outstanding historical significance.", "citations": ["aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472"]}, {"text": "President Recep Tayyip Erdogan has recently opened the Ayasofya Mosque\u2019s Fatih Madrassa, Istanbul\u2019s first Ottoman religious school.", "citations": ["aca9fced-3a95-40a8-82a7-3da41f775387_904412472"]}, {"text": "The reconversions of these historic sites have drawn criticism from the international community, particularly due to their religious and cultural significance.", "citations": ["76e3d61c-e991-43a2-8ebe-637114089506_291378229"]}, {"text": "Many view these changes as carrying strong religious undertones and as political moves by President Erdogan to appeal to conservative and nationalist sentiments within Turkey.", "citations": ["08e56be8-bc6f-4425-87d4-aedb4c7ad5e1_627735049"]}, {"text": "Tourism to Turkey, including visits to historic ruins and sites like Hagia Sophia, remains popular, with the government implementing measures to balance religious functions and visitor access.", "citations": ["8a5b5f0c-d288-4106-8fac-c33115f17aeb_1035332071"]}, {"text": "Turkish authorities are under pressure to preserve the multi-layered history and maintain open access to sites that are important to both Christians and Muslims, as well as to the broader international community.", "citations": ["8a5b5f0c-d288-4106-8fac-c33115f17aeb_1035332071"]}, {"text": "Many changes are occurring in the Middle East, Europe, and the United States today.", "citations": ["78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096"]}, {"text": "In early April, Turkish newspapers reported that President Erdogan would visit Hagia Sophia with AKP leaders and religious authorities to pray.", "citations": ["78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096"]}, {"text": "On April 18, it was clear that Erdogan had politically succeeded, but some felt a personal or ideological loss from this shift.", "citations": ["78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096"]}, {"text": "The conservative and religious population of inner Anatolia felt their support for Erdogan entitled them to present further demands.", "citations": ["78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096"]}, {"text": "This shift in policy is notably slow and calculated by Erdogan, using a tolerant tone to appeal to various audiences.", "citations": ["78791118-f9c5-4ecd-b7a2-e57dcecfb197_751571096"]}, {"text": "Tours often guide visitors through Byzantine sites such as the Hippodrome, Basilica Cistern, and Hagia Sophia, highlighting Istanbul's layered history.", "citations": ["4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879"]}, {"text": "The Hagia Sophia\u2019s massive scale and beauty draw tourists who immerse themselves in its history, architecture, and complex identity.", "citations": ["5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181"]}, {"text": "After the Ottoman conquest, the Christian Hagia Sophia was converted into a mosque.", "citations": ["7c91a665-2672-4d9b-8eae-3ec3168be312_904357446"]}, {"text": "The American Council for the Liberation of Hagia Sophia has demanded it return to Christian worship, with its head Chris Spirou condemned by Turkish authorities as a provocateur.", "citations": ["d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947"]}, {"text": "For three years leading to 2020, there were ongoing efforts to change Hagia Sophia's status.", "citations": ["d0d4acd7-74b5-467f-9c78-985c6a08a9e5_893345947"]}, {"text": "A weakening Turkish lira is expected to raise tourism prices in Istanbul.", "citations": ["6f38cb1a-e23d-4640-b32d-e60c213671a8_857153029"]}, {"text": "Built in the 6th century by Emperor Justinian, Hagia Sophia was the world's largest Christian church for over a thousand years.", "citations": ["6f38cb1a-e23d-4640-b32d-e60c213671a8_857153029"]}, {"text": "Today, it is known as the Great Mosque of Hagia Sophia.", "citations": ["6f38cb1a-e23d-4640-b32d-e60c213671a8_857153029"]}, {"text": "Foreign tourists must now pay 25 euros to enter, while Turkish citizens have free entry.", "citations": ["5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181"]}, {"text": "In 2020, President Erdogan officially decreed Hagia Sophia\u2019s status as a mosque.", "citations": ["5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181"]}, {"text": "Modest clothing and headscarves are required for mosque entry.", "citations": ["c476e990-4372-435e-8621-6165e8d2eff1_1033588193"]}, {"text": "Visitors can book tours that answer questions about logistics, payment, and scheduling.", "citations": ["c476e990-4372-435e-8621-6165e8d2eff1_1033588193"]}, {"text": "Guides express readiness to answer any questions before bookings are finalized.", "citations": ["c476e990-4372-435e-8621-6165e8d2eff1_1033588193"]}, {"text": "Tourists pay partially in advance, completing payment after the tour if they are satisfied.", "citations": ["5f313598-c9ac-40a3-8bae-106d6564ae87_210914181"]}, {"text": "Only verified visitors can write reviews, often praising guides' expertise and historical coverage.", "citations": ["c476e990-4372-435e-8621-6165e8d2eff1_1033588193"]}, {"text": "Tours are suitable for families and offer a range of experiences, including ferry rides and market visits.", "citations": ["c476e990-4372-435e-8621-6165e8d2eff1_1033588193"]}, {"text": "Following the reconversion, some Russian politicians expressed outrage and religious provocation against Turkey.", "citations": ["892fffe3-5739-436a-9741-288b36b59bc7_415039115"]}, {"text": "Turkish Minister of Culture and Tourism Mehmet Nuri Ersoy announced that entry for foreigners would be paid, partially maintaining the site\u2019s museum functions.", "citations": ["f81149b2-9efa-411c-b8fa-ed1ba6062f6f_619383984"]}, {"text": "Erdogan invited leaders of Muslim-majority countries to participate in the first prayer at the newly reconverted Hagia Sophia Mosque.", "citations": ["a8d17c9c-d219-4c0f-b2b9-f79c754a6d8c_960510274"]}, {"text": "*Characters: ~2,350*", "citations": ["4e093f28-baf3-4799-8558-76d16d051ada_992581879"]}, {"text": "New rules have come into force for visiting the Hagia Sophia Mosque in Turkey.", "citations": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}, {"text": "Many visitors welcome the new rules as long as the entrance fee remains reasonable.", "citations": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia has been on the UNESCO World Heritage List as part of Istanbul's history since 1985.", "citations": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}, {"text": "After the building was converted into a mosque, it faced strong criticism from the Greek Orthodox Church.", "citations": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}, {"text": "The reconversion of Hagia Sophia is seen by some as controversial.", "citations": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}, {"text": "Other historic buildings such as the Karya (Khora) Mosque in Istanbul also went through similar fates: built as a church in the Byzantine era, converted into a mosque after the conquest, and later became a museum before reopening for worship.", "citations": ["f958f36f-48c6-484b-b2d1-4046b599b7ce_77694835"]}, {"text": "Sites like Khora are known for their exquisite mosaics and frescoes, reflecting their historical Christian heritage.", "citations": ["d766c719-43c0-4423-80e6-89c1f9dc9d52_954300905"]}, {"text": "President Recep Tayyip Erdogan stated that returning Hagia Sophia from a museum to a mosque represented a major challenge to the idea of global trusteeship.", "citations": ["36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408"]}, {"text": "Greece\u2019s foreign ministry condemned recent events at Christian heritage sites in Turkey as insults and desecration, highlighting the sensitivity around these changes.", "citations": ["2e1275b0-982a-45c8-8362-accedde29467_83629709"]}, {"text": "The reconversion of heritage sites such as Hagia Sophia and Khora has sparked criticism based on religious and political grounds, especially from the Greek Orthodox Church and the international community.", "citations": ["97d76ff6-1c05-45d5-ba89-88ccc0122e21_491069692"]}, {"text": "Critics argue that these moves by President Erdogan have religious undertones and serve as political gestures, emphasizing Turkish sovereignty and local control over global heritage sites.", "citations": ["36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408"]}, {"text": "These actions have drawn concerns regarding the preservation of the multicultural legacy of Istanbul, particularly with respect to the sites' roles as places of shared history for both Christians and Muslims.", "citations": ["36db8615-aa07-4391-a3f5-098dba27f295_1069312408"]}, {"text": "UNESCO continues to classify Hagia Sophia and other sites as World Heritage, and expresses willingness to assist with preservation and maintenance whenever such heritage sites are affected or altered.", "citations": ["c46bf1f4-c851-47b1-91b6-ad9d5afdba20_252477844"]}, {"text": "Since 2019, the coronavirus pandemic has deeply impacted global travel, making visits to places like Istanbul, Ephesus, and Athens rare dreams for many.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "Cappadocia's ancient lime cave castles echo with the calls to prayer, reflecting Turkey's blending of Christian and Islamic history.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "Hot air balloon flights at sunrise reveal its unique geography, while on tours, guides discuss the life and journeys of Saint Paul, his connection to places like Ephesus, his missionary path, and his frequent imprisonments.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "Biblical history, such as Paul's transformation on the road to Damascus and his belief in salvation through Jesus, is a common theme, accompanied by reflections on life, death, faith, and rest.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "Travelers are often surprised to learn that Mary, mother of Jesus, is honored in both Christianity and Islam, pointing to shared reverence across religions.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "The journey through Turkey includes visiting mountains, the beauty of the Aegean Sea, and sites like the cave where Saint John is said to have written the Book of Revelation.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "Istanbul, formerly the capital of the Eastern Roman (Byzantine) Empire, showcases its multi-layered history through landmarks like the Church of St. Anthony of Padua and remnants of the Byzantine city wall.", "citations": ["7acf717e-db06-448e-bcd2-e34241aa5621_334799430"]}, {"text": "The city straddles two continents, with the old city protected by ancient walls and surrounded by the sea.", "citations": ["7acf717e-db06-448e-bcd2-e34241aa5621_334799430"]}, {"text": "Hagia Sophia, central to this history, was converted from a Byzantine cathedral into a mosque by Sultan Mehmed II after the Ottoman conquest, and served as a major place of Muslim worship for over 500 years.", "citations": ["7acf717e-db06-448e-bcd2-e34241aa5621_334799430"]}, {"text": "Modern political tensions surfaced during the Turkish presidential elections, with President Erdo\u011fan facing challenges after losing major cities, yet maintaining influence through controversies like the reconversion of Hagia Sophia into a mosque.", "citations": ["e7099633-61d6-4fd0-b12f-be3400627172_872026028"]}, {"text": "Critics view this reconversion as a politicized move, asserting that it reflects religious undertones, impacts Turkey\u2019s secular image, and generates international concern due to Hagia Sophia\u2019s UNESCO World Heritage status as both a symbol of Christian and Islamic heritage.", "citations": ["e7099633-61d6-4fd0-b12f-be3400627172_872026028"]}, {"text": "Travelers cross the Bosphorus, visit Topkapi and the palaces of the Ottomans, admire gardens like G\u00fclhane Park, and observe the ongoing legacy of empires through architecture and daily life.", "citations": ["e54b5c64-13ce-4319-951c-62f5414ecd22_390949949"]}, {"text": "Sites such as the Anatolian Fortress, orchards on routes to ruins like Troy, and UNESCO-listed wonders like Pamukkale (the \"Cotton Castle\") highlight Turkey\u2019s vast and diverse history.", "citations": ["6ab509b1-4263-4832-a7ca-665ba3b87b8c_438151500"]}, {"text": "Throughout, the enduring synthesis of civilizations in Turkey fosters both admiration and debates about the stewardship of its sacred and historic sites.", "citations": ["6ab509b1-4263-4832-a7ca-665ba3b87b8c_438151500"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1040", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "CCTV cameras were secretly installed throughout the monastery, including the monks' private quarters, without their knowledge.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "Footage captured by these hidden cameras was leaked to the media last week by an unnamed individual who possessed the recordings.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "Some leaked videos included disturbing images such as a monk shouting at a woman and hitting her with a belt, for which the woman was blamed.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "Commentators noted that the series of recordings could almost function as a reality TV show, speculating on internal disputes over its exposure.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "There were suggestions that a disagreement may have occurred if the bishop desired a larger share of something involved.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "It was mentioned that the Russian patriarch had intended to visit the site, but postponed due to the situation in Gaza, though a future visit could still provide him popularity among the faithful.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "One commentator reflected on whether spiritual prayers for peace and justice could be more effective than seeking intervention from the United Nations regarding the Cyprus problem.", "citations": ["2bde6845-9373-481b-9c5d-8a5442f391d5_231216990"]}, {"text": "Meanwhile, within the context of protests in Iran over the death of Mahsa Amini, activists noted the increased attention due to social media, stating their hope for Iranian women to gain the rights afforded to women in Canada.", "citations": ["63c36608-3eac-4843-80c9-b85b71