ecially those who prefer television and radio for news.", "citations": ["705ed5ea-d3ed-43e9-b505-8927674ae80e_883459450"]}, {"text": "Some believe such actions do not necessarily offend believers but can touch on sensitive social issues.", "citations": ["705ed5ea-d3ed-43e9-b505-8927674ae80e_883459450"]}, {"text": "Recent events in Kazakhstan include plans for a visa-free regime with Iran, China, and India, and ongoing connections with Russia are noted.", "citations": ["4fdab56f-132f-4b70-ad88-76b952c3125a_979997267"]}, {"text": "Authorities in Kazakhstan are investigating opinions expressed in a video by Sanan Akhmedov, whose brother is a martyr.", "citations": ["1edfaeb0-873c-48ce-a442-1f687bd4bcde_288470493"]}, {"text": "Mufti Salah Mezhiyev from Chechnya attended events in Mecca, coinciding with local celebrations of Kunta-Haji Kishiyev\u2019s birthday.", "citations": ["575ea64a-20d5-4d16-b39f-bc60cd8fdac1_164834575"]}, {"text": "In Russia, Father Sergius was deprived of his clerical rank following statements about monastic land leasing, yet he continues to reside at the Sredneuralsky nunnery.", "citations": ["62bb3302-7846-4be0-8f30-3ec30791e752_831836536"]}, {"text": "Certainly!", "citations": ["ffdb84f3-2d2d-4a34-a17b-ddc46249d989_509194881"]}, {"text": "Here is a coherent summary of the provided extracts, rewritten with one sentence per line and within the 2500-character limit:\n\nThe Grand Mufti described extremist ideologues as enemies of the homeland.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "President Sisi has undertaken the renewal of religious discourse as a necessary mission for the current era.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "Dar Al Ifta insists it is not politicized and remains committed to confronting extremist groups.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "The institution has a plan to boost communication with the public, aiming to open four branches each year across various governorates.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "Dar Al Ifta recently joined TikTok to provide beneficial content to younger audiences.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "The body is responding to the challenges of fourth-generation warfare with its \u201cFatwa Trend\u201d initiative.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "An Animation Unit was launched to counter extremist fatwas with simple messages accessible to all.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "During Ramadan, Dar Al Ifta focuses on outreach sites to directly engage youth, foster awareness, correct misconceptions, and maintain state stability.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "Social media engagement is significant for Dar Al Ifta, leading to the creation of an account after monitoring many anomalous fatwas on these platforms.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "Dar Al Ifta clarifies it is not politicized in the conventional sense, does not act under instruction from others, but considers the public interest a central part of its legal opinions, sometimes in coordination with state entities or courts.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "Common inquiries include various issues presented to Dar Al Ifta for religious opinion.", "citations": ["f4f0cda9-4acf-42f6-8459-96000192bd42_28845821"]}, {"text": "A statement was released after a controversial mosque video, pointing out that chaos is unacceptable within mosques.", "citations": ["f3080c93-8ab9-4864-a570-f8f940a5b7f7_860810685"]}, {"text": "Baharna activists have circulated a video in which Sheikh Saddi warns of the so-called Abrahamic religion.", "citations": ["8250f2d7-7ca1-4362-bae1-125f4e20025e_894563851"]}, {"text": "A warning was made about a fake video attributed to Egypt\u2019s mufti, and Dar Al Ifta has vowed legal action against those responsible for such forgeries.", "citations": ["cef762bd-1800-4ec5-951a-144a5371170e_1006827530"]}, {"text": "Bloggers have raised concerns over books available in libraries and the defamation campaign against Sheikh Issa via video clips.", "citations": ["e761639c-b698-4796-b34d-8ed29839015f_63851591"]}, {"text": "The program \"My Heart Is Reassured\" was involved in controversy by using Syrian Civil Defense footage of rescue operations in areas outside government control for its reality television show.", "citations": ["d78545e8-744f-44ed-a060-2d827d204592_13250093"]}, {"text": "There is significant competition in religious tourism, and Egypt, after years of limited activity, currently ranks third in tourist arrivals behind the UAE and Saudi Arabia.", "citations": ["ffdb84f3-2d2d-4a34-a17b-ddc46249d989_509194881"]}, {"text": "Renewing and maintaining shrines could elevate Egypt's religious and touristic status in the Muslim world.", "citations": ["ffdb84f3-2d2d-4a34-a17b-ddc46249d989_509194881"]}, {"text": "Debate exists over whether to restore shrines using marble or stone, but the general sentiment is to rely on specialists for these decisions.", "citations": ["ffdb84f3-2d2d-4a34-a17b-ddc46249d989_509194881"]}, {"text": "A story also circulated online about a man in Safaga claiming prophetic status, which was shared on Facebook with further coverage promised in a video.", "citations": ["a894ee1c-e824-412a-8bb0-68bceca04836_956551949"]}, {"text": "This summary captures the main points and issues raised in the extracts provided.", "citations": ["a894ee1c-e824-412a-8bb0-68bceca04836_956551949"]}, {"text": "Many critics argue that President Erdogan\u2019s decision to reconvert Hagia Sophia from a museum into a mosque in 2020 was primarily a political move aimed at consolidating support among his conservative and nationalist base.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "This action was seen by some as an attempt to divert attention from economic troubles and increase Erdogan\u2019s popularity ahead of upcoming elections.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "Concerns have been raised about the religious undertones of this decision, highlighting how the move could deepen divisions between secular and religious communities within Turkey.", "citations": ["22007e11-e905-4961-a00b-afd858aa8348_670697476"]}, {"text": "Internationally, the move was met with disapproval from both Christian organizations and several governments, who noted the unique historical and religious significance of Hagia Sophia as a symbol of coexistence and secularism.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "Many critics within Turkey and abroad pointed out that the 1934 conversion of Hagia Sophia into a museum by Mustafa Kemal Atat\u00fcrk symbolized the secular character of the modern Turkish Republic, and its reconversion was seen as a reversal of those foundational principles.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "The UNESCO World Heritage Committee also voiced concern about the decision, stating that any modification to Hagia Sophia\u2019s status could compromise its universal value as a World Heritage Site.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "Christian leaders, particularly from the Orthodox and Catholic Churches, criticized the move, with the Ecumenical Patriarch of Constantinople describing it as disappointing and urging respect for Hagia Sophia\u2019s multi-religious heritage.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "The Greek government condemned the move as a provocation to the civilized world, while the Russian Orthodox Church expressed regret at the \u201cnon-consensual\u201d change of the monument's status.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "Some scholars and observers underline that the conversion has also been used by Erdogan to project Turkey\u2019s growing assertiveness and reposition its image as a leading power in the Muslim world.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "Others questioned whether opening Hagia Sophia for Muslim worship undermines the inclusive messaging that the site once carried as a museum open to people of all backgrounds and faiths.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}, {"text": "The decision has therefore been seen by many as both a symbolically charged act intended to inspire national pride among Turkey\u2019s Muslim majority and a move that threatens the country\u2019s tradition of secular governance and religious tolerance.", "citations": ["7f25efdc-5ca2-4ba2-98ce-0536b7ebcf9b_817442008"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1042", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "It is important for individuals, especially pregnant women, to consume nutritious foods such as fresh fruits, vegetables, high fiber, and protein-rich meals, which are beneficial for both mother and baby and help ensure a smooth, healthy delivery.", "citations": ["507040e4-0883-4e4c-b5b1-f48220042bae_294299382"]}, {"text": "A Sattvic diet, emphasized in traditional Indian medicine, is highlighted for its ability to calm the mind and energize muscles and bones, supporting women during childbirth.", "citations": ["507040e4-0883-4e4c-b5b1-f48220042bae_294299382"]}, {"text": "Traditional Indian medicine, including herbalism, is gaining renewed interest, with advocates encouraging people to rediscover herbal remedies for everyday ailments like sore throats and skin problems, drawing on the healing properties of everyday herbs and spices.", "citations": ["4d07b9d8-1eb3-4ebe-aaf2-39e5725dc367_859318431"]}, {"text": "Indian companies such as HealthRoots are now offering herbal products aimed at preventing headaches, increasing endurance, and reducing stress and tiredness.", "citations": ["9070a5c5-cd76-46ba-8c07-33e91b535e03_742183461"]}, {"text": "In contrast to Western medicine, which often focuses on treating symptoms, traditional Indian medicine like Ayurveda, Siddha, and Unani adopts a more holistic approach, using herbs, breathing techniques, and meditation to promote overall well-being.", "citations": ["aac1a8d4-cdcd-4808-b67f-a66bd244fac1_661282659"]}, {"text": "Efforts are underway to fact-check and dispel misinformation about Ayurveda in India, with organizations such as THIP Media and the Amrita Centre for Advanced Research in Ayurveda collaborating to provide scientifically supported answers about Ayurvedic practices via the RAKSHA chatbot.", "citations": ["aff59da3-6da1-4757-beaf-37fabdebd098_598370846"]}, {"text": "Experts emphasize that to bring traditional Indian medicines onto a global scientific platform, strategies must evolve to meet scientific standards, especially important during global health crises like COVID-19.", "citations": ["e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735"]}, {"text": "India\u2019s Ministry of AYUSH is actively advancing this integration, recognizing the roles of Ayurveda, Siddha, and Unani in building immunity, enhancing strength, and addressing various disease symptoms.", "citations": ["12285aa1-5cd6-475f-82fe-271921520848_381225395"]}, {"text": "Recent research from IIT Delhi suggests that Ayurveda and Yoga may be beneficial in treating high-risk COVID-19 cases, relieving anxiety, and promoting faster post-recovery, as published in the Indian Journal of Traditional Knowledge.", "citations": ["362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295"]}, {"text": "Patients who received Ayurvedic care for COVID-19 reported increased confidence in its efficacy.", "citations": ["362c2c86-f85e-4fb2-a284-cd4f44e4aee0_498281295"]}, {"text": "Partnerships such as that between Healthy Directions and Dr. Kulreet Chaudhary are working to merge traditional Ayurvedic practices with modern science, leveraging essential herbs with emerging scientific support.", "citations": ["2b3d1f11-a45e-4ea7-ae82-52bef644a2c4_103444846"]}, {"text": "Ayurveda and allied Indian medical systems are set for wider global recognition, with efforts like inclusion in the WHO\u2019s ICD-11 list, providing a standardized framework for health professionals worldwide.", "citations": ["e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735"]}, {"text": "The growing momentum of wellness tourism in India reflects the increasing global emphasis on holistic well-being endorsed by traditional Indian medicine.", "citations": ["e2101fe3-e219-47c1-8300-449bef7dfe12_68754735"]}, {"text": "Traditional Indian medicine, commonly referred to as Indian herbal medicine or Ayurveda, is based on the use of a diverse array of plant species for therapeutic purposes.", "citations": ["d3caa544-d81f-43ac-9135-59e2be0875b3_440986270"]}, {"text": "Modern studies report that up to 160 different plant species are actively deployed in some regions, with approximately 130 of these specifically used for treatments.", "citations": ["4d07b9d8-1eb3-4ebe-aaf2-39e5725dc367_204946748"]}, {"text": "Indian herbal medicine is increasingly researched for its biologically active plant substances, which contribute to many health-promoting functions.", "citations": ["4d07b9d8-1eb3-4ebe-aaf2-39e5725dc367_204946748"]}, {"text": "Many practitioners emphasize that the medicinal use of plants should be overseen by qualified doctors and incorporated mainly as preventive measures, rather than for primary treatment of serious diseases.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "Herbs are commonly used as supportive care for chronic conditions that do not fully resolve with conventional Western medicine, such as diseases of the spine and joints.", "citations": ["d3caa544-d81f-43ac-9135-59e2be0875b3_440986270"]}, {"text": "Herbal remedies may complement standard therapies, aiming to improve organ function and overall quality of life for patients.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "However, medical professionals caution that herbal approaches should not be used to replace scientifically proven antitumor or curative treatments.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "The registration and official approval of herbal medicines in India and globally require rigorous clinical trials to demonstrate effectiveness and safety, paralleling protocols for Western pharmaceuticals.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "Recent research highlights include the synthesis of compounds based on curcumin (from turmeric), which has shown promising anticancer effects and is undergoing further clinical investigation.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "In India, institutional support for herbal medicine is robust, with specialized hospitals, the Department of AYUSH (Ayurveda, Yoga, Unani, Siddha & Homeopathy), and numerous research centers like the Central Council for Research in Ayurvedic Sciences (CCRAS) and the All India Institute of Ayurveda (AIIA) dedicated to studying and validating traditional remedies.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "The practice and teaching of herbal medicine are formalized in medical curricula, ensuring practitioners have a strong background in both traditional and modern medical sciences.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "Public interest in herbal and alternative medicine surged during the COVID-19 pandemic, as people sought preventive and adjunctive health solutions.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "Despite global interest and anecdotal reports of benefit, most doctors and scientists agree that serious diseases, such as cancers and severe infections, cannot be reliably cured with herbal medicine alone.", "citations": ["d3caa544-d81f-43ac-9135-59e2be0875b3_440986270"]}, {"text": "Authorities stress the importance of integrating herbal remedies judiciously into comprehensive treatment plans under professional medical supervision, to ensure patient safety and to prevent fraudulent or unproven claims.", "citations": ["262765a4-72f4-4475-9a99-4e18d21d394f_114004108"]}, {"text": "Traditional Indian medicine, often known as Ayurveda, relies on simple plant and animal products rooted in centuries of empirical use rather than the combination drugs of modern Western medicine.", "citations": ["0053caff-ce50-4f8c-a7e8-dc8d281cc850_665530319"]}, {"text": "This system is founded on an individualized approach, in which people have a dominant dosha and their unique balance among three doshas determines health status and treatment.", "citations": ["e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793"]}, {"text": "Ayurvedic remedies primarily employ medicinal herbs to improve health and treat disease, with a focus on mental, spiritual, and inner balance, reflecting the system\u2019s holistic philosophy.", "citations": ["607faf79-5e21-438a-ba49-23d3cc9c8b7e_1053372583"]}, {"text": "High-quality research on Ayurveda and other traditional medical systems remains difficult to conduct, and side effects of some Ayurvedic preparations have been noted in published studies, such as those in British medical journals.", "citations": ["e02c016b-9a11-4d76-93bc-c339103d09ea_364440793"]}, {"text": "The World Health Organization has expressed great interest in alternative medicine and launched a new center to study its integration and quality control, though some, like Professor Emeritus Edzard Ernst, point out that exaggerated claims must be carefully scrutinized as the center evolves.", "citations": ["cb9ef0c6-8b7e-40ec-a20a-a356d3083fe7_261399576"]}, {"text": "Anthropologists see great value in integrating traditional and Western medical systems, as they are shaped by cultural, religious, and social structures that deeply affect health behaviors, disease explanation, and treatment preferences.", "citations": ["8c8949e9-49b9-4fe5-8e7d-8fdc81147c81_870232379"]}, {"text": "In many regions where access to modern medical care is limited, traditional medicine\u2014including Indian herbal medicine\u2014remains a crucial option, sometimes addressing conditions overlooked by mainstream medicine.", "citations": ["ee7986bf-3004-47d0-96ef-8e6b16e59d08_842613544"]}, {"text": "An example of Indian herbal medicine in practice is the use of figs, which are valued in both Indian and Chinese traditions for their fiber content and purported capacity to slow digestion and reduce chronic disease risk.", "citations": ["dc1da997-972a-45ab-95b6-b564c3c24d5f_741906153"]}, {"text": "Ayurvedic institutions, including hospitals and research centers, conduct studies and provide treatments, while also serving as important cultural resources for communities for whom traditional medicine aligns with spiritual and ethical values.", "citations": ["607faf79-5e21-438a-ba49-23d3cc9c8b7e_1053372583"]}, {"text": "The interaction between religion, medicine, and social life shapes both the application and the ethical framework of Indian herbal medicine, with anthropologists emphasizing that both traditional and Western systems offer complementary benefits.", "citations": ["607faf79-5e21-438a-ba49-23d3cc9c8b7e_1053372583"]}, {"text": "Despite the scientific achievements of Western medicine, Indian herbal medicine holds an important place, especially in disease prevention, mental health, and in settings where cultural beliefs significantly influence health-seeking behavior.", "citations": ["607faf79-5e21-438a-ba49-23d3cc9c8b7e_1053372583"]}, {"text": "Wu Pei-Zhen, author of \"Five Elements of Healthy Healthy Eating\", shared that after her family member with terminal cancer saw their health worsen from chemotherapy and radiotherapy, they were given only one month to live.", "citations": ["a5a5b51d-df08-498c-b13f-426927fb5d11_68445856"]}, {"text": "She emphasized the importance of inheriting traditional medicine and practicing it throughout life.", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "Wu has dedicated over 60 years to researching traditional Chinese medicine (TCM).", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "She noted that her father's lifelong wish was to study Chinese medicine, and she intends to continue his legacy.", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "Wu believes that TCM must be integrated with modern research to encourage innovation.", "citations": ["417dbf82-e0ba-434e-921b-60bdff2549de_370519638"]}, {"text": "For six years, she focused on studying TCM theory.", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "Recently, Zhou Chaofan was listed among famous Chinese medicine practitioners due to his dedicated research.", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "Sharing knowledge is encouraged to reach more people.", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "The Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK) offers a 39-day moxibustion program merging Chinese and Western medicine to treat hypothermia and improve immunity.", "citations": ["4d9b9ce0-3154-45fc-a78f-eb9c22a6b884_727728826"]}, {"text": "In this method, medicine applied to acupuncture points stimulates meridians and organs, enhancing the body's vital qi and dispelling coldness for disease prevention and treatment.", "citations": ["4d9b9ce0-3154-45fc-a78f-eb9c22a6b884_727728826"]}, {"text": "It was also noted that remedies like Lianhuaqing can relieve symptoms but pandemic prevention cannot rely solely on TCM.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "The efficacy of these remedies has not been fully verified by modern clinical trials such as double-blind studies.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "In the 20th century, China recognized the need to catch up with Western medicine and technology.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Yet, traditional medical knowledge must be shared for it to benefit more people.", "citations": ["6af3226f-8a23-485b-83b7-42dd75becf5e_52332329"]}, {"text": "Chinese herbal medicine contains active compounds, and centuries of usage have clarified their effects.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Practitioners maintain that these effects can be reliably predicted based on long-term experience.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "The accumulated herbal experience should be valued.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "German experts highlight that TCM features active ingredients but also caution against direct comparisons with Western medicine.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Historical remedies are considered relatively safe but require modern evaluations to confirm efficacy and safety within healthcare systems.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Even in China, practice is scrutinized beyond historical usage.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Many TCM remedies remain under clinical observation due to limited scientific validation.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Traditionally, the causes of diseases like epidemics were attributed to seasonal factors rather than pathogens.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "Ultimately, scientific methods were key to epidemic control.", "citations": ["420c2aae-8426-41ce-b8fb-44cc214ac8ce_591306816"]}, {"text": "People from diverse backgrounds, such as Malaysian-Chinese like Woolende and young Chinese practitioners, dedicate themselves to TCM.", "citations": ["417dbf82-e0ba-434e-921b-60bdff2549de_370519638"]}, {"text": "Various moxibustion therapies, such as \u201cTian Moxibustion,\u201d and customized herbal soups are applied to boost \u201cyang\u201d energy.", "citations": ["5d913689-c6cb-4cd4-9727-801ce1051b51_834262728"]}, {"text": "Practitioners prescribe different herbal formulas according to body constitution and seasonal timing.", "citations": ["5d913689-c6cb-4cd4-9727-801ce1051b51_834262728"]}, {"text": "A photo by Dr. Chiu Shih-cheung, a registered Hong Kong TCM doctor, is mentioned.", "citations": ["5d913689-c6cb-4cd4-9727-801ce1051b51_834262728"]}, {"text": "A multidisciplinary approach is needed for complex diseases, requiring innovation in TCM research methods.", "citations": ["417dbf82-e0ba-434e-921b-60bdff2549de_370519638"]}, {"text": "CUHK promotes TCM application on specific days for disease prevention and treatment.", "citations": ["0a1f297f-6629-405b-8104-0ef5fe9f916c_881616569"]}, {"text": "The \u201cTrivolta\u201d days, being the hottest, carry particular treatment significance for augmenting \u201cyang\u201d energy.", "citations": ["0a1f297f-6629-405b-8104-0ef5fe9f916c_881616569"]}, {"text": "Personalized herbal teas are also part of the regimen, adapted to climate and mood, as shared by Tim Vukan, a German TCM teacher.", "citations": ["fe695035-cb2e-4479-b4e9-2499592f660c_718846514"]}, {"text": "Interest in TCM is growing worldwide, especially amid the COVID-19 pandemic.", "citations": ["fe695035-cb2e-4479-b4e9-2499592f660c_718846514"]}, {"text": "Tim Vukan acknowledges the strengths of Western medicine but states that TCM can complement it.", "citations": ["fe695035-cb2e-4479-b4e9-2499592f660c_718846514"]}, {"text": "Tim reported firsthand accounts of COVID-19 patients recovering quickly and becoming healthier with TCM treatments.", "citations": ["fe695035-cb2e-4479-b4e9-2499592f660c_718846514"]}, {"text": "He concluded that there is significant unexplored potential in TCM.", "citations": ["417dbf82-e0ba-434e-921b-60bdff2549de_370519638"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1048", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Oceans are experiencing a state of complete imbalance, with acidification almost doubling since the 1990s.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}, {"text": "Ocean acidification, caused by rising CO2 levels, impacts a wide range of marine life beyond coral reefs.", "citations": ["af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060"]}, {"text": "Shellfish such as clams and oysters depend on higher pH waters for survival and growth but are now threatened by acidification.", "citations": ["af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060"]}, {"text": "Kelp has been found to absorb carbon and nitrogen from water, acting as a natural way to fight ocean acidification.", "citations": ["c024df85-6885-448a-ae9d-e9d231319c98_521833846"]}, {"text": "Research has shown that growing kelp can help mitigate acidification and increase the growth of bivalves in both lab experiments and on oyster farms.", "citations": ["af4623f9-11e4-4872-acf1-82ab58601269_463596060"]}, {"text": "Phytoplankton convert carbon dioxide into cellular material and are essential for oceanic life and fisheries, but harmful algal blooms can damage habitats and contaminate water.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "Marine dead zones, areas with low oxygen levels caused by pollution and nutrient overload, are increasing due to environmental imbalances.", "citations": ["d381a959-ef93-41ce-aeb8-490a933c9477_186257362"]}, {"text": "NASA\u2019s PACE Mission studies microscopic oceanic particles (like phytoplankton) and atmospheric aerosols that influence weather, climate, and the health of marine ecosystems.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "Aerosols in the atmosphere affect cloud formation, weather, and solar energy, further impacting ocean and climate dynamics.", "citations": ["c27ea17b-2954-4f2d-a161-ed453632d5b7_864436468"]}, {"text": "Marine ecosystem protection involves educating younger generations about climate change and promoting sustainable behaviors.", "citations": ["bf6475e6-f8d3-460b-939e-9825c935a3fd_459604371"]}, {"text": "School programs are shifting toward sustainability education, with student-led campaigns encouraging activities like bicycling to reduce emissions.", "citations": ["40494713-a3b7-4c5a-9331-c2e1b4d232d7_946968091"]}, {"text": "Community-driven efforts, such as composting and reducing waste, help keep litter and plastics from reaching the ocean and contribute to carbon sequestration.", "citations": ["13b82c67-6c6c-45b6-84a0-f1c81ebf88a3_673637388"]}, {"text": "Groups like nuns and Indigenous women are joining forces to create kelp farms to clean up coastal waters and fight acidification.", "citations": ["c024df85-6885-448a-ae9d-e9d231319c98_521833846"]}, {"text": "Families can help the marine world by not littering at beaches, reducing plastic use, considering the source of their seafood, choosing renewable energy, and composting food waste.", "citations": ["bf6475e6-f8d3-460b-939e-9825c935a3fd_459604371"]}, {"text": "Efforts like the Long Island Sound Study show collaboration is needed to restore ocean health, but there is still much work to be done.", "citations": ["c024df85-6885-448a-ae9d-e9d231319c98_521833846"]}, {"text": "Protecting ocean life requires both individual choices and larger community or scientific initiatives, as ocean conditions continue to change with climate.", "citations": ["bf6475e6-f8d3-460b-939e-9825c935a3fd_459604371"]}, {"text": "Education, sustainable choices, and science-based solutions are all critical in addressing the threats posed by ocean acidification to marine life.", "citations": ["bf6475e6-f8d3-460b-939e-9825c935a3fd_459604371"]}, {"text": "The distribution of salt by ocean currents plays a crucial role in regulating the global climate.", "citations": ["a4a87dd7-d6d2-46e9-914a-8713a36eec6c_201241564"]}, {"text": "Studying climate anomalies like the Little Ice Age is significant because it helps scientists understand mechanisms and processes that can be caused by global warming due to human activities.", "citations": ["a4a87dd7-d6d2-46e9-914a-8713a36eec6c_201241564"]}, {"text": "In this context, the advection of tropical salt to high northern latitudes helps maintain the stability of large-scale ocean circulation, including the transfer of warm Gulf Stream waters which are responsible for temperate temperatures in Europe.", "citations": ["a4a87dd7-d6d2-46e9-914a-8713a36eec6c_201241564"]}, {"text": "A reduction in the movement of salt to high northern latitudes can disrupt this circulation and alter regional climates.", "citations": ["a4a87dd7-d6d2-46e9-914a-8713a36eec6c_201241564"]}, {"text": "Such research contributes to our understanding of climate variability over time.", "citations": ["a4a87dd7-d6d2-46e9-914a-8713a36eec6c_201241564"]}, {"text": "Elections are an opportunity to draw the attention of society to the main issues of our life, including environmental challenges.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "Today it is necessary to consider ecology not only as a section of biology, but also in the broader context of the biosphere, its development, and the role of humans.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "We must strive not to lag in developing environmental awareness.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "Safe development can only be achieved by revising the concept of economic growth to prioritize ecological balance and the preservation of pristine nature.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "People must consciously embrace the need to preserve ecological balance.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "In 2004, Kazakhstan adopted a law \"On technical regulation\" that affects environmental policies.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "The importance of clean ecology and industrial safety is a key idea in state programs.", "citations": ["64f8d23d-33c6-41c4-8b78-83f7fc472f47_570929620"]}, {"text": "Environmental initiatives involve collaboration within communities.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "American scientists have identified new sources of carbon dioxide emissions into the atmosphere.", "citations": ["d3721dc1-024c-47b7-981d-80ab0f716d78_921043055"]}, {"text": "Scientists have used shells to determine how Earth\u2019s climate changed in the past.", "citations": ["4971bfa3-32c6-4832-a6ff-fb91155da654_1056925569"]}, {"text": "About 100 million years ago, underwater volcanic eruptions led to a lack of oxygen in the ocean and a decrease in pH levels.", "citations": ["4971bfa3-32c6-4832-a6ff-fb91155da654_1056925569"]}, {"text": "Environmental lessons in schools are conducted to foster useful habits beneficial to the environment.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "For example, students learn to separate waste, use reusable containers, and repair items for long-term use.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Mobile laboratories in some areas take regular air samples and publish rapid results to engage public interest.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Such initiatives aim to foster environmental responsibility among young people.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Educational projects teach students what materials they use daily are made from, and how to recycle plastic.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Before the school year, students learned about the benefits of garbage sorting and recycling.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Events like sports matches are sometimes used to collect recyclable materials such as plastic bottles.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Human activities alter nature, often negatively impacting human well-being in return.", "citations": ["60009997-28f3-4001-891a-83762f2f8982_260189587"]}, {"text": "Projects and media highlight the challenges, including marine pollution and the importance of water for all living things.", "citations": ["be23f594-6bf2-4109-a880-58531c71d583_167298728"]}, {"text": "Oceans are both crucial for life and sources of global challenges, particularly pollution.", "citations": ["be23f594-6bf2-4109-a880-58531c71d583_167298728"]}, {"text": "Large scientific and educational projects feature lectures and exhibitions on environmental themes including the \u201cOcean of Science.\u201d  \nRaising environmental culture and responsibility among students is a key goal of educational and outreach efforts.", "citations": ["ba061fea-b336-4a91-a475-718c73ed3298_450653877"]}, {"text": "Emissions must be further reduced to contain global warming to 1.5\u00b0C.", "citations": ["996a01d1-566d-4dec-9fa3-8d4a444ee736_849769993"]}, {"text": "One technique to reduce atmospheric CO\u2082 is to spread crushed, mineral-rich rocks that absorb carbon dioxide into soil or water.", "citations": ["996a01d1-566d-4dec-9fa3-8d4a444ee736_849769993"]}, {"text": "This process imitates a natural one that usually takes tens of thousands of years, but scientists are trying to accelerate it.", "citations": ["996a01d1-566d-4dec-9fa3-8d4a444ee736_849769993"]}, {"text": "However, the effects of large-scale use of this method on ecosystems are still uncertain.", "citations": ["996a01d1-566d-4dec-9fa3-8d4a444ee736_849769993"]}, {"text": "The environment consists of everything that surrounds us: humans, animals, plants, and non-living things, which must remain in balance to prevent environmental disruption.", "citations": ["a793a16e-3781-434b-ad64-5817df215b72_282573853"]}, {"text": "Ocean acidification is primarily caused by the absorption of carbon dioxide from the atmosphere, mainly resulting from human activities like burning fossil fuels.", "citations": ["3e2309c5-d384-4b5a-9e39-63b12b32aa69_521538089"]}, {"text": "A study by Espinel Velasco et al.", "citations": ["e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048"]}, {"text": "revealed that larval breathing rates increased significantly when exposed to both acidification and warming.", "citations": ["e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048"]}, {"text": "Zooplankton\u2014the small, often microscopic, organisms that drift in the ocean\u2014are a major food source for many marine species.", "citations": ["e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048"]}, {"text": "Copepods, a type of zooplankton, play a key role in the Arctic food web.", "citations": ["e35a74c7-1c1d-4f5d-b2ec-ccc9befc043b_968649048"]}, {"text": "Acidification can disrupt the balance of aquatic ecosystems, just as acid rain once rendered Lake Colden in New York too acidic for fish life.", "citations": ["453e8758-3711-4e19-8699-bc8d38becae7_89856718"]}, {"text": "There is always uncertainty about the full extent of the consequences of acidification on marine environments.", "citations": ["453e8758-3711-4e19-8699-bc8d38becae7_89856718"]}, {"text": "Coastal ecosystems, while covering only 2% of global ocean areas, can store more carbon per area than terrestrial forests.", "citations": ["b5d8211f-a7cd-4026-8776-fac7d9234b22_910196607"]}, {"text": "The U.S. was the first country to include blue carbon\u2014carbon stored in coastal and marine ecosystems\u2014in greenhouse gas inventories.", "citations": ["b5d8211f-a7cd-4026-8776-fac7d9234b22_910196607"]}, {"text": "Different forms of carbon, including black carbon and red carbon, impact the environment in various ways; black carbon contributes significantly to global warming, while the role of biochar is also being examined for carbon storage.", "citations": ["b5d8211f-a7cd-4026-8776-fac7d9234b22_910196607"]}, {"text": "Wetlands are vital for preventing floods, storing water, and combating climate change, but many are degraded and need restoration for continued service to biodiversity and people.", "citations": ["0eff4cba-a185-476c-837c-d07bdfb721cd_138446460"]}, {"text": "Many marine animals, especially those with calcium carbonate shells or skeletons, are negatively affected by lower pH levels in seawater\u2014particularly in the early life stages.", "citations": ["eabaa8bc-af88-4b73-a1b2-dec0f49336fd_390178312"]}, {"text": "Seas and oceans, which cover over 70% of Earth\u2019s surface, are crucial for planet health but are threatened by acidification and other forms of pollution.", "citations": ["3e2309c5-d384-4b5a-9e39-63b12b32aa69_521538089"]}, {"text": "The children\u2019s animated series Noor and the Happy Planet highlights the danger of marine pollution, such as oil spills, on marine life.", "citations": ["3e2309c5-d384-4b5a-9e39-63b12b32aa69_521538089"]}, {"text": "Tools and policies are needed to protect and restore important aquatic ecosystems, including wetlands, lakes, and the ocean, to safeguard their crucial services.", "citations": ["0eff4cba-a185-476c-837c-d07bdfb721cd_138446460"]}, {"text": "Sustainability means preserving quality of life over time through the responsible use and stewardship of natural resources, which is directly related to the health and balance of marine and coastal ecosystems.", "citations": ["4563d49c-1281-4a86-a81e-fe7a2e6ad04b_940166519"]}, {"text": "The 61st National Science Exhibition was announced on the 13th, and Kaohsiung Ming-Hua National University won second place in Life and Applied Sciences (II), Environmental Protection and Livelihood, Mathematics, and Earth Science.", "citations": ["d23c8f55-b03b-4542-a578-8865bf855660_740071897"]}, {"text": "To educate the public about detection technology and scientific verification, the National Museum of Marine Science and Technology held a \"Water Spiritual Health Examination Experience Workshop\" during the winter holiday this year.", "citations": ["a72c22cb-8fc9-4715-af59-9bd8d63f3f72_750333072"]}, {"text": "Ap Lei Chau Harbour School was chosen as a finalist for the Best Environmental Action Schools Award 2023 and is the only Hong Kong school on the shortlist.", "citations": ["09ef5f7e-f47e-4b8e-b301-c32e10823525_213029033"]}, {"text": "The $100 million carbon reduction competition, initiated by Elon Musk, has selected 23 student teams to develop their own carbon reduction plans and methods.", "citations": ["8c962aae-737c-42c2-aa71-5e4bbf8453b3_85792730"]}, {"text": "Elon Musk will fund the competition for up to four years, provided teams demonstrate their ability to capture CO2 from the air and store it for at least 100 years.", "citations": ["8c962aae-737c-42c2-aa71-5e4bbf8453b3_85792730"]}, {"text": "Five million dollars of the competition prize is dedicated to student awards to motivate school-based groups.", "citations": ["8c962aae-737c-42c2-aa71-5e4bbf8453b3_85792730"]}, {"text": "One team\u2019s objective is to scale up algae production to improve ocean health, with some algae to be incorporated into building materials like refractory bricks for efficient carbon storage.", "citations": ["8c962aae-737c-42c2-aa71-5e4bbf8453b3_85792730"]}, {"text": "Their method involves liquefying plants, turning them into juices, and infusing them underground.", "citations": ["8c962aae-737c-42c2-aa71-5e4bbf8453b3_85792730"]}, {"text": "The \u201cNew Taipei Institute for Sustainable Future\u201d camp, titled Green Life for Young People, encourages students to let \"green seeds\" grow in New North.", "citations": ["82d8d37b-c2f7-4002-8f77-55a29d716309_796927702"]}, {"text": "Some students pledged not to overconsume and waste clothing as part of their group\u2019s green declaration.", "citations": ["82d8d37b-c2f7-4002-8f77-55a29d716309_796927702"]}, {"text": "A junior high school experiential camp led students to study the rich ecology of the Ma Gang tidal zone.", "citations": ["82d8d37b-c2f7-4002-8f77-55a29d716309_796927702"]}, {"text": "Efforts are also focused on educating the next generation about marine life protection and sustainable use of marine environments and resources.", "citations": ["737716dd-54d2-4f21-bd65-aa30afb3f743_253838142"]}, {"text": "Taitung University\u2019s USR Y-2 Project earned the Silver Award at Asia\u2019s Most Influential Design Award.", "citations": ["bfa42ac1-80c4-4b2c-84de-c5b601616cfc_666385872"]}, {"text": "The event showcases steps from ocean experience to beach clean-ups and creative projects from sea waste, aiming to inspire ocean stewardship.", "citations": ["bfa42ac1-80c4-4b2c-84de-c5b601616cfc_666385872"]}, {"text": "EdUHK is piloting the Primary Science Curriculum in three schools to test polar expedition knowledge and social service experience.", "citations": ["df153f4c-8e9e-4929-8879-e821675c279a_207588701"]}, {"text": "The course is divided into three parts, focusing on promoting understanding of global climate change.", "citations": ["df153f4c-8e9e-4929-8879-e821675c279a_207588701"]}, {"text": "To foster ocean conservation, Chenggong Junior High School organized a beach clean-up at Crescent Bay in Zhubei City, leading students to reflect on human relationships with the ocean.", "citations": ["03b8f703-dbe1-45c1-a82d-40c6157ec2a4_856744375"]}, {"text": "Teachers and students gathered significant marine waste in two hours during the clean-up.", "citations": ["03b8f703-dbe1-45c1-a82d-40c6157ec2a4_856744375"]}, {"text": "The excess consumption of resources means the Earth cannot replenish or absorb more waste sustainably.", "citations": ["d1e130e3-fccb-41cd-884a-33f077736f02_269068601"]}, {"text": "While reducing resource use in wealthy countries appears simple, it is a just and smart path.", "citations": ["d1e130e3-fccb-41cd-884a-33f077736f02_269068601"]}, {"text": "GDP, originally a war-time economic measure, fails to count harmful or non-monetary positive activities.", "citations": ["d1e130e3-fccb-41cd-884a-33f077736f02_269068601"]}, {"text": "Continuous GDP growth requires ever-increasing outputs without regard for environmental consequences.", "citations": ["d1e130e3-fccb-41cd-884a-33f077736f02_269068601"]}, {"text": "Historically, rising production was feasible, but today, humanity\u2019s impacts have made this approach unsustainable.", "citations": ["d1e130e3-fccb-41cd-884a-33f077736f02_269068601"]}, {"text": "We have reached a threshold where more GDP growth can increase poverty rather than reduce it.", "citations": ["d1e130e3-fccb-41cd-884a-33f077736f02_269068601"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1054", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "The United States recently lifted its temporary ban on imports of Mexican avocados, bringing relief to food industry workers and investors on both sides of the border.", "citations": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532"]}, {"text": "A Mexican inspector who raised concerns over the avocado trade received a voice-mail threat, illustrating the risks facing those attempting to regulate the industry.", "citations": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532"]}, {"text": "A growing Hispanic population in the U.S., particularly among Generation Z, has driven increased demand for avocados, according to analysts.", "citations": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532"]}, {"text": "Economists view this demand as a positive story about growth and trade facilitated by agreements between the U.S. and Mexico.", "citations": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532"]}, {"text": "However, the avocado industry's growth has also led to concerns and challenges.", "citations": ["3f2668d2-a695-4d4c-a2be-36032d9a07f4_87857532"]}, {"text": "Mexican avocado production was forecasted to fall by eight percent year-on-year for the 2021-22 season, according to a USDA GAIN report.", "citations": ["114d1622-c9c5-4614-b132-9c9189790987_442554566"]}, {"text": "The forecast for exports to the U.S. in that period was 1.04 million metric tons.", "citations": ["114d1622-c9c5-4614-b132-9c9189790987_442554566"]}, {"text": "Nutritional campaigns in the United States promote avocados and sandwiches as healthy choices in line with dietary guidelines.", "citations": ["22d1bde3-9e53-4f32-8e5f-1b5543ff06ac_95655205"]}, {"text": "Organizations like the Hass Avocado Board and National Wheat Foundation are involved in education and research related to avocados and grains.", "citations": ["22d1bde3-9e53-4f32-8e5f-1b5543ff06ac_95655205"]}, {"text": "Almost all avocados consumed in the U.S., and most worldwide, are descended from a single tree cultivated by Milwaukee mailman Rudolph Hass.", "citations": ["d4cf71aa-8523-4555-bbbd-50f6ad116aa8_793168503"]}, {"text": "The Hass variety, prized for its eating quality and post-harvest performance, became globally dominant after the 1970s.", "citations": ["d4cf71aa-8523-4555-bbbd-50f6ad116aa8_793168503"]}, {"text": "Despite the popularity of his avocados, Hass earned little financially due to the unauthorized propagation of his tree.", "citations": ["d4cf71aa-8523-4555-bbbd-50f6ad116aa8_793168503"]}, {"text": "The brand \u201cAvocados From Mexico\u201d recently celebrated a decade as the U.S.'s preferred avocado provider, emphasizing its positive impact on all stakeholders and its growing sales channels.", "citations": ["8ca9c8e9-43b5-47a1-b8c7-47fcb66e4530_31759721"]}, {"text": "Data shows that \u201cUltra\u201d retail shoppers are more likely to buy avocados from multiple outlets, reflecting diverse consumer habits.", "citations": ["18b0c150-d33b-4cb5-9835-b64b393fa50f_34495004"]}, {"text": "In Australia, local avocado growers have struggled due to poor seasons and competition from imports, with some lamenting that their produce is being overlooked.", "citations": ["16a00b71-6e6c-4015-b1b2-d5437d613bb8_463765569"]}, {"text": "Growers emphasize the importance of consumer support for local fruit and vegetable shops to help their industry survive.", "citations": ["49294516-8781-4816-902e-aed083d255fe_712225785"]}, {"text": "Avocado imports have risen in Europe but declined in China, and this has not resulted in price drops, as Peruvian avocados dominate the market in certain periods.", "citations": ["fd214626-2761-443a-aee5-3562ee536d85_342391363"]}, {"text": "In the U.S., prices for avocados have recently dipped slightly across grades.", "citations": ["16a00b71-6e6c-4015-b1b2-d5437d613bb8_463765569"]}, {"text": "The recent U.S. ban affected Michoacan, the only Mexican state fully authorized to export avocados to the U.S., raising concerns about supply if the ban persisted.", "citations": ["e4fbae76-8864-456f-a77d-b9388c3fe828_80897540"]}, {"text": "Global avocado sales have increased by over 25% in the past year, but low prices have put additional pressure on struggling growers.", "citations": ["16a00b71-6e6c-4015-b1b2-d5437d613bb8_463765569"]}, {"text": "By 2050, avocados may begin to disappear from Earth, with prices soaring according to a new report by the London-based charity Christian Aid.", "citations": ["c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141"]}, {"text": "Avocados are popular and nutritious, but they are not suitable for hot, drought-prone climates, which are expected to become more common due to the climate crisis.", "citations": ["c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141"]}, {"text": "This changing climate will make it difficult for avocado trees to grow and produce fruit.", "citations": ["c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141"]}, {"text": "The report also states that avocados are not the only product at risk from climate change; coffee and cashews will also be vulnerable.", "citations": ["c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141"]}, {"text": "Avocados contain a large amount of fiber and vitamins and are seen as a major source of nutrition.", "citations": ["05c36d53-00e7-49c4-948b-ba7eb7772281_232796181"]}, {"text": "There are dozens of avocado varieties, but only a few are widely sold in stores, with certain varieties best bought in summer and autumn.", "citations": ["861e6a80-d443-495c-ad29-37fc509e0e23_914971541"]}, {"text": "Avocados are valuable for their oil, which is rich in a complex of fatty acids.", "citations": ["861e6a80-d443-495c-ad29-37fc509e0e23_914971541"]}, {"text": "The fruit is high in potassium, even more than bananas, and helps muscles recover faster after training.", "citations": ["05c36d53-00e7-49c4-948b-ba7eb7772281_232796181"]}, {"text": "Monounsaturated fatty acids in avocados help reduce levels of bad cholesterol in the body.", "citations": ["ecd6b238-6fad-49a4-bc96-8d1d5338a898_659621063"]}, {"text": "Eating avocado daily can improve metabolism, normalize intestinal function, and confer benefits for eye and cardiovascular health.", "citations": ["ecd6b238-6fad-49a4-bc96-8d1d5338a898_659621063"]}, {"text": "Avocado is also considered an ideal snack for those dieting due to its high fiber and healthy fat content, making you feel full longer.", "citations": ["c3288c91-d39a-4b1b-b0e7-d8c7cdd380c8_1062070444"]}, {"text": "Scientific studies show avocados help prevent heart disease and lower blood pressure through their beneficial composition of potassium, folic acid, fiber, and healthy fats.", "citations": ["ecd6b238-6fad-49a4-bc96-8d1d5338a898_659621063"]}, {"text": "Despite benefits, avocados are high in calories and should not be overeaten; no more than two medium avocados per day are recommended for those without contraindications.", "citations": ["05c36d53-00e7-49c4-948b-ba7eb7772281_232796181"]}, {"text": "People with birch pollen allergies may experience cross-reactions when eating avocado, and it is not recommended for people who are overweight due to its calorie content.", "citations": ["05c36d53-00e7-49c4-948b-ba7eb7772281_232796181"]}, {"text": "Ripe avocados are soft but not mushy, with a light yellow flesh and dark brown outer skin for the \"Hass\" variety; they can be stored for up to two weeks.", "citations": ["255cffed-9128-4d3c-aeb9-60ac4940c381_1058826612"]}, {"text": "Signs of spoilage include dark spots on the peel, white or gray mold, or a mushy texture, and spoiled avocado should not be consumed.", "citations": ["05c36d53-00e7-49c4-948b-ba7eb7772281_232796181"]}, {"text": "Popular ways to eat avocado include using it as a face mask, on toast with eggs, with red fish or cream cheese, or blended into smoothies and desserts.", "citations": ["05c36d53-00e7-49c4-948b-ba7eb7772281_232796181"]}, {"text": "In summary, global avocado demand is rising due to its health benefits, but this increase, coupled with climate change, is expected to significantly impact its availability and production, affecting both consumer access and producing regions.", "citations": ["c0a6998e-f6dc-4da7-9421-f8e7e575bd75_992753141"]}, {"text": "Global demand for avocados has surged in recent years due to their recognized health benefits, such as improving digestive, brain, eye, and heart function, reducing high blood pressure, and providing essential nutrients like fiber, minerals, and vitamins.", "citations": ["d2c61fd8-2697-4a53-aef7-daa8e78c22b3_1037474445"]}, {"text": "Studies have shown that a daily intake of avocados can lower body fat accumulation, enhance cognitive health, and even contribute beneficial compounds in the fight against diseases like acute myelogenous leukemia.", "citations": ["7ea6248f-34db-4bbf-9d4d-6bdffa3190e2_72947050"]}, {"text": "Despite these health advantages, avocado production comes at a significant environmental cost, primarily due to its very high water requirements compared to other crops\u2014one kilogram of avocados needs substantially more water than tomatoes, for example.", "citations": ["9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657"]}, {"text": "The water footprint of avocado cultivation has created water scarcity and resulted in the depletion of underground aquifers in major production areas.", "citations": ["9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657"]}, {"text": "In the state of Michoac\u00e1n, Mexico, which produces around 80% of the world\u2019s avocados, expansion of avocado farms has caused deforestation, soil erosion, and chemical contamination of water sources, leading to severe environmental degradation.", "citations": ["9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657"]}, {"text": "The economic benefits of the avocado boom have included increased income for some local farmers and the export sector, but the environmental damage and reduced water availability have threatened the sustainability of traditional farming and contributed to rising food inflation and bankruptcies in some regions.", "citations": ["9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657"]}, {"text": "Local farming communities in major producing countries report difficulties competing internationally because of price competition and the lower production costs of some countries, risking their livelihoods as land becomes less suitable for other crops.", "citations": ["9762174a-cfc3-4c89-b053-eb9f17c3a689_91630562"]}, {"text": "Climate change is expected to worsen these challenges, as rising temperatures and altered rainfall patterns make current avocado-growing regions, especially in the tropics, less viable in the future, potentially shifting production to new areas in countries like China, Argentina, and the United States.", "citations": ["9f7babf6-335c-4686-b3fe-7602641d29a4_195587657"]}, {"text": "Most of these changes are likely irreversible for the rest of the century, regardless of the global response to climate change, making it essential for agricultural sectors in the tropics to adapt by shifting which crops are cultivated and where.", "citations": ["807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_655254533"]}, {"text": "There has been little research on adapting tropical agricultural systems sustainably, even as the population living in these regions is projected to grow by up to a billion people by 2050.", "citations": ["807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_655254533"]}, {"text": "Debates continue in producing countries, including Morocco, over the ongoing expansion of avocado farms, given the impact on water resources, forests, and wider agricultural inflation, calling into question the future sustainability of the global avocado market.", "citations": ["18665f57-7b47-4cae-9c9d-5fc30625182f_930516690"]}, {"text": "Given these factors, while avocado is a valuable and nutritious food, consumers are urged to consider the environmental and social impacts of their choices.", "citations": ["3624ad80-21b0-4779-a0bf-139136df3885_307995514"]}, {"text": "Avocado has risen sharply in global popularity as a \u201csuperfood\u201d due to its taste and versatility, commonly featured in salads and sauces for its health benefits, particularly among women.", "citations": ["ed28e7a7-da90-4a40-b12e-0760be78ebed_839177627"]}, {"text": "Environmental awareness about avocados is increasing, with concerns about the high water required for their cultivation and their significant carbon footprint, leading some restaurants worldwide to replace avocados with alternative ingredients.", "citations": ["e723799f-1810-462b-b84e-a0b5e5a4749d_1052218110"]}, {"text": "Growing avocados is very water-intensive, as reported by outlets including The Guardian and The Hill.", "citations": ["e723799f-1810-462b-b84e-a0b5e5a4749d_1052218110"]}, {"text": "In Mexico, especially the state of Michoac\u00e1n, avocados can be harvested up to four times a year due to the mild climate, making the crop extremely profitable and earning it the nickname \u201cgreen gold\u201d among local farmers.", "citations": ["0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_25051651"]}, {"text": "About 70% of all Mexican avocados are grown in Michoac\u00e1n, and most are exported to the United States, which consumes almost half the global avocado supply.", "citations": ["0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_55923929"]}, {"text": "The surge in avocado demand has significant economic benefits for local farmers; however, it also attracts criminal organizations who seek to control this lucrative trade.", "citations": ["c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_639626865"]}, {"text": "Violence has become a major concern in avocado-growing regions, with reports of crimes against politicians and community leaders; on one day, two mayoral candidates were killed in or near avocado farms in Michoac\u00e1n.", "citations": ["0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_55923929"]}, {"text": "The presence of criminal groups like the powerful Jalisco New Generation Cartel (CJNG) has led to fears that attacks may worsen during political events.", "citations": ["0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_25051651"]}, {"text": "Authorities in Mexico have vowed to restrict the export of avocados grown on illegally deforested land, responding to environmental and legal concerns.", "citations": ["0647188f-9964-4a4f-ae8e-63483708d38d_25051651"]}, {"text": "Michoac\u00e1n\u2019s environment has suffered, with deforestation and the loss of evergreen forests resulting from expanding avocado plantations.", "citations": ["c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_639626865"]}, {"text": "Avocado farming\u2019s high water needs and land requirements contribute to environmental degradation, while criminal violence brings severe social consequences for local communities.", "citations": ["c4df1771-8297-4414-adac-d7cd6bb376e0_639626865"]}, {"text": "Globally, avocados have grown from being a rare treat to an everyday food, driving up demand and making them more valuable.", "citations": ["ed28e7a7-da90-4a40-b12e-0760be78ebed_839177627"]}, {"text": "Because avocados blacken quickly after cutting, and must be shipped over long distances, this may contribute to food waste and further environmental cost.", "citations": ["ed28e7a7-da90-4a40-b12e-0760be78ebed_839177627"]}, {"text": "Though branded as a health food, nutritionists caution about excessive intake and the calorie density of avocados.", "citations": ["ed28e7a7-da90-4a40-b12e-0760be78ebed_839177627"]}, {"text": "Rising demand for avocados mirrors historical trends in other foods, where popularity has driven both price increases and environmental strain.", "citations": ["ed28e7a7-da90-4a40-b12e-0760be78ebed_839177627"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1056", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Fish oil is the fat or oil that\u2019s extracted from fish tissue.", "citations": ["3182f50b-5ca2-4c5a-b67f-fb7d793b213b_790782815"]}, {"text": "Studies have shown that fish oil supplements can improve liver function and inflammation, which may help reduce symptoms of NAFLD and the amount of fat in your liver.", "citations": ["3182f50b-5ca2-4c5a-b67f-fb7d793b213b_790782815"]}, {"text": "It is recommended to check the supplement label to ensure the fish oil has been tested for heavy metals like mercury to avoid further health issues.", "citations": ["3182f50b-5ca2-4c5a-b67f-fb7d793b213b_790782815"]}, {"text": "Omega-3 fatty acids are crucial for cell health but cannot be produced by the human body.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Supplements are an effective way to add vital nutrients into our diets, and many people rely on them for daily requirements.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "The body struggles to convert ALA into DHA and EPA, which can result in many people falling short of DHA and EPA needs.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "In recent decades, more Americans have turned to krill oil to meet their Omega-3 requirements.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Astaxanthin is a compound that gives salmon and flamingos their pink color and provides antioxidant health benefits.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Krill are a type of zooplankton, marine life that drift with ocean currents and serve as a food source for other marine animals.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Krill contribute to the ocean\u2019s carbon cycle by transferring waste to the ocean floor.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Using new methods, some companies now farm algae to develop a plant-based Omega-3 solution, which is seen as healthier and more sustainable.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Sustainable farming is an important aspect for some companies producing Omega-3 supplements from algae.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Since fish and krill obtain Omega-3s from algae, producing Omega-3 directly from algae is considered a potent and direct source.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Premium farmed salmon is not necessarily higher in Omega-3s than value brands, according to studies.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "Fish provide the Omega-3 fatty acids EPA and DHA, which boost heart health and cognitive function.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "Farmed salmon are usually fed a mixture of fish and vegetable oils; vegetable oils lack EPA and DHA found in seafood.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "Salmon contains not only Omega-3, but also selenium and phosphorus, important nutrients for health.", "citations": ["e9e0e25f-b317-4e99-8bf7-431ab1e290be_110862371"]}, {"text": "The feed acidifiers market, which includes products for animal nutrition such as salmon, is expected to grow significantly by 2027.", "citations": ["f5d0e854-eb55-4d44-ab24-b5048804780e_793015685"]}, {"text": "In animal farming, additives such as acidifiers, antioxidants, and binders are used for nutrition and processing purposes.", "citations": ["8d1dd922-41b0-47a2-b1eb-f924d97ee68f_337649161"]}, {"text": "Canned salmon is a good source of calcium, and salmon patties may use eggs, cream, or binding agents like flour or mashed potato as substitutes.", "citations": ["dec3ffef-8650-4ecc-8988-796331b84205_231908294"]}, {"text": "The white substance that seeps from cooked salmon is coagulated protein (albumin), which is harmless.", "citations": ["dec3ffef-8650-4ecc-8988-796331b84205_231908294"]}, {"text": "Ultra-processed foods (UPFs) include flavored yogurts and certain breads, and have mixed associations with health risks, including diabetes.", "citations": ["62134a86-7597-4cc1-8cd8-e1cc43452214_892870789"]}, {"text": "Despite debates over processing, these foods remain an important source of nutrition and are recognized as food.", "citations": ["62134a86-7597-4cc1-8cd8-e1cc43452214_892870789"]}, {"text": "Read the label to know what additives are present in products, but not all are harmless or beneficial.", "citations": ["789149d5-fe7b-459e-8fed-736f1975ecfe_996410336"]}, {"text": "E123 is banned in the food industry in Ukraine, the United States, and Europe.", "citations": ["789149d5-fe7b-459e-8fed-736f1975ecfe_996410336"]}, {"text": "E320 is considered highly dangerous and is on the red list in many countries.", "citations": ["789149d5-fe7b-459e-8fed-736f1975ecfe_996410336"]}, {"text": "Nutritionist Solomatina has linked the consumption of canned food to cancer development.", "citations": ["0b511100-9dd0-49b2-b0f8-03f05007f84c_891356597"]}, {"text": "Nutritionist Pisareva has highlighted the increased use of \u201cmeat glue\u201d in both meat and dairy products.", "citations": ["2907f781-1cd4-46e9-a487-a1ef0e32af48_228976823"]}, {"text": "Consuming large doses of fish oil supplements can increase the risk of stroke.", "citations": ["48b0913c-789a-4b7e-be6f-c45fa487b6bf_551487075"]}, {"text": "Oily fish is an excellent source of omega-3 fats and it is recommended to eat at least two servings of fish per week, with one being fatty fish.", "citations": ["48b0913c-789a-4b7e-be6f-c45fa487b6bf_551487075"]}, {"text": "Many modern food products would not exist without food additives, and the variety of products would be much smaller.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Additives like E330 (citric acid) occur naturally in citrus fruits.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Supplements with E numbers can cause consumer concerns and suspicion.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "E621 is the code for monosodium glutamate, which is used to enhance the meaty taste of foods.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "A Japanese study found that large doses of sodium glutamate caused blindness in rats, but such harmful doses are hard to reach for humans.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Glutamate is an amino acid and is not harmful for most people, but some sensitive individuals, especially children under three, may have issues.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Some preservatives\u2019 benefits are questionable, especially concerning why long-expired food is consumed.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Food additives should not increase the risks associated with food consumption.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Certain additives were first banned domestically, and then internationally.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "A daily allowance of 50 mg/kg nitrite was established for final products.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Products with very long shelf lives should be avoided.", "citations": ["9f3385a7-2658-4bd3-bcab-aea79e68b23c_109467898"]}, {"text": "Fish meal, including from sardine-ivasi, is an important component in feed and its high nutritional value has been confirmed by studies.", "citations": ["a9ff63c6-08c4-4648-8aa3-60eb3f0177fb_147069410"]}, {"text": "Fish and seafood allergies can require consultation with a specialist before using related supplements.", "citations": ["b6fb4342-3bba-47b7-852a-325e7aa4f3f6_123127076"]}, {"text": "Soluble fiber in fruit aids in removing heavy metals and radionuclides from the body.", "citations": ["b6fb4342-3bba-47b7-852a-325e7aa4f3f6_123127076"]}, {"text": "Vitamins are concentrated under the peel, but store-bought apple skins should be removed.", "citations": ["b6fb4342-3bba-47b7-852a-325e7aa4f3f6_123127076"]}, {"text": "Foods rich in omega-3, such as nut and olive oils, are important since the body cannot produce these fatty acids, and regular consumption is necessary.", "citations": ["7d58bb9a-7e94-4dfb-a9c9-a216979237a6_671049623"]}, {"text": "The uncontrolled use of dietary supplements can be dangerous, but supplements based on medical indications can be useful.", "citations": ["bcb41651-cd8e-411c-9a3d-5f0eacddbc7b_521746842"]}, {"text": "In Russia, such food additives are considered food products, and studies show a full set of required nutrients only exists in a high-calorie diet of 6,000 kcal.", "citations": ["1eb49566-5c7a-47fd-a909-e31a8d4a953a_764742955"]}, {"text": "Always consult a doctor with any health-related questions or before taking supplements.", "citations": ["7d58bb9a-7e94-4dfb-a9c9-a216979237a6_671049623"]}, {"text": "Many people over 60 take fish oil supplements for heart health benefits, but new studies suggest these supplements may not provide such benefits.", "citations": ["cefa0569-54ca-4f87-82eb-271295a6003f_108443026"]}, {"text": "Salmon, compared to other meats, is lower in saturated fat and is a good source of omega-3 fatty acids.", "citations": ["cefa0569-54ca-4f87-82eb-271295a6003f_108443026"]}, {"text": "Some people avoid fish due to allergies, preferences, or an aversion to its taste.", "citations": ["cefa0569-54ca-4f87-82eb-271295a6003f_108443026"]}, {"text": "For those new to fish, experts suggest starting with less oily, milder-tasting fish and serving it with other foods to make it more appealing.", "citations": ["cefa0569-54ca-4f87-82eb-271295a6003f_108443026"]}, {"text": "It is important to read the list of ingredients in any supplement, as they often contain more than just the fish oil.", "citations": ["cefa0569-54ca-4f87-82eb-271295a6003f_108443026"]}, {"text": "Large randomized trials, such as VITAL and ASCEND, have not found heart disease prevention benefits for fish oil supplements.", "citations": ["cefa0569-54ca-4f87-82eb-271295a6003f_108443026"]}, {"text": "To lower cholesterol, diets including fatty fish like salmon are recommended, with research linking compounds in salmon to improved cardiovascular health.", "citations": ["2ce269af-79cd-47d4-802a-9380284d341a_283971590"]}, {"text": "The Mediterranean diet, which emphasizes fish consumption, is considered a gold standard for health.", "citations": ["2ce269af-79cd-47d4-802a-9380284d341a_283971590"]}, {"text": "Convenience foods, including many products in vending machines, are often low in nutrients and high in sugar, preservatives, and artificial flavors.", "citations": ["2e6fcce7-0fbe-4f6b-8df5-b166f040da51_20109923"]}, {"text": "Processed foods can negatively affect health, and preparing healthy food in advance is recommended.", "citations": ["4478c79c-9d40-44ac-9b06-359294d40814_392610616"]}, {"text": "Eating too much salt leads to water retention and high blood pressure, while nuts, seeds, avocados, and oily fish offer healthier fats.", "citations": ["4478c79c-9d40-44ac-9b06-359294d40814_392610616"]}, {"text": "Oily fish, rich in omega-3 fats, should be incorporated in the diet at least twice per week.", "citations": ["4478c79c-9d40-44ac-9b06-359294d40814_392610616"]}, {"text": "Increased consumption of fiber and reduction of red meat and processed food improve bowel health and reduce cancer risk.", "citations": ["a9664608-1a4c-44fb-8434-ef74eee7f004_285231060"]}, {"text": "Nuts are highlighted as beneficial for brain health due to their protein, fat, fiber, and mineral content.", "citations": ["f9a8cecc-7fac-445f-aac5-4121cda22c66_210036713"]}, {"text": "Hydrogenated oils and modified fats can raise blood sugar, increase obesity risk, and have possible negative mental health effects.", "citations": ["61c92094-6e35-4911-ab94-774b3678ac54_398138047"]}, {"text": "Almost all foods are processed to varying degrees, and ultra-processed foods (UPF) make up a large portion of modern diets, especially among children and lower-income groups.", "citations": ["6038884b-2191-4eb9-9f0d-2fd3db9ff7b2_1009086867"]}, {"text": "To identify UPF, check for ingredients such as palm oil or multinational brands, and use open-source resources for food information.", "citations": ["6038884b-2191-4eb9-9f0d-2fd3db9ff7b2_1009086867"]}, {"text": "Fresh meat and fish are not considered ultra-processed.", "citations": ["6038884b-2191-4eb9-9f0d-2fd3db9ff7b2_1009086867"]}, {"text": "Fish oil is a widely used supplement for its omega-3 content, naturally found in the fatty tissue of fish like salmon, sardines, mackerel, herring, and trout.", "citations": ["d56edf75-4d08-4685-ad65-c646d88fe071_277963270"]}, {"text": "Recent studies highlight the importance of natural food sources for nutrients rather than relying solely on supplements, with vitamin D also emphasized as necessary for health.", "citations": ["d56edf75-4d08-4685-ad65-c646d88fe071_277963270"]}, {"text": "Frozen convenience foods often contain high levels of unhealthy fats and salts.", "citations": ["dc901cf7-47c1-45fc-97fd-58475f2fc539_558940326"]}, {"text": "Consumers should not blindly pursue \u201czero additive\u201d or \u201cpure natural\u201d labeled foods and should consider nutritional value as well.", "citations": ["0122fa0a-aafd-4451-8f97-e4a39a9dd88a_574761245"]}, {"text": "A nutritionist recommends eating about 100 grams of mackerel per week to meet the WHO\u2019s suggested intake of fish oil.", "citations": ["404b070d-f8bd-4b6d-839b-9cefe9de1c9e_161966176"]}, {"text": "Owing to climate change and rising temperatures, farmed fish are more susceptible to bacterial infections, leading to the use of additives in salmon feed.", "citations": ["206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288"]}, {"text": "Experimental studies have shown that adding lactic acid bacteria (such as B4 yogurt) to salmon feed can promote growth and enhance resistance to disease.", "citations": ["206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288"]}, {"text": "Fish raised without such additives in a control pond showed poorer appetite and slower growth, requiring drug treatments instead.", "citations": ["206276b7-7de2-4dab-9189-36c5eec717e8_576973288"]}, {"text": "Increased public food safety awareness in recent years has led to worries about additives not only in salmon but also in processed foods and seasonings.", "citations": ["a5472620-34cf-489b-bb7a-1bb01ae020f4_747436476"]}, {"text": "When applied lawfully and within regulatory standards, food additives are considered safe for health.", "citations": ["a5472620-34cf-489b-bb7a-1bb01ae020f4_747436476"]}, {"text": "Ingredients of processed foods must be disclosed per regulations from the Food and Drug Administration, ensuring consumers\u2019 right to know.", "citations": ["a5472620-34cf-489b-bb7a-1bb01ae020f4_747436476"]}, {"text": "Fish oil is valued for being rich in omega-3 fatty acids, crucial for human health, and is best sourced from clean waters like those in Norway for safety.", "citations": ["91aee897-fe74-4b54-9356-6771d0074425_312538134"]}, {"text": "Some processed fish foods, such as canned seafood, retain or even exceed the nutrient levels (for example, calcium) compared to their natural counterparts.", "citations": ["da8050c6-44cd-4f2b-b09d-20be779836d2_289222277"]}, {"text": "Proper storage is important for canned fish products to prevent contamination or leaching of can materials.", "citations": ["da8050c6-44cd-4f2b-b09d-20be779836d2_289222277"]}, {"text": "Fish sausages and similar processed foods are often high in fat, sodium, and contain flavor enhancers such as monosodium glutamate (MSG, E621) and disodium 5\u2019-ribonucleotide (E635).", "citations": ["9033d61f-3c6f-4c88-876c-a409bb2edabb_360529707"]}, {"text": "E635, when combined with MSG, increases the flavor enhancement effect up to fourfold compared to MSG alone.", "citations": ["9033d61f-3c6f-4c88-876c-a409bb2edabb_360529707"]}, {"text": "People with high blood pressure, heart, or kidney disease should limit intake of sodium and flavor enhancers.", "citations": ["9033d61f-3c6f-4c88-876c-a409bb2edabb_360529707"]}, {"text": "Processed fish products such as crab fillet sticks are high in sugar and various additives, contain little protein, and cannot substitute real fish or seafood as a protein source.", "citations": ["20ab6244-1bf9-4dd1-803b-156d39c6fd6e_847347059"]}, {"text": "Despite cost differences, such processed seafood alternatives usually have low protein content, high carbohydrate, and high additive levels.", "citations": ["da8050c6-44cd-4f2b-b09d-20be779836d2_289222277"]}, {"text": "Food safety standards and additive usage are regulated, and compliance with these regulations is crucial for minimizing health risks.", "citations": ["a5472620-34cf-489b-bb7a-1bb01ae020f4_747436476"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1066", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Labubu, a collectible toy monster elf created by Hong Kong designer Kasing Lung and marketed by Chinese toy giant Pop Mart, has rapidly become a viral sensation among teens and young adults globally.", "citations": ["27398311-0d51-4a3e-9c7c-7984b6ce6c57_710906697"]}, {"text": "The character's quirky design and whimsical facial expressions have fueled its mass appeal, capturing the affections of fans across Asia and beyond.", "citations": ["66ff9214-a746-4a1e-810b-c4cd893fd31c_841431456"]}, {"text": "Labubu's surging popularity is often attributed to its exclusivity and the social status it confers, as well as its frequent use as a playful fashion accessory among influencers and celebrities such as Rihanna.", "citations": ["27398311-0d51-4a3e-9c7c-7984b6ce6c57_710906697"]}, {"text": "On social media platforms, particularly TikTok, unboxing videos, display collections, and \"hunt\" stories for rare Labubu toys have proliferated, boosting the character's mystique and desirability.", "citations": ["800f4884-e725-4c28-8c02-74690335435c_79290377"]}, {"text": "This trending phenomenon taps into the broader appeal of mystery box collectibles and surprise elements, which encourage repeat purchases and elevate the sense of discovery for buyers.", "citations": ["8e02eb27-799d-4299-9b65-4a034d7227e6_224958643"]}, {"text": "Pop Mart has capitalized on this demand by staging limited edition releases and collaborations, which often see fans forming long queues and the toys selling out within minutes of launch online and in stores.", "citations": ["800f4884-e725-4c28-8c02-74690335435c_79290377"]}, {"text": "The hysteria is also fueled by the resale market, where rare Labubu figurines can fetch many times their original price, intensifying the \"must-have\" factor among collectors.", "citations": ["800f4884-e725-4c28-8c02-74690335435c_79290377"]}, {"text": "As a result, Pop Mart's revenue and global reach have surged, with financial reports indicating double-digit growth internationally and a significant increase in brand visibility.", "citations": ["8e02eb27-799d-4299-9b65-4a034d7227e6_224958643"]}, {"text": "The immense demand and strategic marketing have significantly boosted the net worth of Pop Mart's founder, reflecting the company's rapid ascent in the designer toy market.", "citations": ["8e02eb27-799d-4299-9b65-4a034d7227e6_224958643"]}, {"text": "Labubu's success epitomizes the impact of viral, youth-driven trends in the digital era, leveraging social media amplification, influencer adoption, and the psychology of collectible culture to create a global phenomenon.", "citations": ["27398311-0d51-4a3e-9c7c-7984b6ce6c57_710906697"]}, {"text": "Certainly!", "citations": ["6fdb3016-6928-4543-9e20-4f26c47b6d70_1031629894"]}, {"text": "Here is a coherent summary of the provided extracts, following your guidelines:\n\nTeenagers have adopted the trend of running on all fours, which has sparked debate about whether it should be considered a sport and raised safety concerns, particularly in Russia where calls for a ban have emerged.", "citations": ["3fcd0df2-8c79-4a4a-b2b2-989de7b0626b_773706126"]}, {"text": "The trend, called quadrobika, includes wearing animal masks and costumes, which fosters a sense of group belonging among participants, highlighting the importance of social connection.", "citations": ["3fcd0df2-8c79-4a4a-b2b2-989de7b0626b_773706126"]}, {"text": "However, experts warn of potential dangers when enthusiasm becomes all-consuming, such as children insisting on behaving as their character in inappropriate settings like school or family events.", "citations": ["3fcd0df2-8c79-4a4a-b2b2-989de7b0626b_773706126"]}, {"text": "In the UK, the government recently banned laughing gas at parties due to concerns over its accessibility and potential harms, while public support for the ban remains strong.", "citations": ["79f00492-3b07-42fb-885d-23219c8b51ae_671012000"]}, {"text": "In the United States, \"gaslighting\" was recognized as the word of the year, reflecting a growing awareness of psychological manipulation in relationships and society.", "citations": ["733a8dce-59f1-49fd-85fd-559b7edd11c6_351317058"]}, {"text": "Psychoanalyst Georgy Amusin explains \"gaslighting\" as a behavior that undermines an individual\u2019s sense of reality, causing them to doubt their own memories or perceptions.", "citations": ["733a8dce-59f1-49fd-85fd-559b7edd11c6_351317058"]}, {"text": "It originated from a story where a husband manipulates his wife into thinking she is losing her sanity by altering their environment and denying the changes.", "citations": ["733a8dce-59f1-49fd-85fd-559b7edd11c6_351317058"]}, {"text": "Gaslighting tactics include insisting the victim has a bad memory, discouraging them from seeking help, and convincing them that others will see them as irrational or crazy.", "citations": ["5fe5dc83-c887-47d8-ab07-6ff0fe9f75b0_584035312"]}, {"text": "Abusers can be relatives, colleagues, or friends, and the victim\u2019s continued acceptance often enables the abuse.", "citations": ["5fe5dc83-c887-47d8-ab07-6ff0fe9f75b0_584035312"]}, {"text": "Experts recommend recognizing manipulation, maintaining self-confidence, and recording experiences as ways to prevent or overcome gaslighting.", "citations": ["5fe5dc83-c887-47d8-ab07-6ff0fe9f75b0_584035312"]}, {"text": "Societal pressures, such as the habit of constant productivity and comparing oneself to others, may contribute to unhappiness and a lack of purpose.", "citations": ["6fdb3016-6928-4543-9e20-4f26c47b6d70_1031629894"]}, {"text": "It\u2019s important to question overly generous promises and cultivate doubt to preserve a healthy sense of autonomy and dignity.", "citations": ["733a8dce-59f1-49fd-85fd-559b7edd11c6_351317058"]}, {"text": "Establishing internal harmony, regular self-care, and being mindful of negative habits can improve wellbeing and support resilience against manipulation or external pressures.", "citations": ["6fdb3016-6928-4543-9e20-4f26c47b6d70_1031629894"]}, {"text": "Medical professionals have raised concerns over weighted blankets\u2019 safety for babies, while parenting anecdotes highlight the significance of understanding and adapting to children\u2019s unique behaviors as they grow.", "citations": ["1305380f-8ee3-4ede-a642-65a5aeaf9853_642119343"]}, {"text": "Scientific studies have also found links between early childhood lead exposure and later criminal tendencies, emphasizing the importance of protecting children\u2019s health.", "citations": ["4a37fe83-87cd-4456-a481-c132f9b1f86a_325620102"]}, {"text": "Finally, guidance on protecting teenagers from vaping addresses emerging health risks for adolescents in the modern environment.", "citations": ["bacb1669-27ab-4056-b155-9303ede38029_974718814"]}, {"text": "Certainly!", "citations": ["d5e7633e-4964-44ea-86b2-578d7f85d75a_686722537"]}, {"text": "Here is a coherent summary of the provided extracts, rewritten into one sentence per line, adhering to the facts and within a 2500-character limit:\n\nThere are numerous fake websites on the internet and social media that sell hazardous items, often run by individuals with no medical expertise.", "citations": ["a874023e-781f-4440-9c1e-f8647ce2dc46_297631098"]}, {"text": "Sher Khan agrees on the necessity for authorities to confront this issue and monitor online platforms promoting questionable products.", "citations": ["a874023e-781f-4440-9c1e-f8647ce2dc46_297631098"]}, {"text": "TikTok is reportedly encouraging children to use anti-aging products, leading to questions about why young people are so captivated by these items.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_448935490"]}, {"text": "Some adults advocate for young people to learn about skincare, while others note that these children are simply having fun.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_448935490"]}, {"text": "Healthcare professionals warn parents against allowing their children to use age-inappropriate anti-aging products, citing significant health risks and urging discussions about their harms.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_448935490"]}, {"text": "The aftermath of using certain filters, such as a crying filter, can be emotionally impactful.", "citations": ["77f9b977-0b93-4dd4-b1c8-d8956a54ade7_761500080"]}, {"text": "Photo filters may have serious mental health consequences, potentially contributing to suicide risk.", "citations": ["77f9b977-0b93-4dd4-b1c8-d8956a54ade7_761500080"]}, {"text": "Professor James Jackson\u2019s book, \"Clearing the Fog,\" provides guidance for people coping with cognitive impairment and mental health challenges associated with long-term symptoms.", "citations": ["93863b13-9ebb-456f-8ab6-f4136609d58a_393493202"]}, {"text": "Studies question the impact of television on autism in infants, observing issues such as lack of social engagement and attention.", "citations": ["d5e7633e-4964-44ea-86b2-578d7f85d75a_686722537"]}, {"text": "Premature babies exposed to screens before age two are at higher risk for developmental issues, with additional factors like genetics and family history increasing autism risk.", "citations": ["d5e7633e-4964-44ea-86b2-578d7f85d75a_686722537"]}, {"text": "A parent named Rania documented her six-month-old son's lack of reaction and social engagement, supporting research linking early screen exposure to developmental delays.", "citations": ["d5e7633e-4964-44ea-86b2-578d7f85d75a_686722537"]}, {"text": "Experts identify early screen exposure, genetics, and family history as critical factors behind autism development.", "citations": ["d5e7633e-4964-44ea-86b2-578d7f85d75a_686722537"]}, {"text": "A 30-year-old Brazilian singer died on stage during a concert that was broadcast on social media, drawing public comments and reactions.", "citations": ["1ce866bc-0426-452f-9539-2d1dc706f289_914809483"]}, {"text": "A report indicates a suspicious purchase of PCR kits in Wuhan months prior to the COVID-19 epidemic.", "citations": ["39c7d1bc-8c69-4094-a1f8-4fbe6092db20_484870247"]}, {"text": "Research suggests that people often experience heightened happiness in their early thirties.", "citations": ["39c7d1bc-8c69-4094-a1f8-4fbe6092db20_484870247"]}, {"text": "It is noted that entertainment media often focuses on pranks or jokes at the expense of public figures or regular people.", "citations": ["e5c37140-3ff3-403d-9eba-2860dba81436_774746961"]}, {"text": "One example is a dangerous prank call made by Australian radio hosts pretending to be members of the royal family to a London hospital nurse, illustrating the risks of media stunts.", "citations": ["e5c37140-3ff3-403d-9eba-2860dba81436_774746961"]}, {"text": "Media producers are urged to carefully assess the impact of their content to avoid preventable negative side effects.", "citations": ["e5c37140-3ff3-403d-9eba-2860dba81436_774746961"]}, {"text": "Published articles reflect the views of their respective authors, and users are encouraged to review the privacy policy and consent to cookies on the website.", "citations": ["e5c37140-3ff3-403d-9eba-2860dba81436_774746961"]}, {"text": "TikTok has introduced a new feature for teenagers that displays a time alert after 60 minutes of usage for users under 18.", "citations": ["aeddb490-41b6-4800-b532-edb34ab9fe00_3637286"]}, {"text": "This alert will apply to new and existing accounts not already using time management tools.", "citations": ["aeddb490-41b6-4800-b532-edb34ab9fe00_3637286"]}, {"text": "If teenagers choose to disable this TikTok feature, they will be unable to use the app for more than 100 minutes in a day.", "citations": ["aeddb490-41b6-4800-b532-edb34ab9fe00_3637286"]}, {"text": "**The Labubu Phenomenon: A Summary**\n\nLabubu, a character and collectible plush toy monster elf, was created by Hong Kong designer Kasing Lung and is marketed by Pop Mart, a Chinese toy company.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "In recent years, Labubu has become a viral sensation, particularly on social media platforms such as TikTok, where posts featuring the figurines often attract millions of views and interactions.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "Fans of all ages, especially teenagers, have lined up at Pop Mart stores and online releases to purchase Labubu toys, contributing to frequent sold-out launches and a booming secondary market with resale prices soaring above retail.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "The toy's adorable, mischievous appearance, together with limited-edition releases and mystery box packaging, has fueled a \"blind box\" craze, enticing consumers to collect entire series and share \"unboxing\" experiences online.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "Pop Mart's strategic marketing, collaborations with well-known artists, and partnerships with major IPs have increased brand visibility and desirability, bolstered by celebrity endorsements such as Rihanna being spotted with the toys.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "The Labubu phenomenon has not only driven up global revenue for Pop Mart, but also significantly increased the net worth of its founder, Wang Ning, making him one of China's youngest self-made billionaires.", "citations": ["afaa4245-6aaf-41c9-b9ad-0ee10e258f9e_43621515"]}, {"text": "This surge in popularity is further amplified by social trends among youth, who value unique self-expression, collectible culture, and a sense of community derived from sharing and trading Labubu figurines both online and offline.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "The toy\u2019s packaging as a surprise item, combined with the rarity of special editions, appeals to consumers\u2019 desire for novelty, exclusivity, and the thrill of discovery, turning Labubu into more than just a toy but a lifestyle collectible.", "citations": ["882df913-6d81-4044-9fdb-716bcb8da32e_202146098"]}, {"text": "As a result, Pop Mart has expanded rapidly into overseas markets, opening flagship stores and pop-ups in major cities across Asia, Europe, and North America, consolidating Labubu\u2019s global cultural impact.", "citations": ["afaa4245-6aaf-41c9-b9ad-0ee10e258f9e_43621515"]}, {"text": "The viral nature of Labubu is further reinforced by user-generated content, creative storytelling, and trends on TikTok, where popular hashtags and themed challenges keep the character in the public spotlight.", "citations": ["afaa4245-6aaf-41c9-b9ad-0ee10e258f9e_43621515"]}, {"text": "Together, these factors have made Labubu a symbol of contemporary collectible culture, blending art, commerce, and internet-driven virality into one of the most remarkable toy phenomena of the decade.", "citations": ["afaa4245-6aaf-41c9-b9ad-0ee10e258f9e_43621515"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1068", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Robotic animal companions, such as the Joy for All pets, are increasingly being recognized by caregivers like Diana Wise and Carol Brown for their ability to provide comfort to aging adults with Alzheimer\u2019s, dementia, or those struggling with social isolation.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Wise witnessed the positive effects of these robotic pets firsthand with her own mother in a memory care unit, inspiring her to create the \u201cShare the Love\u201d Helen Espinoza Memorial Fund to help provide more pets to seniors in need.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "These lifelike dogs and cats can be muted when desired and even placed in animal crates at night, mimicking routines of real pet ownership.", "citations": ["6a873279-c9a2-4442-8cc2-8b258cf59e4d_842687117"]}, {"text": "Seeing the improvements in seniors\u2019 moods and a renewed sense of purpose, Wise is determined to raise more funds and spread awareness so others might purchase these pets for their loved ones as well.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "The Joy for All pets\u2019 manufacturer specifically targets the loneliness epidemic among older adults, as many lack close family or friends nearby due to loss or distance.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Area Agency on Aging CEO Charlotte Mather-Taylor notes that half of American adults feel lonely, a need that such companion robots are intended to address.", "citations": ["86a5cace-32cc-4d47-84d0-f7cc4c349c73_788487252"]}, {"text": "Seniors like Rosemary Mullarkey have been among the first to receive these pets, and in response to community needs, developers are working on Spanish-language versions.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Other advanced AI companions, such as ElliQ, engage seniors in conversation, greet them in the morning, and inquire about their well-being to help combat isolation.", "citations": ["d1d4726c-6f01-4b2d-b52c-0fc4f631de1e_501256233"]}, {"text": "Greg Olsen, director for the New York State Office for the Aging, acknowledges a role for technology in caregiving, while cautioning that it is not a substitute for human interaction.", "citations": ["8d3cfa15-2f2c-4024-b792-0a8eb09c20cc_478295722"]}, {"text": "Users report that robotic pets bring joy and purpose, displaying behaviors like barking, meowing, seeking affection, and responding to touch, which make them seem almost real.", "citations": ["6a873279-c9a2-4442-8cc2-8b258cf59e4d_842687117"]}, {"text": "At tech shows like CES 2024, innovations in robotic pet technology are highlighted alongside advancements in other AI-driven household robots that assist with chores and elderly care.", "citations": ["683d920a-717e-458d-997b-97c42fa52075_217671007"]}, {"text": "A growing market for household and service robots underscores their expanding use for education, entertainment, and support of older adults.", "citations": ["29d7ca89-34f0-4714-9823-b40934a865be_32797163"]}, {"text": "International efforts, such as distributing robotic pets in Poland, demonstrate the global interest in these devices for therapeutic settings among seniors.", "citations": ["97c97600-0100-4af1-b0d9-3ca92daf1359_450224422"]}, {"text": "Experts caution that while AI and robotic pets can reduce feelings of loneliness, they are not a perfect cure and should not entirely replace real human or animal connections.", "citations": ["1f64ec71-b884-4f7d-bf83-86fa509e92a2_291318248"]}, {"text": "Scientists predict that robots will increasingly serve as companions for elderly or lonely individuals in the future.", "citations": ["c7f55dcc-7139-4a18-95bb-5898d9544a17_162742656"]}, {"text": "Research has focused on identifying the qualities that make dogs enjoyable companions, informing the development of robotic alternatives.", "citations": ["c7f55dcc-7139-4a18-95bb-5898d9544a17_162742656"]}, {"text": "Fourier GR-1 is a robot with a height of 165 cm and weight of 55 kg, capable of moving at 5 km/h and carrying loads almost equal to its own weight.", "citations": ["2b3f0c20-66bd-44a8-9806-ae6598e3b296_127267195"]}, {"text": "Fourier Intelligence promotes this robot as both a therapeutic assistant in medical institutions and as a companion for lonely seniors.", "citations": ["2b3f0c20-66bd-44a8-9806-ae6598e3b296_127267195"]}, {"text": "A new generation of robotic pets with individually trained AI is now available in the United States.", "citations": ["daaa2d55-82b5-47a4-acfb-4aa775ba6971_982434132"]}, {"text": "The Aibo robot uses an AI Cloud Plan to develop unique characteristics and behaviors based on interactions with its owner.", "citations": ["daaa2d55-82b5-47a4-acfb-4aa775ba6971_982434132"]}, {"text": "After three years of free use, continued access to Aibo\u2019s cloud-based features will require a paid subscription.", "citations": ["daaa2d55-82b5-47a4-acfb-4aa775ba6971_982434132"]}, {"text": "Scientists have developed a guide robot that responds to a handheld leash, addressing the shortage of guide dogs which are costly and require years to train.", "citations": ["aa5f798f-69d2-477a-8a06-6f4d295cd7c9_728844304"]}, {"text": "While robot dogs can guide visually impaired individuals through environments, current technology cannot yet fully replace human-trained guide dogs, especially regarding judgment and safety.", "citations": ["aa5f798f-69d2-477a-8a06-6f4d295cd7c9_728844304"]}, {"text": "Designers aim to make these robots appear non-threatening to alleviate user concerns about technology.", "citations": ["728b791f-977a-44bc-aa11-5be625f1fcae_205612430"]}, {"text": "Ongoing advancements have improved how well robots mimic human behavior, though this raises ethical issues about replacing real animals with machines.", "citations": ["9a278663-a589-4188-872b-dff36e348fe3_278000558"]}, {"text": "Lola\u2019s robot uses advanced AI, machine learning, and sophisticated hardware to complete a wide range of tasks, including cleaning, cooking, and providing emotional support.", "citations": ["83d30fb2-a731-4e8f-9b56-b3c2578131ce_1015156649"]}, {"text": "Lola\u2019s versatility allows use across multiple industries, with the humanoid design expanding potential applications.", "citations": ["83d30fb2-a731-4e8f-9b56-b3c2578131ce_1015156649"]}, {"text": "Privacy and data security are important considerations for users of these AI-enabled robots.", "citations": ["83d30fb2-a731-4e8f-9b56-b3c2578131ce_1015156649"]}, {"text": "Robots are also used in medical settings, such as remote examinations or procedures, increasing efficiency and safety for doctors and patients.", "citations": ["c8974212-3cab-441f-9771-a5ef06a98f7b_177231758"]}, {"text": "Voice robots are deployed in some hospitals to streamline workflows and allow for more patient interaction.", "citations": ["c8974212-3cab-441f-9771-a5ef06a98f7b_177231758"]}, {"text": "The development of robotic pets is not limited to one company; SONY, among others, offers robotic dogs, and several such dogs are currently used in parks.", "citations": ["d2953e8c-53d2-41f9-b88e-0b5f2a217caf_503108124"]}, {"text": "Robotic cats pose unique challenges in design.", "citations": ["d2953e8c-53d2-41f9-b88e-0b5f2a217caf_503108124"]}, {"text": "Robots like Wehead provide remote communication for users, simulating interaction with humans from a distance.", "citations": ["9a278663-a589-4188-872b-dff36e348fe3_278000558"]}, {"text": "In the U.S., demand for the rental and purchase of robots is increasing, particularly in commercial environments.", "citations": ["d2953e8c-53d2-41f9-b88e-0b5f2a217caf_503108124"]}, {"text": "Noted challenges in robotic design include creating recognizable facial features for more natural interaction, as seen with the UK\u2019s humanoid robot Ameca.", "citations": ["d2953e8c-53d2-41f9-b88e-0b5f2a217caf_503108124"]}, {"text": "Some robots, such as the Retriever model, can navigate stairs, fetch trays, and perform basic household tasks, benefiting people with disabilities.", "citations": ["b39949fa-dfd7-4c48-8677-1606ad0be544_891975818"]}, {"text": "Public attitudes are shaped by both the convenience and concern surrounding the replacement of real pets or caretakers with machines, highlighting ongoing societal and ethical debates.", "citations": ["9a278663-a589-4188-872b-dff36e348fe3_278000558"]}, {"text": "Robotic pets are increasingly being designed to provide emotional companionship and assistance to elderly or lonely individuals, aiming to improve their quality of life.", "citations": ["f392961d-2eee-4530-9ae9-a90b1c4edcc2_176724923"]}, {"text": "Products such as Sony's \"AIBO\" and the \"Tombot\" robot dog exemplify this trend, with interactive features that simulate the behaviors and responses of real pets.", "citations": ["807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_282342600"]}, {"text": "Tombot was inspired by the founder\u2019s mother, who suffered from Alzheimer\u2019s and could no longer care for her live dog.", "citations": ["807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_282342600"]}, {"text": "PARO, a robotic seal, moves its tail and fins, opens its eyes when caressed, and imitates authentic seal sounds, providing sensory engagement and comfort.", "citations": ["807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_282342600"]}, {"text": "While humanoid robots have attracted significant attention, specialized robots are increasingly developed for specific tasks, including providing care or companionship.", "citations": ["38f008ec-c0e6-4fd1-8550-41bd1afa6510_778879506"]}, {"text": "Assistive robotics applies these technologies to support individuals with disabilities or older adults, ranging from manufacturing to entertainment applications.", "citations": ["38f008ec-c0e6-4fd1-8550-41bd1afa6510_778879506"]}, {"text": "Researchers are testing robotic guide dogs to assist visually impaired people, potentially offering independence where traditional animal companions are unavailable.", "citations": ["f392961d-2eee-4530-9ae9-a90b1c4edcc2_176724923"]}, {"text": "Robots such as Epo X can also personalize lighting, music, and take photos, responding to user preferences to enhance daily life.", "citations": ["4b0c0b4b-b31c-48d1-92fc-154a88708a14_704962202"]}, {"text": "In Germany, the robot \"Garmi\" was designed by Munich Institute for Robotics and Machine Intelligence specifically for geriatric care, combining a robotic arm and screen with expressive \"eyes\" to interact with users.", "citations": ["b8982b36-f5a3-44bb-8b49-1b55b03eab83_915537933"]}, {"text": "Garmi's introduction is considered urgent because of the rapidly ageing population, although its full market availability and cost are still unknown.", "citations": ["b8982b36-f5a3-44bb-8b49-1b55b03eab83_915537933"]}, {"text": "Robots like Garmi can offer functions such as physical assistance, companionship, and even facilitating video conferences or meal set-ups for users.", "citations": ["38f008ec-c0e6-4fd1-8550-41bd1afa6510_778879506"]}, {"text": "Samsung\u2019s Bot i and other new concepts demonstrate the industry's aspirations for robots as lifelong companions, integrating seamlessly into daily routines and offering social support.", "citations": ["fcb51352-88d8-433f-956c-55aa2c3d2cb8_1027102145"]}, {"text": "Some robots, including exoskeleton-equipped or shape-changing models, have applications beyond companionship, such as search and rescue or traversing rough terrain.", "citations": ["807bfe6e-889d-4f05-ac83-bac40ada16b9_282342600"]}, {"text": "Public attitudes to robotic pets are mixed, with some expressing concern about replacing living animals with machines, along with fears about loss of employment or misuse as weapons.", "citations": ["d3d11b2b-892a-406a-9c7d-b89edae7fb46_513694664"]}, {"text": "Experts also note that humanlike robots, although growing more advanced in mimicking behaviors, lack true self-awareness or consciousness.", "citations": ["d3d11b2b-892a-406a-9c7d-b89edae7fb46_513694664"]}, {"text": "Despite these limitations, developers see an imminent and expanding role for artificial companions, especially as demographic changes increase demand for supportive care solutions for seniors.", "citations": ["38f008ec-c0e6-4fd1-8550-41bd1afa6510_778879506"]}, {"text": "In central New York, a robot plays games and music for Marie Broadbent, 92, who is blind and receiving hospice care.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Marie and other women were among the first recipients of the ElliQ robot in the United States, according to Intuition Robotics and the Aged Aid Program.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Anita Montague, 76, reported that before using ElliQ she only sat at the computer, but now she can do more sports and feels energetic and motivated to work.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Some users like Carmichael initially found it odd to talk to a robot but later made friendly suggestions, such as improving the appearance by putting false eyelashes on the Mango robot.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Robotic companion pets and AI assistants were originally designed in Japan and have been studied in Asian countries for years.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Healthcare investments aim to fill manpower gaps, as increasing numbers of elderly people living at home outpace available care resources, and AI robots can help ease this workload.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Governments hope that AI development will be a solution to social challenges like elderly care, emotional companionship, and health management.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Introducing artificial intelligence into elder care has become a popular trend, especially for those living alone.", "citations": ["ce41b0e4-14af-454a-8cb6-a7080315d64b_871982918"]}, {"text": "Joyce Loaiza, a retired office worker in Florida, chats daily with a friendly robotic assistant upon returning home, and Deanna Dezern, 83, found comfort from the same device after a friend's death.", "citations": ["16558a0a-dd11-4797-ae19-489b5920b4af_747976703"]}, {"text": "ElliQ robots remember users\u2019 interests, hobbies, and conversations to personalize chats and discuss both complex topics and light banter such as horoscopes.", "citations": ["16558a0a-dd11-4797-ae19-489b5920b4af_747976703"]}, {"text": "ElliQ offers virtual city and museum tours, guides users to exercise, checks health, and sends medicine or hydration reminders.", "citations": ["16558a0a-dd11-4797-ae19-489b5920b4af_747976703"]}, {"text": "It can also make emergency video calls to family, friends, or doctors.", "citations": ["16558a0a-dd11-4797-ae19-489b5920b4af_747976703"]}, {"text": "AI-powered elderly products also serve to assist in early detection of eye disease, encouraging users and families to pay attention to health concerns.", "citations": ["b34eee7e-e17d-4af2-8a0c-a375493f94ab_937724767"]}, {"text": "China's elderly care market is rapidly expanding, with entertainment and social robots like \"Yunyun\" providing company, guidance, and conversation to users such as 68-year-old Song Lixia.", "citations": ["8bcd1f68-5957-42cf-94a7-2cbfb7582ecc_767198400"]}, {"text": "Users appreciate that robots can give advice, such as suggesting to wear a coat, and say the machines make life more interesting in the absence of busy family members.", "citations": ["78a7d039-6fdb-4e1d-8fd5-7c0fb6e7bcf2_486676237"]}, {"text": "Many escort robots, such as Yunyun, are now available and some elderly users express attachment, feeling they cannot live without them.", "citations": ["8bcd1f68-5957-42cf-94a7-2cbfb7582ecc_767198400"]}, {"text": "At events like the World Robot Congress, advanced humanoid robots demonstrate realistic facial expressions, with pet robots and robotic dogs able to respond to voice commands and perform tricks.", "citations": ["436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_887925875"]}, {"text": "Engineers claim robotic dogs are smarter and easier to train than real dogs and can, for example, dance on command.", "citations": ["436f6dca-3571-4e87-b474-e70ec06c96ce_887925875"]}, {"text": "New York is planning distribution of AI companion robots to elderly people living alone, anticipating a growing market.", "citations": ["d5bd112e-b517-41c6-972a-6ed7276dd547_900627080"]}, {"text": "While Japan has historically led in robot technology, its use in care settings is plateauing as other countries like South Korea and Germany catch up.", "citations": ["e7e6c73b-66b8-4b4f-a199-55f37a56213e_284451624"]}, {"text": "In Japanese nursing homes, robotic pets like Sony\u2019s AIBO are present alongside robots that assist with daily tasks such as bathing and mobility.", "citations": ["e7e6c73b-66b8-4b4f-a199-55f37a56213e_284451624"]}, {"text": "Most Japanese robots are now used in industry, but smart care systems like ITRI's PECOLA are being pilot tested in nursing homes to enhance elder support.", "citations": ["e7e6c73b-66b8-4b4f-a199-55f37a56213e_284451624"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1070", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "LiveJournal began as a personal journaling application created by Brad Fitzpatrick in 1999 while he was still in high school.", "citations": ["699bbb1c-8d29-446e-8a56-8c42e1300039_331097074"]}, {"text": "He designed it initially to keep up with friends, but soon opened it up so others could also use the platform.", "citations": ["d15a580b-3ee1-42a5-be38-0d60db9d1280_1046851966"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal quickly became known for its strong community features, allowing users to \u201cfriend\u201d each other and to form and participate in interest-based communities.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "Unlike traditional blogging platforms, LiveJournal allowed for privacy controls on journal entries, letting users make posts public, friends-only, or private.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "This created flexible opportunities for interaction and sharing that were not typical on other journaling or blogging websites at the time.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "The unique \u201cfriends\u201d page let users easily follow posts from people they knew or communities they joined, making the site feel personal and social.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "Users could comment on each other\u2019s posts, and the sense of community was deepened by a culture of interaction and support between members.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal also allowed for customization, so users could personalize the appearance of their journals through various themes and layouts.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "At its peak in early 2005, LiveJournal boasted more than 2.5 million active accounts and was a central platform for blogging and online discussion, especially in the English-speaking world.", "citations": ["72cc1696-8a57-4e7e-9def-2735ab07af79_228451741"]}, {"text": "Features like threaded comments and polls set it apart from other blogging options and encouraged unique discussions and group activity.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "However, as new social media platforms emerged and grew, LiveJournal faced strong competition, notably from sites like Facebook and later Tumblr, which offered even more robust sharing and networking features.", "citations": ["d15a580b-3ee1-42a5-be38-0d60db9d1280_1046851966"]}, {"text": "Regulators and users increasingly viewed Facebook and similar platforms as synonymous with \u201cthe internet,\u201d boosting their dominance.", "citations": ["53771f36-e205-47fa-9bad-b8de615490f6_945743342"]}, {"text": "The shift of user attention and time to these newer platforms, combined with evolving online habits, led to a decline in LiveJournal\u2019s popularity over time.", "citations": ["d15a580b-3ee1-42a5-be38-0d60db9d1280_1046851966"]}, {"text": "Changes in ownership and shifting content moderation policies further affected trust and participation among the site\u2019s core user base.", "citations": ["44070418-2e3a-4378-8c4c-13a5801e4220_346094005"]}, {"text": "By the 2010s, most of the English-speaking internet had moved on from LiveJournal, though a dedicated minority, including public figures like George R. R. Martin, remained active.", "citations": ["c51001b6-76d1-4bed-a1e9-94df959605e7_69591583"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal\u2019s legacy remains in pioneering many social and technical features that helped shape today\u2019s online communities and blogging culture.", "citations": ["72cc1696-8a57-4e7e-9def-2735ab07af79_228451741"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal was created by Brad Fitzpatrick in 1999 as a personal journaling application during his time as a college student.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "Fitzpatrick originally designed the tool for himself but soon opened it up, allowing others to join and use the platform.", "citations": ["44473f01-030e-454a-93a6-54db73582bed_405877616"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal quickly evolved into a website where users could write entries, share thoughts, and connect with friends in an interactive community.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "Unlike other blogging sites, LiveJournal allowed users to create friend lists, join interest-based communities, and control privacy settings on a post-by-post basis.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "The platform enabled not only public blogging but also selective sharing with friends or specific groups, fostering honest discussions and support networks.", "citations": ["5d4c61f0-d2f5-4bbb-8a9b-ef739b282120_1009098888"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal had features such as threaded comments, user icons, and the ability to follow individual users or communities, which made conversation and discovery easier.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "By the early 2000s, LiveJournal had fostered a strong sense of community, especially among young people, writers, and those interested in fandoms and subcultures.", "citations": ["962222fc-dff0-4995-a62c-c45dd9a8b1cc_429523175"]}, {"text": "At its peak in early 2005, LiveJournal boasted over 2.5 million active accounts, largely among English-speaking users but with growing Russian engagement.", "citations": ["5d4c61f0-d2f5-4bbb-8a9b-ef739b282120_1009098888"]}, {"text": "The site became popular among bloggers who were looking for more interaction and feedback than traditional static blogs could offer.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "The Russian user base expanded rapidly, and LiveJournal became a key platform for social and political discussion in Russia.", "citations": ["25730d40-5bfc-41b5-a011-b31dcb46cf2b_234104152"]}, {"text": "However, LiveJournal eventually faced challenges from the emergence of alternative platforms such as Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram, which offered simpler interfaces and more immediate ways to interact.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "The shift in Internet culture towards quicker, shorter updates and microblogging led to a decline in long-form blogging and journaling.", "citations": ["962222fc-dff0-4995-a62c-c45dd9a8b1cc_429523175"]}, {"text": "Management changes and the sale of LiveJournal to Six Apart in 2005 and later to Russian company SUP Media in 2007 led to concerns among users about privacy, censorship, and the direction of the site.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "Over time, many in the English-speaking community left the platform as conversations and audiences migrated to newer social media.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "Despite its decline in global popularity, LiveJournal remains influential in certain regions and subcultures, especially in Russia, where it is still used for blogging and discussions.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "The history of LiveJournal shows the importance of community features and user interaction in the early evolution of online blogging.", "citations": ["84823b1a-3f3b-45ef-a243-a9ae5d3dd381_320801207"]}, {"text": "The web has dramatically transformed global communication and media consumption, effectively making the world a \u201cone room.\u201d  \nTechnologies such as the fax and the rise of news agencies illustrate how innovations can change information delivery, a trend that continued with the advent of the internet.", "citations": ["dea4218a-eb2a-4902-987f-a8d7885e39b6_939417818"]}, {"text": "Smartphones further accelerated this change, serving as incubators for media applications and enabling news notifications to reach users instantly.", "citations": ["119caa65-fd6a-40e8-b337-0fc4ca3cfbe8_102383802"]}, {"text": "Social media platforms, like LiveJournal, have allowed people to follow and engage with news and events as they happen, often focused on their immediate geographic surroundings.", "citations": ["119caa65-fd6a-40e8-b337-0fc4ca3cfbe8_102383802"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal was developed by Brad Fitzpatrick originally as a journaling application for his use before expanding it into a website others could use.", "citations": ["f12a176e-ed24-4ac0-9ffc-0a1511193166_630768689"]}, {"text": "Distinct from many blogging platforms, LiveJournal allowed users to keep journals, join communities, and manage a friends list that controlled the sharing and visibility of posts.", "citations": ["54438e60-acb4-4311-9d8f-d08f584c660c_1026056731"]}, {"text": "The friendship and privacy management tools meant users could share posts with chosen groups, creating tightly-knit social circles and fostering a sense of community.", "citations": ["54438e60-acb4-4311-9d8f-d08f584c660c_1026056731"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal also enabled interaction through commenting, community posts, and interest-based groups, offering a richer social experience than traditional blogs.", "citations": ["119caa65-fd6a-40e8-b337-0fc4ca3cfbe8_102383802"]}, {"text": "At its peak in early 2005, LiveJournal boasted more than 2.5 million active accounts, making it a central hub for online communities and creative expression.", "citations": ["f12a176e-ed24-4ac0-9ffc-0a1511193166_630768689"]}, {"text": "High-profile users, such as George R. R. Martin, continued using LiveJournal even as its popularity waned in the English-speaking world.", "citations": ["54438e60-acb4-4311-9d8f-d08f584c660c_1026056731"]}, {"text": "Over time, the novelty of digital communication and freedom of expression led to a proliferation of content creators and shifted interactions from paper to digital platforms.", "citations": ["cba80c64-2393-454e-802b-6de0b1ce626b_726663434"]}, {"text": "Despite the benefits of wide audience reach and convenience, user feedback did not always equate to visible engagement, as many readers did not comment or \u201clike\u201d posts.", "citations": ["54438e60-acb4-4311-9d8f-d08f584c660c_1026056731"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal\u2019s early innovations in social networking were eventually overshadowed by the arrival of newer, more dynamic social media platforms like Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram.", "citations": ["119caa65-fd6a-40e8-b337-0fc4ca3cfbe8_102383802"]}, {"text": "These newer platforms offered broader features, easier sharing mechanisms, quicker feedback, and mobile-friendly interfaces, leading to LiveJournal\u2019s decline in popularity.", "citations": ["54438e60-acb4-4311-9d8f-d08f584c660c_1026056731"]}, {"text": "The shift in media and audience engagement habits contributed to LiveJournal being largely forgotten in the English-speaking world, though it persisted in some regions and among dedicated users.", "citations": ["54438e60-acb4-4311-9d8f-d08f584c660c_1026056731"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal started as a journaling application created by Brad Fitzpatrick for his own use while in high school, which he later transformed into a website that allowed others to use the service as well.", "citations": ["35b8ffac-1e7f-4f57-874e-c502e68ec388_558808302"]}, {"text": "The site quickly grew in popularity because it enabled users to not only publish their thoughts online but also to interact with other users in new ways, such as by adding friends and reading their journal entries on a personalized \"Friends page.\"", "citations": ["35b8ffac-1e7f-4f57-874e-c502e68ec388_558808302"]}, {"text": "This social networking aspect, along with mechanisms for creating and joining communities, made LiveJournal distinct from other early blogging platforms that focused more exclusively on individual publishing.", "citations": ["35b8ffac-1e7f-4f57-874e-c502e68ec388_558808302"]}, {"text": "LiveJournal also allowed users a range of privacy controls, so that posts could be fully public, restricted to Friends only, or visible to select groups, fostering a sense of intimacy and trust.", "citations": ["35b8ffac-1e7f-4f57-874e-c502e68ec388_558808302"]}, {"text": "At its peak in early 2005, LiveJournal boasted over 2.5 million active accounts, with particularly strong communities among English-speaking youth, writers, and fans of various subcultures.", "citations": ["8b1fb7b0-35fb-4a04-b24d-b9756a92638b_290705475"]}, {"text": "Its features facilitated a vibrant literary and creative exchange, as people published fiction, reported news, and shared thoughts\u2014often motivated by peer recognition and community feedback.", "citations": ["940b83f7-af87-4242-9615-8597f9087952_612954639"]}, {"text": "Blogging on LiveJournal became a way to participate in a new era of online media, blending personal expression with interactive news sharing and the dissemination of information in a manner different than traditional magazines or newspapers.", "citations": ["03678fc3-0932-4143-af88-2b7d6bae1f5b_208584876"]}, {"text": "However, changes in the media environment, the rise of faster, more visually-oriented social media like Facebook, Twitter, and later Tumblr, and the migration of user communities led to a steady decline in LiveJournal's visibility and influence in the English-speaking world after 2005.", "citations": ["35b8ffac-1e7f-4f57-874e-c502e68ec388_558808302"]}, {"text": "Other factors contributing to its decline included shifting internet trends, controversies over censorship and privacy, and a 2007 sale to a Russian company, which distanced many American users.", "citations": ["5d7b8177-ae11-4452-bbe6-6993c8be01d1_24237508"]}, {"text": "Despite its reduced prominence, LiveJournal's impact persists in the way it pioneered key features of online social interaction, community-based content, and privacy controls on the internet.", "citations": ["03678fc3-0932-4143-af88-2b7d6bae1f5b_208584876"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1076", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "AI voice over generators are revolutionizing interactions by enabling the creation of text-to-speech in 24 languages and handling cultural nuances.", "citations": ["dbcd9185-14fc-44d0-8e55-a39ed591687a_648233976"]}, {"text": "ElevenLabs has developed an AI voice cloning tool that can mimic voices and generate speech in multiple languages with just a three-second audio sample and text input.", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427"]}, {"text": "This technology now allows anyone to clone voices, making it accessible to the general public.", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427"]}, {"text": "AI-generated voice content can be used for entertainment, such as generating new songs featuring popular artists like Drake and The Weeknd.", "citations": ["79ebd9ed-d25a-485c-b9d2-54a988b77025_299669427"]}, {"text": "China Media Group has utilized AI to dub English documentaries, pioneering broader global communication.", "citations": ["3fe50e8c-745c-497f-9ba9-0f03c0f990cd_628094452"]}, {"text": "ElevenLabs' AI tutor can refine users\u2019 English and accent across various topics, with LLMs trained on proprietary data.", "citations": ["1c226a6a-72ce-4f97-9550-28bd7665d3e9_1060089943"]}, {"text": "AI-generated virtual faces and voices can be combined, raising concerns about identity security and the impact on careers that depend on authentic human presence.", "citations": ["ed0e0ccd-fad8-4211-be2e-11f7d99b17a0_405519036"]}, {"text": "While AI can enhance education by making schools more flexible and fostering greater critical thinking and creativity, attention must be paid to issues of access, data privacy, and teacher training.", "citations": ["02a45eac-6b6e-4791-9bb8-ccb19ad50ea6_60370729"]}, {"text": "UNESCO has called for regulations on the use of generative AI (GenAI) in schools, including tools like ChatGPT that can automate creation of text, images, audio, video, and code.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_829150911"]}, {"text": "Generative AI models use large datasets, often scraped from the Internet without the data owners\u2019 permission, raising ethical and legal concerns.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_829150911"]}, {"text": "Young learners are particularly at risk from exposure to AI-generated content without adequate prior knowledge.", "citations": ["515c5776-a50e-4782-835a-77bfb011b38e_829150911"]}, {"text": "The spread of AI tools, especially in educational contexts, provokes debate about their effects on traditional learning processes like writing and critical thinking.", "citations": ["6c9729c2-360a-41c7-9633-1a43c0b27c14_64899518"]}, {"text": "Global voice and speech recognition technologies are helping bridge language barriers, though translation accuracy remains an issue.", "citations": ["8f3f12ad-a7a4-450a-b410-09e5a5d380da_495855107"]}, {"text": "Tools like Vidnoz AI enable users to create personalized AI-narrated videos from text within minutes, offering a wide range of video templates and avatars.", "citations": ["b1238ffd-d137-4b78-9528-3f8db718b532_586577709"]}, {"text": "Users can also clone their own voice quickly for video narration, add subtitles, and automatically lip-sync videos to new languages.", "citations": ["b1238ffd-d137-4b78-9528-3f8db718b532_586577709"]}, {"text": "The accessibility and power of these tools make them attractive for content creation but simultaneously amplify risks related to deepfakes, data privacy, and consent.", "citations": ["ed0e0ccd-fad8-4211-be2e-11f7d99b17a0_405519036"]}, {"text": "AI serves as a valuable tool in expert hands for creating educational content but should not be relied on blindly, as neural networks may generate inaccurate or fabricated information.", "citations": ["ddb555df-de05-4b27-ad40-2d420b422fa0_6008076"]}, {"text": "When developing educational courses, AI tools like ChatGPT and other text generators can assist with content creation and can even handle sound and video by voicing written scripts.", "citations": ["ddb555df-de05-4b27-ad40-2d420b422fa0_6008076"]}, {"text": "Despite these advantages, AI in education poses risks such as the proliferation of untested courses that might undermine training quality, highlighting the need for robust oversight systems.", "citations": ["ddb555df-de05-4b27-ad40-2d420b422fa0_6008076"]}, {"text": "The diverse applications of artificial intelligence today range from talent discovery and skill development to offering content accessible from any device at any convenient time.", "citations": ["0d10cb5d-1c05-44c8-aabb-51e7cd4294af_972260600"]}, {"text": "In educational settings, peer motivation and the assessment of IT skills using experience from initiatives like School 21 play important roles.", "citations": ["0d10cb5d-1c05-44c8-aabb-51e7cd4294af_972260600"]}, {"text": "Innovative uses of voice AI include an Israeli-developed system that can duplicate original film voices in multiple languages, with expansion plans for more languages in progress.", "citations": ["f9a625be-2737-4581-8b39-a6c427a41162_998921916"]}, {"text": "A team at UCSF developed a brain-computer interface with AI enabling a paralyzed woman to communicate through a digital avatar by translating brain signals into speech, following earlier successes in decoding such signals into text.", "citations": ["8d30b0d1-d949-4329-baee-c3d48cf9ba5f_1008604131"]}, {"text": "NVIDIA demonstrated AI systems capable of synthesizing natural-sounding human speech, allowing, for example, a male speaker\u2019s words to be rendered in a female voice or simulating the expressive performances of famous singers.", "citations": ["4653bd22-4bfc-469f-b110-ead294010684_486965522"]}, {"text": "Tech companies like Adobe have launched AI audio tools, such as Enhance Speech, designed to process and improve podcasts by training on large datasets of varied recordings.", "citations": ["09956187-3394-4e0d-952a-2f62bd4103cb_200226784"]}, {"text": "Major AI language models like ChatGPT by OpenAI and Gemini, capable of highly fluent, contextually accurate text generation across various industrial applications, are at the forefront of technological advancement.", "citations": ["de75a4b0-cdee-4609-b222-29e71321b3b7_837429303"]}, {"text": "These models can adapt to different communication styles and learn from user interactions, continually improving their usefulness.", "citations": ["de75a4b0-cdee-4609-b222-29e71321b3b7_837429303"]}, {"text": "AppMaster and other no-code platforms now enable rapid, cost-effective development of web, mobile, or server apps powered by AI.", "citations": ["de75a4b0-cdee-4609-b222-29e71321b3b7_837429303"]}, {"text": "OpenAI has developed Voice Engine, an AI tool capable of replicating any person\u2019s voice for text-to-speech, though it currently remains restricted due to concerns about deepfakes and misuse.", "citations": ["becad082-6f78-4957-b06f-2743ffe92fd3_215629305"]}, {"text": "There is increasing excitement and concern about the accessibility and realism of voice cloning, which has profound implications for entertainment, accessibility, law, and ethical standards.", "citations": ["f9a625be-2737-4581-8b39-a6c427a41162_998921916"]}, {"text": "OpenAI has released a guide for teachers integrating ChatGPT into the classroom, sharing examples of how educators are accelerating student learning using the tool and offering guidance for getting started.", "citations": ["2cb179b6-6caa-4222-bdf8-b122b62a3da1_839844493"]}, {"text": "Universities in the Kingdom held forums to increase professor and student awareness of generative artificial intelligence and large language models.", "citations": ["6f9c2df9-f476-4468-aaec-972871325c3f_522863884"]}, {"text": "Correct word selection and accurate context remain essential challenges in deploying these technologies for educational tasks.", "citations": ["6f9c2df9-f476-4468-aaec-972871325c3f_522863884"]}, {"text": "Delays in adopting AI can cause educational institutions to lose global competitiveness, affecting the quality of education and students\u2019 ability to meet future labor market needs.", "citations": ["6f9c2df9-f476-4468-aaec-972871325c3f_522863884"]}, {"text": "Artificial Intelligence is an emerging area with the potential to transform many aspects of living and working by using computation to simulate, learn, and develop human intelligence.", "citations": ["734c5a11-142b-4664-9617-8ff28bee055f_400079713"]}, {"text": "AI is being applied in vocational and technical training to improve industrial processes, reduce costs, and help workers gain new skills or enhance their job performance using interactive simulators.", "citations": ["734c5a11-142b-4664-9617-8ff28bee055f_400079713"]}, {"text": "Adopting AI in education promotes access to knowledge, reduces cost and time, but introduces risks such as algorithmic bias and redundancies in the workforce.", "citations": ["734c5a11-142b-4664-9617-8ff28bee055f_400079713"]}, {"text": "It is essential for educators and policymakers to balance these advantages and risks, ensuring that AI adoption is informed by ethical and scientific standards.", "citations": ["734c5a11-142b-4664-9617-8ff28bee055f_400079713"]}, {"text": "AI technologies, particularly voice cloning and speech synthesis, are advancing quickly, improving by accurately replicating people\u2019s voices.", "citations": ["9d791aa4-99a3-4bbe-ae36-0d89e9917955_850492047"]}, {"text": "These advances have benefits but are also exploited by fraudsters who use cloned voices to perpetrate scams, like impersonating loved ones in distress.", "citations": ["9d791aa4-99a3-4bbe-ae36-0d89e9917955_850492047"]}, {"text": "Scammers can spoof phone numbers, making calls seem legitimate; creating a secure password or asking personal questions can help verify identities in such situations.", "citations": ["9d791aa4-99a3-4bbe-ae36-0d89e9917955_850492047"]}, {"text": "Deepfake technology, relying on AI and deep learning, is used to convincingly replicate videos, images, and sounds, with few limits as the technology evolves.", "citations": ["108a8fe3-a2ab-4b9c-827f-97ef502f8d69_843117468"]}, {"text": "Voice cloning requires training AI models on samples of a person\u2019s speech, after which they can produce synthetic recordings that closely mimic the original voice.", "citations": ["108a8fe3-a2ab-4b9c-827f-97ef502f8d69_843117468"]}, {"text": "Techniques include analyzing pitch, speed, rhythm, and tone to reproduce the characteristics of the target voice, enabling nearly indistinguishable audio for new content.", "citations": ["e3eac26f-b4ab-4cad-a17b-244b8a501047_871210594"]}, {"text": "Innovations like NeuralSpace\u2019s developments highlight progress toward culturally rich speech synthesis and enhanced speech recognition, driven by advanced AI hardware and algorithms.", "citations": ["78afd60b-a91a-4f94-a9fa-e4bb859ed906_872306689"]}, {"text": "These tools also aid language teachers and learners by speeding up translation, promoting cultural exchange, and fostering dialogue, though their reliability must be critically assessed.", "citations": ["22043178-071c-4785-9a8d-0d496341bd88_286124084"]}, {"text": "Despite concerns, AI-powered language and translation applications are now indispensable aids, improving efficiency and the quality of learning and translation work.", "citations": ["22043178-071c-4785-9a8d-0d496341bd88_286124084"]}, {"text": "After the rise of ChatGPT, the application of large language models to various industries has become a major societal focus.", "citations": ["4fb7cad0-d46f-4141-9f24-93317f3c0bf5_345455411"]}, {"text": "In language learning and mathematics, multiple major approaches now exist, and AI is increasingly used as a tool rather than being viewed with apprehension.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Combining large models with educational enterprises is expected to impact the education industry and teachers, but also presents new opportunities.", "citations": ["4fb7cad0-d46f-4141-9f24-93317f3c0bf5_345455411"]}, {"text": "OpenAI, however, states that releasing certain tools now is too risky.", "citations": ["1ff8bd8e-1523-49e3-9cb6-0f37279c3aee_270236282"]}, {"text": "51Talk employs AI to identify and address children's weaknesses in English learning by adapting conversation to the user\u2019s proficiency level.", "citations": ["e7099633-61d6-4fd0-b12f-be3400627172_496994414"]}, {"text": "AI enables learners to practice without fear of embarrassment from mistakes.", "citations": ["91c55b74-6a41-42f8-99b7-995b0d2cc9b4_314086775"]}, {"text": "There are plans to further develop AI for junior high school students.", "citations": ["91c55b74-6a41-42f8-99b7-995b0d2cc9b4_314086775"]}, {"text": "Qilu Normal College advocates making AI a valuable supporter for primary and secondary school teachers.", "citations": ["b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_39568615"]}, {"text": "Yu Dongyan notes that manually correcting 50 student compositions can take over four hours, motivating the push for AI-assisted grading.", "citations": ["b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_39568615"]}, {"text": "Qilu Normal University's research team seeks to expand AI applications across more educational domains, aiming to provide comprehensive and intelligent support for teachers.", "citations": ["b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_39568615"]}, {"text": "AI models can also help teachers monitor student attendance with precision.", "citations": ["b4568a97-2125-422d-b744-7ceb6ce8de83_39568615"]}, {"text": "Sharing effective AI practices is encouraged so more people benefit.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Both teachers and students gain advantages from implementing AI in education.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "AI chatbots offer student support, fostering more inclusive education environments where all students can flourish.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "AI integration in education could fundamentally reshape teaching and learning methods.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Low-code AI platforms play a critical role in this transformation by bridging sophisticated AI with everyday classroom tools.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "These platforms are not a fleeting trend but an ongoing movement in education.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Low-code AI enables educators to create custom educational tools without extensive IT knowledge.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Platforms such as AppMaster offer accessible entry points for educators to adopt new technologies and quickly adapt based on feedback.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Such platforms empower teachers and signal a new era of personalized, effective, and dynamic education.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Key requirements include technical literacy, ethical conduct, and careful attention to data privacy and security.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Close collaboration between educators and developers is essential to ensure AI tools support student well-being and are used responsibly.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "As AI develops further, its role in curriculum design and assessment is expected to increase, helping identify optimal teaching strategies from large-scale academic data.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "AI can tailor teaching methods to enhance individual learning experiences by adapting to students\u2019 emotional and cognitive needs.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Low-code AI allows users to build and deploy AI-driven educational apps quickly and with minimal coding experience.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "For example, AppMaster offers cloud deployment, AI-driven features, and improved classroom and online learning experiences.", "citations": ["2781f548-219e-4abd-984b-29860a90a659_605669624"]}, {"text": "Real-time AI interaction in educational apps, as demonstrated by Meta enabling Fukien-English conversation, exemplifies this technology's potential.", "citations": ["72fbcefd-e1d3-4efc-8ce2-7756a9e30ef3_945017306"]}, {"text": "Generative AI is also used in other sectors, such as smart home management, where voice queries provide responsive customer service.", "citations": ["577550d7-bbe8-48ef-bd1a-f02860a5074c_404820265"]}, {"text": "This surge of AI innovation has driven record high interest and activity in places like Hong Kong.", "citations": ["577550d7-bbe8-48ef-bd1a-f02860a5074c_404820265"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1078", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "President Javier Milei of Argentina, an openly anarchocapitalist leader, has quickly implemented a radical libertarian policy agenda since taking office.", "citations": ["474c6eec-ebe5-4196-bca0-46e92bb6f014_959262116"]}, {"text": "Milei views the state as \"an enemy\" and has promised to drastically shrink its role in Argentina\u2019s economy and society.", "citations": ["2a1072be-ae9d-4584-a0eb-b9f28d881bf3_245687516"]}, {"text": "He pushed through an Emergency Decree and a sweeping Omnibus Bill but faced significant resistance in Congress due to a lack of majority support, forcing him to compromise on some elements of his proposals.", "citations": ["de62bbf7-5a19-4522-a025-9cc9f72e3f03_277776986"]}, {"text": "Despite these obstacles, Milei maintains strong popularity, standing out as one of the world\u2019s most well-liked heads of state at present.", "citations": ["e8c236e0-322e-4ea5-b004-7de7b3c473f9_797680631"]}, {"text": "He authorized the sale of all Social Housing units and removed rent controls as part of his pro-market reforms.", "citations": ["e8c236e0-322e-4ea5-b004-7de7b3c473f9_797680631"]}, {"text": "Milei blames Argentina\u2019s economic woes on longstanding statist policies associated with the Peronist tradition, which he contrasts with his own libertarian and free-market approach.", "citations": ["42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_948388057"]}, {"text": "While critics have accused Milei of extremism, comparisons with past leaders show his distance from authoritarian or fascist doctrines, aligning instead with market-driven ideology.", "citations": ["e8c236e0-322e-4ea5-b004-7de7b3c473f9_797680631"]}, {"text": "A major pillar of Milei\u2019s economic agenda is the proposed dollarization of the economy and abolishing the Central Bank, though such moves require Congressional approval and possibly constitutional changes.", "citations": ["4b67c948-7841-4206-b5b8-acbb37d68ba2_104775091"]}, {"text": "Observers highlight the practical challenge that Argentina lacks sufficient US dollar reserves to fully implement dollarization.", "citations": ["4b67c948-7841-4206-b5b8-acbb37d68ba2_104775091"]}, {"text": "On foreign policy, Milei pledges alignment with the US, Israel, and the \u201cfree world,\u201d but clarified he will not break relations with major trade partners like China and Brazil.", "citations": ["4b67c948-7841-4206-b5b8-acbb37d68ba2_104775091"]}, {"text": "His ministers launched immediate austerity measures, including deep spending cuts, subsidy reductions, and hikes in taxes and public service prices, aiming to reach a fiscal surplus within their first year.", "citations": ["f07189c5-e66f-4350-b753-b6364c16813a_91241603"]}, {"text": "These policies have led to widespread social unrest; thousands have protested, fearing that spending cuts will worsen living conditions, especially among vulnerable groups.", "citations": ["2a1072be-ae9d-4584-a0eb-b9f28d881bf3_245687516"]}, {"text": "Labor unions have vowed to resist Milei's reforms, promising national strikes to oppose reductions in the power of the central government and to defend public sector jobs and welfare.", "citations": ["474c6eec-ebe5-4196-bca0-46e92bb6f014_959262116"]}, {"text": "Milei admits the transition to a market-driven economy will bring hardship, warning that society must \"suffer on our way to libertarian utopia.\"", "citations": ["f07189c5-e66f-4350-b753-b6364c16813a_91241603"]}, {"text": "The government has responded to protests by stressing fiscal necessity, but social tensions continue to rise as the cost of living increases and public sector layoffs begin.", "citations": ["2a1072be-ae9d-4584-a0eb-b9f28d881bf3_245687516"]}, {"text": "The outcome of Milei\u2019s reforms remains uncertain, and the next four years will determine whether his radical reconfiguration of Argentina\u2019s institutions delivers economic prosperity or deeper social divisions.", "citations": ["42be5d07-d89d-4122-acf5-333f49984d59_948388057"]}, {"text": "Javier Milei, who won 55.7% of the vote in the second round of the presidential election, promised Argentina a radical change with a libertarian, market-oriented program.", "citations": ["0c807e00-49d4-4d11-9f61-28bd7d910b30_66376477"]}, {"text": "Taking office on December 10, Milei became popular among young people and those tired of traditional politics, earning attention with his provocative statements and public gestures like raffling his congressional salary.", "citations": ["0c807e00-49d4-4d11-9f61-28bd7d910b30_66376477"]}, {"text": "Milei criticized extensive state intervention, arguing it is immoral to manage public money in a way that enables political patronage and inefficiency.", "citations": ["e96ce4be-85b6-4acb-88c5-d1b2149f34f2_635541066"]}, {"text": "He emphasized the main task for his government is achieving a zero budget deficit, introducing immediate economic reforms to reduce public spending, including significant layoffs in the state apparatus and dismissing officials appointed in 2023.", "citations": ["9fb78d5e-18e3-488f-9d85-fa0cc4f7e79b_904219577"]}, {"text": "Milei and his administration aim to contain inflation, which experts estimate to reach 30% by the end of December, stating that solving the problem could take at least a year and a half.", "citations": ["9fb78d5e-18e3-488f-9d85-fa0cc4f7e79b_904219577"]}, {"text": "He publicly supports \"shock therapy\" to bring down inflation and fiscal deficits, despite warnings that this approach will mean \"the hardest times are yet to come\" for Argentines.", "citations": ["9fb78d5e-18e3-488f-9d85-fa0cc4f7e79b_904219577"]}, {"text": "Milei strongly opposes socialism, trade union influence, and any \"excess of state guardianship,\" pledging to reduce state control and regulatory oversight over individuals and businesses.", "citations": ["b2df5861-523f-4a76-90ac-5cf3cb635b76_335549156"]}, {"text": "He proposes abolishing the Argentine peso and adopting the US dollar as the national currency, insisting the move will stabilize the economy and end the uncertainty around daily exchange rates.", "citations": ["b2df5861-523f-4a76-90ac-5cf3cb635b76_335549156"]}, {"text": "Milei has called for the closure\u2014or \u201cblowing up\u201d\u2014of the Central Bank, identifies trade unions as obstacles to economic growth, and argues for introducing the free sale of weapons.", "citations": ["b2df5861-523f-4a76-90ac-5cf3cb635b76_335549156"]}, {"text": "He has rejected Argentina's planned entry into BRICS, citing lack of funds and alignment with his anti-communist policy stance.", "citations": ["2205e4de-bfc5-4f26-b4a2-eb6f0587709f_1039257773"]}, {"text": "Milei aims to realign Argentina's foreign policy closer to the United States and Israel, while distancing from countries like China, Cuba, and North Korea, which he labels as communist regimes responsible for global instability.", "citations": ["b2df5861-523f-4a76-90ac-5cf3cb635b76_335549156"]}, {"text": "He has announced plans for a \"summit of Latin American support\" for Ukraine, reflecting a shift in Argentina\u2019s international alliances.", "citations": ["ee5035b6-df71-4c0b-8839-ffe0ac24d00e_570961446"]}, {"text": "Milei promises to prosecute political opponents like the outgoing vice president for alleged corruption once their immunity expires.", "citations": ["b2df5861-523f-4a76-90ac-5cf3cb635b76_335549156"]}, {"text": "His reforms have prompted strong social reactions, including street protests and clashes, as he seeks to override entrenched interests and implement his radical political and economic agenda, marking a significant departure from Argentina's recent political tradition.", "citations": ["e96ce4be-85b6-4acb-88c5-d1b2149f34f2_635541066"]}, {"text": "Javier Milei began his presidency in Argentina declaring, \u201ctoday marks the beginning of a new era,\u201d as the country grapples with a severe economic crisis and the highest inflation in 30 years.", "citations": ["a7b50f51-50af-4d3b-a12e-d1472ab4a94e_328556231"]}, {"text": "Milei, elected in October amid public frustration, has focused on libertarian, market-oriented reforms to tackle soaring annual inflation of 140% and a poverty rate of about 40%.", "citations": ["e11322d5-e20d-410c-b5d3-a3e74f101aee_708694162"]}, {"text": "Upon assuming office, he announced austerity was unavoidable because \u201cwe have no money, no alternative to austerity,\u201d and warned that conditions would deteriorate in the short term before improvement.", "citations": ["f1f16c1c-1e25-4224-8ccb-b455374573c5_362692412"]}, {"text": "His government immediately devalued the Argentine peso by more than 50%, slashed government subsidies for fuel and transportation, and pledged to cut public spending by 5% of GDP.", "citations": ["a7b50f51-50af-4d3b-a12e-d1472ab4a94e_328556231"]}, {"text": "Milei presented an extensive reform package to Parliament, including measures to reduce the number of ministers, limit labor protections such as the constitutional right to strike, and implement sweeping deregulation.", "citations": ["aaac306e-9089-47b3-99c3-3ed7ec59bcd5_834223093"]}, {"text": "Facing strong opposition, Milei\u2019s early moves triggered mass protests, with tens of thousands demonstrating against his budget cuts and decrees outside parliament.", "citations": ["c1d0da66-16aa-4a2a-8f32-36dd0555f8c3_185829324"]}, {"text": "To deter protests, his government required organizers to pay for the cost of deploying security forces.", "citations": ["a7b50f51-50af-4d3b-a12e-d1472ab4a94e_328556231"]}, {"text": "The IMF supported these reforms by agreeing to disburse $4.7 billion to Argentina following the announcement of Milei\u2019s program.", "citations": ["c1d0da66-16aa-4a2a-8f32-36dd0555f8c3_185829324"]}, {"text": "Milei did not hold a majority in Congress and had to engage in intensive negotiations with lawmakers and other parties to move his reform package forward after marathon debates.", "citations": ["aaac306e-9089-47b3-99c3-3ed7ec59bcd5_834223093"]}, {"text": "His policies have provoked polarization in society, with some voters seeing him as the only candidate with strong, transparent proposals, while others expressed fear and skepticism about his capacity to deliver.", "citations": ["c650553c-9d54-4b8e-9d4c-57adbb29aa6e_1019456408"]}, {"text": "Experts, such as Professor Gabriel Fumarro, noted recent elections reflected more rejection of alternatives than genuine support for Milei.", "citations": ["bc022113-04c8-4952-83c0-e1f04939a604_672661270"]}, {"text": "The new president took office on December 10, 2023, facing persistent economic decline, currency depreciation, and an expanding debt burden, while promising further legislative actions soon.", "citations": ["bc022113-04c8-4952-83c0-e1f04939a604_672661270"]}, {"text": "He vowed that his administration\u2019s first package of measures would be submitted to parliament within days of his inauguration.", "citations": ["c6f6eef6-19c2-4309-9d91-dca343e3f54c_407634260"]}, {"text": "While Milei\u2019s agenda has drawn accusations of extremism and generated intense debate, it signals a sharp shift toward libertarian and market-driven governance in Argentina.", "citations": ["e11322d5-e20d-410c-b5d3-a3e74f101aee_708694162"]}, {"text": "Javier Milei, a far-right liberal economist often dubbed the \u201cTrump of Argentina,\u201d was elected president after decades of Peronist (Belondist) rule, with his main rival Sergio Massa conceding defeat before the official results announcement.", "citations": ["fa9a1610-d109-4613-9f32-478df67c33d3_437223029"]}, {"text": "Milei, who addressed supporters as president-elect on December 10, campaigned on shock therapy economic reforms to tackle Argentina\u2019s severe crisis, where inflation surpasses 100% and up to 40% of citizens live in poverty.", "citations": ["a90e2020-b2f3-409d-aa2e-4ef940a8dd50_379485360"]}, {"text": "His supporters argue that only Milei can dismantle Argentina's entrenched political class and end decades of economic decline, as Argentina once ranked among the richest countries in the world.", "citations": ["58c21ede-b496-40c4-bd1d-1ce85e6a9b90_830969761"]}, {"text": "Milei has declared an economic emergency, vowing to make Argentina \"the freest country in the world,\" and to transform it into a world power again after 35 years.", "citations": ["86cfdfa1-4ed1-49e2-b47a-8486afa964f3_111809641"]}, {"text": "Key elements of his agenda include drastic fiscal reforms\u2014slashing public spending, laying off over 5,000 government workers, cutting pensions, and loosening labor rights.", "citations": ["86cfdfa1-4ed1-49e2-b47a-8486afa964f3_111809641"]}, {"text": "He also seeks to abolish the central bank and dollarize the economy, aiming to stabilize prices by adopting the US dollar as Argentina\u2019s currency.", "citations": ["a90e2020-b2f3-409d-aa2e-4ef940a8dd50_379485360"]}, {"text": "Milei signaled a change in Argentina's geopolitical orientation, withdrawing from plans to join the BRICS group and stating his government will not actively foster ties with China or other socialist-ruled countries, though he allows private companies to do business there.", "citations": ["58c21ede-b496-40c4-bd1d-1ce85e6a9b90_830969761"]}, {"text": "He is known for his flamboyant personal style, effective use of social media, and for channeling public frustration\u2014especially among impoverished youth\u2014against Argentina\u2019s traditional politicians.", "citations": ["ea24f83f-5e3e-4947-8778-25e69824066a_245913622"]}, {"text": "His policies have triggered public protests amid concerns over the impact of fiscal austerity and fears that \u201cshock therapy\u201d could worsen short-term hardship, though Milei insists that short-term pain is required to achieve long-term stability.", "citations": ["453bb4aa-916e-409e-95e9-03e4379d9f33_453851601"]}, {"text": "Support for his presidency comes mainly from the political right; nonetheless, society remains deeply divided, with many voters choosing him as the \u201clesser of two evils\u201d given disillusionment with past leadership.", "citations": ["ea24f83f-5e3e-4947-8778-25e69824066a_245913622"]}, {"text": "Institutionally, Milei's proposals may lead to significant restructuring of state functions, challenging the legacy of state intervention and prompting debate over the future direction of Argentina\u2019s democracy and social safety nets.", "citations": ["a90e2020-b2f3-409d-aa2e-4ef940a8dd50_379485360"]}, {"text": "As radical reforms are implemented and political opposition mounts, the success of Milei\u2019s libertarian and market-oriented strategies remains uncertain, leaving Argentina at a crossroads for its future governance, economy, and society.", "citations": ["a90e2020-b2f3-409d-aa2e-4ef940a8dd50_379485360"]}], "references": []}
{"metadata": {"team_id": "pregnancy", "run_id": "pregnancy-expert", "topic_id": "1080", "task": "multilingual"}, "responses": [{"text": "Jane Goodall emphasizes the crucial importance of taking immediate action to address the environmental disaster humans have created, warning that failure to act will doom our future.", "citations": ["1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734"]}, {"text": "She urges individuals to recognize their daily impact on the environment and to make conscious choices about the kind of difference they want to make.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "Goodall insists that humans are not separate from nature but are an integral part of it and utterly dependent on it for survival.", "citations": ["1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734"]}, {"text": "She describes ecosystems as intricate networks of plants and animals, highlighting the vital need to protect these interrelationships for a sustainable future.", "citations": ["1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734"]}, {"text": "Speaking to younger generations, she acknowledges their heightened awareness of environmental crises, but cautions against losing hope in the face of widespread negativity.", "citations": ["1fa58c5e-416a-418f-8de6-22f4a81873e8_687307734"]}, {"text": "Goodall\u2019s central message is to never give up hope because there remains a window of time to make meaningful change.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "She believes that inspiring positive action is more effective than overwhelming people with facts they do not want to receive.", "citations": ["f684acbb-658a-47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399"]}, {"text": "Goodall\u2019s career was shaped by an early lesson: meaningful, collaborative dialogue and practical suggestions can effect real change, even within powerful institutions.", "citations": ["75f9a366-7e3e-49e4-af6f-d8831cf2bb03_861453067"]}, {"text": "Her approach encourages people to focus on making actual changes rather than seeking personal credit.", "citations": ["f684acbb-658a-47ca-aaad-05e0fb187180_520597399"]}, {"text": "Goodall\u2019s Roots & Shoots program embodies her belief in the power of young people; it provides them opportunities to address problems in their communities, fostering problem-solving skills and empowerment.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "This collaborative spirit is echoed in innovative student-led projects, such as Maryland\u2019s water-quality monitoring initiative, which connects youth, educators, and local communities to protect and restore habitats.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "Such projects demonstrate how accessible technology and teamwork can empower individuals to actively preserve local ecosystems, as seen with Chesapeake Bay conservation efforts.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "Through these endeavors, students experience personal growth, enhanced problem-solving skills, and a deeper connection to their environment.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "Ongoing improvements in conservation tools\u2014like affordable water quality kits\u2014encourage broader community engagement and greater environmental awareness.", "citations": ["d517e941-02bb-4a66-b9d6-18cd8ce9b171_598062037"]}, {"text": "Jane Goodall\u2019s influence is evident in the growing emphasis on education, collaboration, and hope, inspiring new generations to take responsible action for global conservation.", "citations": ["95f67cee-331c-42fd-9d52-cb7bad432c19_898632871"]}, {"text": "About 90% of the population lives in rural areas and, as of the second quarter of this year, the regional labor force was 837.9 thousand people.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "The regional job creation plan includes the establishment of 109,617 jobs this year, with most being permanent and only a third temporary.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "Since the beginning of the year, 837 families have received support, totaling 269.3 million tenge paid to address their challenges.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "The Turkestan region ranks among the top three in the country for agricultural sector development by all indicators.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "Currently, the total area of closed ground is 1,640 hectares, accounting for 71% of the national figure.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "Land under water-saving technologies reached 34,000 hectares, supported by a project valued at 32 billion tenge.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "Pasture needs exceed two million hectares, due to the presence of more than a million head of cattle in settlements.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "There is a goal to increase fish farming output to 20,000 tons by 2030.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "Several roads in Kazakhstan have closed due to adverse weather.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "A new eight-lane street opened in Astana.", "citations": ["349fd219-a7c7-42da-98f3-6a7d15c681a9_903050047"]}, {"text": "A philosophical perspective suggests that self-awareness is required to address personal wounds, analogous to seeking solutions for regional or societal problems.", "citations": ["0fdf8a11-3acd-47e2-9415-901fcb59fa0d_529947063"]}, {"text": "People may react differently when faced with challenges, and self-reflection is encouraged before acting.", "citations": ["b46d30d4-0297-4d11-afc1-e725ea412b18_146888306"]}, {"text": "Metaphorically, individuals are presented with two choices: seeing themselves as a victim or as the author of their life.", "citations": ["b46d30d4-0297-4d11-afc1-e725ea412b18_146888306"]}, {"text": "Letting go of victimhood and taking authorship enables constructive change.", "citations": ["b46d30d4-0297-4d11-afc1-e725ea412b18_146888306"]}, {"text": "Through active participation, one can transform an undesirable situation into a preferred outcome.", "citations": ["b46d30d4-0297-4d11-afc1-e725ea412b18_146888306"]}, {"text": "The advice is to cherish pleasant emotions from work, not fear stepping out of comfort zones, and to pursue actions that bring freedom and fulfillment.", "citations": ["170c9f11-52fa-44a2-bd80-54871bb3a971_715833231"]}, {"text": "Reducing unnecessary contacts is suggested, while paying attention to supportive or significant people nearby.", "citations": ["170c9f11-52fa-44a2-bd80-54871bb3a971_715833231"]}, {"text": "It is a favorable period to take professional risks or start new relationships, with the potential for significant personal and career growth.", "citations": ["170c9f11-52fa-44a2-bd80-54871bb3a971_715833231"]}, {"text": "The relationship between Russia and China is marked by cooperation in physical culture and sports, opposing politicization and boycotts in international sports.", "citations": ["2af1935e-a992-4e19-a952-4a617dfa1cfc_1012090614"]}, {"text": "The cities have hosted cooperative events, such as the participation of Xi Jinping in the Sochi Olympic opening and the initiation of a Russia-China cooperation year in 2022-2023.", "citations": ["2af1935e-a992-4e19-a952-4a617dfa1cfc_1012090614"]}, {"text": "Art can play a role in supporting animals, demonstrated by updated horse figures by street artists at MEGA Dybenko in support of animal causes.", "citations": ["1c7b6b7c-f9a7-4f7f-8133-08930d3d9120_266565726"]}, {"text": "The regional government delegation has reviewed progress on a waste processing complex, with plans to launch high-tech PET processin